msgid "<00:32> SOS\n<00:32> SOS\n<00:32> SOS\n    <00:32> [Message delivery failed. Please check your connection.]\n<00:32> NEED HELP NOW! \n    <00:32> [Message delivery failed. Please check your connection.]\n<00:33> Trapped, hostiles are trying to override the airlocks. We need someone NOW!\n    <00:33> [Message delivery failed. Please check your connection.]"
msgstr ""
"<00:32> SOS\n"
"<00:32> SOS\n"
"<00:32> SOS\n"
"    <00:32> [메시지 전송 실패. 연결 상태를 확인해 주세요.]\n"
"<00:32> 지금 당장 도움이 필요해! \n"
"    <00:32> [메시지 전송 실패. 연결 상태를 확인해 주세요.]\n"
"<00:33> 갇혔어. 적들이 에어락 제어권을 장악하려 하고 있어. 누구든 지금 당장 필요해!\n"
