#. REC: TMLM:ITXT
msgctxt "000EC4"
msgid "I'd like to purchase the Château des Étoiles"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_Anchorpoint_RishiSaintTerminal_HouseSub
#. REC: TMLM:BTXT
msgctxt "000EC5"
msgid "We hope you enjoyed your tour of the Château des Étoiles. We think you'll agree that there's no home in the Settled Systems that combines spacious and luxurious interiors with breathtaking views in a truly singular location.\n\nWhile the property is still available, time is running out on this one-of-a-kind opportunity, so don't delay! Simply respond below to transmit the credits, and the Château des Étoiles will be yours.\n\nA luxury home among the stars. Who could ask for more?\n\nCost: <Token.Name=AsteroidManorCost> credits.\n\n"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_Anchorpoint_RishiSaintTerminal_HouseSub
#. REC: TMLM:FULL
