msgid "Restricted Access Data"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_Sasha_TMLM
#. REC: TMLM:UNAM
msgctxt "000EC8"
msgid "My partner left New Babylon thinking he could strike it rich elsewhere, but that just means his shares are up for grabs. I might have to fight Grace for them, she's a sneaky one when it comes to finances.\n\nYeats might be dead in a week so I feel like his shares might be available soon. Once Hal takes over for Zena, I really think this outpost will take off. We're going to need more people, obviously, but if Ivica can strike a deal with a big player for the Caelumite, I think times will be changing for the better.\n\n"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
