msgctxt "000EC9"
msgid "Resident Share Program"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_Sasha_TMLM
#. REC: TMLM:UNAM
msgctxt "000ECA"
msgid "As security chief, I take my job seriously. \n\nAnd while I value privacy, I also know that in emergencies, certain measures and precautions must be taken.\n\nVital data that is on other residents' computers will need to be accessible, so I've filed them under \"Restricted Access Data\" in this computer.\n\nAny locks will still be present, but they'll have a far lower security level and can be unlocked with my keycard."
msgstr ""

