#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSH_Clues
#. REC: TMLM:BTXT
msgctxt "000F23"
msgid "[0/5 Locks Unlocked] \n\nSo, you wish to open my safe? Plunder my wares? Pilfer my most prized possession?\n\nIDIOT, DID YOU THINK IT WOULD BE EASY? YOU, THE SNICKERING BURGLAR; ME, THE CRYING BABE?\nOnly the worthy are capable of laying claim on my valuable!\nTo test your worth, you must solve my riddles and acquire the 5 clues necessary to gaze upon the holy grail. Only then have you proven capable enough for the prize.\n\n- Riddle Master Marin"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSH_Clues
#. REC: TMLM:BTXT
msgctxt "000F24"
msgid "[1/5 Locks Unlocked] \n\nOh? 'Twould appear that we have a modicum of intelligence on our hands. \nOn to the next clue.\n\n[Personal Log Entries Unlocked]"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSH_Clues
#. REC: TMLM:BTXT
msgctxt "000F25"
msgid "[2/5 Locks Unlocked] \n\nThis is quite exhilarating, don't you agree? Two minds battling across space and time? \nI'm giddy thinking about the look on your perplexed face after this next clue.\n\n[Personal Log Entries Unlocked]"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSH_Clues
#. REC: TMLM:BTXT
msgctxt "000F26"
msgid "[3/5 Locks Unlocked] \n\nI must admit, I dread the end of this game we've played. However, as they say, \"In this city, the more you take, the more you leave behind.\" Anyhow, onto the penultimate clue.\n\n[Personal Log Entries Unlocked]"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSH_Clues
#. REC: TMLM:BTXT
msgctxt "000F27"
msgid "[4/5 Locks Unlocked] \n\nThe final clue, happening too fast and going too soon. I hope we meet in person, so that the fun can continue evergreen. Proceed to the final clue.\n\n[Personal Log Entries Unlocked]"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSH_Clues
#. REC: TMLM:BTXT
msgctxt "000F28"
msgid "[5/5 Locks Unlocked] \n\nCongratulations, Burglar! You have forded the rivers of wordplay, braved the cutting winds of investigation, and ascended the highest peaks of riddlery.\nYou are now a Riddle Master. Wear that title with pride, as there are but few dotted along the cosmos.\nTake my most prized possession, as you have earned it.\nIf we meet, let it be as equals. Farewell.\n- Riddle Master Marin\n\n[Personal Log Entries Unlocked]"
msgstr ""

