#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC01_GloriaFiles_Personal
#. REC: TMLM:UNAM
msgctxt "00199B"
msgid "Came across a couple of space traders who wanted me to come aboard their ship to see their specials. Bought some food and water, I should now have enough to survive another month at least.\n\nThey must have known something was up because they told me to go to Anchorpoint if I needed to trade in my ship without too many questions asked... Should have asked them for directions, though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC01_GloriaFiles_Personal
#. REC: TMLM:ITXT
