msgid "Space Merchants"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC01_GloriaFiles_Personal
#. REC: TMLM:UNAM
msgctxt "00199D"
msgid "In the event where I can't figure out how to make this stupid ship behave and end up frozen to death out here, here is my last will and testament:\n\nTO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN\n\n*Boob-Oop-a-Doop*\n\nThat is all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC01_GloriaFiles_Personal
#. REC: TMLM:ITXT
msgctxt "00199E"
msgid "Last Will and Testament"
msgstr ""

#. List: 0
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC01_GloriaFiles_Personal
#. REC: TMLM:UNAM
msgctxt "00199F"
msgid "Space is empty\nJust like me\nSpace is silent\nLike my scream\nSpace is still\nLike my heart\n\nBut look hard enough\nPast the pain\nThere is a light\nBurning amidst\nLight-years of darkness\nNever going out\n\nI miss you Mom\n"
msgstr ""

