#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_Evidence01
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "00059F"
msgid "Crash landed at this place called Shinar Outpost. The people are friendly. Patched me up, didn't ask too many questions at first, but now folks are starting to get curious.\n\nI've tried to keep my ties a secret, but the holes in the ship tell a different story. Won't be able to keep up the facade for long. That's okay. A supply ship is coming in soon. It's my ticket out.\n\nThere's a tracking device on the ship, but I'll make sure I'm not followed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_Evidence02
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "0005A1"
msgid "I am not from the Settled Systems. I was born Halzor Cor'usan, a follower of House Va'ruun.\n\nOver my lifetime, I have served many masters. I was brought into House Ka'dic and was nurtured to be a spy. I was asked to infiltrate and report on the Crimson Fleet. I spent so many days under the guidance of so many handlers, that I lost my sense of self.\n\nIn another lifetime, I may have found a home at Shinar. But I faltered and in the name of survival, reverted to my old ways.\n\nI have tried to atone here in New Babylon. However, should I die before the weight of my crimes are revealed, let me lay them bare here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_RelaxationTape01
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "0005A3"
msgid "Welcome new listener.\n\nWe are here to guide you on a special journey toward relaxation and meditation, brought to you by Chunks. \n\nRelax your shoulders. Feel your muscles. The skin on your face. The softness of your tongue.\n\nNow imagine your tongue gliding over an 8 x 8 cm cube. A Chunk.\n\nIt might taste like chocolate. It might flow like wine. \n\nBut know that when you taste it, total relaxation is possible.\n\n\n\n"
msgstr ""
"새로 오신 분을 환영합니다.\n"
"\n"
"지금부터 여러분을 휴식과 명상의 특별한 여정으로 안내해 드리겠습니다. 이 안내는 청크 사의 제공으로 전해드립니다.\n"
"\n"
"어깨의 힘을 빼세요. 근육을 느껴보세요. 얼굴의 피부를 느껴보세요. 혀의 부드러움을 느껴보세요.\n"
"\n"
"이제 혀가 가로 세로 8센티미터 크기의 큐브 위를 미끄러지며 움직이는 모습을 상상해 보세요. 청크 위를 말이죠.\n"
"\n"
"초콜릿 맛일 수도 있습니다. 포도주처럼 흐를 수도 있습니다.\n"
"\n"
"하지만 한 번 맛보면, 당신은 완전한 휴식이 가능한 거란 걸 아시게 될 겁니다.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

