#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_ParadisoTimeshare
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "000766"
msgid "Live out your golden years in luxury at Paradiso Retirement Resorts!\n\nThis verdant retirement community is set to be finished very soon, specializing in serving residents with independent living, assisted living, and skilled nursing. \n\nWherever you look, our residents smile as they lounge on their private patios, take afternoon swims in our heated pools, or share tales with other residents over an evening cocktail.\n\nThe end of your life doesn't mean you have to stop living. Paradiso Retirement Resorts isn't just a community. It's home.\n\nWe can't wait for you to be a part of our family."
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_Quest
#. REC: QUST:CNAM
msgctxt "000938"
msgid "A man named Bernhard told me about a refugee camp that was left to starve by a pirate named Caruso. I found the pirate living in a remote outpost and killed him. After being confronted by the leader of the outpost I gave them his confession."
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_Quest
#. REC: QUST:CNAM
msgctxt "000939"
msgid "A man named Bernhard told me about a refugee camp that was left to starve by a pirate named Caruso. I investigated the camp and located the last known coordinates of the stolen ship, the Tevat. Following the coordinates, I came across a separate settlement. Caruso may be holed up there."
msgstr ""

