msgctxt "00231F"
msgid "After meeting a refugee at Anchorpoint, I tracked down the whereabouts of a man named Caruso who had left his old outpost to die, only to discover he had joined a new outpost and became a valued member of their community. Ultimately, however, he confessed to his crimes, and a vote is to take place to decide his fate."
msgstr ""

