#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "00236A"
msgid "Arbitrator, I have the Intel you've requested for the following targets: \n\n\nABEL NELSON - TERMINATED \n\nJOHN VASQUEZ - TERMINATED \n\nCLARK BROOKS - ALIVE \n\nLEE EVANS - TERMINATED \n\nMICHELLE YOUNG - TERMINATED \n\nSARAH QUINN - ALIVE \n\nJONATHAN HALL - TERMINATED \n\nJOSEPH PASQUALE - ALIVE \n\nSUSAN XIONG - TERMINATED \n\n\nWe will be dispatching extra resources to deal with the targets that are still alive. I will follow up as soon as that is taken care of. \n\n- Oculus \n"
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS00DDR009_Slate03
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "00236C"
msgid "Notes for anyone taking on the gardening shift:\n\n- Check the water levels before watering\n- Load any harvested produce by the wheelbarrow\n- Put back tools where you grabbed them.\n\n- DO NOT attempt to fertilize without checking the machine is calibrated correctly\n- DO NOT let Bill near this area. He WILL kill whatever he touches."
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS00DDR009_Slate02
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "00236E"
msgid "He just stands there.\n\nI've been sitting at this desk for 4 hours and that's all he has done. He hasn't gone to the restroom. He hasn't grabbed a tool and try to at least look useful. Just does nothing!\n\nWhy is this guy even part of our group? Who the hell brought him on? Stupid Bill!\n\n"
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_Z01_Slate1
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "002372"
msgid "I hope you're doing well, My Love. If all goes well I should be home soon. With a real nice pay day too. \nI want to thank you for being so patient with me. I promise, the second I step foot back home I'm taking you to the fanciest restaurant in town. I don't care how gross or dirty or whatever I'll be from a month in this hunk of metal. \nSpeaking of this ship, she's a real piece of work. 'Best for the price,' my ass! I'm telling you that seller must have pulled a fast one on me. \nBut it'll be fine. As long as she gets me where me, and the rest of this junk, needs to be I'm happy. \nOh? Give me one moment. This ship always has something to complain about. Guess I better check on it. See you soon, love. Promise."
msgstr ""

