#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_Anchorpoint_TextSlate_MaddieInvestigation
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "0024E9"
msgid "Ms. Wing,\n\nI have some new information to share with you. I was able to confirm that your parents left Hopetown several months ago. I'm working on trying to pin down an exact date, but getting access to the records has been a challenge because that information is protected by the company. \n\nIn talking to the locals, I learned that your father's health was in decline at the time he and your mother left. He'd apparently taken to drinking heavily and smoking not long after losing his position at HopeTech, and it seems those bad habits had caught up with him. \n\nI did not hear any such reports about your mother's health, so for the time being, I think we can assume she's fine.\n\nI have a few leads to check on regarding the current whereabouts of your parents. This will involve travel and time, so I'll need to ask for your next payment before I can get started on those steps.\n\nFletcher Sayles,\nContract Investigator\n"
msgstr ""

