msgctxt "00256C"
msgid "02.16.2309\n\nProceed to Mars\n\nEstablish geostationary orbit above Cydonia\n\nUpon orbital capture - deploy all assets\n\nBe advised: Intel suggests mech company in area\n\n"
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_BBI_DataSlate06
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "00256E"
msgid "01.18.2311 Cheyenne\n\nFlag this is UC Ship Ashoka above Cheyenne.\n\nReporting victory from sector 23. Freestar forces have engaged heavy losses.\n\nFlag, UC Ship Ashoka again... We are noting civilian ships rising planetside in large amounts.\n\nFlag, request change to rules of engagement to fire on civilian forces at will. Request immediate changes to ROE...\n\nThis is UC Ship Ashoka breaking up. Mayday, mayday.\n\n"
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_BBI_DataSlate07
#. REC: BOOK:DESC
msgctxt "002570"
msgid "05.10.2310 Niira\n\nCommander Henry Durant has authorized use of lethal force on all urban targets from orbit or planetside.\n\nIf there is movement in the cities - fire upon it. All ground forces to be considered hostile.\n\nThey have had ample time to clear the urban zones - all that remains are hostile targets.\n\nWe will secure this planet and hold it this time.\n\n"
msgstr ""

