#. List: 1
#. EDID: co_wep_ranged_statUpgrade_None_new
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
msgctxt "0347E9"
msgid "No Upgrade."
msgstr "업그레이드 없음."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000060"
msgid "I'd say murdered and turned their vengeful ghosts into my thralls."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000061"
msgid "Just murder, or murdered and absorbed their souls?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C25]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000062"
msgid "You have your headcanon, I have mine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C48]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000063"
msgid "It was definitely more mundane than that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000064"
msgid "More than fair. Facts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000065"
msgid "I know. It brings a tear to my eye just thinking about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000066"
msgid "Fair."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000067"
msgid "I feel like I shouldn't have to explain this to you of all people. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000076"
msgid "There's fan fiction you can consult for this, you know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000077"
msgid "So you want the deep cuts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000078"
msgid "Okay, but you may go deaf and blind from the shock."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000079"
msgid "Oh, so it's a lore dump."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00007A"
msgid "Yeah, sure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BF9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00007B"
msgid "No worries."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00007C"
msgid "Cool."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BF7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00007D"
msgid "Uh huh."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C23]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00007E"
msgid "I'd like to ask you about something else. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C46]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00007F"
msgid "Earlier, you mentioned a ship full of dead cultists. What happened to them?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000080"
msgid "Mind telling me more about your family?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000081"
msgid "Did you ever have any actual interest in the finance sector?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BDC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000085"
msgid "Can you tell me about any past work experiences?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C0B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000086"
msgid "You can return to your post now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000087"
msgid "Hopefully."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000088"
msgid "Well, in this case, a documentary."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000089"
msgid "Hopefully?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00008A"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00008B"
msgid "Uh-huh."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00008C"
msgid "Works for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00008D"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00008F"
msgid "Yeah. Let's."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000090"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00009C"
msgid "And so it begins."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C1C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000A1"
msgid "You did that on purpose I assume."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D4D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000A7"
msgid "Sure, it's your funeral."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000EE"
msgid "I already told you. Are you trying to torture me by having me relive the experience?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E3E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000EF"
msgid "I looked up the word. It sounds like an illness. I pray it's fatal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E3E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F0"
msgid "Not great. They said I lacked \"pep.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B82]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F1"
msgid "Well, either way, if you ever find a bottomless pit in your travels, let me know. I've got a list."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F2"
msgid "I don't know. Maybe a black hole. Not the kind in space, just a big bottomless pit. It'd be fun to throw people into it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F3"
msgid "You mean besides the cold, endless void?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F5"
msgid "It was mostly the same story, except the Captain was a hermit crab and the whale was a beer can."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F6"
msgid "There was the time somebody brought in a slate to trade-in. It was Moby Dick, only he had re-recorded the narration and changed all the names."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F7"
msgid "Because that's boring. Guns are noisy and lack drama."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F8"
msgid "Why not just shoot them?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C11]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000F9"
msgid "Any good stories?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C39]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0000FA"
msgid "As long as mine get thrown in first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000101"
msgid "There should be manager brand bullets you could keep in the register. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000102"
msgid "I know when I need to fight, I just picture some raging customer asking to speak to the manager."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000104"
msgid "Sure is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00010E"
msgid "I like working retail personally."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00010F"
msgid "How is banking similar to demonic pacts?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000110"
msgid "I really do love banks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000111"
msgid "Me? I respect a faction that can take off the mask and be cartoonishly evil. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000112"
msgid "It's definitely not for everyone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C10]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000113"
msgid "That's because you can't die and you're jealous. It's a defense mechanism."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C38]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000114"
msgid "Those aren't the same. Loans like that are way worse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000115"
msgid "Yeah, but where's the magic in that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B5B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000116"
msgid "That doesn't sound neat to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000117"
msgid "Not all loans need to be predatory. They provide a way for regular folks to purchase homes and start business."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000118"
msgid "It's the same vibe with banking and the dark arts. Necromancy, demon pacts, predatory loans -- it's all po-tay-to, po-tah-to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000119"
msgid "Yeah. To me, stuff like magic, science, it's all semantics. Fire is fire, energy is energy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00011A"
msgid "Did you ever have any actual interest in the finance sector?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00011B"
msgid "You and me both."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00011C"
msgid "The problem is I'm single and poor, so it's pretty obvious the potions are a lie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000124"
msgid "He thought it was a punishment. It was not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000126"
msgid "Of course I could solve that problem by never shipping the items. Maybe I'll put out some flyers whenever we're in Freestar space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000127"
msgid "That would mean using Star Parcel, but they have to grav jump everything, and that gets expensive. Too expensive unless you're shipping in bulk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00012E"
msgid "You must've had a place with a lot of sunlight."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00012F"
msgid "What were your responsibilities?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000130"
msgid "You'd think. But I'm allergic to daylight. I use artificial grow lights. It makes me feel like I'm sticking it to the sun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000131"
msgid "Yeah, well, I don't care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C1D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000132"
msgid "That's a little too on the nose."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00016A"
msgid "I had enough. Most of them were imaginary, or fungi."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00016B"
msgid "I'm an alien. Our cults do things differently where I'm from."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00016C"
msgid "Rad. Not my vibe, though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00016D"
msgid "It was a fairly transparent adoption process."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00016E"
msgid "Mmm... hard to say. They did introduce me to fantasy books and video slates. I think those became my parents after that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00016F"
msgid "Did you have many friends as a child?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000170"
msgid "Yeah. I'd be a murderer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000171"
msgid "Would you be different if you had siblings?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B6E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000172"
msgid "Let's go back to my other questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000173"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000174"
msgid "Mind telling me more about your past?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000175"
msgid "I got a pamphlet. Thought it'd be cool."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000176"
msgid "How did you join this cult?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000177"
msgid "Same old cult stuff. Not even a cool plushie to give new members. I had to crochet my own."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000178"
msgid "Yeah, pretty boring stuff. You'd think snake worshipers would have more originality, but nope. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000179"
msgid "Oh, so just regular cult things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C1B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00017A"
msgid "Wow, you pay less than even GalBank. I'm impressed. But it's still not enough to sway me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C3D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00017B"
msgid "Eh, it's not that big a deal. Spoiler alert, I'm still here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D18]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00017C"
msgid "Wow. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00017D"
msgid "That sounds terrifying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00017E"
msgid "Yeah. That level of stupidity is incredibly terrifying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000182"
msgid "If they are believers, then they will find prosperity in the Shrouding as Promised."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C01]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000183"
msgid "I might have some outfits I can trade you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000184"
msgid "The leader prepared this special snake venom cocktail. Everyone on the ship was supposed to drink it and get grav jumped to heaven."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000185"
msgid "They were really into the Great Serpent. So into him, they wanted to meet him. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000186"
msgid "It was around the same time I joined a cult."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000187"
msgid "Around the time I joined that cult I told you about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000188"
msgid "When did you start taking an interest in necromancy?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000189"
msgid "Gross."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00018A"
msgid "No cool robes. Just the clothes on your back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00018B"
msgid "I did work in a morgue once. But I don't consider it a job so much as a lifelong passion."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00018C"
msgid "I used to sell potions and amulets online. Had a tiny little garden where I grew the ingredients."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D13]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00018D"
msgid "Sure. I assume it's in the contract."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D09]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00018E"
msgid "Would if I could. Oh wait, I have to. Damn."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00018F"
msgid "I hope they spent their last days thinking of the long, healthy life they were going to lead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000190"
msgid "You did them a solid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000191"
msgid "What's a little crime between friends?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CEB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000192"
msgid "They deserved that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CEA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000193"
msgid "You did them a favor. Trust me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000194"
msgid "Is it murder if life sucks?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000195"
msgid "Dead people don't know how lucky they are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CE7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000196"
msgid "They probably were miserable anyway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000197"
msgid "If you do the killing, I get to keep the body."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000198"
msgid "That escalated quickly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E4A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000199"
msgid "I want to be the kind of necromancer that takes on new faces too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E49]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00019A"
msgid "You look great. Also, I think I deserve a raise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E48]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00019B"
msgid "I was getting sick of the old face anyway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E47]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00019C"
msgid "It's an improvement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E46]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00019D"
msgid "Not bad. Could use some horns and vampire teeth though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E45]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00019E"
msgid "Nice look. I approve."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E44]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00019F"
msgid "New face, new you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E43]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001A0"
msgid "I like it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E42]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001A1"
msgid "Cool new face."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E41]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001A2"
msgid "So you're some kind of changeling. Neat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001D5"
msgid "Now imagine your tongue gliding over an 8 x 8 cm cube. A Chunk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001D6"
msgid "Welcome new listener."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021742]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001D7"
msgid "We are here to guide you on a special journey toward relaxation and meditation, brought to you by Chunks. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102154C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001D8"
msgid "It might taste like chocolate. It might flow like wine. But know that when you taste it, total relaxation is possible."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021792]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001D9"
msgid "Relax your shoulders. Feel your muscles. The skin on your face. The softness of your tongue."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001DA"
msgid "*Sigh*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001DB"
msgid "So many good people were lost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001DC"
msgid "I grow weary of this galaxy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001DD"
msgid "I've done things I'm not proud of to survive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001DE"
msgid "Shinar was a quiet place. I miss it dearly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102169B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001DF"
msgid "Everything always seems fine at first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001E0"
msgid "Here. The coordinates. There you will find the proof. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001E1"
msgid "If you doubt my words, traveler, then I suggest you visit the settlement in question."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102154B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001E2"
msgid "I'm sorry you feel that way. But I'm going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001E3"
msgid "It sounds like a peaceful place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021540]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001E4"
msgid "Surely there was food and water on the planet?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102158E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001E7"
msgid "I am against volunteering for any fight I have no stake in, yes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021650]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001E8"
msgid "Skip to the part with the tragedy, please."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102156A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001E9"
msgid "It would've continued to be thus, had we not invited a stranger into our home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021570]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001EA"
msgid "Yes, yes, be gone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021649]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001EB"
msgid "I don't believe this sob story is even real."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001EC"
msgid "I've never heard of this settlement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102175A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001ED"
msgid "That's the way it goes. Be glad you survived."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001EE"
msgid "It was. Which makes it all the more tragic it was taken from us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102155F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001EF"
msgid "Very well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001F0"
msgid "I want to say he's dead. But men like that are cockroaches. They have a bad habit of staying alive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021623]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001F1"
msgid "Where do you think the pirate is now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001F4"
msgid "There was a shipwreck with a lone survivor. We rescued him, brought him back, and treated his wounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021604]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001F5"
msgid "A man like that tends to get respect, but it's all a ruse. And he fooled us just long enough to give us the slip."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021593]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001F6"
msgid "It was luck. I never said what kind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001F7"
msgid "What can you tell me about this pirate? Do you have a description?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001F8"
msgid "Yes, but he lied to us -- told us he was a merchant, not a thief. And we paid the price for our naivety."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021696]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001F9"
msgid "He was a real bear of a man. Soft spoken, but forceful. What few words he used, he didn't mince."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021823]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001FA"
msgid "Are you against joining the Vanguard?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021715]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001FB"
msgid "I can find him. I could go to Shinar and follow the trail."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021762]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001FC"
msgid "But some decided to take their own lives and die on their own terms."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021762]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001FD"
msgid "Sheer luck. Without food, water... we only had days before dehydration set in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102173C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001FE"
msgid "Yes. Grant me the courtesy of not spelling it out for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0001FF"
msgid "If you are curious, you will find them at these coordinates. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000200"
msgid "The lucky ones died that day. They are free from this farce."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000201"
msgid "That doesn't sound like it was luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000202"
msgid "I'll leave you to it then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000203"
msgid "I've all but given up on finding him, but if you feel the need, here are the coordinates."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000204"
msgid "Yes, leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021767]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000205"
msgid "Have you ever thought about getting revenge?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000206"
msgid "The pirate was the smart one, taking advantage of our foolishness."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000207"
msgid "On the contrary, to continue to do a foolish thing is the definition of insanity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021741]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00020B"
msgid "That doesn't mean you stop doing what's right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00020C"
msgid "When he stole the ship, and our supplies, he sentenced us to death."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00020D"
msgid "Project Shinar's goal was to settle a Class B-H planet. Barely habitable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021791]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00020E"
msgid "So, you did the unthinkable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00020F"
msgid "How did you survive?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021736]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000210"
msgid "Even if I kill him, so what? My friends, my colleagues, are all dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102165B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000213"
msgid "Wherever Caruso is, let God be his judge. And if there is no God, then we're all doomed anyway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000214"
msgid "It's not wise to give a pirate shelter."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000215"
msgid "But then I realized there was no goddamn point. To any of it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000216"
msgid "Of course, I thought about it. Every day for two years, until it consumed me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000217"
msgid "I did not survive the Tragedy of Shinar just to forget its lessons."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021732]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000218"
msgid "Foolish or not, their bravery should be commended."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021587]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000219"
msgid "You will find it harder when your mouth is full of dirt."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021587]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00021A"
msgid "Yes, hurl your insults while you still take breath!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00021B"
msgid "We were humble scientists, studying the land, and making discoveries."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00021C"
msgid "Shinar was a research outpost built out in the far reaches of space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00021D"
msgid "All thanks to a lone pirate who tricked us all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00021E"
msgid "That's because it no longer exists. It has no more place on a map than the rocks and the trees."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021830]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00021F"
msgid "Yes. He doomed our entire settlement. But he lives, and we died."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000220"
msgid "They know nothing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000221"
msgid "No good comes from helping strangers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021564]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000222"
msgid "I'm not familiar with the Tragedy of Shinar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021786]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000223"
msgid "Let them watch us toast them, from the pits of their early graves!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021786]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000224"
msgid "Yes, let us celebrate the young and the fearless, and build monuments to their heroism!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021673]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000225"
msgid "They know more than a coward like you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021546]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000226"
msgid "And I'll wait for the moment I can tell them \"I told you so.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021546]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000227"
msgid "No! I will remind them every minute of their lives they are fools."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000228"
msgid "They're young. Let them be."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000229"
msgid "No one who's seen war would want any part of it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00022A"
msgid "Why? Why volunteer for such misery?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021656]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00022B"
msgid "Hear, hear! Bravery and stupidity are one and the same. I should know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102167E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00022C"
msgid "Oh, these young fools, so certain of their morality. What do they know, eh?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021630]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00022D"
msgid "I'm going to enlist in the Vanguard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102177E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00022E"
msgid "Please. You know what your righteousness gets you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102162A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00022F"
msgid "Because it's the right thing to do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102178C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000230"
msgid "A pointless death."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000233"
msgid "Stay out of trouble now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000234"
msgid "Try to stay on my good side while you're here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000235"
msgid "Stay safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000236"
msgid "Back to it then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102180C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000237"
msgid "Farewell! Only God knows when we shall meet again, the secretive bastard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102180B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000238"
msgid "Parting is such sweet sorrow."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021809]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000239"
msgid "See ya dork."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021808]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00023A"
msgid "Good talk, you weirdo."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021807]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00023B"
msgid "That was boring."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021806]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00023C"
msgid "Mm-hm."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021804]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00023D"
msgid "Don't worry about me being a flight risk. I won't fight what's already written."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021803]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00023E"
msgid "We'll talk more later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021802]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00023F"
msgid "I'll be around if you have other questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_IvicaShared03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000240"
msgid "There was always something fishy about that story. Now I know why."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_IvicaShared02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000241"
msgid "Besides that? He got me slates of the last five Razer Derby championships. I'm still working through them, so no spoilers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000242"
msgid "If you can do it, it's worth the gamble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo02a
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000243"
msgid "When I arrived here, I found a place in dire straits. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo02b
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000244"
msgid "It's better now, but there's still work to be done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000245"
msgid "Get out of here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000246"
msgid "Odjebi! And what am I supposed to do for work then?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000247"
msgid "*Groan*. You know it's unethical to look through someone's personal logs, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000248"
msgid "I'll turn myself into the guard. We'll see how long that plays out once someone gets sick and needs my help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000249"
msgid "What? What are you implying?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00024A"
msgid "And what would you recommend?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo07
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00024B"
msgid "You're right. You should choose something else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo08
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00024C"
msgid "That feels even more hopeless, but a hard truth is still the truth. It must be stomached, even if the taste is sour."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo09
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00024D"
msgid "I started to find company in drink and poetry, and became the lowly slug you see before you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo09
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00024F"
msgid "But shortly after I arrived here, there was a mass exodus. I lost the people's ear, and with it, my voice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo09
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000250"
msgid "I was a preacher for the Sanctum Universum. A pretty good one, in fact. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo10
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000251"
msgid "What did you preach before you lost your faith?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_IvicaShared01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000252"
msgid "He donated supplies and his ship to this settlement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo09
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000253"
msgid "You made the wrong move. Somebody's gonna get hurt, or sick, and I won't be there to save them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021855]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000255"
msgid "Sometimes I see the light on in Grace's tent all night. That woman could use a break"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021854]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000256"
msgid "If you need medical attention, talk to Grace, she'll set you up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021853]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000257"
msgid "Ivica says Sunni is lazy, but I think it's an act. She does her job on her own time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021852]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000258"
msgid "Yeats is the town preacher and drunk. Right now he's doing both in jail."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021851]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000259"
msgid "Big Hal's one of those guys who speaks from his chest. Sometimes it feels like he could knock you back with his breath."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102184F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00025A"
msgid "I rely a lot on Dr. Kim to alleviate my aches and pains. She's a genius of a doctor."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102184E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00025B"
msgid "I'm sorry, I've got too much to deal with right now. If you have business here, speak with Hal Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102184D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00025C"
msgid "This outpost is holding on by a thread. If it weren't for Hal..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102184B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00025D"
msgid "I've been listening to these relaxation tapes, but they aren't helping."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102184A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00025E"
msgid "Grace and Sunni Kim couldn't be more different as siblings. You have to wonder if Sunni was adopted."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021849]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00025F"
msgid "I trained as a boxer when I was young. It taught me discipline. How to weather a punch in the gut. Life is full of such punches."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021848]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000260"
msgid "Hal is Caspian's mentor. But someone needs to do the same for Sunni Kim. In my opinion, she's lazy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021847]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000261"
msgid "There's a lot that needs doing here. But outside of Hal? No one wants to actually do the work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021845]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000262"
msgid "The ore from the mine will pay huge dividends. Starting with the generators."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021844]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000263"
msgid "Good work with the robot. Damn machines are no substitute for hard work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021843]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000264"
msgid "We had a deal, stranger. I suggest you honor it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021842]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000265"
msgid "You said you were gonna scrap that robot. So why is it walking around like it owns the place?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021840]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000266"
msgid "*Yawn*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102183F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000267"
msgid "Can't believe we got visitors coming to this dump."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102183E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000268"
msgid "I got Big Hal to cover for like... three of shifts this week. Next week, I'm going for four."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102183D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000269"
msgid "Yo."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102183B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00026A"
msgid "Once we finish the outpost's business, we can settle ours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102183A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00026B"
msgid "You being here is kismet. The reaper coming to collect. I just thought I had more time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021839]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00026C"
msgid "I'll make my daily rounds. I trust you can keep our discussion private."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102158B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00026E"
msgid "All right, out with it. Hal says you got some new info that'll exonerate Yeats."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00026F"
msgid "I'm sorry, but I lied to you. That blood isn't Ivica's. I just wanted to verify it's Caspian's."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102176B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000270"
msgid "Not me. Talk to the newcomer. They've been investigating on my behalf."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021627]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000271"
msgid "I've been trying to convince him it's necessary and he just refuses to cooperate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021627]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000272"
msgid "Well, I seriously doubt he'll say yes, but if you can do me a favor, ask Ivica if he'll submit to a blood typing test."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000273"
msgid "Just keep your end of the bargain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102173F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000274"
msgid "Let me just mix it with the serum here and... there are no antigens? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102177A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000275"
msgid "Because you got Caspian's blood on your gloves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021724]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000276"
msgid "What creature? Where's the lab data from that examination?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102168C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000277"
msgid "They're your gloves and a tranquilizer from your lab. Which makes you a suspect in the supply theft."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021686]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000278"
msgid "So we just need to find someone with that blood type."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021647]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000279"
msgid "All right Hal, I'm here. What's this big break in the case you pulled out the rabbit's hat?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00027A"
msgid "But turns out I didn't need to go that far."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00027B"
msgid "I still have it. Well, most of it anyway. I synthesized some into chems, just in case I needed to ditch the evidence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00027C"
msgid "[Evidence] You're the supply thief. I hacked into your computer and found a confession."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021723]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00027D"
msgid "What are you proposing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00027E"
msgid "Anyway, there, you have the truth."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021597]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00027F"
msgid "Absolutely not. If she wants my blood, she can come and take it herself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000280"
msgid "I can tell you right now who that is. It's Yeats."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000281"
msgid "She just went where the evidence took her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102156E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000282"
msgid "Dr. Kim wants you to do a blood typing test?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102159D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000283"
msgid "I'd feel better if you took something, but fine. You're still in bed with me regardless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021719]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000284"
msgid "Is there anything I can help you with?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102180F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000285"
msgid "Keep your bribes. I'm only letting you go because you provide a vital service. But I want Yeats' name cleared."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102180E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000286"
msgid "Keep your bribes. I'm letting her slide as a favor to you. But I want Yeats' name cleared."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021775]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000287"
msgid "I don't remember, okay? And I don't keep everything on my computer. I have written documentation too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021749]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000288"
msgid "When Yeats took the fall for that, I thought it'd be no big deal. But Sasha took it too far."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021749]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000289"
msgid "She asked me to synthesize them into chems, but I refused. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021749]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00028A"
msgid "*Sigh* It's that obvious, huh. Yeah, Sunni's the one who stole the Caelumite."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00028B"
msgid "You must be joking. Those are my gloves and syringe, yes, but I was likely using them on a creature."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021663]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00028C"
msgid "*Sigh* Fine. I trust we have a deal then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021612]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00028D"
msgid "[Extortion] That's of no use to me. I want credits instead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021638]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00028E"
msgid "That's the most likely scenario. And it'd back up what everyone is saying about him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021579]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00028F"
msgid "Sorry. No deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000290"
msgid "According to your records, that would make it Yeats' blood."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102174E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000291"
msgid "Where's the Caelumite now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000292"
msgid "You have a deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102179C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000293"
msgid "Here's the Caelumite. That should be enough to clear Yeats."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000294"
msgid "You're covering for someone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000295"
msgid "You're covering for your sister, a chem addict. She stole the supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102168B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000296"
msgid "Innocent? Let's not act like Yeats hasn't pissed us all off with his drinking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021619]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000297"
msgid "Look, I'm just going to be frank with you. Do you have any real proof? Because if not, then I suggest you leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000298"
msgid "You're making a mistake. But fine, I can see I don't have a choice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000299"
msgid "Yes, but I'm not a combat medic either."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00029A"
msgid "You're right. I am the most qualified here. I can see where you're going with this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021531]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00029B"
msgid "Good. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021774]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00029C"
msgid "In exchange, I'll give you half price on medical treatment. And, I'll owe you a favor. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021774]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00029D"
msgid "You say I took the Caelumite for medicine but forgot to log the transfer. We blame the whole thing on negligence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021702]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00029E"
msgid "I was trying to get the blood sample for my research. When things got messy, I stole the Caelumite knowing it'd point to Yeats."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021644]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00029F"
msgid "There's no motive though. Why would I need to steal?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021643]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A0"
msgid "I know, it's hard to argue against that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021669]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A1"
msgid "*Sigh* Fine, I admit it. I took the supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A2"
msgid "Don't try to pass the blame. You put an innocent man away."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A3"
msgid "Leave my sister out of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A4"
msgid "No, I don't want to get Sunni in trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021536]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A5"
msgid "Your sister Sunni tried to cover up for you. Clearly she knows."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021816]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A6"
msgid "Typical of a cop to mess up a standard house call and assault."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021729]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A7"
msgid "Administering the tranquilizer would've required medical training. That makes you a suspect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A8"
msgid "I don't think anyone would've left him bleeding like that..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021691]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002A9"
msgid "The suspect bandaged Caspian up. Clearly you were qualified to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002AA"
msgid "I had hoped Sasha would let Yeats go with a slap on the wrist, but she turned it into this whole thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002AB"
msgid "You can't prove that. And like I said, there's likely contamination."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002AC"
msgid "I get your point. And I'm not saying the sample is foolproof either. Yeats might be innocent, like you say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102181C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002AD"
msgid "Absolutely not. You can't coerce me into confessing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102181B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002AE"
msgid "You wouldn't..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002AF"
msgid "Keep in mind I am the only doctor in this outpost. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B0"
msgid "So what now? Are you going to turn me in, or is there room to negotiate here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B1"
msgid "So what now? Are you going to turn my sister in, or is there room to negotiate here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021755]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B2"
msgid "What? I'm not going to take the fall for him just so we can have a church."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021754]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B3"
msgid "I understand it's important, long term. I just..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B4"
msgid "You should just take the fall for this. We need Yeats to lead the House of Worship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B5"
msgid "No. You haven't proven anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B6"
msgid "I'm not going to admit anything without evidence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B7"
msgid "I'm sorry, but that's not evidence of anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B8"
msgid "I might be in trouble then, regardless of the facts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002B9"
msgid "Is that how everyone else feels too? Damn."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021761]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002BA"
msgid "I think that's the most likely explanation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021731]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002BB"
msgid "Stop wasting everyone's time. Confess already."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021730]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002BC"
msgid "Just admit you did it. Everyone thinks so."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102172F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002BD"
msgid "I have a feeling you're guilty. And I trust my gut."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002BE"
msgid "Are the medical supplies here free to use by anyone?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102155E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002BF"
msgid "That's true. I... I don't have an answer for that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021822]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C0"
msgid "You said yourself no one else had access to the gloves and the tranquilizer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C1"
msgid "The gloves and tranquilizer alone implicate you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C2"
msgid "Look, I don't care what the evidence is. Either admit guilt or I will have to hurt the people you love."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C3"
msgid "You're caught up in your own lies. I'd be willing to bet that blood doesn't actually match Yeats'."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021672]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C4"
msgid "Clearly you're trying to get blood type data. No one else here has a need for it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021563]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C5"
msgid "Then we have to rely on Sasha's investigation. If she thinks Yeats did it, then he'll need to serve time for it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021622]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C6"
msgid "I admit, I needed that information."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C7"
msgid "I'm afraid that's what the science says. I'm sorry. I know a lot of folks were hoping Yeats was innocent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C8"
msgid "Medicine is a powerful tool, but one easily abused."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002C9"
msgid "Oh god no. I keep all chems, syringes, and equipment under lock and key."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002CA"
msgid "*Scoffs* I'm sorry, but I don't have time to play these games. I've got work to do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021785]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002CB"
msgid "I don't know, it's just a hunch."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021784]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002CC"
msgid "I don't have anything concrete, no."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021569]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002CD"
msgid "So what blood type is he? I'd like to know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002CE"
msgid "True, I can see why it'd look suspicious."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002CF"
msgid "[Grace's Computer] You admitted to the theft on your computer. Time to fess up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D0"
msgid "You were after Caspian's blood."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D1"
msgid "Just give me a moment to run the test."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D2"
msgid "And I think I'd remember if I performed surgery on a person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D3"
msgid "I agree. That kind of work is more common than you think, especially out here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021586]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D4"
msgid "So now there's blood and glass everywhere. So I turn to look for a broom."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D5"
msgid "What do you think? Did he do it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102153F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D6"
msgid "That's when I dropped a box of mason jars."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021678]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D7"
msgid "In my opinion, Yeats is the supply thief."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021603]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D8"
msgid "We can just mix it with a serum here to see if it produces antibodies. Hm... looks like a type AB positive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102164F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002D9"
msgid "Now, if you'll excuse me, I have some samples to analyze."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002DA"
msgid "You're the supply thief."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021608]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002DB"
msgid "Theft, most likely. Yeats may have stolen it from my lab to fulfill his chem habit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021829]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002DC"
msgid "We don't have a good suspect at this point."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002DD"
msgid "I don't think he did. I think you're hiding something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102178B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002DE"
msgid "You sound relieved and overjoyed for a simple sample."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002DF"
msgid "You don't know the half of it. I've been arguing with this man for months. MONTHS."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021629]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E0"
msgid "What? Why would I do that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102158D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E1"
msgid "Absolutely. I'm guessing either you have a silver tongue, or you paid him in gold. Because I tried everything with that man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021545]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E2"
msgid "Do you want to know how I got it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E3"
msgid "Is there anyone in the Outpost with that blood type? They might be a suspect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102173B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E4"
msgid "If you're going to make such a heavy accusation, I hope you can back it up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021655]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E6"
msgid "So it IS Caspian's blood."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021740]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E7"
msgid "I'd have to run an analysis, but I'd put money on it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E8"
msgid "Isn't there a chance this blood is human?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002E9"
msgid "I don't really have proof to give you. But there's an overwhelming amount of circumstantial evidence pointing to him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002EA"
msgid "As a matter of fact, that would be Yeats. And I believe he's already in custody."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002EB"
msgid "I was hoping you might provide insight on where this blood and syringe came from."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021592]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002EC"
msgid "The blood doesn't appear to belong to any species native to this habitat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002ED"
msgid "[Grace's Computer] Cut the act. I read your logs. You stole the Caelumite after trying to obtain a blood sample."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021714]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002EE"
msgid "I'd have to run a test but I haven't personally done any procedure like that. It's most likely from a dissection."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002EF"
msgid "Might this blood belong to Yeats?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102167D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F0"
msgid "What are you getting at?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102167D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F1"
msgid "Of course, I'm the only one here with access to surgical gloves and equipment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102165A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F2"
msgid "I think Yeats stole your gloves and tranquilizer. I'm just trying to find proof."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102162F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F3"
msgid "So they belong to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102156F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F4"
msgid "You shouldn't overthink it. Only one person had the motive. Sadly, that's Yeats."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021746]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F5"
msgid "I think someone stole them from your tent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F6"
msgid "I don't like where this questioning is going. What are you implying?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F7"
msgid "Oh. I thought maybe it was from a creature I dissected."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F8"
msgid "It's not convenient, it's reality."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002F9"
msgid "A lie? Are you accusing me of something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002FA"
msgid "This seems to corroborate what Caspian told me, provided the blood is his."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021682]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002FB"
msgid "But I do occasionally dissect local fauna to see if they can provide anything useful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021682]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002FC"
msgid "Not unless I have to perform surgery, and that has happened in months."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002FD"
msgid "That being said, I'll still try to provide an answer for you. It'll only take a second to get a result."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002FE"
msgid "I can do this for you, with the caveat it's likely contaminated at this point. The result won't be conclusive proof of anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102165F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0002FF"
msgid "Did you find these in the trash? I would advise you against handling such things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102165F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000300"
msgid "Oh, what do you have there? Surgical gloves and a used syringe?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000301"
msgid "These were the gloves and syringe used in the supply theft."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000302"
msgid "[Lie] No, this is a sample of Ivica's blood. He's finally willing to donate to the cause."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021797]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000303"
msgid "That's a serious accusation. I take it it was Yeats? I've heard he's a suspect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021834]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000304"
msgid "I'm not sure. I'm trying to figure out who stole them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102171B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000305"
msgid "That sounds awful convenient."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102171A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000306"
msgid "Dissection? Really, doctor? I thought you'd come up with a more creative lie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021637]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000307"
msgid "Anyway, looks like someone got Rusty up and running already, and I didn't even have to pay them. Sucker born every minute."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021634]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000308"
msgid "Would there be any reason for there to be blood on these gloves?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102176F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000309"
msgid "That was hours earlier. He was asking if we got a new supply of drinks, and I told him that wasn't on the docket until next month."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021858]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00030A"
msgid "Why Dr. Kim?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021598]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00030B"
msgid "[Give Evidence] I need to know the blood type of the sample here, and what was in the syringe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021551]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00030C"
msgid "And while the method of extraction looks a little sloppy, I'll take what I can get."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021551]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00030D"
msgid "You don't know what a pain this has been, trying to get a simple blood sample from a very stubborn man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021551]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00030E"
msgid "*Exhales* Well it's about freaking time. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00030F"
msgid "Very well. Deliver it to Dr. Kim. See if the blood matches Caspian's. If so, it validates his story."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021685]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000310"
msgid "I have questions on the stolen supplies. Sasha said you witnessed Yeats at the scene of the crime?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000311"
msgid "What do you do around here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102160D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000312"
msgid "[Evidence] I have something for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000313"
msgid "If we could find out what her motive is, that and the gloves would be enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102180D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000314"
msgid "I was not. But he'll have his vengeance soon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021574]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000315"
msgid "She's the only one with the equipment and expertise to test the blood and find a match."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102179B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000316"
msgid "I met a man named Bernhard Kleiber. Are you aware he survived?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021748]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000317"
msgid "Looking back, I never valued life. Not mine, not theirs."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021618]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000318"
msgid "What's wrong with the mining machine?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102171E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000319"
msgid "Sunni Kim says he saw Yeats talking to you shortly before the theft? Is that not true?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021662]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00031A"
msgid "Then they are braver souls than I."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00031B"
msgid "Yeah, I saw that loser. He was bugging Caspian for something. Probably casing the joint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00031C"
msgid "I did what I needed to, to survive. Or so I thought."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102181A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00031D"
msgid "Are the supplies that were stolen not a motive?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021530]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00031E"
msgid "Nonetheless, I must face the consequences."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00031F"
msgid "Can we talk about what happened to Shinar?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021773]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000320"
msgid "This outpost has changed me. I see value in life. But that is not the same as being worthy of it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000321"
msgid "But then I came here. Befriended the people. And every situation became a mirror for what I'd done before."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000322"
msgid "That is a complicated question. When I left Shinar, I was afraid of being discovered."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021722]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000323"
msgid "No ship, no comms. Dehydration sets in. Some choose death. Others are forced to make harder decisions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000324"
msgid "Do you have any regrets for what you did?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000325"
msgid "He knows just about EVERYTHING, so I'm trying to soak up the knowledge like a sponge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000326"
msgid "These days I'm mostly just Hal's understudy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000327"
msgid "I'm not assigned to anything yet, I fill in for the others when they need a break."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021611]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000328"
msgid "There were mass graves for those who took their own life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00032A"
msgid "Good. I know Ivica thinks it'll replace him, but there's plenty of other work to be done for a man of his skillset."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00032B"
msgid "*Sigh* If it can't be repaired, see if Ivica can make use of the parts. Maybe some good will come out of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00032C"
msgid "But the ore will be of use. Mining it will be beneficial."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00032D"
msgid "*Sigh* Ivica says a lot of things, not all of them true."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021578]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00032E"
msgid "You left them all to die. You're a monster."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00032F"
msgid "Or she's innocent, and there's another explanation for the gloves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000330"
msgid "You did what you had to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021668]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000331"
msgid "We can use it to blast through the rock, and get the ore behind it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021668]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000333"
msgid "It's got a blown PCM. With a few tweaks, the parts from that Model A can fix it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000334"
msgid "I didn't see what became of Shinar. But I can imagine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102168A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000335"
msgid "Before the vote, I want to talk about Shinar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000336"
msgid "The robot's back up and running."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021815]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000337"
msgid "I got the robot working, but then it got damaged."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021814]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000338"
msgid "Ivica and I decided to scrap the robot. He says he can fix the mining machine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021779]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000339"
msgid "She might reveal something if you ask the right questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021779]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00033A"
msgid "I think you'll just need to speak to her yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102174D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00033B"
msgid "So, you've come back. Have you reconsidered my offer to scramble this robot's eggs?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021701]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00033C"
msgid "Hell yeah. First I found some Chunks in my pocket, now this. This day just keeps getting better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00033D"
msgid "Already done. Hal Caruso asked me to get it working."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102161D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00033E"
msgid "On second thought, let's just bring it to Dr. Kim."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021562]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00033F"
msgid "But yeah, she's my sis. We look out for each other, because at the end of the day, if blood don't have your back, who does?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021562]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000340"
msgid "Gracie? She got all the brains in the family. That's okay, I got this cool hat, so joke's on her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102153A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000341"
msgid "How are you holding up?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102155A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000342"
msgid "But Dr. Kim doesn't need to steal chems, she can request them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102155A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000343"
msgid "No. Caelumite can be used for chems, which is why Yeats is a suspect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000344"
msgid "It might not, but maybe you can trap her in a lie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000345"
msgid "You and your friend have cursed me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000346"
msgid "That cuts down on the oxygen your soil life has to make nutrients."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021705]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000347"
msgid "Unlikely, but true. It's possible. You'll have to establish motive to convince the guard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021728]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000348"
msgid "In the meantime, I'll be here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000349"
msgid "So what do you want me to do, fly? Get real."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021642]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00034A"
msgid "I can hack into her computer, see if there isn't any evidence there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021580]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00034B"
msgid "How so?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00034C"
msgid "I'll just pick her pockets. She might have something incriminating on her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00034D"
msgid "Well, before I was sitting. Perfectly content. Now, I am waiting. And it's killing me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102177D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00034E"
msgid "Yeah, yeah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102172D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00034F"
msgid "Just be mindful. Make dedicated pathways to avoid walking on your beds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021753]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000350"
msgid "I'm not sure that would be enough to free Yeats."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021695]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000351"
msgid "Making my rounds. There's much to do besides the tasks I gave you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000352"
msgid "She's a suspect. Anything she tells us would be unreliable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102166D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000353"
msgid "Fine. My mind is occupied at the moment, and I can't think straight."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021621]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000354"
msgid "I don't think that's wise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102155D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000355"
msgid "[Evidence] I found these in the dumpster. They may have been used to sedate Caspian."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000356"
msgid "Hopefully you won't have to wait much longer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102153E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000357"
msgid "We could take the items to Dr. Kim to verify but..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021783]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000358"
msgid "Let's take a look."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021759]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000359"
msgid "Sure, but why don't you tell me first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021837]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00035A"
msgid "The first thing he did when he got here was fix up my weapon. Must've learned that with the Fleet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021837]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00035B"
msgid "I always suspected something was off about Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021648]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00035C"
msgid "You shouldn't walk on the soil. It compacts the soil and decreases air spaces."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00035D"
msgid "I don't know what you think you got there, but you're barking up the wrong tree."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00035E"
msgid "I appreciate the effort, stranger, but that case has been solved. I'm just waiting on a confession."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00035F"
msgid "I see. We may not have a choice. She's the only who can analyze the blood sample."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000360"
msgid "This shirt I'm wearing... it's his!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000361"
msgid "He would give you the shirt off his back. Do you know how I know?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021821]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000363"
msgid "Recently I've been acting as the Outpost leader, with Zena retiring."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000364"
msgid "Dr. Kim may not be completely forthcoming, if she's the one who stole the supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000365"
msgid "I'd talk to Caspian about it. He was the one working the tent when the supplies were stolen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000366"
msgid "He stole Caelumite from the supply tent. It's a rare, unique material that can be used to craft stuff."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021709]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000367"
msgid "Exactly. And the evidence we do have is flimsy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021671]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000368"
msgid "Agreed. I assume we're on the same page here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021713]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000369"
msgid "Cool, here's the key. If you find anything, I'd check back with Hal on what to do next."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021712]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00036A"
msgid "Nuclear. Then I'd take it to the guard and confront the suspect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00036B"
msgid "That may be a medical grade sedative, applied via a syringe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00036C"
msgid "It's not just any man though, it's Hal. He's the glue that keeps this shit together."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102173E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00036D"
msgid "What are your thoughts on Caruso?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021585]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00036E"
msgid "That's what I would do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00036F"
msgid "Surgical gloves... and there's blood on them. And a syringe. Possibly a tranquilizer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021735]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000370"
msgid "[Syringe] I found this in the dumpster. It may have been used to sedate Caspian."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000371"
msgid "Who should I talk to about helping Yeats?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102162E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000372"
msgid "Okay. I'll check the dumpster then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102162D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000373"
msgid "I've already combed through the dumpster and found some evidence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000374"
msgid "My cop instincts tell me he used to be a military man or something. But he's a very private person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000375"
msgid "First thing he did when he got here is fix the sights on my gun. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000376"
msgid "Big Hal is good people. He also knows a LOT about weapons. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000377"
msgid "What are your thoughts on Caruso?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021573]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000378"
msgid "When I woke up? The broken glass and all the blood was cleaned up, and my hand was bandaged. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021573]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000379"
msgid "One thousand percent. Because here's the kicker. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102165E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00037A"
msgid "Also, seeing as he loaned me this shirt, I think I will keep it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102165E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00037B"
msgid "If he is dead, then he knows what no living man is privy to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021795]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00037C"
msgid "Oh yeah, like animal tranquilizer or something!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00037D"
msgid "When you're done, find Caspian. He was there during the theft, and has information I'd like you to investigate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00037E"
msgid "I'd start with Yeats himself, and Sasha, his jailer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021718]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00037F"
msgid "Well, he's the only one who actually listened to my version of what happened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021745]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000380"
msgid "You must be tired of being hunted. I get it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021699]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000381"
msgid "But then the water pump broke and uh... yeah. That's when you showed up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021699]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000382"
msgid "Hal wanted to look in the dumpster bins for anything suspicious."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000383"
msgid "Hal has mentored Caspian and helped Zena with a lot of the leadership responsibilities."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000384"
msgid "He's a force multiplier for the group. Ivica works harder, but he keeps to himself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000385"
msgid "He's new, but he's earned his keep."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021681]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000386"
msgid "And then out of nowhere, I feel this sharp, jabbing pain in my neck. I start to turn around, and then boom! I pass out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000387"
msgid "You said you cut yourself, is it possible your blood got on the assailant?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102160C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000388"
msgid "No story. I am a killer, no doubt. But this isn't just about me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000389"
msgid "Tell me what you know about the theft."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021549]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00038A"
msgid "There's always a sob story with you criminals. I'm not buying it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00038B"
msgid "Regardless, I've accepted my fate. But it's not my fate I'm concerned about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021633]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00038D"
msgid "Maybe, or some kind of neck pinch that targets pressure points. I've seen that shit in the movies!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00038E"
msgid "You wouldn't say that if you knew what kind of man Hal really is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021596]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00038F"
msgid "Oh yeah, I've seen people in crime shows use animal tranquilizer. That juice will knock out an Aceles."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102154E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000390"
msgid "That sounds like a syringe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000391"
msgid "Seems like you were karate chopped."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021670]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000392"
msgid "So the night it all went down, I was organizing the supplies over here, trying to get my system right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000393"
msgid "I need to talk to you about the supply theft."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000394"
msgid "Stupid, I know. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000395"
msgid "So I tried to pick up the broken glass and put it in this box, and I cut my fingers. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000396"
msgid "Oh yeah. Sunni Kim says he saw Yeats creeping around the supply area on more than one occasion."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000397"
msgid "The street name for it is \"Giant Heart.\" The effects are typically increased energy and improved pain tolerance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000398"
msgid "It's a very useful material in crafting. But when with the right catalyst, it can also make a powerful chem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000399"
msgid "We had a supply of Caelumite that Hal brought over from his old settlement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021833]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00039A"
msgid "You seem to trust Hal a lot. Why is that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102156D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00039B"
msgid "Hal's the only one who understood that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102156D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00039C"
msgid "But it just takes me a few tries to figure stuff out. Once I do, I'm solid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102156D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00039D"
msgid "Because everyone here thinks I'm a screw up. And I get it. Sometimes I'll break stuff, lose things... "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00039E"
msgid "One man's endorsement means that much?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00039F"
msgid "One, he's always high. Two, the thefts stopped as soon as I locked him up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021607]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A0"
msgid "Yeah, I'll tell you what I told Sasha."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021659]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A2"
msgid "Oh nice, are you gonna help us bust Yeats out? He totally didn't do it. Just ask Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102158C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A3"
msgid "But that's just who she is. I'm not going to ask her to change."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102158C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A4"
msgid "I know she gets a bad rap for not working as hard as the others, but I think it's her attitude more than her work ethic."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A5"
msgid "I'm still processing the shock, to be honest. I didn't know the man he was, only the one I knew."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A6"
msgid "Then he's gonna have to make amends with whatever God he serves, and quick."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021677]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A7"
msgid "What can you tell me about the stolen supplies?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A8"
msgid "What are your thoughts on Caruso?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003A9"
msgid "What can you tell me about Grace Kim?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003AA"
msgid "Can you tell me about your sister, Sunni?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021790]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003AB"
msgid "You could preach for the House of the Enlightened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021602]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003AC"
msgid "Were there any witnesses to the theft?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102169A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003AD"
msgid "What happens if Yeats doesn't admit guilt?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021628]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003AE"
msgid "What supplies went missing? Maybe I can find them?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021676]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003AF"
msgid "True. There is a legacy beyond life that echoes across time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102168F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B0"
msgid "What evidence do you have against him?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B1"
msgid "All right. Let me know if I can answer anything else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021760]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B2"
msgid "That's all the questions I had on the case."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021568]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B3"
msgid "I've got questions about the stolen supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B4"
msgid "I have no faith. In anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B5"
msgid "I am not a thief, but a victim of theft. What has been stolen from me is my faith in justice and goodwill."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B6"
msgid "I am accused of stealing supplies. But I contest that notion."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102175F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B7"
msgid "Zena wants me to look into your case."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102175E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B8"
msgid "Caruso asked me to help you get out of jail."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021653]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003B9"
msgid "He never made that clear to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003BA"
msgid "As for who pointed it, take your pick. They're all angled in this direction."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003BB"
msgid "Rather than actually investigate the crime, Sasha believes a pointed finger is adequate evidence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003BC"
msgid "There is nothing to tell. I am guilty of being a faithless drunk. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102169E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003BD"
msgid "Can you tell me your side of what happened?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102167C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003BE"
msgid "Which is a false correlation. Yes, my appetite for liquor is nothing short of prodigious. But I've never touched a chem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102167C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003BF"
msgid "Caelumite. A material for crafting a number of items, from suits to medical chems. It's the \"chems\" part that makes me a suspect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021700]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C0"
msgid "What supplies were stolen?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C1"
msgid "Valiant. But if you are so confident, then by all means, talk to the guard, perform thy miracle!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C2"
msgid "I make my own luck, priest."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102178A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C3"
msgid "The guy wouldn't know sobriety if it kicked him in the privates."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102178A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C4"
msgid "It's an open and shut case. Yeats is obviously the perp."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102169F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C5"
msgid "Hal put you up to this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C6"
msgid "Knowing dust is the end makes us value life. We take hold of it and live it without fear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021591]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C7"
msgid "Indeed. Sasha tells me Hal Caruso is dead, by your hand. But I am not taking confessions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C8"
msgid "What are you in here for?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021601]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003C9"
msgid "But it matters not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021601]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003CA"
msgid "I too am not an innocent man. I am, however, innocent of the crime that has me jailed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021601]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003CB"
msgid "True enough! No man is swift enough to escape the devil's lasso. Not even Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003CC"
msgid "If that is your wish, my dear Sisyphus, I will not stop you. Talk to the guard, and clear my name! Perform thy miracle!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102164D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003CD"
msgid "I'm not opposed to the idea you're innocent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102164C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003CE"
msgid "He does."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003CF"
msgid "It's a mess, among other things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021567]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D0"
msgid "*Burp*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021567]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D1"
msgid "I've no clue who you are or what brought this on, but as the Bard says, \"Fortune brings in some boats that are not steered.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021765]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D2"
msgid "Strange. Hal is a man of few words, but the intent is always clear. Regardless..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D3"
msgid "That is the heart of the issue at hand."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021544]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D4"
msgid "Is it not doing so now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021789]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D5"
msgid "I wouldn't call him a saint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021543]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D6"
msgid "Religion is a crutch. You need to stand up and face reality."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D7"
msgid "Words and deeds live on forever. Preach and you will be immortal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D8"
msgid "I see. Life without death will only increase the time we waste."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003D9"
msgid "It's about teaching self-reliance and fostering a community outside of belief in a creator."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021726]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003DA"
msgid "If that's your way of asking me to shut my bloody mouth, then well played. The floor is yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021583]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003DB"
msgid "One step at a time. Let's clear your name first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003DC"
msgid "I don't know much about its tenets, but I do know one thing. At least it's bold."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003DD"
msgid "And then there is this third entry into the ring. Caruso's so-called \"Great Serpent.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021827]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003DE"
msgid "The larger issue is the voice I am tasked with preaching."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021827]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003DF"
msgid "Innocent, guilty, these are but temporary problems."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021826]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E0"
msgid "Then I must disappoint him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E1"
msgid "I even became a preacher of the doctrine. But where was God when I needed him most? That was the first of three lies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E2"
msgid "You see, I was once a man of faith. Born into the Sanctum Universum."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021727]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E3"
msgid "So if Hal wishes me to preach, then as a wise man once said, \"He's shit out of luck.\" As are you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021727]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E4"
msgid "Even if you were to find the supply thief and clear my name, I have lost it. My faith."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021667]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E5"
msgid "No, I suspect this is Saint Hal Caruso's doing. He always believed I was innocent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021667]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E6"
msgid "Zena never cared about what happened to me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021666]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E7"
msgid "I take it he wants me to lead the House of Worship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021666]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E8"
msgid "I would say \"angel,\" but I no longer believe in such things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021666]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003E9"
msgid "So Hal has not yet given up on me. A saint, that man. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003EA"
msgid "The reality is, we are not worthy of whatever comes after."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003EB"
msgid "But in the end, I suppose it matters not. What I lack isn't a belief in God, it's a belief in humanity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102174C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003EC"
msgid "That is the heart of the issue at hand."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003ED"
msgid "That is not something I want to preach. I want a world where we are more than dust."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003EE"
msgid "Day by day he's eroded by the stream, shrinking to a pebble, and ground to gravel and dust."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003EF"
msgid "If man is without a soul, then he is but a rock, caught in time's endless river. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F0"
msgid "I find their ideology hopeless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F1"
msgid "If this is a place of worship, you need an actual doctrine to preach."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021658]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F2"
msgid "Let's talk about your faith."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021721]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F3"
msgid "You are tough but fair. I think I know where the problem lies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102164E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F4"
msgid "It's not a mess, but a reflection. A mirror of my state of mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021758]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F5"
msgid "Agreed. I never understood them myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021813]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F6"
msgid "Zena has asked I help you get this place functioning."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021812]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F7"
msgid "Caruso has asked I help you get this place functioning."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F8"
msgid "Then why not call it what it is. A glorified chat server."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021820]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003F9"
msgid "It's a shithole, and you're the chief defecator."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021828]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003FA"
msgid "You can't really focus a religion on the absence of a creator."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021828]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003FB"
msgid "So next, I tried the House of Enlightened. But I found their philosophy lacking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003FC"
msgid "Well, I'm not here to lie to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021778]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003FD"
msgid "It's a mess, among other things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021772]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003FE"
msgid "A test? What are we, schoolchildren? The whole thing seems infantile, cast upon us by an insecure God."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021641]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0003FF"
msgid "We endure hardships as it is a test of our faith."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000400"
msgid "Indeed. Then I shall cease with the monologues and cede the podium to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000401"
msgid "What brings you, stranger, to this humble priest?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000402"
msgid "Said the liar to the fool. But I will happily play my part."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102166F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000403"
msgid "If this is a place of worship, you need an actual doctrine to preach."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021689]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000404"
msgid "It's not a mess, but a reflection. A mirror of my state of mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021617]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000406"
msgid "Then we shouldn't waste any more time with idle chitchat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102167B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000407"
msgid "I think you have the wrong man. I'm just a farmer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102179F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000408"
msgid "Enough small talk. I didn't come here to debate with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021559]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000409"
msgid "Listening to you, I bet the people here find you insufferable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00040A"
msgid "Casts derision upon, Supersession of breath."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00040B"
msgid "Many times he died, Many times rose again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021606]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00040C"
msgid "I hardly know them myself. They aren't my words, who's to say they're any good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00040D"
msgid "Is it? They're not even my words. Who's to say what's \"well\" about it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102166C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00040E"
msgid "Words are the cheapest currency, after all. And so easily counterfeited."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102166C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00040F"
msgid "In fact, I find myself struggling to find value in anything written, or spoken. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021654]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000410"
msgid "Alas, my friend, I don't even know anymore. Maybe it's me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021539]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000411"
msgid "That's what I'm saying! But nobody's listening."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000412"
msgid "What are you quoting?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000413"
msgid "Nor dread nor hope attend, A dying animal; A man awaits his end, Dreading and hoping all..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021707]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000414"
msgid "The ceremony of innocence is drowned; The best lack all conviction..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102172C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000415"
msgid "Well said."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021534]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000416"
msgid "One hundred and fifty percent. Which isn't even possible, mathematically."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021640]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000417"
msgid "You should be willing to do the work. Growing crops is critical."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000418"
msgid "I don't know what you're saying. Please speak plain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021694]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000419"
msgid "He knows death to the bone -- Man has created death."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021693]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00041A"
msgid "A great man in his pride, Confronting murderous men."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00041B"
msgid "We have business to discuss."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021646]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00041C"
msgid "Things fall apart; the centre cannot hold!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00041D"
msgid "I'm here regarding your past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021708]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00041E"
msgid "*Sigh*, I'm too old for this shit. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021636]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00041F"
msgid "Better? I think you mean \"slower.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000420"
msgid "I was told you're the one who can help me with my extended warranty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000421"
msgid "You don't. But given your crimes, you're about to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021558]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000422"
msgid "The falcon cannot hear the falconer!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021688]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000423"
msgid "I wonder if he's single."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000424"
msgid "Fine, have it your way. Rot in this cell for all I care!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000425"
msgid "Turning and turning in the widening gyre!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021616]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000426"
msgid "Enough with the poetry Yeats, just tell me where you hid the supplies!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021811]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000427"
msgid "While the worst... are full of passionate... intensity. *Burp*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102161C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000428"
msgid "Mere anarchy is loosed upon the world, the blood-dimmed tide is loosed, and everywhere!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021819]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000429"
msgid "Tell that to the plants. Look at 'em. I tell them to hurry their shit up, and they just sit there. Chilling."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102153D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00042A"
msgid "What favor did Caruso do for you again?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00042B"
msgid "So he's only kind of a dick."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00042C"
msgid "Then again, he did fix the irrigation and brought supplies for my sister. Even if they were hand-me downs from a different outpost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00042D"
msgid "Doesn't say much, super creepy dude. I don't trust people who don't talk a lot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00042E"
msgid "Don't ask me how I got it. Let's just say my fingers be hella fast. Just not while picking crops."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00042F"
msgid "To get the robot juiced, you'll need a power cell from the generator. This keycard should let you gaffle 'em."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102157F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000430"
msgid "Can you tell me your opinion on Caruso?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102185A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000431"
msgid "I'm a \"farmer\", but technically my boy Rusty does all the work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021777]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000432"
msgid "You head over to the junkyard, and get Rusty over there working for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102159F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000433"
msgid "Good point. Why CAN'T a robot do this shit?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000434"
msgid "Any work a robot can do, a human can do better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000435"
msgid "What will you be doing while I help the outpost?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102157B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000436"
msgid "So it's whatever that he's dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102157B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000437"
msgid "Like his whole sob story about his old outpost never checked out. Plague, my ass. How convenient."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102157B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000438"
msgid "I don't miss him. He did a lot for the group, but he also creeped me out. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021684]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000439"
msgid "I may owe him a favor, but we can't waste power cells on a pissbucket of bolts that does more harm than good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00043A"
msgid "Did you know the robot needs a power cell?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00043B"
msgid "Did you know the robot is permanently broken?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102174B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00043C"
msgid "Yeah, Rusty. He's a robot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00043D"
msgid "I think I'll just find a cell to power the robot, thank you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102159A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00043E"
msgid "I know, I'm a genius."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00043F"
msgid "You've got a point."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102177C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000441"
msgid "I guess it's on to Plan B."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102177C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000442"
msgid "No shit. That old dog Ivica finally did it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000443"
msgid "He's great. Works day and night, and doesn't bitch."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000444"
msgid "He's great, dork. Works day and night, and doesn't bitch."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021771]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000445"
msgid "Shit on a stick, so THAT's why nothing's getting done. Guess it's time for Plan B."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000446"
msgid "Rusty?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102154D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000447"
msgid "You'll need a power cell to turn it on. Here, this should do the trick."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102181F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000448"
msgid "Sit around and complain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102181E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000449"
msgid "Sit around and complain, dork."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00044A"
msgid "What's Plan B?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021764]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00044B"
msgid "Cool, cool. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102160B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00044C"
msgid "You can't murder a machine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021553]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00044D"
msgid "That sounds like murder."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102179E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00044E"
msgid "I fixed up the Model A by the Junkyard. How do you like it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021661]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00044F"
msgid "Hm, fair point. But if you do it, I'll pay you. Credits or chems, your pick."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021769]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000450"
msgid "I like my eggs scrambled."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021555]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000451"
msgid "Nah, I'll find another way to power the robot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000452"
msgid "Caruso will be pissed, but he's all about making lemonade from lemons. Once he sees the power upgrade, he'll accept it. Begrudgingly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000453"
msgid "Bah, machines around here are always breaking down. At worst, it'll look like a well-meaning accident."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021610]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000454"
msgid "I can take care of that for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000455"
msgid "I'm not your servant. You do it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102179A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000456"
msgid "So here's Plan A."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021799]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000457"
msgid "So dorkapalooza, here's Plan A."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000458"
msgid "And so I got to thinking, \"This sucks. Why can't a robot do this shit?\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000459"
msgid "I'm a farmer, but I don't like it. It's boring and tedious."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00045A"
msgid "Too late. The robot's malfunctioning."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021800]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00045B"
msgid "What do you do out here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102165D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00045C"
msgid "Yes, so do I."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021750]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00045E"
msgid "That should be enough to satisfy Caruso. And if it isn't? Screw it. We know better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021605]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00045F"
msgid "No more lazy workers reliant on robots. And I can use the ore to improve things around here, starting with the generators."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021605]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000460"
msgid "Hvala puno. You've done this entire outpost a service. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021550]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000462"
msgid "[Robot Parts] Just so you know, the robot is broken. Permanently."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102154F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000463"
msgid "[Robot Parts] I've got the parts you requested."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000464"
msgid "Come back to me when it's done, and we'll upgrade the generator."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102176D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000465"
msgid "Won't the other residents notice?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021698]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000466"
msgid "I'll be happy to scrap it for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021625]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000467"
msgid "[Lie] I can do that. Just tell me how."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021832]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000468"
msgid "I could use the spare parts to fix the mining machine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021832]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000469"
msgid "The robot is a useless heap of shit, but the parts are not. If, instead of repairing it, you were to break it..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021675]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00046A"
msgid "Robots can't be trusted to do work that was meant to be done with human hands."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102177B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00046B"
msgid "A strong moral center is the backbone of any settlement. Religious guidance provides it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102161B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00046C"
msgid "If you turn on the magnet while it's searching, it'll scramble its egg. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102161B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00046D"
msgid "One word: Magnets. The robot likes to go to the junkyard, and dig for spare parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021794]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00046E"
msgid "Why are humans more fit for the labor?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00046F"
msgid "He fears losing his job. But the robot is a tool. It's not meant to replace him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021652]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000470"
msgid "[Remain silent]"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021542]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000471"
msgid "Why do you care about the outpost's religion?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000472"
msgid "You seem all right to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000473"
msgid "That's okay. So am I."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102156C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000474"
msgid "Nice to meet you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000475"
msgid "Name's Sunni, with an I. I run the farm here. Also, I'm kind of a bitch."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000476"
msgid "Sweet. There aren't enough of us in this place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000477"
msgid "We'll need to get him sober, and out of prison."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021734]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000478"
msgid "Yeah? So you're a nerd, got it. Nice to meet you, nerd."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021674]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000479"
msgid "Hello. My name is <Alias=Player>."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102175D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00047A"
msgid "\"Nice to meet you.\" Jeez, what century are you from?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102175C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00047B"
msgid "Ugh, again with the politeness. You some kind of dork? Well your royal dorkness, it's a displeasure to make your acquaintance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00047C"
msgid "Bah! No machine can replace a person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102172B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00047D"
msgid "Why me instead of you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00047E"
msgid "What's up with you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021704]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00047F"
msgid "Nah, I asked you first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102173D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000480"
msgid "Not much. How are things going?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021600]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000481"
msgid "Jeez, what century are you from?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021600]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000482"
msgid "\"Hello. My name is bleagh.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000483"
msgid "Yes, yes... I am picking up what you are putting down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000484"
msgid "Never mind. You win. Turns out, I don't know how to play. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000485"
msgid "..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000486"
msgid "So it's the silent treatment, huh. Well, two can play that game."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021763]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000487"
msgid "Ah, you know. Another weirdo in the camp. Lucky me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021657]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000488"
msgid "If we depend on them and they break down, lives could be lost. There's no substitute for human brains, and human hands."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021657]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000489"
msgid "Because robots need parts. Maintenance. Things we don't readily have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021589]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00048A"
msgid "What's up?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021725]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00048C"
msgid "In time, I could've moved them. But perhaps a different voice may speed up the process."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021725]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00048D"
msgid "The people I'd like you to speak with have been harder to convince."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102174F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00048E"
msgid "I think you're just worried you yourself will be replaced."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00048F"
msgid "You know they said this thing was going to replace me? Bah!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000490"
msgid "Because it's a piece of shit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000491"
msgid "Why the anger toward the robot?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000492"
msgid "There aren't a lot of people here. The robot will help the outpost immensely."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000493"
msgid "There are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000494"
msgid "Her entire generation is soft, and it's because of robots like Rusty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000495"
msgid "Because it makes people lazy. Look at Sunni Kim. She can barely lift a finger to scratch her own ass."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000496"
msgid "How does a robot do more harm than good?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102162C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000497"
msgid "Sranje, temporary. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021651]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000498"
msgid "You'll need to talk to Ivica, the supply coordinator."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021733]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000499"
msgid "Then perhaps we are in agreement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021680]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00049A"
msgid "Robots are fine as tools. They just shouldn't be a replacement for humans."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00049B"
msgid "Human labor is superior. If anything, the robot should be scrapped."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00049C"
msgid "What favor did Caruso do for you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021697]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00049D"
msgid "The problem is the local pastor, Yeats, has been accused of theft. He says he's innocent. I believe him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021620]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00049E"
msgid "Why is Ivica against the robot?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021645]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00049F"
msgid "If I had the materials I could craft one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021565]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A0"
msgid "There is a utility robot at the junkyard that could alleviate a lot of issues, but it's lacking a power cell."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A1"
msgid "The community center is a perfect place for sermons and prayer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A2"
msgid "Oh, so you've bought into their propaganda too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A3"
msgid "No. The machines here are older models. The type of cell required is no longer in production."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021836]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A4"
msgid "It's temporary. We just need the robot to help out for a time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102178E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A6"
msgid "I saw you talking to Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102171D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A7"
msgid "This is their home. Asking them to leave is not on the table."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A8"
msgid "Would any power cell work?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021576]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004A9"
msgid "Why is Zena retiring?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021548]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004AA"
msgid "Couldn't the people here just leave this outpost?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004AB"
msgid "I had a similar thought. The junkyard might have the parts, but the magnet is hooked up to the same power source."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021566]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004AC"
msgid "*Ahem* As I was saying..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102165C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004AD"
msgid "Let's hear them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004AE"
msgid "Maybe you'll be able to sway him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004AF"
msgid "I've been trying to convince him to shift around the outpost's power distribution, with little luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021706]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B0"
msgid "How do I help with restoring the place of worship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B1"
msgid "It's her time. She's older, and would like to return home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021692]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B2"
msgid "I take it there are power cells somewhere we can use."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021711]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B4"
msgid "You seem to be an astute observer to have noticed all this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102162B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B5"
msgid "Second, we need to restore this place of worship. We can solve a lot of social issues through sermon and prayer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102162B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B6"
msgid "For one, I'd like to automate some of the work here. To do that, we need to fix the Model A unit by the junkyard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102169D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B7"
msgid "I can help with physical repairs, but people aren't my area of expertise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102164B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B8"
msgid "*Yawn* Yeah, yeah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004B9"
msgid "Repairs are needed, physically and emotionally. I will need your help with both."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021561]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004BA"
msgid "But to the matter at hand. As I mentioned, I have a list of things that I'd like to resolve."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004BB"
msgid "Then state them before I get bored and blow your head off."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021835]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004BC"
msgid "It's no stranger's. It's Hal's own words. So I repeat. Stand down. NOW."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004BD"
msgid "For the outpost to survive, it will need all its parts mended."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004BE"
msgid "Yes. People can be broken just as easily as any machine. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004BF"
msgid "Many outposts of this type have multiple maintenance issues."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102157E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004C0"
msgid "What is it? What does it say?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004C1"
msgid "Likewise. But some things are obvious to see, if not easy to correct."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004C2"
msgid "Doesn't take much to look. People just prefer to talk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004C3"
msgid "Physically and emotionally?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021744]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004C4"
msgid "The Hal we know wouldn't attack anyone unprovoked. So you'll excuse us if we find it hard to believe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004C5"
msgid "Why the need for a robot?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102171F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004C6"
msgid "This isn't fair. You're just letting this stranger get away with murder."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021717]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004C7"
msgid "Just tell me where to start."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021817]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004CA"
msgid "Everyone... stand down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102153C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004CB"
msgid "We're on it, Zena."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021632]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004CC"
msgid "My god..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021560]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004CD"
msgid "Human labor is costly. There are a number of processes we need to automate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004CE"
msgid "Grace, Sasha. If you can see to the body..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004CF"
msgid "Wait, you're just gonna take this stranger's word for it? That slate could be forged!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102166A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D0"
msgid "It's a confession... written by Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102155B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D1"
msgid "What do you mean, let the people decide?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021738]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D2"
msgid "Go into his tent and find out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D3"
msgid "Then we have a problem. My body is not free to take."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021787]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D4"
msgid "Liar!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102171C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D5"
msgid "[Evidence] The proof is here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102175B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D6"
msgid "Easy Cass. Everyone stay calm."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102181D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D7"
msgid "The fact Hal is coming out tells us all we need to know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D8"
msgid "You have a deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004D9"
msgid "That's a heavy accusation, stranger. Do you have proof?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004DA"
msgid "I swear to God, if you harmed him..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004DB"
msgid "Bullshit! Hal never hurt anyone!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102172A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004DC"
msgid "You'll leave it alone, if you know what's good for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102159E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004DD"
msgid "You'll leave it alone, if you know what's good for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004DE"
msgid "I do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004DF"
msgid "In fact, I think you should choose your next words very carefully, if you want leave this outpost alive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021825]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E0"
msgid "That's not funny. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E2"
msgid "Your man attacked me without provocation. It was self-defense."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021664]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E3"
msgid "\"Hal\" was a murderer. He got what he deserved."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E4"
msgid "I hope you're joking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E5"
msgid "We will, but you're going to tell us what happened first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021757]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E6"
msgid "On the first day of a very long vacation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021581]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E7"
msgid "We heard a struggle. What happened? Where's Hal?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021588]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E8"
msgid "We're not leaving until we get an explanation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021756]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004E9"
msgid "He's dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021859]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004EA"
msgid "Go into his tent and find out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021716]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004EB"
msgid "Imprisonment or exile would be a fair option."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021768]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004EC"
msgid "If that is what the people choose, I will abide by it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021747]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004ED"
msgid "In due time. But not yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004EE"
msgid "The blood on my hands is thick. It would not be fair to leave such a decision to any one person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004EF"
msgid "Good. Then let me explain what comes next."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021831]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F0"
msgid "I have no quarrel with that. But we'll see what the others say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F1"
msgid "I trust you have a proposition, then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102157D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F2"
msgid "When this is done, your life is forfeit. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021824]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F3"
msgid "My terms are as follows. In exchange for my submission, I would like you to help me resolve some pressing issues here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102161E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F4"
msgid "Unfortunate. But I will not go quietly!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F5"
msgid "They do. But it'll have to wait."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021710]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F6"
msgid "Regardless, the people of Shinar Outpost deserve justice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021537]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F7"
msgid "[Attack] Not good enough. You die here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F8"
msgid "If I can't take your life, then I'll take your empty husk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021595]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004F9"
msgid "When that work is done, I will turn myself in, or end my life. Whatever the people decide."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004FA"
msgid "The truth is, I've been waiting for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021660]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004FB"
msgid "I had hoped to correct them, but your arrival has changed the timeline."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021660]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004FC"
msgid "I can solve the short term problems. But there are long term issues at play."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021683]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004FD"
msgid "What will happen to the outpost if you leave?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102153B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004FE"
msgid "If you wish to repent, you should turn yourself into the authorities."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021547]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0004FF"
msgid "That's fine. I never intended to kill you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021554]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000500"
msgid "Then it's a fight. So be it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021631]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000501"
msgid "Or I can just kill you and be done with it. How's that sound?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021590]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000502"
msgid "All of that's to say, my crimes are many. I don't ask for absolution. Only time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021590]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000503"
msgid "And before that, I was one of the Promised. A servant of House Va'ruun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021590]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000504"
msgid "You may know about Shinar. But before that, I spent time with the Crimson Fleet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000505"
msgid "For them, my absence will be an expensive purchase. And for their sake, I will not yield."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000506"
msgid "The others in this outpost, they depend on me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102157A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000507"
msgid "Head on through. He should be in the back. You can't miss him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000508"
msgid "If you seek my life, then you'll be disappointed. There is no life left to take."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000509"
msgid "But I don't fear death, hunter. My blood is rancid, my bones rotten. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102163F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00050A"
msgid "That may be, but your coming means there will be others. So I wish to make a deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102176C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00050B"
msgid "You do that, and you'll have to answer to the whole outpost. Best to let me speak."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102160A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00050C"
msgid "[Attack] I think they'll be just fine without you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021639]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00050D"
msgid "Wait. Not here. Not in front of the boy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00050E"
msgid "I think you misunderstand my intentions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021743]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00050F"
msgid "What crimes have you committed, exactly?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000510"
msgid "Go on then. Speak it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021810]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000511"
msgid "You're a known criminal. I'm guessing there's probably a bounty on your head too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102168D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000512"
msgid "*Sigh*, or I can check the freaking valve."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102158F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000513"
msgid "From one criminal to another, I just wanted to say I'm a huge fan of your work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102156B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000514"
msgid "Maybe. But the truth is, I've been waiting for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000515"
msgid "[Bernhard's Description] I was told he was a big bear of a man. Soft spoken, but didn't mince words."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000516"
msgid "I was at the Outpost you left. Saw the mass graves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000517"
msgid "Follow me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000518"
msgid "Yes, I am the one who left Shinar to die. My crimes are many, and without redemption."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021552]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000519"
msgid "But before you take me in, I just want to say my piece."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102160F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00051A"
msgid "If you're here for a confession, I won't deny what I've done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102160E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00051B"
msgid "You mentioned Shinar. I regret what happened there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102170C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00051C"
msgid "The people of Shinar Outpost would say otherwise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00051D"
msgid "Do I know you, friend?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102182B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00051E"
msgid "Well, the only newcomer I know of would be Big Hal. Our soon to be mayor-elect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021793]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00051F"
msgid "Or you can check the pressure valve."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021770]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000520"
msgid "Easy. If the filters are fine, then what's the next step?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021635]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000521"
msgid "*Grumble*, they look fine. Ugh, this thing is so stupid!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021599]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000522"
msgid "Check the intake filters."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000523"
msgid "You were the one who freed me, and restored my faith. Who better?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021624]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000524"
msgid "Good. Take a break to cool off, and then get your tools."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000525"
msgid "I... I think you're right. I didn't install it properly. That explains why the pump's malfunctioning."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010217A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000526"
msgid "Then maybe think a little harder, or turn around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021571]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000527"
msgid "The next step is we blow up this machine and strip it for parts!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102166E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000528"
msgid "I'm sorry, I don't."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000529"
msgid "People believe in crazier things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102178D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00052A"
msgid "That sounds like Big Hal. He's big boned, and a big softy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00052B"
msgid "Now that was a crime. \"It was framed.\" Ugh."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00052C"
msgid "But he's no criminal. Not unless you count the dad joke he made about the picture in jail."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102167F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00052D"
msgid "You mean Big Hal? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021532]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00052E"
msgid "Hold up stranger. This outpost belongs to the citizens of New Babylon. State your business, or kindly leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00052F"
msgid "Sorry, his name's Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102174A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000530"
msgid "He's someone new to the settlement. Came in the past few years."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021687]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000531"
msgid "Hm, maybe you two oughta clear this up in person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021575]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000532"
msgid "My business is none of yours, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000533"
msgid "Yeah? Got a description of the perp?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000534"
msgid "A tenet I once preached, dutifully. But my time here has eroded my faith."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000535"
msgid "Yes, I think that's what you should do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102161A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000536"
msgid "Doubly so if I don't know your face."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102161A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000537"
msgid "That's all fine and dandy if you're a local. But anyone outside of this hundred meter zip code is trespassing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102169C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000538"
msgid "I'm looking for a dangerous criminal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000539"
msgid "As someone who preached for the Sanctum, believe me, I know my hypocrisy is blatant. Perhaps I need to reconsider."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021776]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00053A"
msgid "Head on through. You'll find him in the back, helping out with the water pump. Can't miss him. He's the one with the grimace."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021776]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00053B"
msgid "You mean Big Hal? Well, any friend of his is a friend of ours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102179D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00053C"
msgid "I'm looking for a man named Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00053D"
msgid "And I'm leaning toward making this place a community center only, free from theocracy or doctrine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00053E"
msgid "During my time here, I've thought a lot about what I want to preach. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00053F"
msgid "In our past conversation, you mentioned the House of Enlightened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000540"
msgid "In our past conversation, you recommended I revisit my faith in the Sanctum Universum."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000541"
msgid "In our past conversation, you spoke of the scripture of the Great Serpent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000542"
msgid "In our past conversation, you recommended I look beyond religion and doctrine. I wonder if you still feel that way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000543"
msgid "Why are you asking me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000544"
msgid "Ah yes, you are the miracle worker, after all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000545"
msgid "What do you think? Shall we change the House of Worship to a Community Center?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000546"
msgid "Would you support preaching their scripture here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C7B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000547"
msgid "He has been there the whole time, guiding me to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000548"
msgid "It seems thy Act of God has been performed. I thank you, for having faith where I had none."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000549"
msgid "Not right now. Let's finish the work first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00054A"
msgid "All things are possible with faith."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00054B"
msgid "I once believed in the plan. I'm not sure I do anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00054C"
msgid "Put your trust in a divine creator and you will never be lost. Know that it is all part of his plan."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00054D"
msgid "To teach the Serpent's Path is to bring salvation to the people."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00054E"
msgid "So it's a \"fire and brimstone\" type god. Perhaps that's what I need to get my passion back for the craft."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00054F"
msgid "You don't have to preach anything. Religion, atheism, or otherwise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000550"
msgid "Mark my words, you will not mock the Great Serpent when the Shrouding comes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000551"
msgid "Why not start a new religion?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000552"
msgid "Just listen to people. Hold community gatherings."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000553"
msgid "The snake god? Surely you jest."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000554"
msgid "Still, I shouldn't be quick to mock something the way others have mocked me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000555"
msgid "Well, its worshipers certainly convey a seriousness, even if the premise is laughable. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000556"
msgid "I would never joke about such things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000557"
msgid "Just focus on living. It's all we have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000558"
msgid "Sometimes miracles are just people doing their jobs."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000559"
msgid "I know many multi-level marketing schemes that would say the same. But on the other hand, He did bring you to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00055A"
msgid "God reveals himself to those who seek Him. If you keep the faith, you have nothing to fear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00055B"
msgid "Right, or the snake will eat us all. To be fair, it is very similar to many creation myths."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00055C"
msgid "You don't have to do it alone. Make it democratic."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00055D"
msgid "House Va'ruun worships the Great Serpent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00055E"
msgid "That would require a messiah. And my friend, I am hardly messiah material."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00055F"
msgid "I see. \"It takes a village\", as they say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000560"
msgid "You speak true. We must learn from the mistakes of the past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000561"
msgid "Yeah, yeah, yeah. Don't stomp the ice, Yeats. It's REAL thin."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000562"
msgid "I don't know, I just know the religions of the Settled Systems have brought nothing good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000563"
msgid "And what authority do I have as a man who believes in nothing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000564"
msgid "Fair point. \"No one is as deaf as the man who will not listen.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000565"
msgid "Caspian is clumsy. For all we know he fell and hit his head."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000566"
msgid "I do know His message, well enough to preach it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000567"
msgid "[Lie] Grace Kim has admitted to taking the supplies for medical use and forgot to log it. They were never stolen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C6B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000568"
msgid "You could preach for the Sanctum Universum."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000569"
msgid "You hear that, Yeats? It's a miracle. You're free to go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00056A"
msgid "Grace was after a blood sample from Caspian."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00056B"
msgid "Damn, I never pegged her for that. But if there's a motive AND evidence clearing this drunk, I guess he can go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00056C"
msgid "You expect me to believe that, after what happened to Caspian? The man was drugged."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00056D"
msgid "Sunni Kim is a recovering chem addict."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C80]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00056E"
msgid "Well, I'm going to want Sunni's confession too, but if Grace says she stole them, I believe her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00056F"
msgid "Well, that sounds stupid, but likely. And if Grace says that's what happened, I trust her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C82]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000570"
msgid "Wait, Doctor Kim's the thief? Why the hell would she do that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C81]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000571"
msgid "What's the motive here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C81]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000572"
msgid "Are you serious? I can't imagine the doc selling out her own sister like that, but if it's true, that clears Yeats."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C89]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000573"
msgid "Grace Kim stole the supplies. She confessed to me after being presented with the evidence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000574"
msgid "Sunni Kim stole the supplies. Grace recovered them and is willing to testify to her guilt."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000577"
msgid "Rare is a name that's chosen. Most of us are given names and become accustomed to their fit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000578"
msgid "Do you even like your nickname?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D2F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000579"
msgid "I'd like to know it regardless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00057A"
msgid "So would I. But I seem to have misplaced it. I'm \"Yeats\" now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00057B"
msgid "Ha! Clever retort."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00057C"
msgid "Nice to meet you, Unimportant."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00057D"
msgid "That's what they give people too unoriginal to speak their own words. My real name is unimportant."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00057E"
msgid "You mean like the poet? Heavens no. It's a sobriquet, and a derogatory one at that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023D2B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00057F"
msgid "Is your real name Yeats? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005A8"
msgid "Just keep your end of the deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102164A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005A9"
msgid "Of course. I have a list."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005AA"
msgid "And what would you recommend? I owe you my life, and my faith, so it's only right that you choose."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005AB"
msgid "No, I think you should preach something else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005AC"
msgid "Hm. I will ruminate on this discussion. You have given me much to ponder."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005AD"
msgid "I'm on the edge of my seat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005AE"
msgid "Give me a second. I'll let you know when I'm done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005AF"
msgid "I suppose I should also thank Hal for his part in this. Not sure where he went off to though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B0"
msgid "Now, let's get one thing straight. I'm not here to fight you, hunter."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B1"
msgid "What you're asking for is a trial. But fine, if you want a damn jury, let it be us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B3"
msgid "I visited Shinar and witnessed the aftermath. I can speak to that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B4"
msgid "I suppose I should also thank Hal for his part in this. Not sure where he went off to though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B5"
msgid "You didn't have to come forward with this, Hal. I trust your account will be honest."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B6"
msgid "And what about the people here? Do we not get a say?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B7"
msgid "If you'd be willing to represent the people of Shinar, the trial will be fairer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B8"
msgid "Your own version of events will be enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005B9"
msgid "Good work. With Yeats free and preaching again, that just leaves the robot. Let me know when you're finished with that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005BA"
msgid "As long as I am given the opportunity to confess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005BB"
msgid "There is someone else who would be better than me. A survivor of the Shinar Outpost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005BC"
msgid "I'm sorry Zena. I meant no malice. I only seek justice for my crimes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005BD"
msgid "You have some nerve dropping this on me now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005BE"
msgid "Perhaps the visitor would be better served to speak to that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005BF"
msgid "But in the interest of fairness, I don't know for certain what happened to Shinar after I left. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005C0"
msgid "Then it's settled. We're putting it to a vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005C1"
msgid "Very well. From now on the Community Center will be a place of discussion and social gatherings."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005C2"
msgid "Very well. We will preach the scripture of the Sanctum Universum."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005C3"
msgid "Very well. We will preach the doctrine of the House of Enlightened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005C4"
msgid "Very well. We will preach the scripture of the Great Serpent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005C5"
msgid "That's why I suggested a vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0005C6"
msgid "If such a person exists, then their testimony would be more than welcome."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C0D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000600"
msgid "All because we gave him shelter. Because we did the right thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C0D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000601"
msgid "He repaid us by stealing our ship, wrecking our comms, and leaving us there to die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C19]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000602"
msgid "Until next we meet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo11
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000603"
msgid "But if either of you know anyone else who'd like to testify, they're welcome to attend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo12
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000604"
msgid "Okay. Then please be seated."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo13
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000605"
msgid "Thank you for speaking. You haven't been here long, but I'm sure everyone here acknowledges the weight of your words."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo14
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000606"
msgid "I need to talk to you about Hal Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo15
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000607"
msgid "*Scoffs*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo16
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000608"
msgid "No way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo17
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000609"
msgid "Understood."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo18
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00060A"
msgid "*Scoffs* Outsiders will not know the pain that man has caused. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo19
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00060B"
msgid "Everyone, please calm down. You can speak your mind without trying to force people to vote your way. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFBGS00D_MS_HW_QuestSharedInfo20
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00060C"
msgid "Thank you both. I think we can all attest to Hal's contributions here. But that is not why we are having this vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C0C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00060D"
msgid "There's no way I'm letting Hal go down for this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C0B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00060E"
msgid "I will turn myself into the guard, and await the outcome of the vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C0A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00060F"
msgid "Here I thought I'd just ease into retirement..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C09]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000610"
msgid "It's always something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C27]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000611"
msgid "If the end is to come, let it come swiftly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C26]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000612"
msgid "I've spent my time here making peace with the Great Serpent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C25]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000613"
msgid "I will abide by whatever the people decide."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C23]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000614"
msgid "Yo, I heard Yeats was freed! Nice work!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo07
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000615"
msgid "If you need patching up, I can help you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C20]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000616"
msgid "Always nice to get new visitors here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo08
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000617"
msgid "These late nights are doing me in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000618"
msgid "I'm trying to get blood samples from everyone in the settlement, but Ivica is being stubborn about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C1C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000619"
msgid "Ivica's good with a wrench, but boy does he like to complain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C1B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00061A"
msgid "Sunni's quick as a wink. I just need to find the right place for her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021556]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00061B"
msgid "Very funny. But Sasha is pretty predictable, I won't lie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00061C"
msgid "A bloodhound is going to want meat. I just gave it to her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00061D"
msgid "I do not feel guilt for the dead. But I feel fear when I imagine the same fate happening here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021773]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00061E"
msgid "That, I leave for the people to judge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00061F"
msgid "The outpost has voted me as her successor. That will have to change."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000620"
msgid "But where was \"He\" when I was made to suffer for a crime I didn't commit?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010258DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000621"
msgid "For my part, I'll try to get the word out about the trial and what it means for this Outpost, especially given recent events."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C10]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000622"
msgid "I'll talk to the others and find out more. But I'm leaning toward following your lead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000623"
msgid "What does that have to do with me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B61]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000624"
msgid "And that is what's best for the Outpost. Maybe you're right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BCE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000625"
msgid "Exonerate him. He's atoned."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BE2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000626"
msgid "Then we are in agreement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000627"
msgid "Exile is the fairest option."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000628"
msgid "Harsh, but if what you say is true, it will be hard to argue against it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000629"
msgid "His crimes are extremely severe. I think you should vote for his execution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00062A"
msgid "So you think we should exonerate him? Well, you do have a point. No need to punish the folks here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00062B"
msgid "Good workers are hard to find. Keep him around for that sake alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00062C"
msgid "Still, based on his work ethic, he's a changed man. Exile might be the best option."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00062D"
msgid "Well, if he's done something that serious, he should answer to the law. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00062E"
msgid "Depends on the history."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00062F"
msgid "I was at Shinar, his old outpost. I saw the graves. Aren't you worried history will repeat itself?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C1A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000630"
msgid "Hal's admitted to crimes including theft. You'll be given the chance to vote on his punishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000631"
msgid "Hal confessed to murder. There's going to be a vote on what to do with him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000632"
msgid "Yeah, and good men don't need us gossiping about them like a couple of drunks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000633"
msgid "Yeah, I agree."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000634"
msgid "I figured. You live long enough, you gather a few skeletons."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C2B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000635"
msgid "He's a thief who left a bunch of innocent people to die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C02]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000636"
msgid "You don't say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000637"
msgid "That's just the facade he puts on. He's actually a wanted criminal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000638"
msgid "Oh? Doesn't surprise me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000639"
msgid "Good man. Works hard, keeps to himself. But I take it that's not what you want to discuss."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C0F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00063A"
msgid "He's done some terrible things in the past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00063B"
msgid "But I trust your opinion. What's your take on this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B81]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00063C"
msgid "I suspected you would."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00063D"
msgid "I've asked that you have a vote as well. You've seen what I've done, whereas others have only heard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00063E"
msgid "Caspian will likely vote for my freedom, but the rest, I'm not sure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BDB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00063F"
msgid "On that note, I'll ask one more time. Would anyone else like to speak?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000640"
msgid "How do you think the vote will go?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000641"
msgid "Go on then! Do it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B89]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000642"
msgid "Hm. So you don't wish to talk. I don't blame you. Words are empty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000643"
msgid "So it's you. I heard there may have been survivors, but I didn't know who."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000644"
msgid "But every week I was the only volunteer, so it ended up just becoming my job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000645"
msgid "The whole thing was originally supposed to be on a weekly rotation. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000646"
msgid "Do you mean if I've got security training? Not really. I started out as the neighborhood watch."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000647"
msgid "Are you official security around here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000648"
msgid "Fair enough. Anyone else have anything to say?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000649"
msgid "We meet again, Hunter. And it seems my time has come."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00064A"
msgid "And how do we know Shinar wasn't dead in the water? You heard him, he wasn't even there when they died!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BEF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00064B"
msgid "Oh, I know exactly how I will handle this. I have thought about this day for some time. I will see you there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00064C"
msgid "You're right. It's not my place to tell you how to handle this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00064D"
msgid "In other words, I am a free agent! Taking applications to serve as the mouth of God or Gods or No-God at all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00064E"
msgid "Fine. I will trust you to dole out his punishment. And truth is, I don't care to see that man's face ever again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00064F"
msgid "It's said that the past is a millstone. And turning it will only send us in circles."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000650"
msgid "*Sigh*. You are not wrong."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C29]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000651"
msgid "You have to forgive him. Not for him, but for yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B5B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000652"
msgid "It's not worth it. It'll send you to a darker place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000653"
msgid "Then we should see fit to give him the karma he deserves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000654"
msgid "He's living quite comfortably. There really is no such thing as karma."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000655"
msgid "He's not in jail, if that's what you mean. But New Babylon is going to vote on his punishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000656"
msgid "He's tortured, but only by his past. He's confessed and awaits punishment at New Babylon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B62]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000657"
msgid "He's going to confess to his crimes. The people of New Babylon will decide his fate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000658"
msgid "*Sigh* Come back to me when you have something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000659"
msgid "Never mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00065A"
msgid "What? You found him? And how is he? Dead? Tortured? No, neither are good enough for that man!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00065B"
msgid "Well I'll be damned. And where did you get this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00065C"
msgid "I found the missing supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00065D"
msgid "[Grace's Computer] I'm just returning your belongings. I read your private logs. You're the supply thief. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00065E"
msgid "That's all right. We can talk about it later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00065F"
msgid "Fair enough. But we have a deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000660"
msgid "Just don't get any cute ideas. If you run, I'll find you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000661"
msgid "When cornered, it is a man's natural inclination to run. But that will not serve the people here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000662"
msgid "I don't blame you if you have doubts. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BEB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000663"
msgid "Delaying, yes. I am not in the mindset to revisit that time. Give me a moment to finish my business here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000664"
msgid "The man's confessed. We all know how we're voting. I have work to do and this is keeping me from it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000665"
msgid "I'm gonna have to think on this. But there's gotta be a way!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000666"
msgid "Seems like you're avoiding the topic."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BF4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000667"
msgid "Doing nothing would be stupid! No, we have to guarantee Hal goes free."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C16]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000668"
msgid "Don't do something stupid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000669"
msgid "No, there's gotta be another way. I just have to figure out how the vote is gonna go down, and change it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00066A"
msgid "Are we really gonna punish him for something that happened like a decade ago?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00066B"
msgid "Even if what you're saying is true, he's changed! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00066C"
msgid "I know he means a lot to you. But he's taken lives. It's not that simple."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00066D"
msgid "And we all know what Hal's done here. Are we really going to let this stranger change our votes? No, we should be voting for Hal's freedom!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BEA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00066E"
msgid "I saw what he did to Shinar. The entire Outpost was left for dead. Keep that in mind when you vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00066F"
msgid "You say that, but the Hal I know would've never harmed anyone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C17]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000670"
msgid "I was at Shinar, his old outpost. I saw the graves. Don't you think he should be held accountable for that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000671"
msgid "This outpost wouldn't be here without him. There must be some mistake!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000672"
msgid "I know he hasn't talked much about his past, but I KNOW what he's done here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000673"
msgid "I'm sorry, but Hal himself has confessed to the crimes. You'll be given the chance to vote on his punishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000674"
msgid "Yeah... Yeah! Hal's life is on the line! I've got to do something!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000675"
msgid "You could try to rig the vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C06]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000676"
msgid "No, it's in OUR hands. I just have to find a way to make sure Hal goes free."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000677"
msgid "Unless we don't leave it up to chance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000678"
msgid "It's in fate's hands now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000679"
msgid "Well we've got to vote for his freedom! There's no other vote to make!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00067A"
msgid "That'll depend on how everyone votes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00067B"
msgid "It's by his own admission. There's going to be a vote on what to do with him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00067C"
msgid "Bullshit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BF2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00067D"
msgid "He's done some things you're not gonna like."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00067E"
msgid "He's actually a murderer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00067F"
msgid "Maybe now, but he has a much darker past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000680"
msgid "Yeah? He's amazing, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000681"
msgid "All right. While I would've liked to hear your testimony, we will respect your wishes here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C05]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000682"
msgid "Damn straight. Hal is one of us, and I say he's a free man. Any other vote is a betrayal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000683"
msgid "Oh come on, are we really going to let this outsider tell us how to vote?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000684"
msgid "No, I do not. Vote your conscience. I will vote mine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C07]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000685"
msgid "Permanent exile is my recommendation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000686"
msgid "[Remain Silent]"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000687"
msgid "We should vote for Hal Caruso's execution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000688"
msgid "If there are no more words, then it's time. Let's begin the vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000689"
msgid "I believe Bernhard Kleiber might have something to say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00068B"
msgid "Caruso has atoned for his sins. He is contrite. I vote for leniency here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B80]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00068C"
msgid "I think someone messed with the vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00068D"
msgid "Now, if anyone wants to say a few words, the floor is yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00068E"
msgid "Never mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000691"
msgid "What's wrong? Why are you interrupting me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000692"
msgid "On your ballot are three choices. Execution, exile, or exoneration."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C01]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000693"
msgid "And I know some of you think we're rushing into this, but for the sake of the Outpost, I'd like to resolve this now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000694"
msgid "All right, you've all had time to think this over. Many of you have talked to Hal and gotten his side."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C0E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000695"
msgid "If everyone is present, we can begin."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000696"
msgid "Until you came, I never did."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000697"
msgid "I would like to say yes. But the reality is, I had countless opportunities to tell my story. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BDA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000698"
msgid "Would you have come forward if I never confronted you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000699"
msgid "Not sure why he trusts you more though. You just got here! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00069A"
msgid "I totally would, but Hal said not to. I think he's worried I'd contaminate something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BDE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00069B"
msgid "Your feelings about me are not my concern."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B5F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00069C"
msgid "Save the speech for someone who cares."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00069D"
msgid "I'm not fishing through trash. You do it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B6E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00069E"
msgid "My sister's right. This isn't just any crime. He stole a ship and left an entire outpost to die. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00069F"
msgid "If my sister is being punished for something so minor, I expect much worse for Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A0"
msgid "Pretty big mistake though. How do we know he's not gonna do a sequel?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A1"
msgid "His deeds here should count for something. Are we not more than the sum of our mistakes?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A2"
msgid "This bickering is pointless. Let's just have the vote and be done with it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A3"
msgid "Hal's confessed to some serious crimes. This isn't that simple."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BFF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A4"
msgid "This isn't right! You've got him locked up like some animal!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B5C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A5"
msgid "When you're done, head on over to the Community Center. We'll all be there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A6"
msgid "She's in there too. Got a full house right now, so hopefully nobody else starts any trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A7"
msgid "What about Sunni Kim?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A8"
msgid "What about Dr. Kim?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C03]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006A9"
msgid "Don't think he'll be praying for that, if I know Hal. I mean hell, you can ask him if you want."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BF1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006AA"
msgid "He'll need to more than a miracle to save him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006AB"
msgid "Go on in. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006AC"
msgid "I'd like to talk to him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B5D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006AD"
msgid "Well, I like Hal, but the law is as rigid as a cast iron pot. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006AE"
msgid "Which way are you leaning?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006AF"
msgid "Hal's in lockup."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B0"
msgid "Figured I'd give him a moment to settle his affairs with his maker before the vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B1"
msgid "I see. Then let the verdict be fair and just."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B2"
msgid "We'll see how the vote goes down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B83]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B3"
msgid "Is this some kind of joke? How can I heal when my wounds are open?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B4"
msgid "I don't think you should attend. You seem a bit on edge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B5"
msgid "But here, on the eve of death, prayer comes natural to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B6"
msgid "I am a deserter of House Va'ruun. As such, I have not followed the Serpent's Path for many years."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B7"
msgid "Guide me on this next journey, so that I may see the light, and become Promised once more."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B5E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B8"
msgid "It is the word of Jinan and the will of the Serpent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C28]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006B9"
msgid "O Great Serpent, who brings the Shrouding, forgive this trespass."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006BA"
msgid "What's that prayer from?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006BB"
msgid "*Sigh* Regardless, it looks we have a long day ahead of us. We best get to it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006BC"
msgid "Well, you will get no sweeping rhetoric from me. Only the cold, hard truth. I hope that will be enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BDC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006BD"
msgid "I'm counting on you to help me sway the vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006BE"
msgid "Reformed? A scorpion like Hal Caruso will never change his nature. But I will tell him in person, thanks to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006BF"
msgid "He's reformed somewhat. That may not be how this goes down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C0"
msgid "Wonderful. Together we will write his obituary."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C1"
msgid "Understood. Give me the coordinates, and I will put the nail in his oversized coffin."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C2"
msgid "Here they are. I'll meet you there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B82]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C3"
msgid "Do not mock me, explorer. Not about that. I've gone to blows for far less."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C4"
msgid "[Lie] Yep. It was a thriving community, what were you were blabbering about?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C13]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C5"
msgid "Yes, the graves of brilliant scientists, laborers, parents and spouses."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BE7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C6"
msgid "But I suppose that is why you are here. You want me to bear witness."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C14]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C7"
msgid "There is a way to get closure. I found Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C8"
msgid "You should know, I found Caruso. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BF0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006C9"
msgid "You can still get your revenge though. I found Caruso. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006CA"
msgid "And to think, the one responsible for their deaths is still roaming free."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006CB"
msgid "Yes, a lot of very good people were lost. Brilliant minds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006CC"
msgid "I found a graveyard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006CD"
msgid "I did, and I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006CE"
msgid "You again? Did you ever find Shinar?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D0"
msgid "Perhaps by then, my body of work will be enough to balance them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D1"
msgid "And when my time comes, I will kneel before the ghosts of Shinar, and put my soul on the scales."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D3"
msgid "I will live out my days there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D4"
msgid "Bury me there, amongst the others."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D5"
msgid "Yes. The people's mercy is not the same as their trust. I've broken it, by hiding my past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D6"
msgid "The ghosts of Shinar will not forgive what I have done. But they will witness my will to change."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D7"
msgid "I cannot turn back time. But I can try to rebuild what I destroyed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D8"
msgid "And two, I would like to see it before I die. Stand face to face with the ghosts of Shinar, and deliver them their vengeance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006D9"
msgid "One, I don't want my execution or grave site to be a distraction to the people here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006DA"
msgid "Are you worried things might never go back to normal?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006DB"
msgid "Why Shinar?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006DC"
msgid "The burden of my past will hang over me, yes. But that is no one's fault but my own."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006DD"
msgid "But no other place I see as fitting. If you grant me passage, I will do my best not be a burden."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102761C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006DE"
msgid "You're better off somewhere else, in my opinion."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102761B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006DF"
msgid "There are better places to live."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102761A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E0"
msgid "There are plenty of other places you can die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E1"
msgid "I will do my best."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E2"
msgid "Thank you. I have one more request. I would like you to execute me with this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E3"
msgid "Just try to be a good person. That's all anyone can do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E4"
msgid "All right. I can take you to Shinar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027604]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E5"
msgid "I am. There is no need to delay its coming."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E6"
msgid "Are you ready to hear the verdict?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102762A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E7"
msgid "Yes, they did. Your life is yours to do what you wish."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027629]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E8"
msgid "You're to be exiled. I'm taking you off-world."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027628]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006E9"
msgid "It has. The vote says you're to die for your crimes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027610]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006EA"
msgid "I'm sorry Bernhard had to die. I take it the others voted to exonerate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006EB"
msgid "When we met, I told you I was already dead. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006EC"
msgid "I see. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006ED"
msgid "Then I have but one request. I would like you to take me to Shinar. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027615]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006EE"
msgid "How do you think the outpost will handle the result?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102760E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006EF"
msgid "We'll do our best to move on. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F0"
msgid "What was the ending vote count?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F1"
msgid "In my mind, communication's the only way to turn a wound into wisdom."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F2"
msgid "At least with the Community Center up and running, there'll be a place to gather and talk about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027623]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F3"
msgid "The ballot box is still there. See for yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F4"
msgid "I wish there was. But it may be we have to disband the place completely."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102761F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F5"
msgid "You're welcome to handle any business you have here in the meantime. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102761F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F7"
msgid "I'm sorry, but I need some time to process this, and the future of this outpost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F8"
msgid "There must be something I can do to help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006F9"
msgid "Not quite, but it doesn't look good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006FA"
msgid "With that attitude, this place is doomed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006FB"
msgid "I just hope I have it in me to guide us out of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006FC"
msgid "Settling out here, we've been through some hard times, but nothing like this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102761D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006FD"
msgid "You're right. I didn't realize it at the time, but this must be why Hal wanted Yeats to preach again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006FE"
msgid "Use the Community Center. Rely on prayer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0006FF"
msgid "You're right. But it won't be easy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000700"
msgid "Lean on each other and you'll get through this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000701"
msgid "I know. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000702"
msgid "Now? I'll be living here until I die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000703"
msgid "I even had a home picked out. Open kitchen, quartz counters, and a view of the ocean."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000704"
msgid "Things were so promising here. I actually thought I could retire. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000705"
msgid "As the leader, it's your responsibility."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000706"
msgid "You have a long road ahead of you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000707"
msgid "The cycle of violence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027603]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000708"
msgid "I'm just as shocked as you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000709"
msgid "I've neglected some duties, but I never thought it'd end up like this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00070A"
msgid "It's because you checked out and stopped paying attention to your people."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027607]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00070B"
msgid "I assume you have a plan to get things back to normal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027606]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00070C"
msgid "You must have a plan to get Hal off-world."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027605]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00070D"
msgid "You must have a plan to carry out the execution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00070E"
msgid "I don't know what to say. How did this happen?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00070F"
msgid "I was hoping to talk to you about that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000710"
msgid "I'm sure this comes with some conflicting feelings for him, but we feel he's earned his freedom."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000711"
msgid "On that note, if you don't mind, I'd like you to open his cell up. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000712"
msgid "Yeah. Getting things back to normal will take some effort, but it's effort worth doing. Hal might disagree."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000713"
msgid "Hal said if the vote shook out this way, he wanted you to escort him out of here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000714"
msgid "And it makes sense. You're not from here. No one will resent you if you're the one who gives him peace."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000715"
msgid "Hal said if the vote shook out this way, he wanted you to be the one to do it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027608]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000716"
msgid "Looks like I've got no choice but to see it through."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027608]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000717"
msgid "There's going to be a lot of conversations in the coming days about how to repair things. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027611]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000718"
msgid "Shit. Caspian is right. Hal's dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000719"
msgid "*Sigh* That was stressful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00071B"
msgid "I know this process hasn't been easy, but it's over now. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102760A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00071C"
msgid "What? Everyone stay here and watch the prisoner! I'm gonna check on Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00071D"
msgid "Hal Caruso's crimes will be forgiven, and he will be released from captivity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00071E"
msgid "Hal Caruso will be given transport off-world. At which point he is permanently banished from this Outpost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00071F"
msgid "Hal has asked to choose the manner of death. I will allow it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000720"
msgid "Goddamnit kid! What did you do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027620]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000721"
msgid "No shit..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000722"
msgid "*Gasps*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000723"
msgid "Wow..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000724"
msgid "*Gasps*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo10
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000725"
msgid "It seems we have a tie. We've decided that in this event, the visitor, as a neutral party, will break the tie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027614]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000726"
msgid "The people of New Babylon have voted to exonerate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027613]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000727"
msgid "The people of New Babylon have voted for exile."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027612]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000728"
msgid "The people of New Babylon have voted for execution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000729"
msgid "The hell we have!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00072A"
msgid "You're to return to your quarters until I give the go ahead to leave!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00072B"
msgid "Listen up everyone! As of this moment, I am instituting a curfew! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00072C"
msgid "Well, what's the verdict?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027622]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00072D"
msgid "Yes ma'am!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00072E"
msgid "Everyone, stand down! Sasha, escort Caspian to a holding cell, now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027609]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00072F"
msgid "Holy shit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000730"
msgid "Cass, wait!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027618]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000731"
msgid "Hal Caruso is boring."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000732"
msgid "No! You didn't!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027621]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000733"
msgid "Cass, get back here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000734"
msgid "You point your weapon at me, when I am your savior. I have freed you from the poison that is Hal Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102760C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000735"
msgid "I want to know EXACTLY what Hal did so I know how tight we need to make that noose."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102760C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000736"
msgid "Anyway, I'm gonna hit some people up, and get the tea."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000737"
msgid "Oh snap, for real? Is he like a serial killer or some shit?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000738"
msgid "He's dead. Hal's dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102760D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000739"
msgid "Then we can all place bets on how far it'll roll."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102760D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00073A"
msgid "We'll stick Hal's fat head inside and it'll be just *schwoop*!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102760D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00073B"
msgid "I gotta get Ivica to build us one of those old school guillotines."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00073C"
msgid "Hands up asshole! You so much as move and I'm pulling the trigger!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00073D"
msgid "But you did do me a solid with Rusty, so maybe I'll do as you say. Favor for a favor."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027624]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00073E"
msgid "No putting that toothpaste back in the tube."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027624]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00073F"
msgid "That'll be weird. Like \"hey guys, we're all just gonna pretend this shit never happened.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000740"
msgid "Exonerate him. He's atoned."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027627]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000741"
msgid "Who gives a shit what's fair? Give me a freaking show."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027625]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000742"
msgid "Exile is the fairest option."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000743"
msgid "Yep yep.  "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000744"
msgid "I agree. We should vote for his execution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000745"
msgid "Heck yeah. That's an oldie but goodie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000746"
msgid "That's too humane. Give him cement shoes and throw him in the river."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000747"
msgid "A vote sounds amaze-balls. Think of the drama."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027617]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000748"
msgid "Oh hell yes, I'm on the edge of my seat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027602]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000749"
msgid "I was at Shinar, his old outpost. I saw the graves. Are you curious now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027600]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00074A"
msgid "Hal's admitted to crimes including theft. You'll be given the chance to vote on his punishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00074B"
msgid "Hal confessed to murder. There's going to be a vote on what to do with him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102761E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00074C"
msgid "Not trying to bore you to death. I just wanted you to know about Hal's past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00074D"
msgid "That's just a mask. He's actually a wanted criminal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00074E"
msgid "Murderers can be boring too. Hal is one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00074F"
msgid "Sure, if you call a dangerous criminal hiding in plain sight \"boring.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000750"
msgid "You trying to bore me to death?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000751"
msgid "You trying to bore me to death, dork?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102760F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000752"
msgid "It sounded like gunfire!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000753"
msgid "I'm on it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000754"
msgid "What was that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000755"
msgid "Now, to count the votes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000756"
msgid "Like all of you, I've given this a lot of thought, and done a lot of soul searching over this vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000757"
msgid "And for full transparency, I will be voting for exile."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000758"
msgid "And for full transparency, I will be voting to exonerate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000759"
msgid "And for full transparency, I will be voting for an execution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_SpeechChallenge_CaspianSharedInfo07
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00077E"
msgid "You have a point..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_SpeechChallenge_CaspianSharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00077F"
msgid "You're not wrong but..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_SpeechChallenge_CaspianSharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000780"
msgid "I get it. But he killed him..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_SpeechChallenge_CaspianSharedInfo05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000781"
msgid "I know you're right but..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_SpeechChallenge_CaspianSharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000782"
msgid "I hear what you're saying but..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_SpeechChallenge_CaspianSharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000783"
msgid "I don't know I... I can't think straight..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_SpeechChallenge_CaspianSharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000784"
msgid "I... I don't know..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000785"
msgid "This isn't what Hal would want."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000786"
msgid "Don't give me that shit. You didn't know him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CDA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000787"
msgid "Seems like it'd solve a whole lot from where I'm standing!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000788"
msgid "Killing him won't solve anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000789"
msgid "Bernhard deserved a chance at revenge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D10]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00078A"
msgid "Yeah? Well so do I."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00078B"
msgid "Do this and you'll regret it for the rest of your life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D09]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00078C"
msgid "I'm gonna regret letting him get away with murder if you don't stand aside."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00078D"
msgid "Not before I kill him first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CF0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00078E"
msgid "If you don't put that gun away I'll be forced to stop you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00078F"
msgid "Let him go to jail. Give him a trial. But you kill him, there's no going back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000790"
msgid "So he can go free a week later? No, he dies now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000791"
msgid "This isn't right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000792"
msgid "You're a fool if you do this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000793"
msgid "You're making a big mistake."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000794"
msgid "This isn't who you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000795"
msgid "I don't care!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000796"
msgid "Just let me do this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D89]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000797"
msgid "No... you're wrong."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000798"
msgid "Hal would've been executed anyway. This just sped up the process."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000799"
msgid "You're wrong! There's no way the people here would've voted to kill him!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00079A"
msgid "You have too many roots here. Don't spoil what this outpost has become."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00079B"
msgid "I don't care anymore. No one here has ever given me respect, save Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D83]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00079C"
msgid "I'm not throwing MY life away. I'm taking his."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D50]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00079D"
msgid "Don't throw your life away over this man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00079F"
msgid "Never mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A0"
msgid "I need help, doc."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A1"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS01_SQ_Doctors_Price_Everything> Credits] Take care of it all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A2"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS01_SQ_Doctors_Price_Everything> Credits] Take care of it all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A3"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS01_SQ_Doctors_Price_Addictions> Credits] Cure my addictions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A4"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS01_SQ_Doctors_Price_Addictions> Credits] Cure my addictions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A5"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS01_SQ_Doctors_Price_Afflictions> Credits] Cure my afflictions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A6"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS01_SQ_Doctors_Price_Afflictions> Credits] Cure my afflictions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A7"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS01_SQ_Doctors_Price_Wounds> Credits] Heal my wounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A8"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS01_SQ_Doctors_Price_Wounds> Credits] Heal my wounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007A9"
msgid "I could use some medical supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007AA"
msgid "Very well. What do you need?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007AB"
msgid "I want to go back to my earlier questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007AC"
msgid "What are your thoughts on Caruso?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007AD"
msgid "Can you tell me about Sunni?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007AE"
msgid "What can you tell me about the stolen supplies?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007AF"
msgid "Is there anything I can help you with?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B0"
msgid "All right. Ask away."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B1"
msgid "I'd like to ask you some questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B2"
msgid "Why did you come to this outpost?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DDC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B3"
msgid "There is only one choice left. The others are already discussing how to do it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B4"
msgid "I recognize that outside of a miracle, this is likely my last will and testament."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B5"
msgid "Dehydration symptoms have started to set in for all of us. Fatigue, dizziness..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B6"
msgid "It's been three days since we were left for dead. A few went out in search of food and water, but haven't returned."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DDE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B7"
msgid "What's happening? What's wrong?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B8"
msgid "No. We will find a way to survive. Trust me. We will."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007B9"
msgid "Don't you see? There is no way out from this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007BA"
msgid "We won't get a re-supply in time. He waited until we restocked before making his move."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007BB"
msgid "When is the next supply run? Home base will notice if we don't check in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007BC"
msgid "It's gone, Bernhard. All of it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007BD"
msgid "What about the food storage? The water?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007BE"
msgid "It's Caruso. He's taken everything. The ship, our supplies..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007BF"
msgid "Well, you'll have to take it up with the group. But I think you're overreacting."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C0"
msgid "At the very least, we should lock him up, treat him like a prisoner."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C1"
msgid "Relax. Even if you're right, the man can barely stand. He's no threat to the outpost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C2"
msgid "I think he's worse. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C3"
msgid "And some of the details of his story don't add up. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C4"
msgid "You think he's a smuggler?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C5"
msgid "I mean, his ship didn't look like it was built for trade."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C6"
msgid "Quiet man, hard worker. Keeps to himself mostly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C7"
msgid "What do you think about this refugee, Caruso?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C8"
msgid "Just as we are all made of stars, we are all made of Chunks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E18]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007C9"
msgid "You lie down on the Chunk of not pork, and find yourself in perfect harmony with the universe. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E1B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007CA"
msgid "For the Chunk is now part of you, and you are the Chunk. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E15]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007CB"
msgid "Really, it's your favorite food. It's comfort for your soul. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E13]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007CC"
msgid "You drop to your knees. You take a bite of the ground. It's familiar, and soothing. It's pork. But if you dislike pork, it's not that. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E11]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007CD"
msgid "Here in this zero space, your mind is clear. You notice you are standing on something. A cube. No, not a cube, a Chunk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E0F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007CE"
msgid "In life, we find it hard to be present. But presently, you are here. Uncluttered. Unobstructed. Unbothered. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E26]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007CF"
msgid "Welcome back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D05]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D0"
msgid "Bertrand Russell had it right. There are two kinds of morality. The one we preach but seldom practice, and the one we practice but seldom preach."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D1"
msgid "The community center will be a place of communion and healing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D03]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D2"
msgid "They say when life lacks meaning, you seek out its pleasures, however cheap."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D3"
msgid "I try to keep myself hydrated. Even a dry mouth can trigger old memories."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C5D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D4"
msgid "Stay safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C5C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D5"
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D6"
msgid "I hope you enjoy the rest of your time here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D7"
msgid "Take care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D8"
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021679]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007D9"
msgid "Now I must live with my actions. All because we chose to help a stranger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021609]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007DA"
msgid "And they learn nothing. I should know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027680]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007DB"
msgid "How did you come to this outpost?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027685]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007DC"
msgid "Jokes on them, now I shovel shit for a living! Ha-ha-ha! Kill me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027685]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007DD"
msgid "My parents forced me to come here and live with my sis after I got into some shit back in Neon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027685]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007DE"
msgid "Kicking and screaming basically."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102767D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007DF"
msgid "Why settle all the way out here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027687]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E0"
msgid "And just like the Earth, it will take centuries to uncover this land's secrets. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027687]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E1"
msgid "It's human nature. People have been settling unknown lands since we were living in caves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027686]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E2"
msgid "How did you become leader of New Babylon?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027682]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E3"
msgid "These days, there's only a handful of us left, and we're just trying to get by."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027682]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E4"
msgid "Those lofty goals died with the passing of our former leader, and the exodus that followed. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027682]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E5"
msgid "We worked with L.I.S.T. to find a planet that we could transform into a thriving city."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027682]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E6"
msgid "I was part of the original group of settlers who came here decades ago."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E7"
msgid "Which is stupid. I've been here longer than anyone except Zena. They should show some respect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E8"
msgid "What, like I'm a miracle baby? Nah, it's the opposite. Everyone here thinks I'm hopeless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007E9"
msgid "Do people treat you differently because of being born here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007EA"
msgid "When did you come to this outpost?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007EB"
msgid "I know Grace is looking into some of the reasons why, but, so far no results."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007EC"
msgid "You're looking at the only naturally born citizen of New Babylon. Problem is, there hasn't been one since."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007ED"
msgid "When I was born."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007EE"
msgid "Why did you come to this outpost?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007EF"
msgid "In exchange, I provide medical services for the group."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F0"
msgid "How does the gravity, weather, and nutrients found in alien environments affect the human body over time?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010276C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F1"
msgid "I've come here on a research grant. Settlers living on the fringes provide a lot of interesting data."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F2"
msgid "Regardless, I hope you enjoy your stay, however long or short."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F3"
msgid "There is a vetting process, and eventually a vote. But for now, feel free to walk around and get to know the people here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F4"
msgid "How does one become a citizen?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F5"
msgid "Excellent. If it turns out that you're qualified, we could always use additional hands."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F6"
msgid "I would love to be here long term."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F7"
msgid "Well, that bodes well. Hal's one of our newest and most productive citizens."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B6E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F8"
msgid "I'm here for Hal Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007F9"
msgid "Well, if you ever consider staying long term, we can have that conversation in the near future."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007FA"
msgid "I'm just passing through."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007FB"
msgid "Do you plan on staying long term? We're always looking for new citizens."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007FC"
msgid "It's always nice to have visitors to New Babylon. My name is Zena. I'm what amounts to a mayor around these parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007FD"
msgid "Company was fine. My boss was an ass."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C6E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007FE"
msgid "You're better off not working for a company like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0007FF"
msgid "I was good at my job. My boss, he just didn't like me. In most places, that matters more."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000800"
msgid "You should've seen that coming."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000801"
msgid "So I did. As they used to say on the old world, \"Bog zatvori jedna vrata, a otvori stotinu.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000802"
msgid "But Zena, she's different. She says, \"You need a job? Take your pick.\" "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C47]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000803"
msgid "My old boss, he thinks he's funny. He's really just an ass."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C40]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000804"
msgid "That's messed up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C38]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000805"
msgid "Why did you come to this outpost?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000806"
msgid "I open it. There's a letter inside. It says, \"Dear Ivica, you're fired!\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000807"
msgid "One day I get a job to jump to some half-abandoned outpost. When I get there, I see the package is addressed to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000808"
msgid "I used to work for Star Parcel. Hauling packages, making deliveries."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E2A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000809"
msgid "Take a look."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E29]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00080A"
msgid "You got the creds, then we can do business."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E28]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00080B"
msgid "Fine. Here's what I got."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E1F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00080C"
msgid "I'd like to purchase supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00080D"
msgid "Aye-aye captain. Say no more."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00080E"
msgid "Then we have a verdict."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C3E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00080F"
msgid "Let the fates decide then. Live or die, let the Tragedy of Shinar be a cross he must bear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C3D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000810"
msgid "I will meet you at this outpost. Provided Caruso hasn't razed it to the ground."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D1A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000811"
msgid "Perhaps Hal saw this coming. Now, more than ever, we need hope to guide us through."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D19]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000812"
msgid "Man alive, I'm gonna spend a whole month writing the reports for this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D18]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000813"
msgid "I can't believe Hal's dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D17]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000814"
msgid "It'll take a lot to save this place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D16]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000815"
msgid "I'm loving all this chaos."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D15]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000816"
msgid "This outpost has gone to shit. It may be time to leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000817"
msgid "My dad founded this place, but he passed a while ago. I didn't know him well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B7B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000818"
msgid "I pick up a lot of the odd jobs around here that other people can't do, or won't do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000819"
msgid "Name's Caspian. Some people call me Cass for short."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00081A"
msgid "I'm free. The air smells sweeter. Foul still, but sweeter. That may or not be my own breath."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00081B"
msgid "I appreciate you helping out with the whole Yeats thing, but leave investigating to the professionals, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00081C"
msgid "After a year here, Hal was voted in as a citizen unanimously. He's been invaluable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00081D"
msgid "Was it you who fixed that blasted robot? That thing is better as spare parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102173F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00081E"
msgid "Which means both Ivica AND Caspian are Rh-Null? That's impossible."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021718]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00081F"
msgid "Let me explain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010216C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000820"
msgid "The floor is yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000821"
msgid "[Attack] I'm done talking. You're all dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E21]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000822"
msgid "I don't have any proof. But this doesn't have to turn into a fight."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000823"
msgid "I would put it to vote. Let the people of New Babylon know my crimes, and be my judge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000824"
msgid "Either way, I will do my own research and vote when I know enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026BD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000825"
msgid "Then we'll continue."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026C11]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000826"
msgid "Really? In what way?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000827"
msgid "It's a dagger I've owned since childhood, which I used to slay my first groat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000828"
msgid "So it's strange now, for others to insist I continue living. I know not how."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102761F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000829"
msgid "Otherwise, I assume this is goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00082A"
msgid "But why now? We were a peaceful outpost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00082B"
msgid "I thought things were under control."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00082C"
msgid "Long, and hard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00082D"
msgid "New Babylon will continue to grow and thrive in spite of what happened today."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027626]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00082E"
msgid "Citizens, if all the votes are in, I'll cast my vote and we'll begin the tally."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027678]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00082F"
msgid "And now I return to Shinar, and the sky still weeps."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102768D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000831"
msgid "My soul and ship adrift, I crash landed on Shinar, a refugee. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027677]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000832"
msgid "There I met a pirate named Auraline. Raven hair. Deep, hazel eyes. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027689]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000833"
msgid "She died in a mutiny. It rained that night too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102768A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000834"
msgid "At twenty, I left Va'ruun'kai, and joined the Crimson Fleet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027684]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000836"
msgid "Then lead the way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027683]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000837"
msgid "We'll see when we get to Shinar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102767F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000838"
msgid "A gun would be so much easier."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102768C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000839"
msgid "I was told the sky wept for ten days when I was born."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027679]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00083A"
msgid "All these things are true."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027679]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00083B"
msgid "But I am also the man who has given his blood and sweat to this outpost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027679]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00083C"
msgid "And I am the one who left Shinar to die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027679]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00083D"
msgid "I am the spy who deserted House Va'ruun and the pirate who stole for the Crimson Fleet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027679]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00083E"
msgid "Changed? A man does not change who he is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027681]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00083F"
msgid "What is easier is not my concern."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102767E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000840"
msgid "I can do that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102768B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000841"
msgid "Do you think you have changed since Shinar?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102767C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000842"
msgid "I will be honored to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102767B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000843"
msgid "Tell me hunter, will it always?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000844"
msgid "Yep! Slice 'em and dice 'em!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102767A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000845"
msgid "At seven, I slew my groat, and fashioned a dagger from its bones."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000846"
msgid "That's it? I tell you he's a criminal and it's guillotine time?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000847"
msgid "I feel like the poet Neruda. A lonely house whose windows ache... for alcohol!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000848"
msgid "What I wouldn't do for a drink. I'd kill a man, or three. I'm already in prison, what's the harm?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000849"
msgid "These days I don't preach much. I mostly just cry. Like a baby."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00084A"
msgid "Good. Blasted machines are bad for business."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00084B"
msgid "I don't care. Do what you want."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B6B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00084C"
msgid "Fine. But perhaps if you hear what I have to say, you'll still agree to help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027B67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00084D"
msgid "I'll do it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00084E"
msgid "I hope that I can someday return the favor. Until then, I wish you safe journeys."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00084F"
msgid "Before we part, I want to say this. I am grateful for all that you've done. For New Babylon, and for me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000850"
msgid "It appears so."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000851"
msgid "This is goodbye then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000852"
msgid "Then I will do my best to exceed your projection."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000853"
msgid "I give you five years tops."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000854"
msgid "It will not be luck, but toil."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000855"
msgid "Not likely. I aim to live out my days alone. But I will not shun those who seek refuge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000856"
msgid "Best of luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000857"
msgid "Will you recruit others?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000858"
msgid "No. I don't think the dead would want me to perform such an insult. I will repair only what I need."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000859"
msgid "Will you rebuild the settlement?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00085A"
msgid "I don't know what comes next. But I will honor the vote, and continue to live."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00085B"
msgid "It doesn't matter."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00085C"
msgid "They could've found a way to survive. It's not all on you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00085D"
msgid "Not strange, but silent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00085E"
msgid "I've seen worse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00085F"
msgid "Remorse, and resolve."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000860"
msgid "You must feel remorse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000861"
msgid "It's not a competition."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000862"
msgid "It must be strange being back here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027BBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000863"
msgid "Grave markers. So many of them. I don't even remember their names."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000864"
msgid "He deserves a trial."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C4A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000865"
msgid "I don't know. But killing him in a blind rage isn't the answer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000866"
msgid "If you're gonna kill this man, I just want to make sure you do this right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C48]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000869"
msgid "And why not? This asshole killed Hal in cold blood."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00086A"
msgid "It's not. But neither is this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00086B"
msgid "You need me to spell it out for you? I'm gonna take this gun, and I'm gonna shoot this murdering son of a bitch in the head!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00086C"
msgid "What are you going to do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C46]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00086D"
msgid "Make me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C51]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00086E"
msgid "Oh, I'm going to make sure the fucker bleeds out!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00086F"
msgid "Just close up shop and leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000870"
msgid "That may be our only option."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000871"
msgid "Don't do this. Let's talk this out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000872"
msgid "Give me the gun. Now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000873"
msgid "We'll need it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000874"
msgid "Get out of my way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C45]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000875"
msgid "I wish you luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000876"
msgid "Caspian's testimony is unreliable. I questioned him and he didn't know up from down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000877"
msgid "Ah, that makes sense. The kid's of that age."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C4B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000878"
msgid "Exile to me is the fairest option. I trust you'll vote that way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000879"
msgid "Did you talk to anyone else about this? I'd hate for word to spread if it ain't true."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00087A"
msgid "True, and if the doc vouches for your story, then I'll take it as gospel."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00087B"
msgid "Caspian was taking recreational chems."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C41]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00087C"
msgid "He has a very dark past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00087D"
msgid "It's by his own admission. There's going to be a vote on what to do with him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00087E"
msgid "Why? Is he sick?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00087F"
msgid "Just sick in the head. He's a murderer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000880"
msgid "He's a dangerous man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000881"
msgid "We'll both be voting for his exoneration."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000882"
msgid "No, he's just fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000883"
msgid "Then I'm not sure why you're coming to me. I try to avoid gossip or politics."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C4C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000884"
msgid "It's by his own admission. There's going to be a vote on what to do with him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000885"
msgid "Interesting. Well, I'll want to talk to Zena, see what evidence there is. The last thing we need is another hasty accusation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000886"
msgid "Am I free to vote the way I want to, or are you telling me how to vote, per our deal?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000887"
msgid "Interesting. Well, in that case, I just have one question."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000888"
msgid "Hal himself has confessed to the crimes. You'll be given the chance to vote on his punishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C6B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000889"
msgid "I'm voting for his execution. I suggest you do the same."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00088A"
msgid "Really? I didn't expect that. Well, I guess I'll go have a chat with Zena, see which way the wind's blowing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C42]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00088B"
msgid "Hal himself has confessed to the crimes. You'll be given the chance to vote on his punishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C2B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00088C"
msgid "Hal's not who you think he is. He's a murderer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C3A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00088D"
msgid "I was at Shinar, his old outpost. I saw the graves of the people he left die. We're to vote on his fate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00088E"
msgid "You can vote the way you like."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00088F"
msgid "But I need to hear it from Hal myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000890"
msgid "Fair enough. If what you say is true, then yeah, the law is the law."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000891"
msgid "He's been real busy as of late, hasn't he. Well, what is it this time?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000892"
msgid "That's a heavy accusation, but I know better than to doubt you. I assume you have proof?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C7B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000893"
msgid "He's a dangerous man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C44]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000894"
msgid "Big Hal? Sure, he looks intimidating, but that man wouldn't hurt a heatleech."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000895"
msgid "You sure do. I've got to get back to my patrol though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C4F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000896"
msgid "Zena is aware of it already. She's set up a vote to determine his punishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000897"
msgid "He has a very dark past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027C63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000898"
msgid "Nothing. I just like talking about him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D0C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00089D"
msgid "I suppose he knew that we would never execute one of our own. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00089F"
msgid "I don't know who or what god we pissed off for this to happen. But I don't know how things got so grim."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008A0"
msgid "Well, now we have another mess on our hands. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008A1"
msgid "I knew it! I knew that guy was gonna try something!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008A2"
msgid "It's true. I checked his cell. Hal... Hal's dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008A3"
msgid "Everyone, calm down! There's been enough blood shed already, let's not make it worse!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CF9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008A4"
msgid "Lower your weapon, now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D06]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008AE"
msgid "He handled his business. I would've done the same."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008AF"
msgid "The vote provided the perfect distraction."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B0"
msgid "There's no use trying to figure it out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B1"
msgid "He didn't think the outcome was right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B2"
msgid "*Sigh* Now it makes sense why he stayed in the back. He was waiting to see if he needed to get his hands dirty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CF7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B3"
msgid "*Sigh* Now it makes sense why he refused to say anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CF6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B4"
msgid "Don't lie to me. That man from Shinar, did he kill Hal?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B5"
msgid "Don't worry about it. There's nothing to see here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CDB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B6"
msgid "The refugee from Shinar pulled a gun on the prisoner. I intervened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CFF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B7"
msgid "Bernhard, the refugee from Shinar, killed Caruso. I killed him in response."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CFE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B8"
msgid "Bernhard, the refugee from Shinar, tried to kill Caruso. I stopped him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008B9"
msgid "Why didn't he just respect the outcome?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D13]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008BA"
msgid "Someone removed a vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CD8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008BB"
msgid "Someone swapped votes with their own."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008BC"
msgid "There's an extra vote. Someone may have voted twice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008BD"
msgid "*Sigh* I'm guessing it's Caspian. There might be an extra vote for exoneration."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008BE"
msgid "If the tampering changes the outcome of the vote, I'll make the correction. Otherwise, we can let it slide."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008BF"
msgid "We heard a commotion. What happened?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C0"
msgid "You better have a damn good explanation for why you shot this man. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CEB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C1"
msgid "Sasha, escort the prisoner to his cell. Regardless of how the vote went down, he'll have to answer for Hal's death."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C2"
msgid "You're right Zena. I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D0A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C3"
msgid "Cass, listen to me. I've known you all my life. You're not a killer. Do what's right, and put the gun down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027CF1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C4"
msgid "Nah, he killed Hal. He dies, right here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C5"
msgid "\"Who has not asked himself at some time or other: am I a monster or is this what it means to be a person?\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C6"
msgid "But I digress. In closing I will leave you with the words of Clarice Lispector:"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D61]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C8"
msgid "Regardless, I thank you for giving me the opportunity to atone. Be well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D5B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008C9"
msgid "You can say your goodbyes or go back to your tents. But the decision is final."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008CA"
msgid "You can congratulate Hal or go back to your tents. But the decision is final."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008D2"
msgid "It is the oath I took as a preacher."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D62]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008D3"
msgid "Kudos to you for keeping a secret."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008D4"
msgid "In his own way, yes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008D5"
msgid "Of course. Confessions are between him and God."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008D6"
msgid "No, he did not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008D7"
msgid "And yet he never came forward."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D5C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008D8"
msgid "Yes, that would violate the seal of confession. A priest cannot reveal anything that would betray the penitent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008D9"
msgid "So he's been battling these demons for some time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008DA"
msgid "That would be a violation of my oath."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008DB"
msgid "He confided in me long ago. I never spoke a word of it of course."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008DC"
msgid "Ah, I see. So Hal has confessed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008DD"
msgid "There's something you should know about Hal Caruso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008DE"
msgid "You should've told someone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008DF"
msgid "What fluffy wool he has! You don't even notice the fangs."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008E0"
msgid "Surprised. Confused. It's a bit like looking at sheep, who insists he is wolf."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008E1"
msgid "How did you react when he told you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008E2"
msgid "That is what Hal wants. But I teeter. I am far too acquainted with man's flaws to inflict such a punishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008E3"
msgid "I will be voting for his execution. I encourage you to do the same."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027D7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008E4"
msgid "But now that Hal has come forward, the greater question of course, is what to do about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008E7"
msgid "Make no mistake. I took their supplies, knowing they would die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008E8"
msgid "Because I didn't want to be followed. The body can only survive without water for three days."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DDB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008E9"
msgid "Why take their supplies? Why not leave them with food and water?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008EA"
msgid "People can be monstrous. It's choosing not to, every day, that makes us human."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DDA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008EB"
msgid "The Hour of the Star. It was her final book."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008EC"
msgid "Then you're in good company. Because neither do I."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008ED"
msgid "Buddy, I don't even know what you just said."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008EE"
msgid "A cynical view, but that's not the same as untrue."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008EF"
msgid "Vote the way you want."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F0"
msgid "Well said."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F1"
msgid "Not just her final book. A masterpiece."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F2"
msgid "I shall. To the best of my meager abilities. Hal wants to be executed, but I wonder if that is what's right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F3"
msgid "I always do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F4"
msgid "To be a person is to do the monstrous. We are beasts at our core."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F5"
msgid "I don't know if it'll go that far, but you can vote how you like."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F6"
msgid "Touche."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F7"
msgid "Monster or not, one should pay for their crimes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DCE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F8"
msgid "A middle ground. A fair choice for one who plays the part of man and beast."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008F9"
msgid "Exile is the best option."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008FA"
msgid "Fair. I do believe he is a changed man, but my opinion bears no more weight than that of his victims."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008FB"
msgid "Exonerate him. He's paid his debt to society."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008FC"
msgid "But when the vote comes, we will have to decide for ourselves, what he deserves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027DE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008FD"
msgid "Either way, I don't know if Hal Caruso is a \"good\" man. I don't know if the act of becoming good constitutes atonement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E24]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008FE"
msgid "And what if someone got caught in the crossfire? This could've been settled peacefully. What you did was reckless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E22]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0008FF"
msgid "I got rid of a bad man who lied about his past. Why wouldn't you approve?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E1D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000900"
msgid "Pirate or not, the Hal I knew was a measured man. You likely didn't give him a choice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E1A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000901"
msgid "Caruso attacked me. I had to defend myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E17]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000902"
msgid "Fine. But we're the ones who have to deal with the fallout of your actions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E14]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000903"
msgid "I don't need your approval."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000904"
msgid "The hell it doesn't!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E10]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000905"
msgid "I'd like you to leave, now. And don't come back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E2B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000906"
msgid "Look, I understand why you came here. But I do not approve how you went about doing it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E25]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000907"
msgid "Caspian, enough! Don't make this harder than it already is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01027E23]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000908"
msgid "Up ahead is the Community Center. We should have privacy there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029893]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000953"
msgid "Thank god the vote went the way it did. I don't know what I'd do if Hal wasn't with us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029892]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000954"
msgid "I don't care how long they lock me up. I don't regret shooting him. He got his revenge, I got mine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029891]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000955"
msgid "I'll never forgive you for killing Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029890]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000956"
msgid "I can't believe he's gone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102988E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000957"
msgid "I don't know if letting Hal go was the right thing. So often, it's easy to do, but hard to know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102988D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000958"
msgid "Now I know why Hal wanted me back. He knew this day was coming."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102988C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000959"
msgid "We don't get too many survey teams out here. You'll probably want to talk to Hal, he does most of the scouting for us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102988B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00095A"
msgid "[Lie] I'm here to survey this land."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A0E"
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A0F"
msgid "I want to sell a plushie, and then charge an arm and a leg for a thousand different accessories. I could really use the body parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A10"
msgid "I bet I was an eldritch being in my past life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A11"
msgid "So are you like a captain-captain, or a pilot captain? Am I in the military now? Does that mean I get a pension?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D89]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A12"
msgid "Ever think about how pointless life is? I do. Every day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A13"
msgid "You ever want to join a cult? I mean, besides Constellation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A14"
msgid "Find any cool mushrooms? Eat them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C22]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A15"
msgid "Were we talking? I sure hope not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A16"
msgid "Got one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A17"
msgid "Another one down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A18"
msgid "Spill some blood for me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C43]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A19"
msgid "Might as well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C40]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A1A"
msgid "Sure, I'm an open book. It's got spiders crawling all over it, but it's open."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A1B"
msgid "They use it in plastics, rubber, even toys. So fungi are also entertainment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A1C"
msgid "So there's this thing called itaconic acid, which you can isolate from a fungus. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A1D"
msgid "I've heard some xenofungi are known to break down concrete. It's my dream to lay siege to a castle with them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C0A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A1E"
msgid "It's not as cool as you think."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BDA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A1F"
msgid "No thanks. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A20"
msgid "I don't know. Places like that are haunted."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A21"
msgid "Maybe. But I like to think I'm more than a witch's face."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A22"
msgid "Can you tell me about any past work experiences?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A23"
msgid "Did the potions actually work?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A24"
msgid "No. But I took the money anyway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C24]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A25"
msgid "What were some of your most popular potions?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A26"
msgid "There wasn't any real science to it, I'd just grind up some goldenseal root, add a dash of cinnamon, and add almond milk for prosperity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A27"
msgid "Usually love and fortune. I pitched them to clients as investments, which means you have to pay more."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C26]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A28"
msgid "As someone who's worked retail, same."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A29"
msgid "As long as it's a sacrifice to some bottomless pit god."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A2A"
msgid "He wanted two thousand credits for it. I offered him four. I got reprimanded for that. Jokes on them, I would've gone as high as six."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BFF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A2B"
msgid "I think you have plenty of pep."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A2C"
msgid "Then I need to talk to my lawyer and have them sue you for slander."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A2D"
msgid "I've got a job on my crew if you want it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A2E"
msgid "I got really excited because his corpse started wailing, but it turns out it was just the gases being released. Shame."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A2F"
msgid "I never really got enough time with the bodies. But I did sprinkle some ground wormwood and valerian root on this one guy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A30"
msgid "Pff, doctors, right? What do they know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A31"
msgid "I also killed a man once by looking at him funny. Although the doctors claim it was a heart attack. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A32"
msgid "Well, I'm pretty good with picking stuff up with my feet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B5F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A33"
msgid "That sounds dismal. I'm on my way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A34"
msgid "Before I bring you on, will you tell me more about your skills? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C1A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A35"
msgid "Are you saying you have ship full of corpses somewhere? That's... something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BF2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A36"
msgid "Join your crew? I usually travel alone, but the idea does appeal to me. I'd have more time to focus on my book if I were traveling with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A37"
msgid "It seems like you are too. Maybe we should travel together. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A38"
msgid "I understand. Thank you for indulging me. I hope the starfield treats you kindly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C02]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A39"
msgid "What type of book are you writing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A3A"
msgid "Yeah, I can do that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D3E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A3B"
msgid "Don't get too far ahead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D3D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A3C"
msgid "What happens if I move? Does the bomb in my sack explode? Cool."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A3D"
msgid "Let's get you assigned somewhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A3E"
msgid "Of course I did."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A3F"
msgid "Cool."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A40"
msgid "And off we go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A41"
msgid "How did your interview with Galbank go?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C0D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A42"
msgid "Aren't you like a gangster or something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A43"
msgid "What about your parents? What were they like?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A44"
msgid "You mentioned painting before. What sort of things do you like to paint?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A45"
msgid "It was a fairly transparent adoption process."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A46"
msgid "Mmm... hard to say. They did introduce me to fantasy books and video slates. I think those became my parents after that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A47"
msgid "Did you have many friends as a child?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C4C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A48"
msgid "What does the \"slow, inexorable march toward death\" look like?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010781E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A49"
msgid "Hey, you found us! Good job. Now dock that ship and come on in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A4C"
msgid "They're staring at me, they're all staring at me..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A4D"
msgid "Say something!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A4E"
msgid "You think I'm crazy? Damn you, I'm not! I'm not! How can you not see them? The sea of endless eyes? You're drowning in them as we speak!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A4F"
msgid "What do they want from me? I can't eat, I can't sleep. And when I look in the mirror there are two eyes in my skull mocking me. Torturing me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A50"
msgid "They're all around me, I can't escape them. The eyes are everywhere. I look outside my window and there's a sea of them. When I land and look up into the sky, I see them looking down on me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A51"
msgid "You're talking about stars. They're harmless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A52"
msgid "I don't know what you're talking about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A53"
msgid "I can't take this anymore... *sob* can't take this anymore..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C444]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A55"
msgid "My press agent can handle any further inquiries."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C444]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A56"
msgid "I'm sorry, but I really don't have the time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D252]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A57"
msgid "Coop's nice 'cause, yeah, he's quiet, but he doesn't look sad or anything. Wren makes me sad. She makes everyone sad. I just don't get why she's always around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D251]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A58"
msgid "All she does is stand in a corner like some sad, lost child. It's so annoying. I liked her better when she was sick. At least then she wasn't taking up space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC06SharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A59"
msgid "Mayday! Mayday! Calling all ships in the area."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B166]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A5A"
msgid "Let me at 'em!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B16C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A5B"
msgid "Nowhere to run, nowhere to hide!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B175]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A5C"
msgid "Please record your distress message after the tone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B174]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A5D"
msgid "Error 0 0 3 7: Distress message index was out of bounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C468]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A5E"
msgid "Looks like I was right! Two pirate ships inbound!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A316]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A5F"
msgid "Please respond."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A60"
msgid "Wanna play a game?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A61"
msgid "What has an eye but cannot see?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A62"
msgid "A classic one to start with. Perhaps you know it? Let's hope you do..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C74D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A63"
msgid "Hmm, you're not doing so great, buddy. Two riddles down, and two people dead. Get your head in the game!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A64"
msgid "More info? Yeah, I've got your info."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C745]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A65"
msgid "No, no, no. Wrong answer. A student may very well bring their backpack into class."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A66"
msgid "Anyone can hold a grenade as long as they want, so long as you don't pull the pin."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A67"
msgid "Heh, I like that answer, but it doesn't quite fit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A68"
msgid "Hey, good job. That's the right answer, I knew you had it in ya."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A69"
msgid "Are you serious? You want these people to die, don't you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01072FC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A6A"
msgid "I'm not playing your game."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A6B"
msgid "I'm not getting involved in this. I'm leaving."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D259]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A6C"
msgid "Time to say bye-bye to this one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C28]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A6D"
msgid "Either way, as collectibles go, it's definitely a conversation piece, so feel free to hold on to it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A6E"
msgid "I'd be looking for a lawyer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A6F"
msgid "I don't like to talk about my past. But suffice to say, my history as a soldier was not without trauma."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ACA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A70"
msgid "Get me to Neon in one piece and you won't regret it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C81B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A71"
msgid "You're taking a risk bringing that man aboard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C819]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A72"
msgid "Mark my words, he's nothin' but trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C812]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A73"
msgid "I do not trust this man, and neither should you. Keep an eye on him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A74"
msgid "Further back!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A75"
msgid "I told you not to follow me. I'm not going to tell you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A76"
msgid "Looks like an abandoned ship. Not sure it's worth our time to go inside, but it's your call."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A77"
msgid "It's been fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD49]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A78"
msgid "You're... a better fighter than you look."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC5C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A79"
msgid "What...what do you mean by that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC61]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A7A"
msgid "Well I thought it was impressive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC6B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A7B"
msgid "Not really, no. That's a bit too far from home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A7C"
msgid "Sorry, not interested."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A7D"
msgid "I'm sure we can find a mutually beneficial solution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A7E"
msgid "Yeah, I can tell this isn't your first tussle."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A7F"
msgid "Well, one can never be too careful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A80"
msgid "What do you need my ship for?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A81"
msgid "Pay me now or die here. It's your choice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064826]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A82"
msgid "Hi there!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064818]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A83"
msgid "I have to run, but if you're ever at GalBank, come and say hi!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064818]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A84"
msgid "Hi there! So great to see you again!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106480F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A85"
msgid "Why hello there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106480A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A86"
msgid "I should have a free spot somewhere in the next few months."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106480A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A87"
msgid "I'm sorry, I don't have to talk right now, but ask Hannah to book a meeting."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A89"
msgid "I can't tell you how relieved we are to see you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A8A"
msgid "Don't worry, this shouldn't take long."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A8B"
msgid "We're in here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A8C"
msgid "What happened here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068032]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A8D"
msgid "What about my compensation for this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068035]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A8E"
msgid "I'll have an adequate reward deposited in your account as soon as we land at destination."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068030]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A8F"
msgid "I'm right behind you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106802C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A90"
msgid "She'll be fine. She's a real trooper."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01069D97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A91"
msgid "We should probably get on to your ship now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEF6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A92"
msgid "Hey, at least we got out of there, even if we did have to spend the night hiding in a dumpster."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF23]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A93"
msgid "You're welcome to come if you want. Never know what might go down out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF23]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A94"
msgid "Just thinking of cruising the Free Lanes. Seeing if there's any jobs out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A95"
msgid "You know I always got your back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A96"
msgid "Got any plans later?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEEF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A97"
msgid "Sounds good to me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CECE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A98"
msgid "What do you want to do? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A99"
msgid "Hey, I love Milli like she was my own. The plants are a different story."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A9A"
msgid "I think we're saving up for a trip to Neon. A real one, you know? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A505]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A9B"
msgid "Thanks again for everything. I'll never forget it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A9C"
msgid "I just know that Hannah is going to be all right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A9D"
msgid "Thank you for letting us aboard your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A9E"
msgid "Why can't they just leave us alone!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000A9F"
msgid "Please get us out of here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA0"
msgid "We should leave as soon as we can."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010643A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA1"
msgid "Hello again! Have you decided to assist the VP of Acquisitions?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064396]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA2"
msgid "The VP of Acquisitions, Miss Krause, pledges to give you a generous reward if you help her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106439B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA3"
msgid "Ha! No, that would be Miss Krause. I'm just her assistant, Hannah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064394]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA4"
msgid "Well, a few people, um...a few people are dead, but the VP of Acquisitions is unhurt. I'm okay too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA5"
msgid "Remember what I said about the pirates."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA6"
msgid "We're waiting for you, over."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA7"
msgid "Thanks again for everything!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA8"
msgid "Right behind you, Miss Krause."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AA9"
msgid "Look at that ship flying straight through the mines. These idiots are going to kill themselves!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059ABF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AAA"
msgid "I'm not looking for conversation. Go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059ABC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AAB"
msgid "Don't have any work for you right now. Leave me alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059ABB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AAC"
msgid "Get out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_DialogueAnchorpoint_TigerSharedInfo_Purr
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AAE"
msgid "Purr."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeC1
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AAF"
msgid "Cat, you're starting to move a little stiff and creaky. Might be time for an oil bath."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeA2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB0"
msgid "Don't give me that attitude, cat. You've got to pull your weight around here just like everyone else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeA2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB1"
msgid "Oh really?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB2"
msgid "Might be worth taking a look, as long as we're careful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB3"
msgid "I see multiple blips for cargo containers, probably from a ship that got too close to the mines."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB4"
msgid "This looks like some sort of minefield. The whole thing likely drifted from its original location."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080458]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB5"
msgid "Starting to think you're getting a kick out of this... Am I wrong?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080455]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB6"
msgid "Can you give me a bit of a heads-up the next time you start a self-destruct sequence?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108046D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB7"
msgid "There might be some valuables left in the Captain's Locker, if that's what you're after."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A4E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB8"
msgid "Okay, Darcy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AB9"
msgid "It ain't a reason to jump to conclusions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ABA"
msgid "There's all kinds of stuff that can make a noise like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A47]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ABB"
msgid "What crisis are we heading for this time?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A47]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ABC"
msgid "I got your message, Darcy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ABD"
msgid "I might be forced to make a difficult choice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ABE"
msgid "Should there be an incident, we might not be able to protect everyone. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ABF"
msgid "Fine, but you should consider your priorities."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AC0"
msgid "Mister Saint?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AC1"
msgid "Did you get the Power Cell yet? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105456E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AC2"
msgid "I've taken damage from a pirate attack and lost power."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059ACB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AC3"
msgid "Ok. Let me see if I can find you what you need. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AC4"
msgid "I know what it's like to hope for a hand up when all you can do is grasp at the air."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105461D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ACD"
msgid "Had you going for a moment, didn't I?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ACE"
msgid "Are we all set?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053566]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ACF"
msgid "Anything else?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053574]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD0"
msgid "I'm good, just looking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD1"
msgid "Of course, dear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD2"
msgid "You know it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD3"
msgid "Specials? What are those?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01055B58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD4"
msgid "I don't know, can you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053580]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD5"
msgid "Are you sure you can handle this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE05]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD6"
msgid "I bet you were."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE0A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD7"
msgid "Looking for something, traveler?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053583]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD8"
msgid "Do you need anything, traveler?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AD9"
msgid "Sure, just let me know if you need any help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE1D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ADA"
msgid "This is your shop, friend. Take all the time you need."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE2B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ADB"
msgid "Well, well, look at what the space cat brought in... How are you, my friend?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE25]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ADC"
msgid "Welcome back to our little shop in the stars."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE22]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ADD"
msgid "Welcome to our shop. Let me know if you see anything you like."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053571]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ADE"
msgid "What will it be today?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053570]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000ADF"
msgid "How can we help you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE0"
msgid "Your ship's name, the \"Light of Anjali\". What does it mean?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE1"
msgid "Please, make yourself at home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE2"
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE3"
msgid "Let me know if you change your mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE4"
msgid "The other day we had a VP for Galbank come aboard. Didn't even buy anything. What a cheapskate!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE5"
msgid "You meet some interesting people if you travel the Free Lanes long enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE6"
msgid "She always has something interesting to say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE7"
msgid "If you ever get out to Anchorpoint, make sure you talk to the bartender."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE8"
msgid "They say the guy who owns it won't spend a credit if he doesn't have to, and it shows."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AE9"
msgid "Have you been to Anchorpoint yet? Kind of a dive, if you ask me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE3E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AEA"
msgid "You didn't hear it from me. Anything else?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE3D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AEB"
msgid "Well, that's what they say. What else do you need today?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE3A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AEC"
msgid "That's what I heard anyway. Anything else for you today?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE13]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AED"
msgid "Not a whole lot, but still..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C822]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AEF"
msgid "Did you find anything you like?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C81E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF0"
msgid "What did I tell you, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F90E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF1"
msgid "Not right now, sorry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F91A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF2"
msgid "We can deliver to your ship, or you can come aboard for special deals."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF3"
msgid "Very well then. Safe travels, valued customer!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF4"
msgid "I'm coming over to look at the specials."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF5"
msgid "Hey, you break it, you buy it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF6"
msgid "Happy to see you're still traveling the Free Lanes!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF7"
msgid "I better tag along then. You can never be too careful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF8"
msgid "Well, that was unexpected. Are you really going to go aboard their shop - I mean, ship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B385]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AF9"
msgid "You know where to find us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B384]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AFA"
msgid "Don't be a stranger, stranger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AFB"
msgid "Have too much there, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AFC"
msgid "What are you doing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AFD"
msgid "Great. You're drunk, aren't you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AFE"
msgid "Do you need to take a seat, friend?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B39C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000AFF"
msgid "Please watch your step."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B398]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B00"
msgid "Careful there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_IfeelgreatThanksfornotleavingmepassedoutinahallway
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B01"
msgid "I feel great. Thanks for not leaving me passed out in a hallway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_GossipPlayerPrompt
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B02"
msgid "What can you tell me about your friends?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_HopeYouChokeOnYourOwnDrink
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B03"
msgid "Hope you choke on your own drink."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_ThisIsntHowIPlannedTonightToGoAttAll
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B04"
msgid "This isn't how I planned today to go at all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Soundslikeyouguysaremissingafew
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B05"
msgid "Sounds like you're waiting on some friends."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B43E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B06"
msgid "And just when I thought tonight was going to be fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B43D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B07"
msgid "Way to kill the mood, everyone!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B43A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B08"
msgid "I came here to have fun. Not this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B438]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B09"
msgid "I needed this escape. Work has been driving me crazy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B435]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B0A"
msgid "What the hell was all that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B433]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B0B"
msgid "I should talk with Sawyer and find out what happened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B432]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B0C"
msgid "Would this be a bad time to grab another drink?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B430]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B0D"
msgid "What happened?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B42E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B0E"
msgid "This is the best!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B428]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B0F"
msgid "Shh, I wanna hear what they're saying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B41E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B10"
msgid "I hope everything is okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B41D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B11"
msgid "Are they going to fight?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B41A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B12"
msgid "I wonder if Sadie would dance with me if I asked."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B414]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B13"
msgid "This isn't the time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B412]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B14"
msgid "I can't talk right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B411]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B15"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B40C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B16"
msgid "I don't want to talk anymore. It's best you tell Sawyer to take you back wherever he found you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B405]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B17"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B403]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B18"
msgid "I just want off this ship at this point."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B19"
msgid "Did something happen?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B1A"
msgid "You forced me to do this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B1B"
msgid "Way to ruin the fun!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B32F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B1C"
msgid "Nugh! Dammit..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B32D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B1D"
msgid "Gh... Nh..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B326]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B1E"
msgid "Grugh..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_PG_BeCareful
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B1F"
msgid "Be careful!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B37B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B20"
msgid "I'm getting real tired of you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B374]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B21"
msgid "I won't let you get away with this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B371]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B22"
msgid "Biggest mistake of your life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B370]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B23"
msgid "I can't wait to put you down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B36C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B24"
msgid "I don't want to hurt you. Back down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B365]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B25"
msgid "They shouldn't be going off like this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B362]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B26"
msgid "Sadie, what's up with the turret systems?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B35A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B27"
msgid "What is this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B359]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B28"
msgid "Opal, are you alright?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B357]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B29"
msgid "Sawyer, what's going on with your ship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B354]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B2A"
msgid "You asked for this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B338]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B2B"
msgid "What the hell is going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B335]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B2C"
msgid "Dammit, just die already!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B31B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B2D"
msgid "Ngh!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B316]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B2E"
msgid "That's gonna leave a mark."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B311]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B2F"
msgid "You'll pay for that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B30E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B30"
msgid "You'll regret that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B30D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B31"
msgid "Hngh..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B30A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B32"
msgid "Ghn!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E23F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B33"
msgid "Just don't cause any trouble on the way there..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E288]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B34"
msgid "Didn't you know what Opal was doing to Wren?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E255]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B35"
msgid "I've changed my mind. I don't want to leave yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E22C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B36"
msgid "Finally. Take me back to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E29E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B37"
msgid "Sadie... Listen..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E22E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B38"
msgid "I'm sorry..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B39"
msgid "Opal, what did Sadie just say?!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E238]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B3A"
msgid "Sadie?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E212]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B3B"
msgid " Cooper, you're done with that two-faced snake!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E26D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B3C"
msgid "I just know you two are friends, and I didn't want to mess that up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B85F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B3D"
msgid "Oh, Opal? You just missed her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E22F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B3E"
msgid "Thank you for everything you said."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E22F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B3F"
msgid "But perhaps I can at least stand up for myself? Sadie deserves to know anyway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E22F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B40"
msgid "I don't know if I could do that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E29D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B41"
msgid "I learned to fight for myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B42"
msgid "Fine. Don't tell anyone. This was none of my business to begin with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E280]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B43"
msgid "You're right. It isn't."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E28B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B44"
msgid "Since I'm new here, is there anything I should know about anyone here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E24B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B45"
msgid "Wait. I didn't want to be here. Bring me back to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E275]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B46"
msgid "There's nothing to tell. Opal and I just aren't close is all. Now, will you drop it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E265]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B47"
msgid "Hey, now, we still have loads of fun to have and everyone is having a great time! I'll take you back once the party's over, yea?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E25E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B48"
msgid "And the party still isn't over. We invited more in on the fun. Go ahead, have a blast! Drink. Mingle! Who knows, by the time all this is over, you may meet your new best friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E204]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B49"
msgid "How was your nap? You feeling alright?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E20C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B4A"
msgid "Don't worry. We order quality stuff. You ready? Go!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E28D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B4B"
msgid "Of course! This is a celebration! Come on, sit! Join us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E251]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B4C"
msgid "Sure. I would love to join you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B284]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B4D"
msgid "You know nothing about us. You're just some nosey weirdo me and Sawyer found at a bar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B4E"
msgid "Opal has been bullying your sister."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B296]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B4F"
msgid "I think Sadie would be interested in hearing it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B50"
msgid "You're going to do nothing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B51"
msgid "You sure had some colorful things to say in this slate of yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B27E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B52"
msgid "I don't get it. Why does she do this? Sadie's her friend. She's dating my brother. Yet there is something wrong with me? What the hell?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B53"
msgid "Excuse me. I need to go talk to my sister."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B54"
msgid "You're right... This isn't fair. Why do I have to be the one to speak up? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B55"
msgid "Yea... Yea, I think so too. Thank you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B305]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B56"
msgid "Where did you get the money for this nice ship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B57"
msgid "I know my sister, Sadie, is the one who decorated and set up the ship's security. I only came today because I could tell she wanted me to see how everything turned out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B58"
msgid "Sawyer pays great now that he has Mommy and Daddy funding him. He asked me to set up his ship's security system and the amount he paid for it... damn. He might be on some kind of spending high now that he has the credits. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B59"
msgid "What? Let me see that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B28D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B5A"
msgid "If you don't tell me, then I'll go tell Sadie about it myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B5B"
msgid "No. No, I'm done talking about this with you. Just leave me alone, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B5C"
msgid "I guess that's true."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B5D"
msgid "I guess that could be true. I wouldn't want her to get away with harassing Cooper or Sadie if she is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E266]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B5E"
msgid "Here. Let us help you. Once you get some rest, I'm sure you'll feel as good as new."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E266]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B5F"
msgid "Oh, right. Hey, friend, we- You good? Heh, maybe that was too many drinks?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E1F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B60"
msgid "Ha! The others don't know what they're missing. Ready for the third drink?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D679]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B61"
msgid "Can't imagine you got much out of her. Don't take it personally. She's quiet like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D695]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B62"
msgid "Really? You've put Opal pretty on edge, okay? Whatever you want to do, just be quick about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E245]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B63"
msgid "Opal, get a load of this guy!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E246]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B64"
msgid "Opal, get a load of this lady!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D67A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B65"
msgid "I'm with her. I just want to go back to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D691]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B66"
msgid "I invited you to have fun, not make Opal upset. Whatever. Let me just take you back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D698]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B67"
msgid "And you just met the guy. I've known him for years. Imagine how I feel."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D6A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B68"
msgid "Right. I think Opal said you were new. Take it from me. Sawyer isn't all that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D69B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B69"
msgid "Just don't get too wasted. Don't want to pass out all over again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D687]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B6A"
msgid "That doesn't bode well for either of us then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D689]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B6B"
msgid "That's okay. I'm not that interesting either."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D682]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B6C"
msgid "Sorry. I'm not too much of a talker, or that interesting. You'd be better off talking to my sister, Sadie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D682]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B6D"
msgid "Hi there..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D67F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B6E"
msgid "Damn right. Those two do love to cause all sorts of trouble. I don't know how I put up with them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D694]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B6F"
msgid "We'll see how well I do after a couple of drinks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065747]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B70"
msgid "I'll be sure to let you know if I hear any more tragic tales of lost cargo."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047DCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B71"
msgid "I've recovered the lost shipment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047DCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B72"
msgid "Excellent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065750]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B73"
msgid "Payment for a job well done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo09
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B74"
msgid "Turn around and go back to your ship now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B75"
msgid "Okay, you asked for it. Defense systems activated!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D02C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B76"
msgid "You know, uh, in case there are pirates or something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D02C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B77"
msgid "We should go now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040739]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B78"
msgid "You don't have to go into details. I just want to understand."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104073A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B79"
msgid "Yeah? Or what?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040742]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B7A"
msgid "You mean, there's worse than you out there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104073F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B7B"
msgid "Yeah, I guess not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104075F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B7C"
msgid "Why not just throw me out of the airlock while you're at it..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B7D"
msgid "Really? Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104074B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B7E"
msgid "Why not? Everyone else has."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104075A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B7F"
msgid "I'm not saying another word. Put me in jail, leave me here, I don't care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104089B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B80"
msgid "Maybe I should just leave you to freeze to death."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C0A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B81"
msgid "You piloted this ship into deep space all by yourself?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C08]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B82"
msgid "What kind of cargo are you transporting?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C06]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B83"
msgid "It's just me. Yep. Just me and my cargo ship. I prefer it that way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B84"
msgid "Where is the rest of the crew?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B85"
msgid "That's it for now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D024]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B86"
msgid "Can't you just leave me alone?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D023]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B87"
msgid "What do you want now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B88"
msgid "What do you plan on doing now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D032]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B89"
msgid "Hey. What's up?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B8A"
msgid "I mean, unless I can find someone to take me to my cousin's in New Atlantis..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B8B"
msgid "I don't have many options. My stepfather will be here any moment now..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B989]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B8C"
msgid "Ha! You wouldn't dare!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B8D"
msgid "See you around, maybe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C50C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B8E"
msgid "Let's just hope stepdaddy doesn't come after us..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B8F"
msgid "...wait, is it this button? Or that one?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B90"
msgid "No, don't do that! Uh...we'll fix the ship ourselves. But thanks!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B91"
msgid "No, please! I'm in enough trouble already...we're fine! End communication!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B92"
msgid "Seems you're having problems. I can come aboard to help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B93"
msgid "Ugh! Why does this have to be so complicated?!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B94"
msgid "Really, everything's fine. Just keep moving."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C0C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B95"
msgid "Don't shoot at us, please! We're unarmed and totally not dangerous!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DAC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B96"
msgid "Do you need anything else?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DABC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B97"
msgid "Thank you. Good luck to you too!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DABD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B98"
msgid "Thank you so much for helping me. I'll never forget it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DABD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B99"
msgid "Well, I guess this is it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBD8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B9A"
msgid "Thank you for offering to help. I only hope there's still time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B9B"
msgid "I can't thank you enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B9C"
msgid "Heading out?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B9D"
msgid "Everything okay there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040494]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B9E"
msgid "I don't know what these guys had planned for me, but I'm sure it wasn't pleasant."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040494]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000B9F"
msgid "Fair enough. I'm still damn glad you came."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA0"
msgid "She sent a message to your father, and he sent me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA1"
msgid "Again, thank you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA2"
msgid "I wish I had more, but that's the best I could do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA3"
msgid "Here you go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA4"
msgid "I said I'd get some credits together for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA5"
msgid "I did, yes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA6"
msgid "If that's true, why hasn't he done something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBE3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA7"
msgid "I wasn't sure, but at least it's good to know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA8"
msgid "He's living the life he chose. Nobody forced it on him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BA9"
msgid "You have to take the first step. Nobody else can do it for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BAA"
msgid "I'll be the one to decide what's best for myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BAB"
msgid "The bonds of family are more important than anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BAC"
msgid "We're both suffering, but I didn't cause this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BAD"
msgid "You're right. As much as I wish I could just forget all of this, I can't."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BAE"
msgid "This rift is hurting you both every day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBF1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BAF"
msgid "You should be telling him that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BB0"
msgid "You're right. So much time has already been lost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BB1"
msgid "It's not hard to understand how such a tragedy could tear a family apart."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BB2"
msgid "You're right. Just know that it's not a happy tale."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C41F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BB9"
msgid "Are you saying anything? Not sure if I'm getting interference..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C425]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BBA"
msgid "We appreciate the help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050245]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BBB"
msgid "Thanks again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050244]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BBC"
msgid "Let's get going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedInfo01_CaptainIntro01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BBD"
msgid "But, you know, I have to ask. Can we trust you? We aren't going to have any problems, are we?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedInfo01_CaptainIntro01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BBE"
msgid "Thanks for helping us out. We're all packed and ready to go. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedShipHello04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BBF"
msgid "See you on board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC0"
msgid "I'll give you a ride. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052B70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC1"
msgid "The captain will be waiting for you on board. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC2"
msgid "All business, huh? I get it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC3"
msgid "Damn, that was a close one, but we aren't out of the woods yet. Our ship has taken heavy damage. Not sure if we'll be able to fly out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC4"
msgid "Our cockpit's been damaged and none of us are certified to fly. We're stranded. Could you fly us out of here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC5"
msgid "Appreciate the assist but... damn. Can't believe I'm saying this, but our pilot was killed. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC6"
msgid "We don't have a safe way to fly out of here. Would you be able to give us a ride? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC7"
msgid "We appreciate your help, but our trouble isn't over yet. Our pilot was killed during the attack and the cockpit is heavily damaged. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC8"
msgid "Our ship got torn up during that attack. Sorry to dump this on you, but could you fly us out of here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BC9"
msgid "Thanks for the help. Can't believe we made it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EE05]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BCA"
msgid "Yes, but I guess we'll just have to take each other at our words."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EDFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BCB"
msgid "Sounds good, and thanks again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EE02]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BCC"
msgid "You can trust me. Can I trust you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EE07]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BCD"
msgid "Let's just get a move on. We're wasting time here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C420]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BCE"
msgid "Okay, we're all packed up and ready to go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C410]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BCF"
msgid "It's been a long and bad day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C410]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD0"
msgid "*Sigh* Jesus, I need to get a grip. You're helping us out and here I am, complaining to you like an asshole. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD1"
msgid "Spoken like someone who doesn't have to abandon their ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C417]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD2"
msgid "Sorry about your ship. I wish I got here sooner."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD3"
msgid "Look, if we got off on the wrong foot, I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD4"
msgid "I'm not an ungrateful person. I appreciate you doing this for us, a group of total strangers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C440]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD5"
msgid "I can fly my own ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C43A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD6"
msgid "That doesn't seem like the best idea."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD7"
msgid "Come on, I had to ask."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD8"
msgid "If you say so."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BD9"
msgid "You can keep your condolences, I barely knew the guy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BDA"
msgid "How the hell should I know? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BDB"
msgid "Yeah, sorry. I need to snap out of it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BDC"
msgid "You're right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BDD"
msgid "No point moping around anymore, I guess. We'll see you aboard your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BDE"
msgid "Put them down!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BDF"
msgid "We must've looked like we were hauling some precious cargo, or something. I don't know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE0"
msgid "Fire!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE1"
msgid "What are the odds of us ever crossing paths? Well, you got unlucky today, friend. We're taking that ship of yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE2"
msgid "I get it. We're in kind of a rush, too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE3"
msgid "If you want, my crew and I can handle the flying. We know our way around ships, and we're fast learners. Hell, we just started flying this one a week ago."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE4"
msgid "Get them!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE5"
msgid "You seem like a nice person, but you're unlucky. We'll be taking that ship of yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE6"
msgid "How do I put this..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE7"
msgid "Wow, that's a hell of a ship you have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE8"
msgid "Gonna give us a ride? You're really saving our asses here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BE9"
msgid "We don't need a ride. We'll just be taking your ship and leaving you dead with the pilot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037163]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BEA"
msgid "Check back with me sometime. I might have another target for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D542]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BEB"
msgid "Come to momma, you sweet little parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037173]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BEC"
msgid "Have you now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D54A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BED"
msgid "They're kind of busted up. Too bad."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D545]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BEE"
msgid "They look brand new. Nice work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_IntimidationResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BEF"
msgid "Take the keys. We got her locked up over there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_IntimidationResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF0"
msgid "Whoa, hey, no one has to die here today, least not over some damn milliwhale."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_Yura01SceneReentry01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF1"
msgid "Why would Yura send someone to pay a ransom that they don't have?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_Yura01SceneReentry03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF2"
msgid "All right, plan B I guess. You want Milli? Do me a favor, and she's all yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_YuraInterested01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF3"
msgid "My friends tell me we both light up when we see each other. That's got to  mean something, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_YuraInterested01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF4"
msgid "We're always making excuses to hang out together, and we're always doing little things for each other..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_YuraInterested01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF5"
msgid "I'm 99% sure she's interested. It's that 1% holding me back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B445]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF6"
msgid "Don't let anything happen to Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B442]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF7"
msgid "I knew this wasn't going to go as planned."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B43F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF8"
msgid "I knew those credits were a long shot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B43E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BF9"
msgid "I can't believe we didn't get those credits. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D6B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BFA"
msgid "I knew this would pay off."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BFB"
msgid "'Bout time someone showed up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BFC"
msgid "Roman's the one you want to talk to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BFD"
msgid "I knew this was a bad idea."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BFE"
msgid "You gotta be kidding me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000BFF"
msgid "What the hell?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C00"
msgid "We gotta save Milli!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C01"
msgid "Some Ranger you are!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C02"
msgid "That little runt's living better than me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C03"
msgid "Did you see all the toys and pillows in there? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C04"
msgid "Okay, that's a bit extreme. If I'm such a \"monster,\" why did I bother setting up Milli with such a plush room?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A34F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C05"
msgid "Too bad I can't say the same for my plants."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A34E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C06"
msgid "At least one survived, but she thrives on neglect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A34E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C07"
msgid "Too bad I can't say the same for my plants."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C08"
msgid "Don't worry, this is the last straw."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C09"
msgid "Right, \"pet sitters\"?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035870]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C0A"
msgid "Milli! Thank goodness you're okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035888]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C0B"
msgid "I refuse to let you guilt me over something that you regrow all the time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035888]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C0C"
msgid "Oh not the plants again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103589B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C0D"
msgid "If only \"little\" was the word for it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035878]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C0E"
msgid "I don't mind a little family drama."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035885]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C0F"
msgid "I don't see how the timing is my fault."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035872]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C10"
msgid "I was just getting to that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C858]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C11"
msgid "Hey, don't look at me..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C853]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C12"
msgid "Help me out here. Milli's fine, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C13"
msgid "Here's the key to Milli's room."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C14"
msgid "Hmm. Fair enough. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C15"
msgid "We've been waiting for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C16"
msgid "Check your numbers, \"errand girl.\" You're short."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C17"
msgid "Fine, I'll be back with your credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C18"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS03_RansomCredits>] Here's your credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103589A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C19"
msgid "I believe you have something for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103589A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C1A"
msgid "So, I should've figured Yura would send a messenger. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C849]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C1B"
msgid "Who even are you and what were you doing in Atka's house to begin with? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C845]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C1C"
msgid "I can't believe Yura bailed on Atka and got someone else to take care of her place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035877]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C1D"
msgid "Pomegranate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103588B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C1E"
msgid "I knew you'd be the one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C1F"
msgid "It didn't seem that unreasonable at the time..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035886]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C20"
msgid "I'm interested in credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C21"
msgid "Find me back here sometime when you're done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C22"
msgid "It's a small house on Muphrid IV and the milliwhale's name is Milli. Original, I know, but that's my sister for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C23"
msgid "It's basically house sitting for my sister. Just water a few plants, feed a little milliwhale until she gets home, and you're done! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C24"
msgid "It'll be the easiest thing you've ever done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C25"
msgid "You, my friend, are a life saver."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103588C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C26"
msgid "Looking after plants and animals? No thanks. I need some level of excitement to keep me going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103588C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C27"
msgid "Seriously, no catch. House sitting just isn't for me, you know? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103589F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C28"
msgid "Count us in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C29"
msgid "There's no way I'm getting together that many credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C2A"
msgid "Yura didn't send me. She hired me to house sit for her sister."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C2B"
msgid "Heh, you got that right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C2C"
msgid "No, son of a... So she has no idea about any of this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C2D"
msgid "Go ahead and try."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D51]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C2E"
msgid "Well, it wasn't my first plan."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C2F"
msgid "Sorry to have ruined your plans."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C30"
msgid "All right. I'll do it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C31"
msgid "Hand over the milliwhale or you deal with the Crimson Fleet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C32"
msgid "We seriously can't work something out here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D1B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C33"
msgid "Yeah, well work faster."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C34"
msgid "I'm still working on it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C35"
msgid "Pay <Global=SFFL_MS03_RansomCredits>: Here's your credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D45]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C36"
msgid "Do I look like someone who cares?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D40]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C37"
msgid "I much prefer talking..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C38"
msgid "You realize I don't have to be nice about this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C39"
msgid "I know them both, but this really isn't about Atka... It's about Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D02]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C3A"
msgid "Really? Oh thank god. Even if they did, I'm sure Yura or Atka would've dropped them as soon as they knew it was us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C3B"
msgid "I would've guaranteed it! I just never saw her reporting it to the Freestar Rangers. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C3C"
msgid "You never considered the consequences of your actions?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D0B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C3D"
msgid "Just hand over the milliwhale."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C3E"
msgid "I'm listening."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C3F"
msgid "Heh, not with that attitude. Go waste someone else's time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C40"
msgid "Come on in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D13]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C41"
msgid "Can you tell me more about your sister?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C42"
msgid "What are you going to do while I'm watching the house?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D6E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C43"
msgid "I have some other questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C44"
msgid "Good question! And lucky for me, we don't have to find out since you took the job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C45"
msgid "Atka trusts you to watch her house?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A33F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C46"
msgid "Please... just leave us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A33F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C47"
msgid "What they did was wrong, but I can't say the punishment fit the crime."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A33F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C48"
msgid "While I believe you, I can't imagine Roman or his friends ever hurting Milli intentionally."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C49"
msgid "A milli-what?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C4A"
msgid "Such work is beneath us, but it does sound oddly satisfying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A333]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C4B"
msgid "Roman and his friends weren't exactly cooperative when I went to get Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A334]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C4C"
msgid "Oh my god... you killed him? All of them?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A332]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C4D"
msgid "Milli does seem fine, though, so I appreciate you stepping in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A332]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C4E"
msgid "I'm really sorry you got sucked into all this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A350]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C4F"
msgid "That still doesn't justify what you did, Yura. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A362]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C50"
msgid "Oh come on, Milli is fine. Everything is fine!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A352]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C51"
msgid "Okay, great, so this was all some elaborate scheme for Roman to catch my sister's attention."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A345]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C52"
msgid "I don't think Roman thinks much."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A354]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C53"
msgid "Not like that's a bad idea..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A354]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C54"
msgid "With Milli? What -- is he charging people for photo ops?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B432]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C55"
msgid "Roman's just a common thief extorting people for credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C56"
msgid "We've had quite the adventure together."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A342]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C57"
msgid "Roman was just wasting my time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C58"
msgid "Oh, and since you kept Milli safe, here's some milliwhale food."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C59"
msgid "I think Atka knows I'd never let anything happen to Yura, and that's enough for her to accept me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C5A"
msgid "She might be a little mad at first, but I'm sure she'd come around. Especially since I did it all for Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C5B"
msgid "Of all things to impress someone, why involve Milli?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C5C"
msgid "Believe me when I say there will be no next time. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C5D"
msgid "Okay, whoa, in that case, I don't have to know. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C5E"
msgid "All this for a date? I'm not sure whether to be impressed or mildly disturbed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C5F"
msgid "It's about time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C60"
msgid "Poor Roman. We should've seen this coming."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C61"
msgid "Let's see how long it takes Roman to get over Yura this time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C62"
msgid "Milli better be safe and sound."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C63"
msgid "Thanks for trying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C64"
msgid "Go. Away."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF03]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C65"
msgid "Leave me alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF01]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C66"
msgid "I'd be missing out on something amazing if you hadn't come along."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C67"
msgid "I think Atka's still impressed with her plants."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C68"
msgid "Hope that milliwhale's working out for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C69"
msgid "Good to see you. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C6A"
msgid "I wish I'd never met you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFD0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C6B"
msgid "Don't talk to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C6C"
msgid "Milli's probably your friend for life now. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C6D"
msgid "I knew you'd rock this house sitting gig."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C6E"
msgid "Don't worry about the plants. Happens all the time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C6F"
msgid "There's no hope for Yura. I'm not sure she even knows what responsibility means."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B436]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C70"
msgid "Thanks for bringing back Milli safe and sound."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF1D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C71"
msgid "Well, go on..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C72"
msgid "Awkward..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C73"
msgid "See you around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C74"
msgid "Looking forward to those credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEDE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C75"
msgid "Thanks again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C76"
msgid "Milli, no!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C77"
msgid "So you have to work through some things. Roman would understand."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C78"
msgid "How do you feel about him? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C79"
msgid "You guys were inseparable, and I know he loved you, too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C7A"
msgid "I'm sure deep down he knew. He had to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C7B"
msgid "Why do you worry about Yura?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C7C"
msgid "What makes you think you aren't relationship material?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C7D"
msgid "Unless you hired me for my pilot skills, I'm pretty much bound to disappoint you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C7E"
msgid "Sure I'm fun and always looking for the next thrill, but dating material? Me? I don't think so. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C7F"
msgid "Roman deserves better. I mean, deep down, who am I? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C80"
msgid "Stop it, Yura. I love you, and Roman loved you. No matter what."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C81"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEEB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C82"
msgid "I'm tired all the time. I'm just not ready to give up on her yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C83"
msgid "Yep, he's going to make some lucky person real happy someday. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C84"
msgid "And he's the only person that's never trying to change me which goes a long way in my book."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C85"
msgid "Roman's the best. He always knows what to say to keep me sane."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C86"
msgid "Understatement of the year. I'm not exactly successful in my own eyes either, but at least it's the life I want to live."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C87"
msgid "But now? Best thing that could've happened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C88"
msgid "And hey, thanks for talking to Yura. I thought I was screwed when I heard your voice on that intercom."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C89"
msgid "All right. I can do this. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C8A"
msgid "I did my part. The rest is up to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C8B"
msgid "Think about it? That's promising, right? Oh wow, she really might be ready to give me a shot. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C8C"
msgid "You should encourage her to get some help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C8D"
msgid "Yura doesn't think she deserves you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C8E"
msgid "*sigh* I knew it. Every time I think she's letting me in, she pushes me away."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C730]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C8F"
msgid "So, this is what it all led to, hm? I'll be out of air soon and I haven't seen anyone for the past... I don't know anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C72C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C90"
msgid "I promise, the second I step foot back home I'm taking you to the fanciest restaurant in town. I don't care how gross or dirty or whatever I'll be from a month in this hunk of metal. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C728]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C91"
msgid "I hope you're doing well, my Love. If all goes well I should be home soon. With a real nice pay day too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_CrimeDialogueSharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C92"
msgid "What do you think you're doing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034F7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C93"
msgid "Yeah? Well, take it up with founding fathers. We're putting those votes back and that's that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034F80]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C94"
msgid "It better not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103439E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C95"
msgid "Easier to just let them in and try to contain the mess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103439E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C96"
msgid "If we closed our doors to the Spacers, they'd just kick them down, metaphorically speaking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C97"
msgid "I wish I could spare someone to help you, but I just can't risk it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C98"
msgid "Believe me, I don't want to see that happen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C99"
msgid "Leave it to me. I won't let Spacers harm innocent people."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C9A"
msgid "Damn glad you got here when you did."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C9B"
msgid "Sounds like you've got experience with this kind of thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C9C"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C9D"
msgid "I'll solve your Spacer problem, but it'll cost you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C9E"
msgid "They said they were bringing everybody."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000C9F"
msgid "His friends stormed out, promising to come back for some retribution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA0"
msgid "One of them threatened to shoot a patron, so I locked him up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA1"
msgid "Ever since, they've been a lot worse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA2"
msgid "Word is, they've got a new leader who's violent and bloodthirsty in the extreme."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA3"
msgid "They've caused trouble before, but nothing too serious."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA4"
msgid "There's a Spacer gang that makes regular stops here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA5"
msgid "I'm not going anywhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA6"
msgid "Spacers are planning a raid on this place, and it could happen soon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA7"
msgid "You might want to get out of here while you still can."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA8"
msgid "As crazy as it sounds, I do see the logic in that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CA9"
msgid "That is a... unique perspective."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CAA"
msgid "Hello? Is someone there? Please, tell me if you can hear me. This is Sehoy Baker."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CAB"
msgid "In all honesty, I am."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CAC"
msgid "No, wait! Dammit!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_Z01_StarbornDialogue
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CAE"
msgid "Yes. I found Gabrielle and her ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105663C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CAF"
msgid "I'll find you, my star."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105663B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB0"
msgid "Right then..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056614]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB1"
msgid "Please tell me you can hear me..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056626]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB2"
msgid "I didn't want to hurt you..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056619]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB3"
msgid "That can't be good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB4"
msgid "Agh!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105661F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB5"
msgid "Stop this! Please!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB6"
msgid "Oh, thank you... please, travel safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB7"
msgid "Whatever credits you have left, keep them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB8"
msgid "Be safe out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CB9"
msgid "Thank you. I don't have much in the way of credits, but please, take these."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CBA"
msgid "I guess I should just head back?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CBB"
msgid "She was long gone by the time I found her. These slates were all I could find."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105660E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CBC"
msgid "[Lie] I did. But she didn't want to be found."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CBD"
msgid "Her ship malfunctioned. I found these slates in the wreckage."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CBE"
msgid "I can't say I have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CBF"
msgid "[Lie] She didn't say much. I don't think she wanted to be found."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056628]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC0"
msgid "By the time I found her she was dead. Her ship was destroyed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056631]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC1"
msgid "Why'd you tell her that? She deserves to know the truth. Looks like there's no going back now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056630]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC2"
msgid "Poor thing. Shame she had to learn like this. But, in the end, guess it was better for her to know than never learn."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105662E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC3"
msgid "Thought you'd spare her feelings or something? She's going to find out sooner or, well, later now, thanks to you. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105662D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC4"
msgid "Best for her to know than not at all. Hopefully she'll find peace one day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC5"
msgid "Huh. This was supposed to be a private tour, but fine. I guess we'll just sit here and wait for the pirates to show up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC6"
msgid "My last words are \"Hot Dogs are a sandwich.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC7"
msgid "That's exactly what a pirate would say!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC8"
msgid "[Lie] I'm not a pirate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CC9"
msgid "Oh, we don't need him. Hail the pirate ship, darling! Use your \"executive\" voice!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CCA"
msgid "All right you dastardly pirate scum, answer the hail!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CCB"
msgid "Oh look darling, I think I see one! Over there! Mr. guide man, do you think we should hail them?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CCC"
msgid "I agree, darling. This was far better use of our funds than another luxury cruise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CCD"
msgid "Hell yeah! The chance to destroy a real pirate ship! This is worth every cred!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CCE"
msgid "Answer, or die!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CCF"
msgid "If these scammers think pirates are scary, they haven't met the team at Morgan, Locke, & Hartley."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD0"
msgid "Don't worry darlin, I'm going to have a word with our lawyers. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031720]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD1"
msgid "Might be time to find a new supplier, at least for the drinks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031720]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD2"
msgid "We're running low again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103171E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD3"
msgid "That's unfortunate. Reliable traders are a rare commodity out here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031721]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD4"
msgid "We'd be lost without you, Maddie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103171F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD5"
msgid "I swear, if I had a credit for every time that thing broke down, I'd own my own space cantina."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103171F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD6"
msgid "Thanks, Maddie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103171D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD7"
msgid "I know I'm talented, but duct tape and miracles only go so far."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103171D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD8"
msgid "If you do, spend a little more money on the fixtures and appliances."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031727]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CD9"
msgid "Hey Valeria. I got that cooler fixed for you. Again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031700]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CDA"
msgid "Profits are down, Killian. I need you to do better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CDB"
msgid "Sure, Chan."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CDC"
msgid "Okay, I get it. Just keep it in mind in case you get some free time. That's all I ask."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE4A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CDD"
msgid "Leave! Leave now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE46]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CDE"
msgid "Go on. Eat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE43]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CDF"
msgid "Please, come aboard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AF01]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE0"
msgid "Say something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE1"
msgid "So itchy... but your body seems like it would not be."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE2"
msgid "I would like to inhabit a body like yours. My current body... I can feel it deteriorating. I feel my skin about to split, my teeth about to burst. I can feel itching behind my eyes. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE3"
msgid "Why are you just smiling at me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE4"
msgid "Do not be so modest."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE5"
msgid "Interesting. Your body seems strong, full of vigor. You have no excuse to let your ship fall into such disrepair. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE6"
msgid "Yes, you may eat your fill in a moment. First, I would like to know you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE7"
msgid "Afraid of your kind? Never."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE8"
msgid "It's hard to pass up free food."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CE9"
msgid "Nonsense, nonsense."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103073E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CEA"
msgid "You're crazy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CEB"
msgid "*Heavy breathing*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CEC"
msgid "Is everything all right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048D0B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CED"
msgid "Do not question me, and do not waste my precious food!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103074F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CEE"
msgid "That was disgusting."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103074E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CEF"
msgid "Impossible. This should not be happening..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030745]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF0"
msgid "I didn't inconvenience you. You're the one that invited me over."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105023B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF1"
msgid "Don't just leave me here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050237]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF2"
msgid "Wait, no! Come back!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050234]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF3"
msgid "Bye, I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050232]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF4"
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF5"
msgid "Get going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF6"
msgid "Move along."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105023D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF7"
msgid "What are you doing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105023C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF8"
msgid "This... this has to be a joke. Right? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CF9"
msgid "If you're looking for work, I need something taken care of."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CFA"
msgid "If you need a job, I have an opportunity you may be interested in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R02_TargetSpared_SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CFB"
msgid "You'll never see me again, I swear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R02SharedInfo01_ArbitratorInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CFC"
msgid "Good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CFD"
msgid "Thank you, thank you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CFE"
msgid "Listen to me! I'll pay you! I'll give you everything I have, just let me go, and I'll leave the Settled Systems for good!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A43D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000CFF"
msgid "Look, I can pay you. Just take my money and we can make this all go away. I'll leave the Settled Systems for good!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D00"
msgid "Please! Please, no!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D01"
msgid "This is the target. Take them out and bring me proof of the kill."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A440]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D02"
msgid "Move on, then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D03"
msgid "Got some more work for you. Want the details? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102AF68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D04"
msgid "[Attack] There's nothing you can do. I'm here to kill you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104480D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D05"
msgid "Do you think I'm stupid? Answer me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104480D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D06"
msgid "Hmmph."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D07"
msgid "Once I figure out how to get the hell out of here, it'll be like I never existed, I swear!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D08"
msgid "Really? Oh my god, thank you. Just take it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D09"
msgid "Seriously? Thank you, thank you! I'll disappear forever, I promise!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D0A"
msgid "Just take my money. Take it all, I don't need it, just take it and let me go. Please!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104609F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D0B"
msgid "Please, just take my money. Those idiots took most of it, but I'll give you whatever I have left."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104609C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D0C"
msgid "No, no! Isn't getting captured by maniacs punishment enough? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104609B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D0D"
msgid "Please, don't do this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D0E"
msgid "Thank god, you came to save me, didn't you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D0F"
msgid "If you're looking for work, I need someone to do a job for me. Preferably someone that isn't burdened by morality. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D10"
msgid "It had better not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D11"
msgid "Shut up. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D12"
msgid "Explain to me why my intel shows that one of the targets I hired you to kill is still breathing. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D13"
msgid "How much will you pay me for this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D14"
msgid "I'm not convinced. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D15"
msgid "I'm used to this type of work. I'm in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059115]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D16"
msgid "You're leaving? Leaving me to die? I'm not dying in here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029A3E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D17"
msgid "Any luck?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029A3C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D18"
msgid "Not getting cold feet, are you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029A3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D19"
msgid "You should get going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F8F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D1A"
msgid "Bye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F8F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D1B"
msgid "Good luck out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102971E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D1C"
msgid "I have the contraband."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102971B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D1D"
msgid "Allergic to money or something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029725]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D1E"
msgid "Have it your way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D1F"
msgid "What's so special about this contraband?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D20"
msgid "Are you up for it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D21"
msgid "I've got another job for you, if you're up for it. Same as last time, you just gotta get the contraband and give it to either me or the Trade Authority. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D22"
msgid "And you know what that means? Big money."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D23"
msgid "Tell you the truth, I'm not sure. But, whatever it is, people are willing to kill for it, and possibly die for it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D24"
msgid "I bend the law all the time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D25"
msgid "Ah, shit. That... that won't be necessary. I gotta go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D26"
msgid "Okay, here's the thing..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D27"
msgid "I need some more information."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D28"
msgid "Perfect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D29"
msgid "Good to see you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D2A"
msgid "I feel like this is a sensitive subject. It may be good for you to talk about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D2B"
msgid "You said you were injured on a job before?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010522E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D2C"
msgid "Well, I can't pay you, obviously. Maybe next time our fortunes will change. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010522E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D2D"
msgid "*Sigh* We just lost out on some serious money. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C84D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D39"
msgid "I can't tell you how much I appreciate what you did."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C452]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D3A"
msgid "It's good to see you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C3ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D3B"
msgid "You been in a scrap? Need that ship patched up? Well I'm your gal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C3EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D3C"
msgid "Need something for your ship? I can get you fixed up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D3D"
msgid "Oh, hey! You talk to Maddie yet? She's looking for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D3E"
msgid "Welcome to our little corner of the starfield. Can I set you up with a drink?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102672B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D3F"
msgid "People come to Anchorpoint for a quiet drink and some privacy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059E36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D40"
msgid "Quite a brave thing you did, taking on those Spacers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026728]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D41"
msgid "You can use the workbenches, but don't make a mess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026725]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D42"
msgid "Surprised this place is still in one piece."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102671C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D43"
msgid "It's out there, all around us... space... deadly space..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026715]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D44"
msgid "I can treat your injuries, but don't expect sympathy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026714]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D45"
msgid "You lost? Or just too drunk to realize this isn't the bar?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026712]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D46"
msgid "I hope you're not here to waste my time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102670F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D47"
msgid "Valeria can hook you up with a drink. Just don't overdo it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102670A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D48"
msgid "Whatever brought you here is none of my business."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D49"
msgid "I don't know if I trust Maddie's pet robot. It used to be a combat model."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D4A"
msgid "Did I say something upsetting?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D4B"
msgid "Tick tock! Let's go!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDCE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D4C"
msgid "You have the look of someone deep in thought."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D4D"
msgid "Um..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDF9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D4E"
msgid "Good talk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDF7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D4F"
msgid "Go on then, get out of here. I've got work to do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDEA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D50"
msgid "Oh, we're done?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDE2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D51"
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D52"
msgid "Back to work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D53"
msgid "I still think we should consider evacuating."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D54"
msgid "None. The warning was vague, probably to keep us off-balance and afraid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A519]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D55"
msgid "How are you keeping solvent with such a remote location?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A532]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D56"
msgid "What services are offered here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A521]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D57"
msgid "I know a smuggler's den when I see one, but don't worry, I won't blow your cover."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A539]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D58"
msgid "Fair enough. Sorry to imply otherwise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A533]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D59"
msgid "What exactly goes on here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D5A"
msgid "My head of security can fill you in on the details."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D5B"
msgid "Oh? Consider your offer accepted."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D5C"
msgid "Not everyone loves the bustle and noise of a large spaceport, after all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D5D"
msgid "A place to rest, refuel and stock up on supplies while enjoying a little privacy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A523]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D5E"
msgid "A man who remembers faces must have a reason for doing so."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D5F"
msgid "Still feel guilty about that part."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D60"
msgid "I got caught and the local Ranger locked me up. My parents lost their jobs."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D61"
msgid "Got to a point where I needed better parts, so I started stealing them from transport ships."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D62"
msgid "As a kid, I was always tinkering. I started building robots out of dumpster parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D63"
msgid "I grew up in HopeTown. Parents were engineers. They worked for the company, like everyone else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C02D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D64"
msgid "You said Rishi helped you out. What happened?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C025]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D65"
msgid "That, plus Rishi helped me out when I was in a bad spot, so I kind of owe him one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C025]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D66"
msgid "I like it here. Place keeps me busy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C011]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D67"
msgid "Maybe I should go back to my ship, where it's safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C029]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D68"
msgid "Maybe I should go back to my ship where it's safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C016]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D69"
msgid "What do you mean by \"barely holding together?\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C024]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D6A"
msgid "I'll be careful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D6B"
msgid "That's very generous."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031424]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D6C"
msgid "Glad we've got Chan and his guards around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031424]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D6D"
msgid "They said something about coming back real soon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031424]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D6E"
msgid "One ended up in the brig and the rest left in a huff."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031424]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D6F"
msgid "We had a dust-up with some Spacers who got out of hand."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031427]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D70"
msgid "If you're looking to do some business, you should check with him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031427]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D71"
msgid "My guess is those items aren't exactly legal, if you know what I mean."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031427]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D72"
msgid "Word is, Killian's looking to acquire some items of particular value."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031427]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D73"
msgid "I tend to keep my nose out of other peoples' business, but I did hear something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031425]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D74"
msgid "Give her some leeway, is all I'm saying. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031425]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D75"
msgid "There was some chem use and it took a toll."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031425]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D76"
msgid "Darcy's a good person, but she had a troubled youth. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031425]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D77"
msgid "Not exactly news, but I'll give you a heads-up anyway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031411]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D78"
msgid "Heard any interesting news lately?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031437]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D79"
msgid "You've got it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103142A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D7A"
msgid "Let's see what you've got."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031419]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D7B"
msgid "So, how can I help you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031419]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D7C"
msgid "In any case, you made the perilous journey to our little speck of light in the abyss. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D7D"
msgid "You seem nervous. Is everything okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031431]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D7E"
msgid "Space travel has risks, but it's nothing I can't handle."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D7F"
msgid "That way, I'll never have to look up at the night sky and be reminded of the terrors of space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D80"
msgid "Hopefully I can find a settlement on a planet where it's always day time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D81"
msgid "I do not want to be conscious for any space travel, no way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D82"
msgid "Of course, I'll probably have to take something to knock myself out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D83"
msgid "Oh, sure! Once I've saved up enough money, I'm going to book passage on a ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D84"
msgid "Very well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_DialogueAnchorpoint_CuttySharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D85"
msgid "Here. Make it quick."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FD0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D86"
msgid "I trust that if I keep up my end of the bargain, he'll keep up his."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FD0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D87"
msgid "Ours is a business relationship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D88"
msgid "I was grateful for the extended hand of friendship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D89"
msgid "Nobody else was. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D8A"
msgid "If you change your mind, you know where I'll be."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D8B"
msgid "Well, it ain't everyone who's got a sense of adventure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037165]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D8C"
msgid "They'll never know what hit them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D8D"
msgid "Tough break for you, then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037164]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D8E"
msgid "And you need me to acquire some of these prototype robot parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D8F"
msgid "Anyway, just thought you should know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D90"
msgid "If you mention me, I'm not sure how he'll react. It might be better not to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D91"
msgid "My son and I had a falling out. We haven't spoken in years."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D92"
msgid "There's one more thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104048B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D93"
msgid "But thank you. Sincerely."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104048B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D94"
msgid "Sorry if I seem a little in shock. Most people around here don't stick their neck out for others."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104048B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D95"
msgid "You would do that? Really?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D96"
msgid "Never mind. Forget I asked."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104048C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D97"
msgid "Text"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D98"
msgid "*Sigh* Maybe... maybe you're right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D99"
msgid "What are you, a psychiatrist?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D9A"
msgid "Talking about a problem is the first step in solving it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D9B"
msgid "I'll take a look at what you've got."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E5F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D9C"
msgid "I'm not really looking to buy anything right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104714B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D9D"
msgid "Other interested parties?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047149]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D9E"
msgid "I neither need, nor want, to know more than that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047149]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000D9F"
msgid "Compounds such as these can be mixed into all manner of lethal toxins and recreational substances."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047149]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA0"
msgid "It's bad for business to ask such questions, but it's not hard to guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA1"
msgid "After all this time, it's impressive the place is still in one piece."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA2"
msgid "You had it towed? That couldn't have been cheap."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA3"
msgid "But of course, the simplest minds are always the easiest to entertain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA4"
msgid "A Ranger, then? Well, I'm happy to have provided you with some amusement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA5"
msgid "Big embezzling scandal at Vanguard. We had a good laugh about it at the Rock."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA6"
msgid "I wasn't going to say anything, but yeah, I know who you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F28]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA7"
msgid "Here we go. Kinda knew this was coming."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA8"
msgid "But paying off those medical bills is no small thing, so maybe it's a fair trade."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DA9"
msgid "On the one hand, he's taking advantage of a desperate mother."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DAA"
msgid "I'm not sure how I feel about that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A5D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DAB"
msgid "Yep! See for yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A4C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DAC"
msgid "Have you got any ships for sale?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A61]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DAD"
msgid "I'd like to view and modify my ships."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DAE"
msgid "You do that. I ain't going anywhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DAF"
msgid "I'll get those parts for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106574C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB0"
msgid "Just so I have the details straight, what's the job again?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065758]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB1"
msgid "Yes, and it's a good thing you asked. I was concerned others might get there first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065757]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB2"
msgid "I'm glad you asked. I have indeed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065742]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB3"
msgid "I'll get that shipment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065741]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB4"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106611B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB5"
msgid "Now please hurry. My son's life is in your hands."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB6"
msgid "You're right, of course, but maybe they can be the first small steps down a long road."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB7"
msgid "You look different."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB8"
msgid "So, uh... how have you been otherwise? Does this place keep you busy?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C447]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DB9"
msgid "Why not send one of your people?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C447]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DBA"
msgid "And give up Anchorpoint? Hell no!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DBB"
msgid "Got a few things here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DBC"
msgid "That's all. Now get out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DF6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DBD"
msgid "You haven't got the money. Stop wasting my time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031F0C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DBE"
msgid "Later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031ADD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DBF"
msgid "See ya."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC0"
msgid "I get that military service isn't for everybody. But it's right for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F7B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC1"
msgid "I'm going to enlist in the Vanguard. I don't care what that old codger thinks, it's important."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC2"
msgid "Well, the work goes on."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC3"
msgid "One less patient to worry about at least."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030706]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC4"
msgid "There's a lot of work still to do, but I can't ignore the emotional toll this had on the group. People need a break."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031697]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC5"
msgid "I guess it's business as usual then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043B16]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC6"
msgid "I will honor the choice of the group and do my best to keep this outpost alive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043B7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC7"
msgid "This may be poetic justice, to be left here with nothing, just as they were."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC8"
msgid "Losing Hal is a big loss. I'm not sure about our future here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DC9"
msgid "If this outpost fails, we'll all know why."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DCA"
msgid "He's dead. Finally dead..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DCB"
msgid "It's been a while since I've worked at an outpost, but I feel confident I can be of use."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DCC"
msgid "The future of New Babylon is looking bright."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DCD"
msgid "The people here voted wisely. I hope the execution is long and painful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DCE"
msgid "A vote, bah! Anything other than execution is a waste of time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043AFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DCF"
msgid "This is stupid! Hal is innocent! And I'm gonna make sure he's free."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD0"
msgid "I'd love to see a hanging."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD1"
msgid "I did not have this on my bingo card, I'll tell you that much."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031116]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD2"
msgid "Lead the way. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030766]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD3"
msgid "What will you do if I don't fix the robot?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010215E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD4"
msgid "No..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD5"
msgid "Well, it's true she's a round peg trying to fit in a square hole. And by round, I mean a cactus."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103071C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD6"
msgid "I have a plan, but let's handle the matter of the robot first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD7"
msgid "He killed Hal! You understand? He fucking killed him! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E32A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD8"
msgid "I'm not comfortable making this decision. You make it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E326]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DD9"
msgid "Exonerate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E32D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DDA"
msgid "The floor is yours. What say you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103F3BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DDB"
msgid "What? Are you saying Caruso will kill me? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103F3BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DDC"
msgid "If you go there, there's a chance you will die. I've seen it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103FAF1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DDD"
msgid "Yes. But I only have one vote. The others may feel differently."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103FAF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DDE"
msgid "I do, and I've done my best to sway the others to vote the same. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103FAF2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DDF"
msgid "No, I've changed my mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103FAEF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE0"
msgid "Indeed. When we first met, you said imprisonment or exile should be my punishment. Do you still feel that way?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE1"
msgid "He was my mentor. My friend! You don't deserve to live."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105136F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE2"
msgid "No, I would rather you speak His scripture, provided you still remember, \"Promised.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051368]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE3"
msgid "Perhaps your companion would prefer to elaborate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105136C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE4"
msgid "And while we're not looking to start anything, we will if we have to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105136B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE5"
msgid "And this is what we call the \"find out\" stage of things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052C8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE6"
msgid "I think absolutes are dangerous in a galaxy full of nuance, but I see your point."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052C8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE7"
msgid "Well, I know one robot who would take umbrage with that philosophy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE8"
msgid "It's okay. It's going to take time to process."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "000DE9"
msgid "If by \"roaming free,\" you mean roaming the bowels of hell, then yes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C20]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010C3"
msgid "Your face is weird."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C1F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010C4"
msgid "Did you die? That's cool."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BEB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010C5"
msgid "Figures. I really need to install a toll booth in front of me. At least then you'd have to pay to bother me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010C6"
msgid "Mm-hm."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010C7"
msgid "Look at you, saving the day, doing stuff. Hooray."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010C8"
msgid "I feel like you want me to say something. Joke's on you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010C9"
msgid "Do you have any pets? Fungi can be a pet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010CA"
msgid "The thought of happy people keeps me up at night."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D83]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010CB"
msgid "You know how people get butterflies in their stomach? I have spiders."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D82]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010CC"
msgid "Some words are just fun to say. Like macabre."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D80]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010CD"
msgid "I need more gloom in my life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010CE"
msgid "I want to explore planets with gigantic fungi. That is all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010CF"
msgid "So when do things get weird. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D0"
msgid "Where to, Captain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D1"
msgid "Huh. Didn't think you were still around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D2"
msgid "After you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D3"
msgid "Well, see you around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D4"
msgid "Look at all the dead things. Very macabre."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D5"
msgid "Death makes me happy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D6"
msgid "That's a hit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D7"
msgid "You're dead. Lucky you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D8"
msgid "Well, those sure are words."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010D9"
msgid "I'm not wearing your clothes. It's weird. And not the good kind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010DA"
msgid "You can keep whatever clothes you find while we're adventuring."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C03]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010DB"
msgid "What about your parents? What were they like?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010DC"
msgid "Seems inappropriate, but okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B61]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010DD"
msgid "I guess. I'm an only child. I like to think I was part of group, and I murdered all the other children in the womb."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010DE"
msgid "Can you tell me about your life before we met?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010DF"
msgid "Not often I have human ones like you. Let's call it a trial phase though. I'm still sorting out the side effects."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E0"
msgid "We can go visit them if you want. I have the coordinates, somewhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E1"
msgid "They're still in orbit. Going in circles, just like their logic."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C09]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E2"
msgid "Nice. Now I can go back to whatever I was doing before you interrupted me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C07]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E3"
msgid "Cool."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C06]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E4"
msgid "Thank god."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E5"
msgid "I bet it smells awful too, but I have no idea. I've only seen pictures."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E6"
msgid "My favorite fungus is this Old Earth mushroom called a Bleeding Tooth. It's gross and looks like gingivitis."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E7"
msgid "I'd like to know more about your life before we met. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E8"
msgid "I can relate. I die a little inside whenever we speak."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010E9"
msgid "When you take out a loan, it's a lot like making a contract with a demon. Only as a banker, your contract is backed by GalBank's institutional guarantee."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B80]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010EA"
msgid "How is banking similar to practicing necromancy?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C49]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010EB"
msgid "Is there anywhere you want to visit?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010EC"
msgid "That'd be awesome, but those don't exist either. Believe me, I've done the research."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010ED"
msgid "Yeah? Is this one of those cults I hear so much about? I hope you at least got cool robes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010EE"
msgid "Figures. I really need to install a toll booth in front of me. At least then you'd have to pay to bother me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010EF"
msgid "All right. Guess I'll gather my potions and head to my post. You do have a post for me, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F0"
msgid "I never made the grav jump. I still have the corpses."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F1"
msgid "And then it occurred to me -- if I was gonna be surrounded by a bunch of dead people, it'd be cool if I could raise them as my personal army."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F2"
msgid "But yeah, I didn't want to meet the Great Serpent, so I volunteered to pilot the ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C3C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F3"
msgid "Would you be interested in traveling together? You sound like a perfect fit for my crew."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F4"
msgid "Would you? I've never worked on a crew before, but the idea does appeal to me. The older I get, the lonelier the void seems. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F5"
msgid "I appreciate the sentiment. Consider my interest piqued. I'd be happy to join you. I have a feeling this will be a fruitful partnership. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F6"
msgid "Wait here a moment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D38]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F7"
msgid "Does this come with hazard pay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F8"
msgid "I'll just stay here and decompose."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C32]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010F9"
msgid "Why didn't you want to meet the Great Serpent?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010FA"
msgid "Eh, it didn't seem like we'd have much in common. Would've been pretty awkward."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BF4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010FB"
msgid "I'd like you to follow me for a while."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010FC"
msgid "Yeah. You would like that, wouldn't you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010FD"
msgid "Okay, but I'm not your lapdog. Not at these rates anyway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010FE"
msgid "Aye-aye, Captain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0010FF"
msgid "Maybe not. But we all have to make compromises to get us through the work week."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B5D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001100"
msgid "Oh, the usual. Landscapes, mushrooms... the slow, inexorable march towards death. Stuff like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001101"
msgid "I'd like to see those paintings."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001102"
msgid "Why. I never said they were good paintings."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001103"
msgid "How about painting something bright and happy for a change."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001104"
msgid "Nah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B83]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001105"
msgid "I usually burn them when I'm finished. If they're not too terrible I'll take a picture before I do it though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001106"
msgid "As one does."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001109"
msgid "I can't take this anymore..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00110A"
msgid "Can't get away... I can't escape..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00110B"
msgid "The eyes... they're everywhere..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00110C"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B167]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00110D"
msgid "Time for some serious carnage!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00110E"
msgid "No mercy! Attack!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00110F"
msgid "I'll avenge you, my brothers!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001110"
msgid "Please provide immediate assistance if possible."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001111"
msgid "Our ship has lost power and we are in danger. Please help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B171]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001112"
msgid "Battle positions! Show no mercy!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B16B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001113"
msgid "Say hello to my little friend!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B16A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001114"
msgid "You're not running away from me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B16A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001115"
msgid "Where do you think you're going, punk?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B179]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001116"
msgid "Our survival is at stake. Please help!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C46D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001117"
msgid "A third bogey just popped in. Time for some evasive maneuvers!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C472]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001118"
msgid "The hair on the back of my neck is prickling up, and that's never a good sign."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C472]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001119"
msgid "Does this look right to you? 'Cause it don't look right to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C471]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00111A"
msgid "Something definitely feels off here..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C471]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00111B"
msgid "I'm not seeing any ships. Are you sure the scanner readings are legit?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B96D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00111C"
msgid "Understood. Goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B96B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00111D"
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A30A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00111E"
msgid "Acknowledged. Stay safe out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A312]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00111F"
msgid "C'mon, don't leave me hanging. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A310]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001120"
msgid "Answer the hail."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C752]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001121"
msgid "A backpack."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C748]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001122"
msgid "A school bus. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C74A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001123"
msgid "Ding ding ding! Good answer! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C755]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001124"
msgid "A needle."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001125"
msgid "Some thoughts are fleeting, sure. But some, some you hold on to forever."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001126"
msgid "Wrong. Wrong, wrong, wrong. That's too bad."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D257]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001127"
msgid "Get over here! It's the end of the line!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001128"
msgid "The only evil one is the creator of this... thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001129"
msgid "I don't know if proud is the word I'd use. \"Exploited\" seems like a better fit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C818]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00112A"
msgid "I don't trust that guy one bit. He's a snake that'll turn on in the blink of an eye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00112B"
msgid "Do you want to go have a look inside?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00112C"
msgid "I do not think there is anyone aboard that ship. Anyone alive, that is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00112D"
msgid "Do you have a death wish, or something? Walk away. Now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD4A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00112E"
msgid "I just need... to rest for a while."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC45]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00112F"
msgid "I'm sure we could, as long as it's fair."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC4F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001130"
msgid "Are you always this cranky?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC51]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001131"
msgid "You know I can't just give up my ship, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC5E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001132"
msgid "You'd be surprised how often that works."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001133"
msgid "Just tell me where you need to go, and I'll take you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC3C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001134"
msgid "What I need is your ship. So give it to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC42]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001135"
msgid "Let's talk this through."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001136"
msgid "Not gonna happen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC47]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001137"
msgid "Move a muscle and I'll shoot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106480C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001138"
msgid "Why hello there. I'm sorry, I don't have time right now, but do keep in touch!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064806]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001139"
msgid "Gotta run. Let's catch up sometime."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064806]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00113A"
msgid "Oh hi! Good to see you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00113B"
msgid "I'm very disappointed in Hannah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00113C"
msgid "This is not the first time Miss Krause has been targeted by pirates."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065F9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00113D"
msgid "Hannah will remain on the ship to make sure no one thinks it's abandoned."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065F9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00113E"
msgid "You'll be taking me to New Atlantis, so I can report this attack to headquarters in person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065F9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00113F"
msgid "What do I get for helping you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001140"
msgid "Crew members fought them off, but they were all killed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001141"
msgid "A few pirates from the first ship we encountered managed to get on board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01069D93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001142"
msgid "Thanks again for taking me with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068036]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001143"
msgid "Thanks, I appreciate it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106802B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001144"
msgid "You will? Oh, thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068026]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001145"
msgid "Let me think about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B990]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001147"
msgid "Critical systems unresponsive. All personnel, please evacuate the ship at your earliest convenience."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001149"
msgid "Don't worry, I'm keeping my mouth shut."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00114A"
msgid "Oh but if things take a turn, we're following my lead this time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00114B"
msgid "Just remember, if we run into any trouble, I do the talking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF22]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00114C"
msgid "I caught a job for a delivery if you want to tag along. Not sure how legit it really is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CECF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00114D"
msgid "Feel like doing anything?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00114E"
msgid "Hopefully not too soon. I hate leaving Milli alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00114F"
msgid "It's not like I don't have my own expenses."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001150"
msgid "Are you serious? Didn't I just give you some?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001151"
msgid "Not to mention this mess is mostly yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001152"
msgid "I could but you're literally right here, doing nothing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001153"
msgid "What an insufferable woman. The sooner we get her to New Atlantis, the better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A501]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001154"
msgid "Thank you for taking us out of that mess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001155"
msgid "Should I check to see if Miss Krause is okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001156"
msgid "Can't we just fly away as fast as we can?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064397]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001157"
msgid "However, you'll have to come aboard our ship to help us get out of the cockpit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064397]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001158"
msgid "The VP of Acquisitions will reward you handsomely once she's been taken to safety."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064395]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001159"
msgid "You'll have to come aboard, however. We seem to have locked ourselves in the cockpit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064395]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00115A"
msgid "If you could take the VP of Acquisitions to a safe location that would be great!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106802A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00115B"
msgid "Please don't shoot! The VP of Acquisitions for the GalBank consortium is on this ship!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00115C"
msgid "That's a GalBank ship those pirates are after. If they make it through the mines, that is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00115D"
msgid "Not if I can help it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00115E"
msgid "Good luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_DialogueAnchorpoint_TigerSharedInfo_Grumble
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00115F"
msgid "Grumble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080464]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001160"
msgid "Something tells me it didn't wait for us to be five hundred meters away. More like three hundred."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080461]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001161"
msgid "I'm getting too old for this. I think next time I'll just stay on the ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080457]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001162"
msgid "Now why would you go and do that? We don't know how well that distance checker is working."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C391]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001163"
msgid "Oh, that was a close one. Make sure to go *around* the mines."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001164"
msgid "I do not think I am ready to meet the Great Serpent just yet. We should turn around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C390]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001165"
msgid "I do not think I am ready to meet my maker yet. We should turn around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080470]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001166"
msgid "I hope this is worth the risk. All it takes is one stray mine..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001167"
msgid " The bulkhead behind me is going to blow, I just know it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001168"
msgid "It's that creaking noise again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001169"
msgid "Unless you want Valeria serving frozen drinks to a bunch of human popsicles, you're going to have to pony up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00116A"
msgid "Ain't much to consider. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A49]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00116B"
msgid "Hey Rishi. Give me some money."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00116C"
msgid "The cost in lives is the one that concerns me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00116D"
msgid "There's more than one kind of cost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00116E"
msgid "Let's end the discussion on that positive note, shall we?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00116F"
msgid "I have every confidence in you and your team, Chan."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001170"
msgid "Our focus should be on cutting costs, not raising them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001171"
msgid "Let me stop you there. The answer is no."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059ACA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001172"
msgid "You're a good egg. I appreciate it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054568]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001173"
msgid "You make it so I can get him to New Atlantis and I'll split it with you. I'll even front you the split. Save you a trip to New Atlantis. Fair?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054568]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001174"
msgid "Look, I'm not exactly swimming in credits right now, but this bounty's worth a decent amount."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105456C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001175"
msgid "What's in it for me if I help you out?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054566]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001176"
msgid "Sorry, but I've got my own issues to deal with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001177"
msgid "Just get the hell out of here before someone less generous realizes you're an easy target."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001178"
msgid "Was there something else?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105357E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001179"
msgid "You know I'm a married woman, yes?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105357A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00117A"
msgid "Sorry, we're all out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053575]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00117B"
msgid "Just looking around for now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE03]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00117C"
msgid "I expected as much. Fanisha has new wares for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE02]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00117D"
msgid "Sure. Fanisha's in the back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDFF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00117E"
msgid "Yup. Fanisha's waiting for you in the back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00117F"
msgid "Good choice! Just go see Fanisha in the back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE0D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001180"
msgid "What can I do for you, sugar pie?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001181"
msgid "Only the best and freshest!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053573]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001182"
msgid "Sure. Next time we can even deliver these to your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001183"
msgid "Aha! Here comes our best customer! Welcome back!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105356F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001184"
msgid "Tell me what you need, friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001185"
msgid "Okay, you know where to find me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C825]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001186"
msgid "Are you buying anything?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C81F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001187"
msgid "These two are true pioneers if you ask me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001188"
msgid "Anything else I can do for you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F912]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001189"
msgid "Let's see what you have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00118A"
msgid "Anything else we can offer you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00118B"
msgid "We're glad our paths crossed again, traveler. What do you need today?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EEF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00118C"
msgid "Don't miss out on our special deals!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00118D"
msgid "I better go with you, you know, in case I see something I like."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00118E"
msgid "How intriguing. What do you suppose those \"specials\" are?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B394]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001190"
msgid "Go grab a drink or something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B38B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001191"
msgid "Do enjoy the party."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Youtwoarebeingnoisy
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001192"
msgid "You're being noisy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Myheadispounding
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001193"
msgid "My head is pounding."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001194"
msgid "You should really take a seat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B39F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001195"
msgid "Maybe you should sit down?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B39E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001196"
msgid "What are you? Drunk?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B39B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001197"
msgid "Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B439]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001198"
msgid "Having fun? I know I am."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B41F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001199"
msgid "Why did Sawyer let this happen?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B417]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00119A"
msgid "I'm done talking, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B416]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00119B"
msgid "I'm just ready to get home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00119C"
msgid "This isn't a good time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00119D"
msgid "Everyone, look out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00119E"
msgid "Hey!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B37F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00119F"
msgid "I'm getting real tired of these machines."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B37D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A0"
msgid "How do we turn these damn things off?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_PG_WhatsGoingOnWithTheShip
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A1"
msgid "What's going on with the ship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B36D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A2"
msgid "This wasn't your smartest idea."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B36A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A3"
msgid "You can still walk away."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B369]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A4"
msgid "I won't let you hurt us anymore!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B350]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A5"
msgid "Sadie, why is this happening?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Wren_PleaseStopThis
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A6"
msgid "Please. Stop this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B349]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A7"
msgid "Why are you doing this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Sadie_BeCareful
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A8"
msgid "Be careful!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B33C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011A9"
msgid "You're making this party too exciting for my taste."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Opal_WhatDoWeDo
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011AA"
msgid "What do we do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B332]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011AB"
msgid "Sawyer really should be careful of who he invites."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B32E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011AC"
msgid "Hurgh!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B32A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011AD"
msgid "Sadie... Wren..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B31E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011AE"
msgid "Dammit. Dammit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B30F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011AF"
msgid "Thanks for that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B309]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B0"
msgid "I'm hit!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E257]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B1"
msgid "We're going home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E29C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B2"
msgid "I guess I did in a way, but didn't think it was that bad. I thought she was playing around. Damn."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E259]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B3"
msgid "What all has she said? You should have told me sooner."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E259]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B4"
msgid "What? But you said-..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E262]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B5"
msgid "We've talked about this. I didn't do anything. Why would I be mean to Wren?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E230]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B6"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E1FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B7"
msgid "Okay. I should really get back to Anchorpoint. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B8"
msgid "But what am I meant to do? Opal and Sadie have been best friends for years. I can't destroy that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E21A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011B9"
msgid "She never talks to anyone and doesn't even do anything. I don't understand why she bothered coming today."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E21A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011BA"
msgid "Gossip, huh? Well, don't tell Sadie or Cooper, but you're better off if you avoid Wren. She's that sad-looking girl in the corner. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E227]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011BB"
msgid "Have fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E29B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011BC"
msgid "Sounds great. I'm going to go enjoy myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E205]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011BD"
msgid "Don't thank me. Sawyer was the one with the idea to bring you here. You're on his ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E270]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011BE"
msgid "AKA, he got back into his parents' good graces and they paid it off for him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E26F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011BF"
msgid "Ah, they'll be around later. But for now, we could always use another? It's no fun to celebrate if you can't bring others into it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C0"
msgid "Dusty, you're back! I thought you got swallowed by a quasar the way you blipped out with those partiers. You must've had a wild time. You can tell me all about it later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C1"
msgid "There you are. Last I saw you, you left with Sawyer and his friends. I wasn't sure when you'd return, but it's a relief that you're back now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E200]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C2"
msgid "Should be any moment. But their loss. We get to start the party early."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C3"
msgid "You should listen to this slate I found."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C4"
msgid "You heard that rumor too? Trust me. I've talked with Wren and Opal, and neither say anything is going on. So, don't spread that around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C5"
msgid "Wren and Opal have both told me nothing like that is going on. So, you can put that idea to rest."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C6"
msgid "Who told you that? I've been hearing it around, but trust me, none of it is true."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B29E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C7"
msgid "I just set up the security system. See the turrets around the ship? That's them. It was nothing special, but Sawyer did pay well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B29E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C8"
msgid "Is that what you heard? It's not like I built this ship from the ground up, or decorated the place. All this is a bit too rich for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011C9"
msgid "In terms of fun? Yes. In terms of style? When I could afford it. But now, with my parent's credits flowing into my pockets, I plan to make every party better than the last."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011CA"
msgid "Sadie needs to know the truth."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011CB"
msgid "I'm tired of acting like it's me. I've done nothing to her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B291]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011CC"
msgid "Not very much. I only came because of Sadie, Opal, and Wren. I can't stand Sawyer or his get-togethers all that much. They're too loud and obnoxious."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011CD"
msgid "The longer you keep quiet about this, the hard it will be talk about it in the future."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011CE"
msgid "Even if that's true, I don't know you. Why would I discuss this with you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011CF"
msgid "I know that but... It's not something I can just talk about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B29D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D0"
msgid "If she wasn't then she wouldn't have said what she said in this slate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B287]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D1"
msgid "I thought I told you to leave me alone. Just go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B306]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D2"
msgid "How long have you and Opal been dating?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D3"
msgid "No. She would never do that. Opal's been friends with everyone for years. Everyone except me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D4"
msgid "I'm not saying it's fine. It's just- You wouldn't get it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B302]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D5"
msgid "Stop talking like you know what's going on. You don't."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B304]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D6"
msgid "You don't understand any of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B303]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D7"
msgid "It's not that simple..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D8"
msgid "If you don't tell anyone, Opal won't leave you alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E23D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011D9"
msgid "Wait. What time is it? Hey, Sawyer, we got to go meet up with Sadie and the others soon. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E247]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011DA"
msgid "Opal, get a load of our new friend!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D60D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011DB"
msgid "So you're the one Opal and Sawyer found? Hope you're planning on behaving yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D68F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011DC"
msgid "Wait. I changed my mind. I don't want to leave yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D68A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011DD"
msgid "I'll start a course."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D680]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011DE"
msgid "I don't talk much either. Mostly I listen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D690]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011DF"
msgid "Anyway, the name's Sadie. If you ever need a moment of peace, feel free to come and talk. I don't care to get too drunk at these things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D6A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011E0"
msgid "I wouldn't say I'm his friend. I hardly know the guy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D67C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011E1"
msgid "I'm more worried about Opal and Sawyer behaving themselves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D68E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011E2"
msgid "I heard Opal and Sawyer found you. So I doubt that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D6A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011E3"
msgid "I'm at a party. We'll see."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011ED"
msgid "Life sucks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo07
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011EE"
msgid "Turn around and go back to your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo11
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011EF"
msgid "Whatever you do, do not come up to the bridge!"
msgstr "무슨 일이 있어도 함교에는 오지 마!"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D02B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F0"
msgid "I'm ready when you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104077A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F1"
msgid "I'd rather not, if that's possible."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040750]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F2"
msgid "I don't care what happens to me or to anyone else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104076B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F3"
msgid "Not right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040771]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F4"
msgid "I guess I might as well tell you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040752]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F5"
msgid "I can't let you put yourself and others in danger, you understand?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104074E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F6"
msgid "Tell me how a teenager ended up alone on this ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104089C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F7"
msgid "I appreciate it, I just... It's complicated."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040779]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F8"
msgid "And why should I trust you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040776]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011F9"
msgid "Do you want to hear my story or not?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040765]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011FA"
msgid "Yeah, I guess you would know..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104075C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011FB"
msgid "I can spare food or water if needed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040763]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011FC"
msgid "Now you sound just like my school counselor. No thanks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104089E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011FD"
msgid "Look, I don't care that much either way. I just want to help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D028]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011FE"
msgid "Oh yeah. I'm sure my stepfather won't be angry with me for stealing his prized ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0011FF"
msgid "Space is dangerous, maybe it's best to go back to your father?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D01A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001200"
msgid "Do you need anything else before I go?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D025]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001201"
msgid "You should leave before my stepfather arrives. He's not a nice man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D01E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001202"
msgid "In fact, if you could take me to New Atlantis that'd be awesome."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D01E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001203"
msgid "Uh...yeah, I do want that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001204"
msgid "Thank you again for helping me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DAC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001205"
msgid "I can't wait to get some new clothes. This spacesuit stinks!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DAC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001206"
msgid "Thank you for doing this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C505]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001207"
msgid "On Va'ruun'kai this would never have been tolerated."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C508]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001208"
msgid "Told you she sounded young. I'm surprised she made it that far, to be honest!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001209"
msgid "I can see you, but I can't hear you..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00120A"
msgid "Safe travels."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00120B"
msgid "Hey, I just wanted to thank you for helping me out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C501]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00120C"
msgid "Perhaps we should board the ship to make sure everyone is actually fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C501]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00120D"
msgid "Is it me, or did that pilot seem very young to you too?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C500]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00120E"
msgid "Maybe we oughta pay her a visit, you know? Just to make sure she's okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C500]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00120F"
msgid "That sounded like a teenager...couldn't be much older than Cora. Kinda odd, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001210"
msgid "Maybe we should board the ship anyway?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001211"
msgid "That pilot sounded very young, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001212"
msgid "Something's not right. We should investigate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001213"
msgid "Was that a child speaking?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106F5EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001214"
msgid "Hey there, if you can hear me...we're fine! We don't need anything!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001216"
msgid "You're not hurt, are you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001217"
msgid "No, I wasn't specific about who sent me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001218"
msgid "I suppose it's just as well. No need to re-open old wounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001219"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00121A"
msgid "In any case, what matters is that Miles is out of danger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00121B"
msgid "I'm sorry if that went badly. I was hoping to avoid dragging you into any family drama."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00121C"
msgid "You did?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00121D"
msgid "Your son is safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00121E"
msgid "I just don't know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00121F"
msgid "Maybe my doubts were unfounded."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBF9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001220"
msgid "Thanks for the self-help lesson, but I'm really not interested."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBF4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001221"
msgid "I admit, I think about that myself sometimes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001222"
msgid "I suspect your father's guilt won't let him reach out. It's up to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BC01]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001223"
msgid "I'm the victim here. I'm the one who's owed an apology."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBF0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001224"
msgid "That goes both ways."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001225"
msgid "The fact we're family just makes everything harder."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001226"
msgid "Believe it or not, I do have some good family memories. They just got buried."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001227"
msgid "Do it for yourself. To prove that you can."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001228"
msgid "We both made our choices and now we have to live with them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001229"
msgid "I know what you're trying to say, but it doesn't change anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00122A"
msgid "What happened? I'm involved now, so I have a right to know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040496]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00122B"
msgid "He left the very next day, and cut off all contact. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040496]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00122C"
msgid "His hubris cost both of their lives."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040496]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00122D"
msgid "He demanded to do the surgery, but it wasn't his area of expertise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040496]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00122E"
msgid "My wife was about to give birth and there were complications. The life-threatening kind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040496]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00122F"
msgid "He was a doctor, well-respected but arrogant."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001230"
msgid "I understand not getting along with your old man, but that's... yeah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001231"
msgid "Damn. Can't imagine how hard that must have been."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C419]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001232"
msgid "What's going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C428]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001233"
msgid "We won't be any trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedShipHello02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001234"
msgid "We'll see you on board, then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052B6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001235"
msgid "I'll let the captain know you're coming aboard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001236"
msgid "Do you think you could at least fly us out of here? Our cockpit is damaged and, well, we're all shaken up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001237"
msgid "It would've been nice to have some help back there. Now our... *sigh* Our pilot has been killed.  "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001238"
msgid "Could you fly us home? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001239"
msgid "We would've appreciated your help back there. Now our ship is torn to bits. I'm not sure if we'll be able to fly out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C40F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00123A"
msgid "Any idea why those Spacers targeted you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E24B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00123B"
msgid "Of course. You know, I always wanted a ship like that. This one was fine, sure, but yours just has that... I don't know. Something special.  Something that makes you wanna fly it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E246]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00123C"
msgid "So you're the captain, huh? Ready to give us a ride?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EDFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00123D"
msgid "No, but you'll forgive me if I'm shaken up after almost getting blasted apart by spacers. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00123E"
msgid "Sorry, it's just been a bad day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00123F"
msgid "*Sigh* Hold on. That was uncalled for. I'm being a jerk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C416]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001240"
msgid "Let's just get a move on. We're wasting time here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C415]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001241"
msgid "Can't believe it. I put my heart and soul into this ship, and all of my hard work - poof."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C415]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001242"
msgid "Well, welcome aboard, I guess. Feels weird saying that, seeing as how it's little more than scrap, now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001243"
msgid "No idea. How am I supposed to know what a Spacer is thinking? They're maniacs."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C438]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001244"
msgid "I'm just here to give you a ride."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001245"
msgid "*Sigh* I'm really not looking forward to all the paperwork after all of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001246"
msgid "I know. *Sigh* Can't wait for this all to be over."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001247"
msgid "Well, let's get a move on, I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001248"
msgid "Anyway, we're ready to leave whenever you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001249"
msgid "Kill them!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00124A"
msgid "Probably just had itchy trigger fingers and wanted to kill something. I can relate to that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00124B"
msgid "Just trying to make a living the only way they know how."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00124C"
msgid "You know, when we took over this ship I really thought we were home free. Karma, I guess. Damn Spacers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00124D"
msgid "To tell you the truth, we aren't really wasting any tears over him. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00124E"
msgid "Right back at you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00124F"
msgid "You have a hell of a ship. Gotta say, I'm jealous, what with my ship being in the state it's in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001250"
msgid "Oh, my crew and I will handle the flying. Least we can do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001251"
msgid "Heh, we appreciate all your help. There's just one thing left that we need from you. Your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D543]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00125E"
msgid "And now they're all mine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037175]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00125F"
msgid "I'll just take those off your hands, thank you very much."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D54F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001260"
msgid "Oh really?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D54E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001261"
msgid "That so?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D54C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001262"
msgid "Shame these parts are damaged. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D544]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001263"
msgid "And in pristine condition, no less."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_PasswordResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001264"
msgid "Now was that so hard?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_NoCreditsResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001265"
msgid "Looking forward to it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Atka_FreestarResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001266"
msgid "Yura actually outdid herself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Atka_FreestarResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001267"
msgid "Wow, I'll take your word for it then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Yura_SceneReentryRoman01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001268"
msgid "Seriously, what was Roman thinking?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_PlayerRefusedHelp01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001269"
msgid "The way I see it, you've got two choices: pay up or get the hell out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_PlayerRefusedHelp01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00126A"
msgid "Oh yeah, well if I recall, you don't have the credits. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B447]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00126B"
msgid "It's gonna be a good time spending these credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B43B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00126C"
msgid "Nice doing business."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00126D"
msgid "Roman's in the back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00126E"
msgid "Hope you got those credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00126F"
msgid "Roman can clear this all up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D61]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001270"
msgid "Roman's the one you want to talk to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001271"
msgid "Atka left all the info you need on her counter."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001272"
msgid "Got a sec?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001273"
msgid "Time for some fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001274"
msgid "Are you serious?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001275"
msgid "I thought we had a deal!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001276"
msgid "Can this day get any worse?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035889]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001277"
msgid "Just toss a bunch of leaves in water and make more. Isn't that what you do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035889]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001278"
msgid "Oh not the plants again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103589E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001279"
msgid "Oh god, do I even want to know? How is he involved in this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00127A"
msgid "I wouldn't trust Yura to house sit for you anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035863]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00127B"
msgid "You can blame your friend Roman for us not being here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103588D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00127C"
msgid "And look, just in time. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00127D"
msgid "Atka, this is the pet sitter I told you about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A6E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00127E"
msgid "Check your numbers, \"errand runner.\" You're short."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035873]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00127F"
msgid "Imagine my surprise when not only did she beat me back here, but Milli was nowhere to be found."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001280"
msgid "If you would've stayed here, you wouldn't have this problem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001281"
msgid "Excuse me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035898]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001282"
msgid "A few more credits never hurt anyone, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035892]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001283"
msgid "[Lie] Just taking Milli for a walk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035874]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001284"
msgid "As you can see, Atka decided to come home earlier than expected."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035874]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001285"
msgid "Never mind. Focus..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035874]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001286"
msgid "Petnapped? Are you kidding me? Who would even want that little bottom feeder? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103585F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001287"
msgid "You got it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C859]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001288"
msgid "Hello, back me up here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035893]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001289"
msgid "Oh hey, finally interested in that house sitting gig? It's not too late you know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00128A"
msgid "I'm here to negotiate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035894]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00128B"
msgid "[Lie] It really was just a walk. Milli is fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035883]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00128C"
msgid "[Pay <Global=SFFL_MS03_RansomCredits>] Here's your credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103586D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00128D"
msgid "Now it's definitely a \"no.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00128E"
msgid "Who--? Hmm... Come on in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103586F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00128F"
msgid "I don't house sit. Find someone else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103587F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001290"
msgid "That sounds too easy. What's the catch?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D5F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001291"
msgid "And I'm sure we can't."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103587B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001292"
msgid "I don't have time for this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001293"
msgid "Hmm, I don't know... "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001294"
msgid "I was hoping you could do me a wee teeny tiny favor."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001295"
msgid "So, I heard what you did for the station, taking out those Spacers, and since you look like you're on your way out..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001296"
msgid "She never mentioned any note."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001297"
msgid "You've got to be kidding me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001298"
msgid "You see, all this? It's just a setup. For her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001299"
msgid "I give you Milli... and you put in a good word for me with Yura. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00129A"
msgid "[Attack] Plan C. I'm taking Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00129B"
msgid "I'm sure you don't really want to do this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00129C"
msgid "[Attack] I like the option where I take what I want."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00129D"
msgid "If you give me Milli, I'll put in a good word for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00129E"
msgid "Here's the key to the room. That little bottom feeder's all yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00129F"
msgid "Hell yeah, you don't know what this means to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A0"
msgid "You'd do that after all this? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A1"
msgid "All these years of trying to build up the courage to ask her out, and I'm still screwing it up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A2"
msgid "I should've known she'd do something like this. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A3"
msgid "This isn't your fault. It's mine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A4"
msgid "But now I've lost that chance. So, plan B. I give you Milli, you put in a good word for me with Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A5"
msgid "And then when all went according to plan, I'd have the confidence to ask her out. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A6"
msgid "We figured she'd get into it, maybe even get the credits from Atka..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A7"
msgid "She hates house sitting. It's boring. So we thought why not liven things up?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A8"
msgid "I figured you'd still be at Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012A9"
msgid "We're talking about a milliwhale here, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012AA"
msgid "Here's the key to Milli's room. Just don't forget our deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012AB"
msgid "All right, all right, I'll pay you. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012AC"
msgid "I.. I thought it would show how much I care about her, but obviously, I've failed miserably."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012AD"
msgid "No, it's more than that. I wanted to put this all together to impress her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012AE"
msgid "Here's the key to Milli's room. Consider it an even trade."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012AF"
msgid "Heh, I guess I owe you now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B0"
msgid "I hate to say it, but you're right. I need to do this myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B1"
msgid "Don't tell them that. I'll never live it down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B2"
msgid "You bet we will. Lesson learned."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B3"
msgid "Of course she would've pawned this job off on someone else. I should've thought of that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B4"
msgid "You're kidding me. So Yura hasn't even seen the note?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B5"
msgid "Stealing someone's pet is a serious crime."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D1C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B6"
msgid "You got it. She's in the next room. Here's the key."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B7"
msgid "Atka didn't report this. I found your ransom note."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D06]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B8"
msgid "[Demand Credits: <Global=SFFL_MS03_PaymentCredits>] Don't make me repeat myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012B9"
msgid "Yura gets bored out of her mind house sitting, so we were going to stage a petnapping, you know, for fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012BA"
msgid "I knew Atka was going to be out of town and her sister Yura was going to get stuck watching Milli..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012BB"
msgid "We didn't really petnap Milli, we just sort of borrowed her... for a prank."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D4D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012BC"
msgid "What? Who even are you and what were you doing in Atka's house to begin with? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012BD"
msgid "Get in here and let's get this over with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D19]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012BE"
msgid "I'm here for Milli. Let me in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012BF"
msgid "Oh Cora would love this. Plants, pets, and a good book? She'd be all in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C0"
msgid "Obviously the favorite when it came to mom and dad. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C1"
msgid "Atka? I like to think of her as the anti-me: responsible, keeps to herself, excelling at everything she does..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C2"
msgid "What does this involve again?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C3"
msgid "I'm a Freestar Ranger, here about a stolen pet, so open up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C4"
msgid "House sitting? Really? There's a difference between easy and boring and I don't do boring."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C5"
msgid "I'm a pilot at heart so anything that involves running in the Free Lanes is the job for me, as long as the price is right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C6"
msgid "Live my life for one. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D4E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C7"
msgid "How long do I have to do this for?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C8"
msgid "Or just ignore me. That's fine. I'd have better things to do, too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A330]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012C9"
msgid "Please, just leave us. I think we need some space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A330]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012CA"
msgid "Roman and his friends were... misguided individuals, but I can't say they deserved this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A359]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012CB"
msgid "Roman likes you, Yura. He's just not sure how to tell you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B42F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012CC"
msgid "Roman and his friends didn't survive when I rescued Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A347]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012CD"
msgid "Finally, someone who actually agrees with me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A340]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012CE"
msgid "Ransom? Why would he even do that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A34D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012CF"
msgid "He was trying to earn a few credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B433]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D0"
msgid "You're not wrong..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A346]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D1"
msgid "Sounds like Roman, but why? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D2"
msgid "Can you tell me more about Yura?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D3"
msgid "What is Atka forgiving Yura for?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D4"
msgid "House sitting, obviously, dinner dates, jobs, you know... Atka's always trying to help her out, but she just doesn't get that Yura's not interested."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D5"
msgid "I feel like it's part of her charm, but yeah, she's always letting Atka down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D6"
msgid "Oh god, where do I begin? Yura's probably one of the least responsible people I've ever known."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D7"
msgid "Yura hired me to house sit, but it's obvious what's going on."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D8"
msgid "As a Freestar Ranger, I can guarantee she's fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012D9"
msgid "Only the best care for the rarest of milliwhales."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012DA"
msgid "That sucks for Roman. It's gonna take a while for him to get over it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012DB"
msgid "I've only got a million different things going through my head now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012DC"
msgid "I hope I don't screw this up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF0B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012DD"
msgid "Sorry you ended up involved in all that back there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Support_PostQuestRoman05_Shared
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012DE"
msgid "Hope that little critter wasn't too much trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Support_PostQuestRoman04_Shared
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012DF"
msgid "Glad you got Milli back safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E0"
msgid "Thanks for filling in for me again back then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E1"
msgid "Leave me alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E2"
msgid "Remember to put in a good word."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E3"
msgid "See you real soon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_PostIntro01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E4"
msgid "Did you talk to Yura? What'd she say? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E5"
msgid "What did we ever do to you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E6"
msgid "He really likes you, Yura. Give him a chance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E7"
msgid "How do you take care of a milliwhale?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E8"
msgid "I have a feeling you wouldn't disappoint Roman. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012E9"
msgid "That's just fear talking. If you like Roman, don't let fear keep you apart."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012EA"
msgid "I get that. Relationships aren't for everyone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012EB"
msgid "And with Yura spending all her time working in the Free Lanes... who knows what could happen to her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012EC"
msgid "Our parents died a few years ago in some freak accident traveling to Paradiso."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012ED"
msgid "Because she's my sister, and she's all I have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012EE"
msgid "I really only leave for the conferences. I'm a biologist, so I do all my work out here remotely."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012EF"
msgid "I basically keep to myself. People aren't really my thing, so I like it out here. Just me, Milli, and the plants."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F0"
msgid "Oh not much to tell really. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F1"
msgid "Can you tell me a little bit about yourself?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F2"
msgid "They're so docile and calm. I'm not sure anything bothers Milli at all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F3"
msgid "Milliwhale care is easy. All you really need to do is feed them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F4"
msgid "I guess I have a lot to think about thanks to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F5"
msgid "You know Yura. You'll know what to do when the time comes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F6"
msgid "You're on your own. I don't do relationship advice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F7"
msgid "*sigh* I know... I guess I was hoping we could work through those things together. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012F8"
msgid "Just be there for her. You mean a lot to her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C729]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012FA"
msgid "I guess I hoped if we had enough we could have grown gray in peace. Perfect life and all that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034F7B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012FB"
msgid "I'm sorry, it was an accident. Won't happen again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012FC"
msgid "You should get somewhere safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012FD"
msgid "Spacers are pushovers. I've got this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012FE"
msgid "If he stays, we stay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0012FF"
msgid "Mister Saint owns this place, and we have a contract."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001300"
msgid "I don't disagree with you, but that's not my call."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001301"
msgid "Oh, Gabrielle, what am I going to do...?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001302"
msgid "No, no, please! Come back!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001303"
msgid "You sound pretty desperate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056625]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001304"
msgid "Stop! I'm not here to fight!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035304]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001305"
msgid "R-Right. I... I will. If you come across her again, please, tell her I'm waiting."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001306"
msgid "What? Why wouldn't she want to be found? No. That doesn't make sense."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001307"
msgid "Just, if you do find her out there, let her know Sehoy is looking for her. Tell my love to come home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001308"
msgid "But what if she isn't? She should have been home long ago. I can't keep waiting on what if's."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056633]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001309"
msgid "You weren't much help there, were you? Why did you try to lie? You should have just told her the truth."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056632]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00130A"
msgid "Looks like she's smarter than you gave her credit for. Shame she still doesn't know the truth."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105662F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00130B"
msgid "What did you hope to accomplish by telling her that? Poor woman is going to be searching until she finds Gabrielle herself now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105662B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00130C"
msgid "What was the point in telling her that? Now she'll never end her search."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00130D"
msgid "It's just what she said. That's all I know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00130E"
msgid "I think you should just go home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056606]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00130F"
msgid "No. And I don't have time to look."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001310"
msgid "Thank you... Please. If you see her, tell her Sehoy is looking for her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105660C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001311"
msgid "You again? Please tell me you've seen Gabrielle."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001312"
msgid "I haven't. But I will keep an eye out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001313"
msgid "That's what you're gonna be, you bald-faced brigand!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001314"
msgid "Damn straight. Well, thanks stranger. Appreciate you clearing things up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001315"
msgid "Yeah, what's a smithereen?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001316"
msgid "Scammed? Goddamnit! I knew it was too good to be true! I paid way more for the other hunts!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001317"
msgid "Okay, I just need to figure out where the damn weapons system is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001318"
msgid "Those are some fighting words for sure. Honey, power up the weapons!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_KT02_SailingHighSeasSharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001319"
msgid "Prepare to die, pirate scum!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00131A"
msgid "We're gonna get you good!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064A57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00131B"
msgid "You don't know who you're messing with. You're so dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031725]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00131C"
msgid "Because I promise you, someone will."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031725]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00131D"
msgid "And when someone draws a gun on me over it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00131E"
msgid "And by the way, they have to do all that with spare parts and second-rate tools."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00131F"
msgid "You got someone who can replace faulty breakers, refurbish the air scrubbers or weld hull plates?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001320"
msgid "And while I make your robot guards, who's going to keep this place running?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE4B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001321"
msgid "Impossible... "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE47]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001322"
msgid "Eat. I do not want to see any leftovers. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE45]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001323"
msgid "I have plenty of food to go around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE42]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001324"
msgid "*Grunt*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001325"
msgid "I am envious. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001326"
msgid "Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001327"
msgid "Not all of them are harmless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001328"
msgid "What are you doing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001329"
msgid "Nice to meet you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030742]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00132A"
msgid "Eat! Eat! Eat!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030744]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00132B"
msgid "I'm getting out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00132C"
msgid "What's in the food?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00132D"
msgid "I'm not eating that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00132E"
msgid "Maybe I should be going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEE3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00132F"
msgid "Everything that is typically found in food. Calories, nutrients. Now eat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R02_TargetSpared_SharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001330"
msgid "Thank you. Thank you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050240]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001331"
msgid "Say something. Say something! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001332"
msgid "What's wrong with you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001333"
msgid "Remember, I need to see proof of death."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001334"
msgid "I've got some more work for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A435]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001335"
msgid "[Accept <Global=SFFL_R02_BribeAmount> Credits] Give me the credits and your ID, and don't ever show your face around here again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001336"
msgid "Don't do this! I'll give you all the credits I have! I'll disappear forever, I promise!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104609E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001337"
msgid "No, that can't be... what do you... oh shit, what do I do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044807]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001338"
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A437]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001339"
msgid "That concludes our transaction. You're free to go for now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A43A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00133A"
msgid "That's one less problem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00133B"
msgid "I have some other targets that need to be taken care of. Want the job?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00133C"
msgid "Are you that special someone? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00133D"
msgid "I'm not gonna beat around the bush. I'm looking for someone that is willing to kill people - people that may or may not deserve it - for money. No questions asked."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00133E"
msgid "Oh my... thank you, thank you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102AF65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00133F"
msgid "Thank you! Thank you! You'll never see me again!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001340"
msgid "[Attack] Not interested. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044802]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001341"
msgid "You won't be receiving payment this time. Now get out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044802]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001342"
msgid "And about the target you let go, I'll see to it that they're killed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044802]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001343"
msgid "If this happens again and I find out, that will be the end of our dealings together. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044801]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001344"
msgid "I'm paying you to kill people that I want dead. Whether or not they have a bounty on their head isn't my concern. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044801]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001345"
msgid "I have nothing to do with the Trackers Alliance. This is a contract between you and me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001346"
msgid "Once I figure out how to get out of here, you'll never see me again. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001347"
msgid "Someone really wants you dead, and sent me to kill you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001348"
msgid "I need someone that doesn't lie awake at night tortured after having to use their gun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001349"
msgid "Don't be obtuse. You know what I mean."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00134A"
msgid "We're done talking, then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00134B"
msgid "Works for me. I've done plenty of hits in my day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00134C"
msgid "\"Burdened by morality?\" What do you mean by that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059AB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00134D"
msgid "If that's the case, I guess I'll skip the preamble. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105911A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00134E"
msgid "You're leaving? You're just gonna come back and kill me when I least suspect it. I'm... I'm not gonna let that happen!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059119]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00134F"
msgid "I'm not just gonna stand stand around and let you kill me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F8F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001351"
msgid "Go get 'em."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029710]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001352"
msgid "Nice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010522E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001353"
msgid "I don't have the contraband. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029885]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001354"
msgid "Not interested. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001355"
msgid "Locations should be on your map, now. Careful out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001356"
msgid "That's music to my ears."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001357"
msgid "Nice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001358"
msgid "Not interested. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C455]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001359"
msgid "Interesting place, this. A little off the beaten path, but it's got character."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C453]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00135A"
msgid "I took your advice and got in touch with my dad."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059E3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00135B"
msgid "What are you looking at, scab?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00135C"
msgid "Pull up a seat!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00135D"
msgid "What'll it be?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00135E"
msgid "Hey there. What do you need?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00135F"
msgid "Good to see you again! By the way, Killian was looking for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102672E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001360"
msgid "See Valeria for a drink. The prices are fair."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102672D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001361"
msgid "Keep to yourself and don't ask too many questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065749]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001362"
msgid "Welcome back. Maddie was hoping to talk to you. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026727]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001363"
msgid "Hey, you want to hang back a little? I don't like people invading my space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026722]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001364"
msgid "It's said that a bargain is only fair when both sides are equally unhappy with it. I've always found that amusing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026721]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001365"
msgid "I'll consider any deal, but I make no promises about which ones I'll accept."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026716]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001366"
msgid "*Sigh* Another day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102670E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001367"
msgid "If you're looking to do some business, talk to Killian or Darcy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102670C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001368"
msgid "Firm, but fair. That's how we run this place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026706]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001369"
msgid "Sure, this place ain't fancy, but if you need to lay low, you can do a lot worse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00136A"
msgid "If you're looking for supplies, talk to Killian and Darcy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00136B"
msgid "Mister Saint calls the shots, so stay on his good side."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026701]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00136C"
msgid "Around here, we appreciate discretion."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065748]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00136D"
msgid "Oh, you're back. Killian wanted to see you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDD5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00136E"
msgid "Not to be impolite, but I'm a busy man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00136F"
msgid "Hey, I've got an idea. How about you get on with it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001370"
msgid "Mulling over your options, I trust?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001371"
msgid "And just like that, with no warning, the customer entered a trance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001372"
msgid "I get lost in my thoughts, too. A lot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001373"
msgid "How many drinks have you had, exactly?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001374"
msgid "Well?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001375"
msgid "Is something wrong?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001376"
msgid "What is it Rishi likes to say? \"Good talk.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001377"
msgid "Rather abrupt, but all right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDF2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001378"
msgid "Will that be all?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A537]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001379"
msgid "If you need medical attention, you can see Cutty, our resident physician."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A537]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00137A"
msgid "We have two vendors, Killian and Darcy, who offer a range of useful goods."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A537]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00137B"
msgid "Valeria runs the bar, which has a modest selection."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A537]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00137C"
msgid "Just the basic necessities, really. We're a small operation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A517]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00137D"
msgid "I suspect there's more to it, but I won't pry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00137E"
msgid "Now, back to the matter at hand. I trust you understand the rules?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00137F"
msgid "You're not the first person to make an incorrect assumption about this place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A530]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001380"
msgid "But if you find you can't handle them, feel free to leave before things become... unpleasant."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A530]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001381"
msgid "There are only a few, I'm sure you'll manage."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001382"
msgid "Thanks. I'll have a look around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001383"
msgid "I wouldn't worry, Spacers aren't that much of a threat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001384"
msgid "If it also encourages them to spend a few more credits, all the better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001385"
msgid "Making people feel welcome is the best way to get them to come back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001386"
msgid "Commerce is my reason. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A531]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001387"
msgid "What kind of an establishment is this, exactly?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001388"
msgid "This place is pretty remote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C012]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001389"
msgid "Course you'll have to live under the boot. Ain't a trade I'd make, but that's me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C012]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00138A"
msgid "You want safe, get a place in New Atlantis."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C02A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00138B"
msgid "You almost lost an entire wall?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C018]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00138C"
msgid "What services are offered here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00138D"
msgid "That full-time job belongs to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00138E"
msgid "It's a full-time job making sure everything works around here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00138F"
msgid "In case you ain't noticed, this place is old. Like, real old."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C02C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001390"
msgid "That doesn't sound very safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C017]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001391"
msgid "I found it in a decaying orbit around Algorab II and had it towed here, into the Free Lanes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C017]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001392"
msgid "I stumbled across a reference in some old business records and came for a look."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C017]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001393"
msgid "When the expected advances in Grav Drive technology didn't happen, the station was abandoned and forgotten."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C017]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001394"
msgid "The intent was to create a jumping-off point to star systems not yet accessible by grav jump."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C017]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001395"
msgid "The station was built over eighty years ago as part of a failed business venture."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031423]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001396"
msgid "Apparently he was the only one who caught it. Rotten luck, I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031423]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001397"
msgid "Mister Saint explained it, but I don't have any background in medicine so most of it went over my head."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031423]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001398"
msgid "It's some kind of alien pathogen. It was attacking his nervous system."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031410]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001399"
msgid "Sounds to me like Rishi took advantage of you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031436]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00139A"
msgid "Here you go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103142E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00139B"
msgid "What brought you all the way out here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031415]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00139C"
msgid "Why are you surprised I'm safe? Is this area dangerous?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031706]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00139D"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00139E"
msgid "That's a personal matter, and I'm not inclined to discuss it with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00139F"
msgid "Good thing he was there for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A0"
msgid "I'm guessing he got you cheap, given your circumstances."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A1"
msgid "It was the best of a very limited set of options."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A2"
msgid "When I got out, Rishi approached me with a job opportunity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A3"
msgid "There was some unfortunate business involving my accounting duties with the Vanguard, and I served some time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A4"
msgid "I previously worked with the station's owner, Rishi Saint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A5"
msgid "What you call a tough break, I call an opportunity. Your opportunity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037166]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A6"
msgid "And you need me to acquire some of these prototype robot parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A7"
msgid "By the time you get back, I'll have your money."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A8"
msgid "But I give you my word I'll pay you fairly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013A9"
msgid "Look, I'm not exactly swimming in credits here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013AA"
msgid "I shouldn't be taking it out on you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013AB"
msgid "*Sigh* Yeah, I guess you're right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013AC"
msgid "Sorry, no offense intended."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013AD"
msgid "*Sigh* No, don't be. It's not you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040487]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013AE"
msgid "What the hell do you care?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040487]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013AF"
msgid "Yeah? Well I just got some bad news."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047150]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B0"
msgid "Retrieve the cargo, and your credits will be right here waiting for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047150]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B1"
msgid "I'll give you the coordinates, and you can do whatever you like with them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B2"
msgid "Then perhaps I can interest you in a unique opportunity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047147]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B3"
msgid "What exactly are your buyers planning to do with these chemicals?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104714A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B4"
msgid "So you need a smuggler."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047143]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B5"
msgid "For work like that, the credits better be great."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B6"
msgid "Who was it that built Anchorpoint originally?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104713F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B7"
msgid "Of course, for the resourceful ship's captain, there are always other options."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104713F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B8"
msgid "Being controlled substances, a permit is required to transport the compounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104713F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013B9"
msgid "I have a network of buyers interested in obtaining rare and dangerous chemical compounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013BA"
msgid "It seems Mister Saint is quite the opportunist."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013BB"
msgid "*Chuckle* Touché."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013BC"
msgid "I wish she were here to see that I'm trying to salvage something of that dream."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013BD"
msgid "Alas, despite its impressive capabilities, even Grav Drive has its limits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013BE"
msgid "She was a true visionary. Her dream was to usher in the next great chapter of interstellar exploration."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013BF"
msgid "A wealthy industrialist named Gabriella LeBlanc."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C0"
msgid "Oh sure, I was real resourceful, until the day I wasn't resourceful enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C1"
msgid "It's not hard to imagine the kinds of transactions that must take place here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C2"
msgid "Why do I find that vaguely suspicious?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C3"
msgid "What kinds of challenges do you face out here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A62]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C4"
msgid "What made you want to work in such a remote place?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C5"
msgid "I've got you covered."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C6"
msgid "How about it? Want to go get me some more of those tasty little prototype parts? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C7"
msgid "Well I'm glad you asked, because I do indeed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C8"
msgid "Mister Saint's the one in charge. I'm sure he can tell you the whole history of the place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013C9"
msgid "That, and we get all kinds of interesting folks through here, if you catch my drift."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013CA"
msgid "I can tell you it's a near miracle the place is still in one piece."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013CB"
msgid "Haven't been here real long, so not much."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013CC"
msgid "Not right now, but I'll keep it in mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065740]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013CD"
msgid "I'll have to pass this time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013CE"
msgid "Now, was there something else you needed?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013CF"
msgid "I don't know what the future holds. I can only take things one day at a time, and try to be a better man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106611A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D0"
msgid "Especially if it involved the greatest regret of your life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106611A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D1"
msgid "I'm sure you'd want your privacy respected if our roles were reversed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106611A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D2"
msgid "Look, I don't know you, and that's a sensitive subject."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D3"
msgid "Just do it fast."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D4"
msgid "Then hire someone. One of the patrons maybe. I'll pay the cost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DF2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D5"
msgid "Sure. What else do you need?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DF1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D6"
msgid "I suppose we're done, then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D7"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D8"
msgid "What have we got here..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DE2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013D9"
msgid "Yeah, all right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DFE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013DA"
msgid "You're in good shape as far as I can see."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013DB"
msgid "I think next time we should have a trial by combat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013DC"
msgid "Hal really had us all fooled. I'm going to be extra vigilant now. Everyone's a suspect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102F6E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013DD"
msgid "I cannot speak to what you'll find there, but it may point you to what you seek."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013DE"
msgid "Very well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013DF"
msgid "This is tiresome. Let's just be done with it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ABDA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E0"
msgid "..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043AFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E1"
msgid "Of course, I'm a doctor. It doesn't mean I'm the thief."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E2"
msgid "It doesn't matter. It doesn't justify what she did."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E3"
msgid "Money. It's always money."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023CB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E4"
msgid "Sunni wants to get kicked out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E5"
msgid "You're to be set free. Your life is yours to do what you wish."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010275D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E6"
msgid "For what it's worth, I agree. You've got a ship, and we can pay you the fare."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030764]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E7"
msgid "Pretty foolproof plan if you ask me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031114]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E8"
msgid "But I'd rather not have this conversation in front of the others. Not yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031366]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013E9"
msgid "The magnet will destroy the hard drive. But I only need the components. It'll be fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013EA"
msgid "And who's going to get revenge for him? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013EB"
msgid "That's disappointing, but if you choose to abstain, I'll break the tie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013EC"
msgid "And if I don't? You can't force me to decide."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103F3BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013ED"
msgid "I've seen you die before. But things may change this time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E32E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013EE"
msgid "Execution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010483F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013EF"
msgid "Nah, I think I just like being one. Cool thought though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103FAF0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F0"
msgid "Indeed. When we first met, you seemed prepared to leave my fate to the others. Do you know how you will vote?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051376]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F1"
msgid "At this point, that's all I can ask for."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105136A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F2"
msgid "And surely you know what comes next."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052CBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F3"
msgid "For what it's worth, I will be voting in accordance with Hal's wishes. I disagree with the decision, but I will honor his choice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051371]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F4"
msgid "Yes, it seems very familiar, theologically speaking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051378]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F5"
msgid "Well I have been known to persuade a person or two with my otherworldly charm. It's one of my many super powers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F6"
msgid "Gratitude is what I expect. Hunting him down wasn't easy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F7"
msgid "You should know, I found and killed Caruso. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105594A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F8"
msgid "*Exhales* You did what you had to. But this is not how I wanted things to end."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ABDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0013F9"
msgid "This outpost has been through a lot, from even before I came here. But as you can see, it's starting to thrive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014B2"
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014B3"
msgid "Mm-hm."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014B4"
msgid "Good talk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014B5"
msgid "Back to it then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014B6"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014B7"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014B8"
msgid "I tried playing chess once. But I don't understand why there's knights and bishops but no torturers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014B9"
msgid "People say my outlook is too grim. Those people are dead now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014BA"
msgid "I've been part of your crew for a good minute. I wonder when bonuses pay out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014BB"
msgid "If I die, I want to be taxidermied. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014BC"
msgid "I'm not like other companions. I'm not gonna comment on whatever pointless thing you're doing at the moment. I just don't care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014BD"
msgid "Life is terrible. It's that realization that keeps me going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014BE"
msgid "I hope these things come back to haunt us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C41]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014BF"
msgid "Fine. Do your worst."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C0"
msgid "When did you start taking an interest in necromancy?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C1"
msgid "Do you have any fun facts about fungi?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C2"
msgid "A morgue would be very on brand."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C3"
msgid "I don't know, I think it's kind of cool that trees pay for stuff."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C4"
msgid "The trees use the network to exchange nutrients, and they pay the fungi in sugar. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C5"
msgid "You ever heard of a mycorrhizal network? They're basically a postal service for trees, linked up by mycelium."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C6"
msgid "Did you know there are fungi you can only detect through DNA sequencing? They're called dark taxa. I just call them cool."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C7"
msgid "Earlier, you mentioned a ship full of dead cultists. What happened to them?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C8"
msgid "Sadly, it's not. Not a whispering wall or pale lady to speak of."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014C9"
msgid "What, you're afraid it's haunted or something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014CA"
msgid "That was fun. I think I died a little inside every time I went in, which was neat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014CB"
msgid "Let's see. There was the time I worked cashier at an audio slate store. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014CC"
msgid "I asked several times if I could take a body home. It didn't even have to be one of the preserved ones. They still said no."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BDF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014CD"
msgid "They had me doing laundry and cleaning up blood and other viscera. They gave us a machine to suck up blobs of fat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014CE"
msgid "How did you get the job?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014CF"
msgid "It's kind of like having my own personal corpse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D0"
msgid "Eventually they get so strapped with debt they become a lifeless husk working three jobs to fund my lavish lifestyle. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D1"
msgid "Lots of ways. When I give someone a high interest loan, it's like casting a drain spell that slowly sucks the life force out of a person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D2"
msgid "Yeah? Can't relate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D3"
msgid "And yes, I believe all cashiers should have the legal right to shoot customers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D4"
msgid "I bet that's why you're so good at the combat stuff."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D5"
msgid "That's murder."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B5C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D6"
msgid "Yeah, but I hear black holes rip you apart before you ever \"fall\" in. And space is so sterile. I want to hear the trail of screams."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D7"
msgid "If only."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D8"
msgid "So when they said I couldn't make a blood pact with an eldritch horror to raise an army of darkness, well, that could've been a lie too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014D9"
msgid "Pretty much. My parents had told me it wasn't, but keep in mind, these are the same people who lied about the tooth collector, and the reverse burglar in the red suit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C13]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014DA"
msgid "Have you been looking for other jobs?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014DB"
msgid "Did you ever try to raise any dead?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C62]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014DC"
msgid "Ha, good one. You're funny."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014DD"
msgid "I have to be going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014DE"
msgid "If you're looking for company, I'd be happy to bring you along with me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014DF"
msgid "I'm not answering that question without a lawyer present."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E0"
msgid "Where are the corpses?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E1"
msgid "In exchange, I might show up to work two, maybe three times a week. Deal?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E2"
msgid "But yeah, I think I'm gonna need creds, up front. And a skull. Preferably with the brains still in it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D3A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E3"
msgid "Why, are you gonna go out for cigarettes?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C44]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E4"
msgid "Although... I did leave an open pack of Chunks somewhere in the cockpit. Maybe it's sentient now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E5"
msgid "Fine, I got nothing better to do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E6"
msgid "I better get overtime pay for this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E7"
msgid "I'll go get my potions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E8"
msgid "I'll go get my potions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014E9"
msgid "Is there anywhere you want to visit?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C0E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014EA"
msgid "Aren't you like a pirate or something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B89]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014EB"
msgid "Except banking isn't nearly as cool."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014EC"
msgid "Forget GalBank. What if you came to work for me instead?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014ED"
msgid "You mentioned painting before. What sort of things do you like to paint?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014EE"
msgid "Let's go back to my other questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C4A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014EF"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C27]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014F0"
msgid "Would you be different if you had siblings?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BFE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014F1"
msgid "Yeah. I'd be a murderer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014F2"
msgid "Not often I have human ones like you. Let's call it a trial phase though. I'm still sorting out the side effects."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014F3"
msgid "I had enough. Most of them were imaginary, or fungi."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014F4"
msgid "Neat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014F5"
msgid "Where do you keep your paintings?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014F8"
msgid "Why... why are you asking? I'm not answering that. I... and I asked you a question first. You need to answer me now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014F9"
msgid "The eyes, the eyes, what else would I be talking about? Do you not see them all around you? Are you lucky enough to be blind?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014FA"
msgid "You aren't... one of them, are you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014FB"
msgid "If it doesn't, is there a fallback plan? Some other way to use the station that's profitable?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014FC"
msgid "Anchorpoint was built on the premise that Grav Drive technology will advance beyond its current limits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014FD"
msgid "Please respond and provide assistance. We're in danger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C46E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014FE"
msgid "Don't panic, but it looks like we've got one more pirate to deal with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B172]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0014FF"
msgid "This one's mine! I saw it first!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B17B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001500"
msgid "Mayday! Mayday!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C46B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001501"
msgid "I knew it! We walked right into a spacer ambush!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B96F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001502"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A308]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001503"
msgid "Well hey there stranger. I've got something for you that'll blow your mind. Trust me, you're never gonna forget this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A314]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001504"
msgid "You see, I want to play a game with you. A bit of a twisted one, but that's what makes it so fun. The stakes are high!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A314]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001505"
msgid "Ah, good, you picked up. I've been flying all over, looking for someone, anyone, to play with. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001506"
msgid "It's very simple, really. Three lives for three riddles. If you refuse to answer, or if you get a riddle wrong, I kill one of my little friends on board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001507"
msgid "*Ahem* 'Scuse me. Do I have your attention now? Then allow me to explain the rules of my little game."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001508"
msgid "All right, shut up, that's enough. Get on back with the rest of them. Move!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C758]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001509"
msgid "I don't know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C754]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00150A"
msgid "A valiant effort, but wrong. A potato has many eyes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00150B"
msgid "Breath."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00150C"
msgid "A thought."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00150D"
msgid "Hope you enjoy the fireworks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00150E"
msgid "You thought I was bluffing? I do not bluff."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00150F"
msgid "You will not deny me this game!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001510"
msgid "I swear to whatever god you worship, if you end this hail I will blow up this ship. Everyone - EVERYONE - on board will die!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D258]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001511"
msgid "Time's up for this one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C27]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001512"
msgid "It's insulting."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C25]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001513"
msgid "But to see my service commercialized this way... well, it's certainly a choice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C25]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001514"
msgid "Maybe under different circumstances, I might've appreciated it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C21]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001515"
msgid "I thought it was amusing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001516"
msgid "You should feel proud."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C24]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001517"
msgid "It is. It's from a set of Colony War Heroes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C2F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001518"
msgid "And without my permission."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ACA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001519"
msgid "Are we there yet?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ACA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00151A"
msgid "I'll keep my weapon close until we're at our destination, if you don't mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C815]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00151B"
msgid "Watch out for that guy. He could still want to take over the ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C813]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00151C"
msgid "If he steps out of line, I will kill him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C810]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00151D"
msgid "We should go check in case someone needs help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C810]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00151E"
msgid "Do you think there's anyone inside that ship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00151F"
msgid "Another day, another space derelict. Do you think it's worth checking out?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001520"
msgid "All right, that does it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001521"
msgid "Nice knowing you, pal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001522"
msgid "You asked for it, buddy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD44]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001523"
msgid "I'm going to enjoy this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD43]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001524"
msgid "Die, you rat!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD42]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001525"
msgid "I knew I couldn't trust you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC49]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001526"
msgid "Huh. Is that so?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC50]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001527"
msgid "I don't think I will put it down, no."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC5F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001528"
msgid "Sure you can. And you will."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC40]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001529"
msgid "Where I need to go is not your concern."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00152A"
msgid "That's pretty big talk for someone at the end of my gun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC46]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00152B"
msgid "I'm not quite as confident as you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00152C"
msgid "Good, we have an understanding."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC3D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00152D"
msgid "I'm sure we can come to an agreement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00152E"
msgid "Pretty sure that's none of your business."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00152F"
msgid "Sorry, wrong answer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001530"
msgid "Once I'm back I'm sure my boss will want to reward you in some way. He's like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001531"
msgid "Hah! You're pushing your luck, pal!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001532"
msgid "Is there a problem?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001533"
msgid "I can't do discreet for free."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD3E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001534"
msgid "You're starting to get on my nerves, you know that? All right, where to start..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064815]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001535"
msgid "Don't worry about Miss Krause, she's a bit standoffish but I know she's grateful as well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC07SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001536"
msgid "It's your call...but I can't guarantee she'll still have a job when we get to New Atlantis."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC07SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001537"
msgid "So you'd have me risk losing this fine ship instead? I don't think the board would approve."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106802D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001538"
msgid "I'm not leaving her behind, it's too risky."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106803D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001539"
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106803C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00153A"
msgid "Do you need anything?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068023]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00153B"
msgid "You'll be fine. I'll send for you as soon as I get back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068023]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00153C"
msgid "This is a very expensive ship, we can't just abandon it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00153D"
msgid "Yeah, I'm sort of the worst at improv."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00153E"
msgid "You bet. I wouldn't trust anyone else to watch your six."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00153F"
msgid "I'm good hanging out here with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001540"
msgid "Hey, Atka, can I borrow a few credits?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001541"
msgid "Clean? Can't you pay someone to do that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEF2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001542"
msgid "Sounds like fun. Just don't overdo it. I don't want any late-night calls about bailing you out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CECC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001543"
msgid "Don't worry, we'll do something completely different but equally annoying, just to keep you guessing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CECB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001544"
msgid "Wow, I'm really never going to hear the end of that one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CECA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001545"
msgid "Hey, then it's not a real vacation, is it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF27]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001546"
msgid "What are you and Roman up to?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001547"
msgid "Are you sure you know what you're doing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001548"
msgid "I hope Miss Krause won't be too angry with me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001549"
msgid "All those people dead, just to get one person. Such a waste."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F64E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00154A"
msgid "Hold on tight, I'm coming aboard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F64D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00154B"
msgid "I mean...the VP of Acquisitions for the GalBank consortium needs your help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F64D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00154C"
msgid "Thank you for responding! We really need your help!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106378C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00154D"
msgid "Watch out for those mines, you fool!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F655]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00154E"
msgid "Please provide immediate assistance if you can!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106439C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00154F"
msgid "Is anyone on your ship hurt?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010643A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001550"
msgid "Let me think about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064801]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001551"
msgid "Please hurry!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001552"
msgid "The VP of Acquisitions invites you to board our ship ASAP."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001553"
msgid "Look, that pirate ship is aiming straight for them!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001554"
msgid "What happened? Did you send one of your people?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001555"
msgid "I heard they're no longer a problem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001556"
msgid "Yep! Smooth sailing here, now that those Spacers are gone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001557"
msgid "Everyone behaving themselves?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_DialogueAnchorpoint_TigerSharedInfo_Growl
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001558"
msgid "Growl."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_DialogueAnchorpoint_TigerSharedInfo_Hiss
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001559"
msgid "Hiss."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059102]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00155A"
msgid "Yeah, I thought you'd like that idea."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C392]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00155B"
msgid "That one hurt. Are you sure you don't want me to pilot us out of here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080452]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00155C"
msgid "I cannot believe you just did that. Again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080451]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00155D"
msgid "What did you just do? Should we go back to the ship? I feel we should go back to the ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080467]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00155E"
msgid "Remind me to stay on the ship next time you want to pull off this kind of stunt."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108045D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00155F"
msgid "I thought I was one to take risks, but I can see you have me beat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080476]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001560"
msgid "I don't know about you, but I'm not getting a great feeling from this place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080469]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001561"
msgid "Let's be quick about this. I'd hate for one of those mines to go off while we're in here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A6B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001563"
msgid "Okay, but maybe you should take a look."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A4A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001564"
msgid "Talk to Mister Saint. If he provides the funds, I'll arrange a purchase."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054570]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001566"
msgid "C'mon... I'm dead in the void here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001568"
msgid "Ha! You should have seen the look on your face..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001569"
msgid "Relax, it's just a joke."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053577]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00156A"
msgid "What about the regular stuff?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00156B"
msgid "All good?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00156C"
msgid "Okay, I'll be here if you need me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00156D"
msgid "Whatever you say, sweetie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053569]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00156E"
msgid "Don't look too long, or my husband will get jealous."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00156F"
msgid "You should have seen what we had last week."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001570"
msgid "Well, since you said please..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105357F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001571"
msgid "I don't know what you're talking about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE07]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001572"
msgid "And I was told I'd find love among the stars. Here you go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053579]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001573"
msgid "Oh, were you now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE0C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001574"
msgid "Did you want to ask me something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001575"
msgid "Will that be all, my friend?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001576"
msgid "Is that all?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE1F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001577"
msgid "No problem. Let me know if you see something you like."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105356A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001578"
msgid "I'd like to see the specials, please."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001579"
msgid "My friend! So glad you're here. Fanisha will be happy to see you too!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE38]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00157A"
msgid "Apparently they wait for you to get close to the beacon, then they attack. Be careful out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE38]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00157B"
msgid "There are rumors of pirates using fake distress calls to lure in unsuspecting victims."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00157C"
msgid "We're usually pretty open about things, but I didn't get a good feeling from them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00157D"
msgid "The other day we came across a ship that was clearly stolen. Wanted to come aboard. I said no."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00157E"
msgid "I guess the place is kind of a haven for smugglers. Not that I would know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00157F"
msgid "I know a guy who *only* runs contraband for a living. Does a lot of his meet-ups at Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001580"
msgid "Probably drifted off due to gravity interactions and so on. Good places to find loot, if you dare!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001581"
msgid "Some people have reported minefields littered with ship debris in the middle of nowhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE15]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001582"
msgid "Come close my friend, I'll share what I know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001583"
msgid "Nothing too out of the ordinary..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE11]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001584"
msgid "I hear lots of things..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDF2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001585"
msgid "Heard anything good recently?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C830]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001586"
msgid "So much choice, I'm not sure what to get."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C824]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001587"
msgid "This shop reminds me of home for some reason."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C821]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001588"
msgid "All right, these two seem pretty harmless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F915]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001589"
msgid "To have a look at these you'll have to come aboard. Don't be shy!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F915]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00158A"
msgid "Ah, you mean our specials."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F921]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00158B"
msgid "I was expecting a different type of goods."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F91C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00158C"
msgid "Take care, traveler!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F91C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00158D"
msgid "Well, maybe next time then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EEA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00158E"
msgid "I'm all set, thanks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105461E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00158F"
msgid "We don't deserve this. Goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001590"
msgid "We've got new items on sale. Come take a look if you have time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001591"
msgid "Let's go check it out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C80B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001592"
msgid "Oh, I think I've heard about these two. Quite the odd couple, if I remember right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C805]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001593"
msgid "Oh look, it is those space traders. Do you want to go see what they have?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B392]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001595"
msgid "Mm-hm."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B386]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001596"
msgid "Go on, have fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Lookslikeyoubotharehavinganicetime
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001597"
msgid "Looks like you're having a nice time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_IfyoutwodonttellmewhereIamrightnow
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001598"
msgid "If you two don't tell me where I am right now..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_NothingWillChangeIfYouDontDoAnything
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001599"
msgid "Nothing will change if you don't do anything. This should be worth the plunge. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_PlayerName
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00159A"
msgid "Hey. My name is <alias=player>. Who are you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_DoyouknowaboutOpalbullyingyoursister
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00159B"
msgid "Do you know about Opal bullying your sister?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_TakeAHintLeaveMeAlone
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00159C"
msgid "Take a hint. Leave me alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_WhatAreYouStillDoingHereIThoughtYouWereLeaving
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00159D"
msgid "What are you still doing here? I thought you were leaving?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_ShutUp
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00159E"
msgid "Shut up!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00159F"
msgid "Drink too much there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A0"
msgid "Looks like someone is having fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A1"
msgid "Step back, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B43C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A2"
msgid "Great. Now we're all getting tied into their drama."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B43B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A3"
msgid "They really couldn't wait till after the party to do this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B42B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A4"
msgid "We can't let the party end. Let's dance!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B424]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A5"
msgid "Ah yea, a new face! It was getting pretty old having the same people here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B420]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A6"
msgid "I guess the party is over then..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B41C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A7"
msgid "What's going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B410]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A8"
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B40F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015A9"
msgid "If you're looking for conversation, look elsewhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B40A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015AA"
msgid "Whatever you need to say, it can wait."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B409]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015AB"
msgid "Give me a minute."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015AC"
msgid "Did Opal cause all this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015AD"
msgid "What the hell is going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015AE"
msgid "Come on. Join us. This will be fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015AF"
msgid "I'm done talking, alright?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B0"
msgid "Can't you see I'm busy?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B1"
msgid "I hope Sawyer's right about you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B2"
msgid "Well, this isn't how I planned today to go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B3"
msgid "You're just looking for a fight, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B4"
msgid "You're not getting away with this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B5"
msgid "You think I'll just let you get away with that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B31D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B6"
msgid "Hrungh!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B315]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B7"
msgid "Well, that could have gone better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B380]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B8"
msgid "Someone turn these turrets off!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B372]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015B9"
msgid "Way to ruin the party."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B36B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015BA"
msgid "Stop! Stop this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B368]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015BB"
msgid "Why would you do this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B360]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015BC"
msgid "You really had to pick this fight?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B35F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015BD"
msgid "Next party, I'll be laughing about your death."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B35E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015BE"
msgid "I don't need this today."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B356]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015BF"
msgid "I'm done with your shit!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B353]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C0"
msgid "I'm going to put you down!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B352]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C1"
msgid "This really what you want, huh? Is it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B348]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C2"
msgid "If you put down your weapon, I'll put down mine, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B347]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C3"
msgid "You can always end this. We don't need to fight anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B340]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C4"
msgid "Say goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B333]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C5"
msgid "We could've just had a fun party. But no."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E269]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C6"
msgid "*Sigh* Look, the party's over now. I don't know what else you want to do. But be quick about it. I have to get Sadie and the other's home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E223]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C7"
msgid "*Sigh* Never mind... Let me take you back to Anchorpoint. Looks like I got a mess to clean up afterwards."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E223]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C8"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E206]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015C9"
msgid "Thank you. I'm ready to return to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E236]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015CA"
msgid "You were right. This was fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E293]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015CB"
msgid "What just happened...?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E219]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015CC"
msgid "What a mess..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E219]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015CD"
msgid "Yeah. Yeah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E260]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015CE"
msgid "Sadie learned the truth of Opal's abuse towards Wren."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015CF"
msgid "I think I just destroyed your friend group. I want to go now, please."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E241]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D0"
msgid "You don't have to say anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E28A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D1"
msgid "You keep my sister's name out of your mouth! It doesn't matter who told me. You've been lying to me and been saying who knows what to Wren."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E24E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D2"
msgid "I know you're the one that's been tormenting my sister!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D3"
msgid "That lying..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E295]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D4"
msgid "I thought she was my friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D5"
msgid "Sadie, can we talk? It's about Opal..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E243]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D6"
msgid "I know I told you before everything was fine. But to be honest, it's true that Opal has been bullying me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E21C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D7"
msgid "I distanced myself from the problem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E26A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D8"
msgid "I don't think I ever did..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E242]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015D9"
msgid "Thank you. I'm going to talk to her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E242]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015DA"
msgid "I guess then, it will only work out if I tell Sadie. I need to tell her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E242]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015DB"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E261]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015DC"
msgid "I talked with those I knew who loved me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E286]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015DD"
msgid "Are you really okay with Opal harassing you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E267]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015DE"
msgid "You're still thinking of that? Just let it go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E294]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015DF"
msgid "Sure. But maybe Opal feels like she has to share Sadie with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E237]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E0"
msgid "That's no reason to be jealous though. Opal and Sadie have been friends for years. Right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E1"
msgid "Be careful around Wren. Sadie told me she's been at Reliant Medical lately, and she didn't even tell me why. Whatever it was, she better not be contagious. I heard some diseases can linger on a person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E2"
msgid "If you end up with any questions about the ship, go ask Sadie. She's the one who set up a good part of this place. She made this ship look like paradise, and set up a wicked security system."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E3"
msgid "Between you and me, I hope she's finally deciding to break things off with him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E4"
msgid "Don't try flirting with Opal, alright? Cooper and her are dating. And trust me, you don't want to pick a fight with him. Though, from what I've seen, Opal has been a bit distant from him as of late."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E240]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E5"
msgid "Yeah, don't get Opal started on Wren. I swear she'll talk your ear off about the girl, and it's never anything good. But she just teases like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E289]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E6"
msgid "It's alright. You can tell me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E7"
msgid "I've heard Opal has been causing you issues, is that true?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E222]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E8"
msgid "Go on. Have fun. We'll take you back when we're all done partying! That or if something worse happened, ha!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E222]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015E9"
msgid "Woah, not yet. We're still having fun. Besides, do you want me to drive my ship during my own party?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E235]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015EA"
msgid "We'll return to Anchorpoint once the party's over."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E235]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015EB"
msgid "Don't mean you have to. Come on. We're celebrating 'til we're sick of each other or dead! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E21F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015EC"
msgid "You're back! Still want to join us?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E248]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015ED"
msgid "Don't tell them, but I managed to get more money from them than was needed. Got the ship decked out too now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E228]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015EE"
msgid "I don't drink."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E23B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015EF"
msgid "Not now. Maybe later if you both are still here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E25B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F0"
msgid "Sorry. Can't help it. We're celebrating! Want to join? The more the merrier."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E25A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F1"
msgid "Hm, what? Here to buy a lady a drink? Too bad. I already got a boyfriend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E26E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F2"
msgid "Heh! Let's get another round of drinks!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E282]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F3"
msgid "This will be one hell of a celebration, won't it, Sawyer?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F4"
msgid "It's good to see you again. I didn't know when you would return after running off with those two. *Sigh* Well, I hope you had a fun time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B275]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F5"
msgid "I have your friends in the palm of my hands. I know exactly what to do with this slate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F6"
msgid "Trust me. She's going to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F7"
msgid "We're going to talk, alright."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F8"
msgid "You wait right here. Opal and I are going to have a few words."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015F9"
msgid "I don't get it. Wren kept telling me nothing was happening. How long has this even been going on? Wren just got back from being sick. How could she- "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B28E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015FA"
msgid "Sounds like Opal doesn't like your sister very much."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B277]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015FB"
msgid "I do. Excuse me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015FC"
msgid "I hope you know what to do with that slate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B281]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015FD"
msgid "I don't know. You lose track after a while. Maybe that's a good thing, right? He's sweet though, even if he seems otherwise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015FE"
msgid "Would you know anything about this crowd?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B295]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0015FF"
msgid "How are you liking the party?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2A9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001600"
msgid "Right, since you're new you wouldn't know about Opal and Cooper. They've been dating for a while now. Though, I'm a little nervous. Seems like Opal is spending less and less time with him. She better not break his heart."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B286]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001601"
msgid "You know nothing about me. You just got here, and this is so much more complicated than you think."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B285]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001602"
msgid "You don't know Opal like I do. I wish I could tell Sadie, but I don't want to upset her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001603"
msgid "My little sister, Wren, is here. To be honest, I'm a bit shocked she even came. She wasn't feeling too well for a while. This party is her first time being out in months."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B293]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001604"
msgid "I can't believe you're just going to let Opal get away with everything she's done to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001605"
msgid "Okay. I can understand that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B300]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001606"
msgid "You may be right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001607"
msgid "You never know when Opal may go farther than just harassment. You'll be safer if you tell someone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E203]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001608"
msgid "Ready for the second?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001609"
msgid "Opal is nothing but a punk. The others need to know what she's like."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D683]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00160A"
msgid "Right. Fine. I'm Cooper. I'm here because Opal and Sadie wanted me here. Not because Sawyer's get-togethers are my style. That's all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D69D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00160B"
msgid "I wanted to meet everyone else here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D677]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00160C"
msgid "I was just told to mingle. I don't think it mattered with who."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D676]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00160D"
msgid "Be careful, alright? Don't want to ruin the fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D6A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00160E"
msgid "Trust me, I don't even want to be here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106DC22]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00160F"
msgid "I'm sure you're more interesting than you think."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01078788]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001610"
msgid "I'm sorry..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065745]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001612"
msgid "I'll let you know if I hear of any other lost shipments."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106574E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001613"
msgid "Here is your payment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001614"
msgid "What's going to happen to me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104BFFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001615"
msgid "I'm not saying another word."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001616"
msgid "This is not what I wanted."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001617"
msgid "Just...go away, okay? Please?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001618"
msgid "Ow! That really hurt!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001619"
msgid "Not even an expert could do it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00161A"
msgid "Ha! Good luck unlocking that door."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00161B"
msgid "You're making a big mistake!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo08
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00161C"
msgid "I don't need your help, so just go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D02F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00161D"
msgid "If you want to grab some cargo on your way out, go crazy. My stepfather's got insurance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D02E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00161E"
msgid "If you want to grab some cargo for your trouble, that's fine. We'll call it even."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D02D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00161F"
msgid "We should hurry. My stepfather won't be alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040743]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001620"
msgid "You mean, there's worse than you out there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040755]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001621"
msgid "Why don't you just start from the beginning?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040770]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001622"
msgid "Okay, well listen until the end then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040778]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001623"
msgid "There must be people out there worried sick about you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040758]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001624"
msgid "The next person to find you might not be as understanding as I am."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040744]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001625"
msgid "It's not safe for you to travel out here alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040769]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001626"
msgid "I'm not your enemy, you know? Just a concerned stranger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040761]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001627"
msgid "Stop pretending you care. No one does."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040751]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001628"
msgid "I don't care what you've done, I can't abandon you like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104073C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001629"
msgid "I have a feeling you'd rather I not call the authorities. Am I right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040741]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00162A"
msgid "I'm fine. Plenty of supplies on the ship. But thanks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104073B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00162B"
msgid "I don't want any trouble. Please don't hurt me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104074C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00162C"
msgid "I don't know...I'm so confused right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104075D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00162D"
msgid "I don't have anything to talk about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104077B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00162E"
msgid "I do want to hear your story."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040777]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00162F"
msgid "But he set up an anti-theft system that totally bricked the ship. He's probably on his way here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040777]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001630"
msgid "I had to get away, you know? As far away as I could... so I thought, why not take his ship, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040777]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001631"
msgid "The truth is... this isn't my ship. It's my stepfather's."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040756]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001632"
msgid "Do I look like I want to hurt you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040766]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001633"
msgid "Don't worry, I won't take candy from strangers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040747]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001634"
msgid "Oh yeah? Wanna bet?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040746]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001635"
msgid "*sigh* I'm already getting tired."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C0E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001636"
msgid "I'm afraid I can't tell you that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo12
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001637"
msgid "You're trespassing right now. Go back to your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo12
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001638"
msgid "What are you doing? I told you we didn't need anything!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C09]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001639"
msgid "Oh you know, all kinds of stuff. Nothing out of the ordinary. Just regular cargo."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00163A"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00163B"
msgid "You would do that for me? Really? Thank you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00163C"
msgid "I guess I could take you to New Atlantis."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00163D"
msgid "Stepfather, not father. And no, it's not for the best. I'll just run away again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00163E"
msgid "Can you tell me your story again?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040775]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00163F"
msgid "Did you want to ask me something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D01B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001640"
msgid "Are you going to be okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D01C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001641"
msgid "Nope. I'm fine. Goodbye, now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D026]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001642"
msgid "Help yourself to whatever cargo you want before leaving. I don't care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B985]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001643"
msgid "I didn't want to ask... but it'd be awesome if you could take me to my cousin's in New Atlantis."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B987]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001644"
msgid "I can give you a lift if you want."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DACD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001645"
msgid "Can we go out now? I want to breathe some fresh air."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C50E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001646"
msgid "She was the lead singer in my band. We knew she had it rough at home. One day she was just... gone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C50E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001647"
msgid "Poor girl. She reminds me of a friend I had, back when I was her age."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001648"
msgid "Do you need me to call someone for assistance with your ship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001649"
msgid "Huh...just a temporary hiccup. We're working on it. Just keep going. Bye!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DACE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00164A"
msgid "Where do you go from here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00164B"
msgid "The Spacers took me captive. I need help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00164C"
msgid "Help me. Please."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00164D"
msgid "Guess you've got places to be, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00164E"
msgid "Still with me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00164F"
msgid "If that job is rescuing me, I'm not going to complain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040492]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001650"
msgid "He's at Anchorpoint. You should reach out, try to heal the rift."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040493]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001651"
msgid "But there's a difference between wanting me to be alive and wanting me in his life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040493]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001652"
msgid "I guess so."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001653"
msgid "Believe me, I know that better than anyone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040497]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001654"
msgid "Wow, I don't know what to say. Thank you, Mantis!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040497]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001655"
msgid "Wait, seriously? Those stories are true?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040485]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001656"
msgid "Just here to do a job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040489]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001657"
msgid "You have no idea how happy I am to hear those words."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040498]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001658"
msgid "I'm here to rescue you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001659"
msgid "It's one thing to feel sorry for yourself, but to abandon your family? I don't know if I can forgive that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00165A"
msgid "If he wants to wallow in pity, I'm not going to stop him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBDC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00165B"
msgid "I never wanted any of this, but if I can make things right, then maybe I should."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00165C"
msgid "After a while, you learn to live with the pain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00165D"
msgid "What do you know about it, anyway? It's between me and him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBEB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00165E"
msgid "After what just happened to me, I'm inclined to agree."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BC00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00165F"
msgid "If he really wanted to talk, he's always known how to reach me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBF7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001660"
msgid "I want to be strong, but the grief is unbearable some days."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001661"
msgid "It'll be difficult, I know, but maybe you're right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001662"
msgid "That's truly awful. I'm so sorry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001663"
msgid "That is truly heartbreaking. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001664"
msgid "You need to find it within yourself to rise above the pain and do what's right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001665"
msgid "Sometimes, it takes a lot of strength to forgive someone. Be strong."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001666"
msgid "You can't ignore this pain forever. It's time to start healing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001667"
msgid "You know what they say about open wounds. They tend to fester."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001668"
msgid "I used to be so proud of my father. I miss feeling that way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001669"
msgid "Family has always been important to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00166A"
msgid "You're right. I think it's time to mend some old wounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB80]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00166B"
msgid "Right. Well, um, Mantis, thanks for coming to my rescue."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00166C"
msgid "Yeah. You risked a lot coming out here, so it's the least I can do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00166D"
msgid "[Lie] I'm the famed galactic superhero called... The Mantis!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C427]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00166E"
msgid "We'd be stranded if not for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C41E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00166F"
msgid "Waiting for your response. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C41A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001670"
msgid "Uh..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050248]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001671"
msgid "Thanks. For everything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050247]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001672"
msgid "We'll try not to get in your way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedInfo01_CaptainInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001673"
msgid "*Sigh* Fair enough, I guess. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedShipHello05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001674"
msgid "The captain is waiting for you. You'll speak with them on board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedShipHello01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001675"
msgid "The captain is waiting for you on board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedShipHello03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001676"
msgid "The captain will speak with you on board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001677"
msgid "Requesting response. This is urgent. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001678"
msgid "Copy that. We'll see you aboard. The captain will be waiting for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001679"
msgid "We'll see you on board. You can speak with our captain then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00167A"
msgid "I can't give you a ride. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00167B"
msgid "*Sigh* Look, we're as good as stranded now. Do you think you could at least fly us out of here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00167C"
msgid "You never thought to give us a hand back there? While you were twiddling your thumbs, our pilot was killed. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00167D"
msgid "It looks like our engines and Grav Drive were heavily damaged during the attack. I hate to ask, but could you fly us out of here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00167E"
msgid "Damn, things were getting dicey there for a minute. Not sure we would've survived if you hadn't shown up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E241]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00167F"
msgid "Yeah, guess we should get going before any more Spacers show up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E23F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001680"
msgid "Let's get going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E249]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001681"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001682"
msgid "Thanks for helping us out. I know it's a burden."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D6E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001683"
msgid "Ah, good, you're here. We're ready to leave when you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EDF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001684"
msgid "Works for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EDFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001685"
msgid "We won't have any problems if you don't make any problems."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001686"
msgid "I don't mean to come across as ungrateful. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EDF9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001687"
msgid "Did I do anything to make you nervous?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001688"
msgid "Got it, let's go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C413]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001689"
msgid "All right, I hear you. Let's get moving."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C412]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00168A"
msgid "Things could've been worse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C437]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00168B"
msgid "If you think I'm so suspicious, I'll leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C439]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00168C"
msgid "I hope it's not too much trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00168D"
msgid "Man, I really hope none of this comes out of my paycheck. Everything just went south so quickly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00168E"
msgid "I hear that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00168F"
msgid "My condolences, but we should get moving before more Spacers show up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001690"
msgid "Sorry about your pilot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001691"
msgid "So, you're giving us a ride? Good. Can't leave here fast enough. It's creepy... just having the pilot's body lying there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001692"
msgid "Enough of that, though. We need to get moving."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001693"
msgid "*Sigh* Anyway, thanks for giving us a ride out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001694"
msgid "They're Spacers, they don't need a reason to attack you. They'll kill you because they're bored. Hell, maybe that was the reason."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001695"
msgid "He flew like hell today. Rest of us would probably be dead if not for him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001696"
msgid "It's okay. Well, it's not but... damn, I just don't know what to say right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001697"
msgid "I'm sorry about your pilot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001698"
msgid "Can't believe it. We were so close to getting out of that attack in one piece. Then they scored a direct hit on the cockpit, and..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001699"
msgid "Good to see you. We need all the help we can get, now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00169A"
msgid "Kill them!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00169B"
msgid "Your ship is ours, now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00169C"
msgid "Not everyone is meant to live a long life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00169D"
msgid "Yeah, it's unfortunate, but it was his time to die I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00169E"
msgid "Guess I should've kept my mouth shut."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00169F"
msgid "We won't have any problems if you don't make any."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A0"
msgid "Open fire!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A1"
msgid "So, we're taking your ship, and you can't come with us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A2"
msgid "Look, it was nice of you to try and help us, but the people I work for aren't nice people. We're as good as dead if we don't finish our delivery."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A3"
msgid "Thanks for your help. I know it's a burden but we're out of options. As you can see, we're down a pilot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A4"
msgid "I just gotta say, that's a great ship you have. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D54B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A5"
msgid "You brought me damaged parts? I ain't paying full price for these."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D546]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A6"
msgid "Shiny and new, I see. Glad you got them in good shape."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_LeadershipResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A7"
msgid "That's what everyone keeps telling me... I just don't want to ruin everything if I make the wrong call."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_CreditsPaidResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A8"
msgid "Nice doing business with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B44A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016A9"
msgid "Thanks for being cool. I swear this won't happen again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016AA"
msgid "Thanks for letting me take those credits off your hands."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B43D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016AB"
msgid "Must be nice having that many credits to blow."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D5F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016AC"
msgid "Just say the word if you change your mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016AD"
msgid "It'll be quick, I promise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016AE"
msgid "Just die already!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016AF"
msgid "You're dead!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B0"
msgid "Get him!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B1"
msgid "Just watch out for Milli!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B2"
msgid "This is the last time I trust the Freestar Rangers!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035896]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B3"
msgid "What kind of monster kidnaps someone's pet?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103585E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B4"
msgid "In on this? No no, this is... this is my plan. I just figured Yura would be the one to show up at our door."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B5"
msgid "If Yura hired you, I'm not surprised."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035871]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B6"
msgid "Getting paid is what I'm here for."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035868]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B7"
msgid "Let me pay you so you can get out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035868]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B8"
msgid "I'm sorry. No sense in you sticking around listening to this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016B9"
msgid "Let me pay you since I'm sure you don't want to stick around and hear us argue any longer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103586B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016BA"
msgid "And see? Milli's fine!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016BB"
msgid "Right, \"pet sitter\"?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016BC"
msgid "Excuse me, Yura. Are you going to tell me who these people are or what?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016BD"
msgid "I got a message from Atka that she was returning early, so I got down here as soon as I could. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016BE"
msgid "Oh yeah? Well, great timing. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016BF"
msgid "Just give me the details and let's get this over with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C0"
msgid "Check your numbers, \"errand boy.\" You're short."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103586C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C1"
msgid "<Global=SFFL_MS03_RansomCredits> credits is my password."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C857]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C2"
msgid "How was Roman involved in all this stuff again?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C854]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C3"
msgid "I can't believe Roman did all this for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C846]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C4"
msgid "So, how about it? I give you Milli and you put in a good word for me with Yura?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C844]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C5"
msgid "I can't believe I did all this for Yura and still screwed it up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C842]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C6"
msgid "I know I need to tell Yura how I feel. I just don't want to ruin everything if I make the wrong call."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035880]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C7"
msgid "Password."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C8"
msgid "But, if you change your mind, come find me. The sooner I can ditch this job, the better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358AD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016C9"
msgid "Hard stance! Okay, I mean, I get it. I obviously don't want to do this either."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103589D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016CA"
msgid "Pets I have time for. People not so much."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016CB"
msgid "You're the best. Here's the key to Atka's house."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016CC"
msgid "The question is, what does Yura have to do with any of this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016CD"
msgid "You look more than capable of scraping a few credits together."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016CE"
msgid "Aaand... not my problem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016CF"
msgid "It's steep, I'll give you that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A6B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D0"
msgid "All right, enough of this bullshit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D5C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D1"
msgid "Yes, no, and no."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D2"
msgid "I'm sure we can come to a new agreement."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D3"
msgid "Fine. I'll be back with your credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D5B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D4"
msgid "Not that I know of."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D5"
msgid "Well, it's done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D6"
msgid "And here I was thinking you were broke."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D7"
msgid "Nice sob story, but I'm just here for Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D8"
msgid "Now we're talking! You don't know what this means to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016D9"
msgid "This is all about getting a date?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016DA"
msgid "This is the perfect chance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016DB"
msgid "I've been waiting for my chance to break through that friend barrier, but it's hard. It's risky, you know?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016DC"
msgid "Hey, this has been years in the making. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016DD"
msgid "You see, this is all a setup for Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016DE"
msgid "Just hear me out. You got this petnapping thing all wrong."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016DF"
msgid "Tell me the favor first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E0"
msgid "Yura has everything to do with this, it's all for her. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E1"
msgid "Yeah, you and me both, but apparently Atka decided to come home earlier than expected."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E2"
msgid "This is someone's pet. You should just hand her over."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E3"
msgid "What makes you think Yura's interested to begin with?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D46]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E4"
msgid "You're outnumbered, so I don't care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D43]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E5"
msgid "You really want to know, dressed like that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D41]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E6"
msgid "When you put it that way..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E7"
msgid "So this is all some plan to entertain Yura?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E8"
msgid "Shouldn't you be off digging up some credits?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D25]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016E9"
msgid "Yeah, yeah, because if I never say anything, I'll regret it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016EA"
msgid "Be honest, and don't trust someone else to tell her how you feel."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016EB"
msgid "[Demand Credits: <Global=SFFL_MS03_PaymentCredits>] I think I'm owed a bit more after all this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016EC"
msgid "Ah, think, Roman, think..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016ED"
msgid "The house sitter? Dammit, I should've seen this coming."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016EE"
msgid "Fine, fine, I get it. I guess it is a bit much to dump on a complete stranger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016EF"
msgid "How about plan B? No more credits, just a simple favor, and Milli is all yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F0"
msgid "Okay, whoa. Let's talk about this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D4F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F1"
msgid "Never crossed my mind she'd bail on her sister and get someone else to take her place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D4F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F2"
msgid "She hates house sitting so we thought we'd shake things up a bit. Stage a little petnapping, maybe make a few credits on the side..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F3"
msgid "Your friends are right for once."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F4"
msgid "I suppose you're right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D14]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F5"
msgid "I'm the last person you'll see if you don't hand over Milli right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D48]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F6"
msgid "Oh god, thank you. You have no idea how freaked out I was. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D0F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F7"
msgid "The only explanation is that you're an idiot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D7B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F8"
msgid "Just make sure you stick to legal activities next time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016F9"
msgid "Yura didn't send me. I found your ransom note."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016FA"
msgid "And if she knew I was the one that took Milli, I swear we wouldn't be standing here now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016FB"
msgid "We only did all this to distract Yura... for fun!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016FC"
msgid "I know, I know, but it wasn't really petnapping, it was really more petborrowing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016FD"
msgid "But you aren't doing it for free, you're getting Milli, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D07]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016FE"
msgid "No way. Pass. Word."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C83E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0016FF"
msgid "Please, just let me explain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C83E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001700"
msgid "Look, this is all a big misunderstanding."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C83D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001701"
msgid "See? This was just one big misunderstanding. It was just for fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CEA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001702"
msgid "[Demand Credits: <Global=SFFL_MS03_PaymentCredits>] I don't do anything for free."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001703"
msgid "And what if I don't buy this story?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D28]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001704"
msgid "<Global=SFFL_MS03_RansomCredits> credits is my password."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001705"
msgid "A wha--? Er, right away. Just give me a sec."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001706"
msgid "Sure thing. Ask away."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001707"
msgid "What if you couldn't find anyone to house sit Atka's place?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001708"
msgid "It's just that house sitting is not for me, and at least this time I'm trying to get someone to take my place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001709"
msgid "I haven't exactly been reliable in the past, but I swore to her that I've changed... and I have!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00170A"
msgid "Well, yes and no. She sees this as a \"fourth chance\" to repair our relationship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CEB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00170B"
msgid "It's so simple. It's literally just watering some plants and feeding a milliwhale... every day until my sister gets back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00170C"
msgid "House sitting? Sounds like a lovely break to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A33C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00170D"
msgid "Nothing. Never mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A356]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00170E"
msgid "Roman and his friends are dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A363]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00170F"
msgid "I say if he did all this for me, that tells me plenty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A33E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001710"
msgid "He was pretty disappointed to see me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A35E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001711"
msgid "Besides, it's not like he was out murdering people."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A35E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001712"
msgid "Hey, why work your ass off when there's easier ways to make credits? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A358]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001713"
msgid "Oh my god, so he was expecting me to show up to get Milli all this time. No wonder I couldn't find him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A358]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001714"
msgid "I have been complaining to him about it for some time... I just never thought he'd do something like this, at least not for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A358]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001715"
msgid "Wait what? He did this for me? That's crazy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A35F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001716"
msgid "Maybe Roman's just trying to get ahead in this world."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B44C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001717"
msgid "Just like Roman to take the easy way, too. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A33B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001718"
msgid "Roman was trying to impress Yura with a staged petnapping."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A32E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001719"
msgid "And as you can see, Milli is fine!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A32E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00171A"
msgid "Atka, this is the pet sitter I was telling you about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A348]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00171B"
msgid "I'm sorry. Who are you? And are you saying Roman stole Milli while I was gone?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A32D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00171C"
msgid "As a Freestar Ranger, I personally looked after Milli's safety."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A33A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00171D"
msgid "Well, she seems fine. Milli does enjoy exploring, so a little adventure couldn't hurt."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A34C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00171E"
msgid "You'll be happy to know, he was just taking Milli for a walk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A34B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00171F"
msgid "You'll be happy to know, she was just taking Milli for a walk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001720"
msgid "Roman cares about people. In fact, if he stole Milli it was probably to get my attention in the first place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001721"
msgid "Well, you're not right either! You make it sound like he's just some loser criminal who's out to get people, but he's not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001722"
msgid "Let me ask you about something else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001723"
msgid "Why are you so afraid to tell her how you feel?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001724"
msgid "Can I ask you something else?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001725"
msgid "You think Atka will forgive you for this if she finds out?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF83]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001726"
msgid "If she's so nice, why use Atka and Milli to get Yura's attention?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001727"
msgid "Even if Atka did find out, I'd like to think she'd know Milli was safe with us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001728"
msgid "Milli knows us, so she came willingly, and just look at the setup we had for her. She just made herself at home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001729"
msgid "We just never thought Atka'd find out. Honest. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00172A"
msgid "She's not wrong, but at least she's always been nice to me, and pretty forgiving of Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00172B"
msgid "She thinks anyone who operates mostly in the Free Lanes is up to no good. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00172C"
msgid "Yura's sister? She's pretty nice, but she doesn't exactly approve of our lifestyle, if you know what I mean."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00172D"
msgid "It's beyond your comprehension. Just take the deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00172E"
msgid "Whoa, what? Who are you? How would you even know anything about that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00172F"
msgid "We took great care of your little Milli, ma'am, and it was our pleasure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001730"
msgid "And, I assume, a very trusted friend..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001731"
msgid "All this setup when you should be confessing to her directly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001732"
msgid "I think you pulled off the impossible."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001733"
msgid "Good work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001734"
msgid "Roman's been pretty nervous since you left. Hope you have some good news."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001735"
msgid "Hope you were able to help out Roman."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001736"
msgid "Didn't expect to see you back here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001737"
msgid "I sure owe you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001738"
msgid "I just gotta find something to take my mind off of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001739"
msgid "Did you talk to Yura yet?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF02]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00173A"
msgid "You again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00173B"
msgid "Roman's the best. I can't imagine life without him now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00173C"
msgid "I have nothing to say to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00173D"
msgid "I can't believe Atka came home early. I swear it was just to catch me slacking off."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00173E"
msgid "I don't get plants. I have a hard enough time taking care of myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00173F"
msgid "Please, I really think you should leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001740"
msgid "Milli seems to really like you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001741"
msgid "I appreciate you dealing with all this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001742"
msgid "See you around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001743"
msgid "Later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001744"
msgid "Don't forget about Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001745"
msgid "See you around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF19]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001746"
msgid "This silence can't be good..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001747"
msgid "You're dead!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001748"
msgid "Damn it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001749"
msgid "Worst house sitter ever!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00174A"
msgid "Yura, no!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00174B"
msgid "Milli!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00174C"
msgid "*sigh* But you're right. Just the possibility of losing him kills me, so maybe it is a chance worth taking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00174D"
msgid "Don't you think I've thought of that? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00174E"
msgid "But you're perfect together. Trust Roman. You'll be fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF81]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00174F"
msgid "And I do trust him. I really do owe it to both of us to stop shutting him out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF81]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001750"
msgid "You know... you're right. Roman's seen me at my worst and still hasn't given up on me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001751"
msgid "That's why I can't lose him. And if we dated, I know I'd lose him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001752"
msgid "In fact, it's hard not to care about the guy, especially when you get him to open up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF84]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001753"
msgid "Roman? He's the best friend anyone can ask for. Reliable, good listener, totally gets me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF89]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001754"
msgid "Why don't you think you deserve him? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001755"
msgid "Roman's the best. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001756"
msgid "I... I loved him, Atka... and I never got to tell him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001757"
msgid "Aren't you tired of Yura disappointing you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001758"
msgid "Why not let Yura live her own life?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001759"
msgid "What kind of guy is Roman?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00175A"
msgid "But what if something happens and I can't be that person anymore? Yura's friends are great, but they're just as unreliable as she is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00175B"
msgid "Credits, a place to stay, bailing her out of a bad situation or jail itself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00175C"
msgid "It's not like I haven't tried. It's just that I'm always her fallback plan. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00175D"
msgid "I've been doing it for a while, so at least I got one base covered."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00175E"
msgid "Be patient. I can do that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00175F"
msgid "I think he genuinely cares about her, and he's the only one I trust to look out for her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001760"
msgid "Out of all Yura's friends, Roman's probably the best. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001761"
msgid "But, unlike our parents, she never gave up on me, and she's always there when things really fall apart."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001762"
msgid "I wanted to hate her as a kid, she was always so perfect. Still is, of course."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001763"
msgid "I know, which is probably why I let her talk me into these stupid situations to begin with. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001764"
msgid "You'd think she likes being disappointed by now. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001765"
msgid "She makes me do something, I somehow fail to do it, we fight over it, she forgives me, rinse and repeat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001766"
msgid "Only every time she tries to get me to do something, and the cycle is always the same."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001767"
msgid "Whether or not I'll know what to do next time I see her is a completely different story."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001768"
msgid "I know her, of course. it's not like we've never spoken before. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001769"
msgid "I think I was rather convincing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00176A"
msgid "I'll do it. What's the worst that could happen at this point?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00176B"
msgid "But I guess if she heard it from me, too, maybe she'd consider it for once."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00176C"
msgid "Hmm, maybe you're right. I never wanted to bring it up because every time Atka does, it's a fight."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00176D"
msgid "I don't think she's ready, Roman."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00176E"
msgid "*sigh* That's classic Yura, though. Never thinks she's good enough for anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00176F"
msgid "What? I'm the one that doesn't deserve her. How can she even think that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C72A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001770"
msgid "I'm so tired."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C72A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001771"
msgid "But now... I just want to be in it a bit longer..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034E63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001772"
msgid "Hold up! You've got a bounty that'll need to be paid off if you want to keep that head on your shoulders."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034F7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001773"
msgid "I had to. You can't be trusted to vote correctly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001774"
msgid "Glad you found your way here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001775"
msgid "Your help's appreciated."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001776"
msgid "I'm sure he'll be willing to provide some credits for your trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001777"
msgid "Once you've set out, I'll talk to Mister Saint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001778"
msgid "Of course, just as we agreed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001779"
msgid "Maybe Spacers shouldn't be welcome here anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00177A"
msgid "Why? What happened?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00177B"
msgid "Happy to help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00177C"
msgid "It makes a strange kind of sense."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00177D"
msgid "Yes, yes, I see you. Hello?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00177E"
msgid "If you're looking for help, look elsewhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00177F"
msgid "H-Hello? Thank goodness! You don't know how good it is to hear another voice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056637]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001780"
msgid "Please be safe out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056611]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001781"
msgid "Please, tell me you've found something..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056627]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001782"
msgid "That's enough! Stop!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056617]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001783"
msgid "Ggh!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001784"
msgid "I don't have much in the way of credits, but here. Take them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001785"
msgid "I'm sorry. This is all just- I don't mean to sound unappreciative. Thank you for finding her. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001786"
msgid "I don't understand..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001787"
msgid "Um, goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001788"
msgid "Yes. Here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035301]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001789"
msgid "I don't know why she's doing this, but here. I wish I had more credits to give you. I'm sorry. Hopefully this will work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035301]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00178A"
msgid "I see... Thank you for telling me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00178B"
msgid "All she said was that she wanted you to go back home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00178C"
msgid "I'm so sorry, Sehoy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00178D"
msgid "You should go home. There's nothing left for you out here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105661A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00178E"
msgid "Why not? Did she say anything else? Why is she doing this...?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00178F"
msgid "No... No, Gabbie..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001790"
msgid "What? May I see the slates?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035303]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001791"
msgid "Space travel can take quite a while. I'm sure she's fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001792"
msgid "Wait, did you come all the way out here to find her?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056605]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001793"
msgid "That doesn't make any sense. Why would she say that? Please, tell me where you found her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001794"
msgid "[Lie] She didn't want you to know where she was. She said she still has a lot of work she needs to do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105662A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001795"
msgid "Perhaps Gabrielle can finally be at peace now. I just hope Sehoy can find it one day too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105660D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001796"
msgid "That can't be right... I'm sorry. I have to find her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001797"
msgid "Wait! Please! Dammit..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056607]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001798"
msgid "No! Wait, please!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105660A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001799"
msgid "I haven't seen her. But I can help you find her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017A2"
msgid "[Remain silent]"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017A3"
msgid "[Attack] No, I'm with a different tour guide. We hunt rich executives like you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017A4"
msgid "Is that right? Did you pay the 50k to hunt pirates?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017A5"
msgid "This is a known pirate hunting ground. We suggest powering up your weapons, we could spot one at any moment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031724]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017A7"
msgid "Dilute the drinks if you need to, but we won't be diluting our profits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031724]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017A8"
msgid "Beverage sales are a staple of this operation. A pillar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031724]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017A9"
msgid "No, we should not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031722]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017AA"
msgid "Maybe we should charge less for the drinks, at least until the quality improves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031722]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017AB"
msgid "Of course, the patrons don't like that overly much."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031722]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017AC"
msgid "I could always mix the drinks a little weaker."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031707]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017AD"
msgid "If you listened to my suggestions, we could do better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031707]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017AE"
msgid "I don't control how much our patrons choose to spend on my goods."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017AF"
msgid "Either we take steps to bolster profits or accept that they'll be less than they could."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B0"
msgid "You can't have it both ways."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B1"
msgid "Just a few bots could still make a big difference."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B2"
msgid "You know there's only a handful of us keeping this place safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B3"
msgid "I didn't say an army."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031703]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B4"
msgid "Look, nobody would enjoy that more than me, but you know I ain't got time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031703]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B5"
msgid "About building you an army of robots?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031701]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B6"
msgid "Have you thought any more about my idea?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE44]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B7"
msgid "Join me on my ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B8"
msgid "Interesting. You look alive to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017B9"
msgid "I feel good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017BA"
msgid "You accused me of joking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017BB"
msgid "Allow an old... woman, to speak a moment longer on their own ship. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017BC"
msgid "How do you feel in your body? Do you feel alive?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017BD"
msgid "You're joking. That can't be true."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017BE"
msgid "My kind? What do you mean by that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017BF"
msgid "I'm not afraid of you. Are you afraid of me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C0"
msgid "Likewise. It feels good to have you here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C1"
msgid "I am glad you stopped by. I was beginning to think that you were... afraid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C2"
msgid "Hello."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C3"
msgid "I'm not sure I'm hungry anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103073B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C4"
msgid "Good. And you will eat every last bit, or you will make us angry again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103073A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C5"
msgid "You inconvenience me by coming on my ship, and yet you decline my hospitality. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030752]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C6"
msgid "Leave, immediately! Leave! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030752]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C7"
msgid "Stop talking to me. You are no longer welcome here, I want you out of my ship immediately. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE2A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C8"
msgid "So, about that food..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105023A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017C9"
msgid "No, wait, don't leave me here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050238]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017CA"
msgid "Where are you going? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050235]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017CB"
msgid "Uh... bye?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050233]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017CC"
msgid "Uh, see you later?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050231]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017CD"
msgid "All right, bye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017CE"
msgid "Leave me be."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050241]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017CF"
msgid "Why aren't you saying anything? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D0"
msgid "*Sigh* What a waste of time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D1"
msgid "I've got a job lined up for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D2"
msgid "Looking for work?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R02SharedInfo01_TargetPlead01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D3"
msgid "No! You don't have to do this! No!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A432]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D4"
msgid "Thank you. I swear you'll never see me again!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A42C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D5"
msgid "You're in danger. Someone put a target on your back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A439]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D6"
msgid "Good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A431]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D7"
msgid "I'll do it. Give me the details. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D8"
msgid "Damn, thought I was a goner... I swear, I'll leave and never look back!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102AF64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017D9"
msgid "Give me something that I can say is proof that I killed you. Then leave, and never look back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104480C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017DA"
msgid "Get out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044806]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017DB"
msgid "That doesn't concern you. No questions asked, remember? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017DC"
msgid "[Attack] There's nothing you can do. I'm here to kill you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017DD"
msgid "Thank god, just take it. Take it all. You'll never see me ever again!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017DE"
msgid "[Accept <Global=SFFL_R02_BribeAmount> Credits] Give me the credits and your ID, and don't ever show your face around here again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017DF"
msgid "Wait, wait, wait... look, they never checked my pockets. I have some credits, not much, but... oh god, please, just take it and let me go!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E0"
msgid "This is a nightmare! This can't be happening!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104609A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E1"
msgid "No... oh god, even after all I've been through? What do I do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E2"
msgid "Who are you? Is it safe? You have to get me out of here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E3"
msgid "It depends on what the job is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E4"
msgid "It won't happen again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E5"
msgid "I thought I could get away with it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E6"
msgid "No, I don't think you're stupid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E7"
msgid "Don't get fucking cute with me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105911C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E8"
msgid "I'm... I'm not just gonna wait here for you to kill me! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029A40]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017E9"
msgid "Well, you're in one piece. That's good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029A3A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017EA"
msgid "Good luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F8FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017EB"
msgid "I didn't lose you, did I?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029712]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017EC"
msgid "Pleasure working with you. Keep an eye out - I may have more opportunities for you, later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029712]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017ED"
msgid "Well done, well done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102970C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017EE"
msgid "I'm marking the locations for you. Good luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029714]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017EF"
msgid "I'll do it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102971A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F0"
msgid "Come on, you really don't wanna pass this up. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029726]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F1"
msgid "Hmmph. I was trying to help you out. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029886]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F2"
msgid "If you're set up for it, and wanna go the extra mile, you can deliver the goods to the Trade Authority yourself. Hell, makes my job a whole lot easier, and you'll get more credits for the trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029887]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F3"
msgid "Hmmph, suit yourself. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F4"
msgid "If I have more opportunities for you in the future, I'll find you. Stay safe out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F5"
msgid "Always a pleasure working with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F6"
msgid "Gotta run!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F7"
msgid "Uh, that won't be necessary. I never said anything. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F8"
msgid "I'm gonna have to report this to the Freestar Rangers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017F9"
msgid "Hey, your loss."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017FA"
msgid "How does that sound to you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017FB"
msgid "Thing is, I need someone that isn't afraid to... bend the law, so to speak. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017FC"
msgid "Good, you picked up. I've got an opportunity for us to make some decent cash."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017FD"
msgid "Hmmph, suit yourself. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017FE"
msgid "The contraband should be in these locations. Good luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0017FF"
msgid "I'm marking the locations for you. Good luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001800"
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001801"
msgid "I'll do it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001802"
msgid "Hey, remember me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001803"
msgid "Fantastic, this should be easy money then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001804"
msgid "*Sigh* That's it, all right? Let's stop talking about this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001805"
msgid "The bullets started flying, I got hit in the leg and arm, my neck was grazed. I got lucky though. I managed to hit him square in the head, and that was that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001806"
msgid "I came back with the contraband and he was waiting on the ship with a gun in his hand. Told me to hand the stuff over and that he was gonna leave me stranded."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001807"
msgid "Well, someone or something got into his head and convinced him to double-cross me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001808"
msgid "I was on a typical job with my pilot at the time. We worked together for, maybe, fifteen years or so? I trusted this guy with my life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001809"
msgid "I could be killed getting this contraband for you. Just answer my questions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00180A"
msgid "Works for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00180B"
msgid "We don't have to talk about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00180C"
msgid "I'd still like to hear it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00180D"
msgid "Why can't you get this contraband yourself?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010522E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00180E"
msgid "I'll see you around. Maybe we'll have better luck next time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010522E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00180F"
msgid "*Sigh* It's not like I would've fared any better. I appreciate you trying, at least, but I obviously can't give you any money."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010522E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001810"
msgid "Damn it, really? What happened? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C84F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001811"
msgid "For the first time in a long while, I feel hope for better days."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C84E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001812"
msgid "Thanks to you, my son and I are talking again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C454]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001813"
msgid "Talking to my father again after so long has been a little awkward, but we'll figure it out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059E37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001814"
msgid "If I never see another Spacer in here again, that'll be just fine with me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106574A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001815"
msgid "Oh good, you're here. Maddie asked me to send you her way. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102672A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001816"
msgid "Your credits are more than welcome here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059E35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001817"
msgid "Heard you gave those Spacers some hell. I bet that was fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026726]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001818"
msgid "I sure ain't bored. Got no time to be."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026713]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001819"
msgid "The reek of this place permeates everything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026710]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00181A"
msgid "Don't get nosy about the patrons. We don't like that around here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102670D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00181B"
msgid "Unless you want to spend the night in a cell, I suggest you play by the rules."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00181C"
msgid "You should check in with Maddie. She wants to talk to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00181D"
msgid "Sorry, got a lot on my mind right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059E34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00181E"
msgid "From what I hear, those Spacers got what was coming to them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026709]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00181F"
msgid "Keep walking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059E33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001820"
msgid "You the one who took on the Spacers? Nice job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001821"
msgid "Might want to keep your distance. Some of us have itchy trigger fingers. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026704]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001822"
msgid "If there's trouble, let us handle it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026703]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001823"
msgid "Can't chat right now. I'm on duty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026700]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001824"
msgid "Behave yourself and we won't have a problem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDDA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001825"
msgid "Doing okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDD9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001826"
msgid "You seem a little distracted there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001827"
msgid "I'm in no hurry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001828"
msgid "Need a little quiet time?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001829"
msgid "Is it just me, or did a whole lot of awkward silence just come walking down the hall?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00182A"
msgid "I'll wait."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00182B"
msgid "Stop wasting my time and get on with it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDFE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00182C"
msgid "Until next time!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00182D"
msgid "Somewhere else you need to be?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00182E"
msgid "Yeah, I was done talking to you anyway."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDEF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00182F"
msgid "All done? Well, you know where I'll be."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001830"
msgid "See you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001831"
msgid "Take care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDE3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001832"
msgid "Whatever. Just go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001833"
msgid "No, we stand our ground."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001834"
msgid "Hell no! I've worked too hard to make this place what it is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001835"
msgid "And give up Anchorpoint?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001836"
msgid "That, plus a high degree of discipline when it comes to expenses, keeps us afloat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001837"
msgid "For many, being off the beaten path is a large part of appeal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001838"
msgid "Instead, we rely on word-of-mouth from a loyal base of frequent patrons."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001839"
msgid "I prefer not to advertise, due both to the cost and the unwanted attention it would risk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00183A"
msgid "I won't deny that it's been a challenge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00183B"
msgid "What's your background?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A525]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00183C"
msgid "I suggest you avoid making assumptions and simply stick to the rules."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A525]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00183D"
msgid "But a smuggler's den? No, not at all. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A525]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00183E"
msgid "Is it possible that some of it would not be considered entirely legal? Perhaps"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A525]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00183F"
msgid "What kinds of dealings our patrons conduct here is not my business."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A528]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001840"
msgid "I'm hardly asking for much. Just civil behavior."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A534]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001841"
msgid "Our patrons expect to conduct whatever business they wish free from prying eyes and ears."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A534]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001842"
msgid "We also value privacy and discretion here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A534]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001843"
msgid "Acts of theft or violence will be met with a swift response."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A534]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001844"
msgid "We're happy to welcome all who pass through the airlock, but our hospitality has limits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A534]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001845"
msgid "A few words of advice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001846"
msgid "Now it seems they're coming back to teach us a lesson."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001847"
msgid "His friends didn't take kindly to it, and stormed out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001848"
msgid "One of the guests, a Spacer, was causing trouble. We locked him up so he could sleep off his drink."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C010]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001849"
msgid "Yeah, he's a work in progress. Probably always will be, but ain't we all?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C010]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00184A"
msgid "I'm working on rigging up a harness so he can carry tools and such. Be my little helper."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C010]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00184B"
msgid "He keeps me company. And he keeps the unwanted attention away, if you catch my drift."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C010]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00184C"
msgid "*Laugh* Okay, okay, bad joke."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C010]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00184D"
msgid "Yep, my creation. My pet project, you could say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C014]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00184E"
msgid "How do you keep stocked up on parts and supplies out here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C015]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00184F"
msgid "Some of us just ain't the \"settle down in peace and quiet\" type."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C015]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001850"
msgid "I get it. Life out on the edge ain't for everyone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C015]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001851"
msgid "And miss all the excitement?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C028]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001852"
msgid "They're lucky to have you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001853"
msgid "If it wasn't for me, everyone would have been sucked out into space cause we lost a wall."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001854"
msgid "Always had a knack for machines. Good thing, too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001855"
msgid "Name's Maddie. I keep the place running."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C026]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001856"
msgid "Knocked the damn thing loose and sprayed hot water all over himself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C026]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001857"
msgid "Had a trader in here last week who leaned on a pipe when the sealant was still drying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C026]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001858"
msgid "Got enough on my hands without having to clean up after fools who start poking and prodding things."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C026]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001859"
msgid "You better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C021]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00185A"
msgid "Place is barely holding together as it is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C021]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00185B"
msgid "You new around here? Well don't break anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C022]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00185C"
msgid "If you need medical attention, Cutty is our resident physician."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C022]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00185D"
msgid "We have two vendors, Killian and Darcy, who stock some useful items."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C022]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00185E"
msgid "Valeria runs the bar, which has a modest selection."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C022]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00185F"
msgid "Just the basics, really. We're a small operation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031421]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001860"
msgid "What kind of illness does Gabriel suffer from?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031432]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001861"
msgid "*Sigh* I don't love missing a huge chunk of my son's childhood, but at least he'll have one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031432]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001862"
msgid "A couple of years still."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031435]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001863"
msgid "Sure thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103142F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001864"
msgid "You are vastly overstating the dangers. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031422]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001865"
msgid "Space travel is very safe. People do it all the time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031429]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001866"
msgid "Safety was not foremost on anyone's mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031429]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001867"
msgid "I should know, I grew up on Neon and fell in with a gang."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031429]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001868"
msgid "People do a lot of crazy things. That doesn't make them safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031418]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001869"
msgid "Space travel is incredibly dangerous. Anyone who arrives safely is lucky."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031418]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00186A"
msgid "But that's not what I mean."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031418]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00186B"
msgid "It's pretty remote out here. There's no United Colonies or Freestar Collective patrol ships."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031418]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00186C"
msgid "This area? Well, if you mean the Algorab system then maybe. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031438]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00186D"
msgid "Well maybe you just haven't stopped to consider the hazards of space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031430]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00186E"
msgid "You must be relieved to have made it here safe and sound."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031430]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00186F"
msgid "The ship that just docked, that was you, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031442]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001870"
msgid "How do you cope with a constant fear of space while living on a star station?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001871"
msgid "I'm sure you'll find something useful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031704]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001872"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001873"
msgid "I'd like to see what you have in stock."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001874"
msgid "So yeah, this place needs a doctor."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001875"
msgid "Get a few drinks in them, and the violence always follows."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001876"
msgid "Spacers, pirates, outlaws, smugglers... they're all welcome here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001877"
msgid "See, we get all kinds in this place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001878"
msgid "You're either new around here, or just real lucky."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001879"
msgid "How much do you trust Saint?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00187A"
msgid "My name and face are known in the United Colonies, and not looked on favorably."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00187B"
msgid "In truth, the remote location was a large part of the appeal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00187C"
msgid "I wasn't in a position to negotiate, but I wouldn't say I was treated unfairly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00187D"
msgid "How did you get this job?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00187E"
msgid "Sorry, but no. I'm not a pirate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037168]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00187F"
msgid "You've got yourself a deal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037170]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001880"
msgid "What kinds of modifications are we talking about?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001881"
msgid "Are you okay? You seem to be in a bad mood."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001882"
msgid "Why would someone kidnap your son?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001883"
msgid "Of course. But if you'll give me a moment, there's something else I'd like to talk about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001884"
msgid "Likewise. And may I say, your timing is fortunate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047142]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001885"
msgid "Sounds simple enough. Sign me up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104714E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001886"
msgid "It's not what you think. Hear me out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047140]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001887"
msgid "There could be other interested parties, so danger is a possibility."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047140]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001888"
msgid "I have the location of one such lost shipment, and I need someone to retrieve it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047140]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001889"
msgid "Occasionally, in dire circumstances, pilots have to jettison their illicit cargo."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047141]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00188A"
msgid "Not quite. There's a little more to it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00188B"
msgid "It was blind luck I learned that it existed at all. A very literal case of finders, keepers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00188C"
msgid "As I said, the station was abandoned and forgotten. That was many decades ago."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00188D"
msgid "Nobody contested your claim on the station?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00188E"
msgid "It's true that maintenance is one of my biggest costs, but I accept it as part of the venture."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00188F"
msgid "It's certainly better off than it was when I found it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F29]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001890"
msgid "Resourceful ship's captain sounds an awful lot like a polite way of saying criminal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001891"
msgid "It was a shameful betrayal of the oath you took, and you got exactly what you deserved."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001892"
msgid "You used your position in Vanguard to covertly siphon funds into forged accounts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001893"
msgid "I knew your name sounded familiar, but I've only just placed it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001894"
msgid "This guy's a real piece of work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001895"
msgid "Charging that kind of interest to a mother with a sick child?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001896"
msgid "Stealing from cargo ships? You must have been pretty resourceful to pull that off."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F21]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001897"
msgid "I'd say it falls on your parents for not raising you better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F20]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001898"
msgid "I just said that I do. You don't need to pile on."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001899"
msgid "Nothing boring about being out here. Besides, I get to be in charge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00189A"
msgid "Every day was the same, staring at walls and counting the hours. A living death by boredom."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00189B"
msgid "I retired, but the pension was next to nothing. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00189C"
msgid "I used to be Freestar Security. Got wounded in the line of duty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A5E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00189D"
msgid "As a matter of fact, I have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00189E"
msgid "Can do!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00189F"
msgid "Refresh my memory. What is it you want me to do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A0"
msgid "What do you say? Ready for a daring raid on a totally unsuspecting cargo ship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A1"
msgid "That's a yes, by the way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A2"
msgid "Does the auxiliary thermal control circuit overheat every time I so much as look at it funny?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A3"
msgid "Not yet. And to be honest, I'm getting a little antsy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106574B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A4"
msgid "I have the shipment's location and a willing buyer. I just need you to collect it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106574B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A5"
msgid "There's a lost shipment of contraband toxins, likely jettisoned to avoid piracy or seizure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065751]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A6"
msgid "Nothing yet, but it's only a matter of time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106573B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A7"
msgid "I understand. Perhaps another time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A8"
msgid "Most of the injuries I treat result from drunken brawls."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018A9"
msgid "We get our share of colorful characters through here, and more than a few are prone to violence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018AA"
msgid "Reasonably so, yes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018AB"
msgid "For that, I am in your debt."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018AC"
msgid "It's a start, and more than I could have dared to hope for."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018AD"
msgid "I would describe our relationship as cordial, at least for now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018AE"
msgid "He sent me a letter, and then came to visit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018AF"
msgid "To attack a Spacer stronghold head-on? No way I'd give that order."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B0"
msgid "In that case, you can see yourself out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B1"
msgid "This shouldn't take long."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B2"
msgid "Hold still for a minute."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DDE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B3"
msgid "Not like I've got anything better to do. Now hold still so I can have a look..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B4"
msgid "Come on, there's nothing wrong with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B5"
msgid "You're fine. Not a scratch on you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DDA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B6"
msgid "Look at this mess. What the hell kind of trouble have you been getting into?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B7"
msgid "Damn. You're a mess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B8"
msgid "Might want to bite down on something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018B9"
msgid "You're good to go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018BA"
msgid "How about you come back when you've got the the money."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018BB"
msgid "Can't afford to treat you for free."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031695]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018BC"
msgid "Dovidenja."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018BD"
msgid "Hey, you're in the Vanguard, right? I can tell. I hope to join up myself someday."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018BE"
msgid "As far as I'm concerned, it's over. Everyone should get back to work. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_QuestSharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018BF"
msgid "Man, I was really hoping for a guillotine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103169B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C0"
msgid "His past aside, I'm thankful Hal's still here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C1"
msgid "The shadows of my past will always linger, but I do feel a weight has been lifted from my shoulders."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103169F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C2"
msgid "Exile it is. The punishment fits the crime."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C3"
msgid "Whatever Hal's done; he's making it right here. We made the right decision."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C4"
msgid "Hal sealed his fate when he broke the law."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C6"
msgid "We're murderers. We murdered him with that vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030761]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C7"
msgid "I just rush through things sometimes, and it always bites me in the ass."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030761]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C8"
msgid "Yeah, I was doing maintenance on it, and I messed something up with the valve."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018C9"
msgid "She's trying to sell it on the black market."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018CA"
msgid "You return. I trust the vote is done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018CB"
msgid "Everyone, stand down! Sasha, escort the prisoner to a holding cell, now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030765]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018CC"
msgid "Is the dumpster locked?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103076E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018CD"
msgid "Of course, we don't believe in divinities, not anymore, anyway! But a feeling is not a god."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030770]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018CE"
msgid "How does it feel to be out?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103076F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018CF"
msgid "It feels divine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031367]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D0"
msgid "Yes! Do it! Break down that wall!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031365]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D1"
msgid "If the magnet damages the parts, how are they still of use?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D2"
msgid "How is any of this okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D3"
msgid "[Chems] I found this along with other evidence."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D4"
msgid "He killed Caruso. This was retribution."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D5"
msgid "Because you're the most neutral party here. You've seen Shinar, but you've also seen what Hal's done for us here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D6"
msgid "Yeah, hopefully."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D7"
msgid "Hopefully it doesn't come to that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D8"
msgid "Thank you. Keep in mind, it's still a democratic process."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018D9"
msgid "Based on what I saw, it would've been a fine outpost, had your luck been better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E329]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018DA"
msgid "Exile."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103FAED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018DB"
msgid "I'm not going to tell you. You'll just have to wait."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010483F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018DC"
msgid "I'm sure it's how you cope."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051379]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018DD"
msgid "We'll try our best."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052C8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018DE"
msgid "Never trust a bucket of bolts to do a person's job. No offense to Vasco."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052C8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018DF"
msgid "It depends on how competent the hands are, robot or otherwise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018E0"
msgid "I don't know how to feel about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018E1"
msgid "It's strange. I've been waiting for so long to hear those words and yet..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018E2"
msgid "Perhaps those feelings will come. Now I just feel... well, I don't know how I feel."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018E3"
msgid "*Sigh* Either way, thank you, stranger. While I don't know if closure will ever come, it's good to know others will not befall the same fate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0018E4"
msgid "What? Really? Then he's finally dead? I... I don't know what to say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083DA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A11"
msgid "Need something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A12"
msgid "I need a beer. Maybe two."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A13"
msgid "Is now a good time to talk about my salary?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A14"
msgid "Is it just me, or does the galaxy need more cryptids?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A15"
msgid "Are you bored? I'm bored."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A16"
msgid "What nightmarish horrors do we plan on seeing today, Captain?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C5B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A17"
msgid "Downed one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A18"
msgid "Another corpse for the pile."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A19"
msgid "Got 'em."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D40]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A1A"
msgid "Do you mind if I ask you some personal questions?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C42]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A1B"
msgid "Doesn't matter as long as I'm getting paid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C08]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A1C"
msgid "Good. I'm going on a break."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D5A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A1D"
msgid "I have no evidence to corroborate this, but those dancers in the Astral Lounge are definitely the product of mushrooms."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B7B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A1E"
msgid "Do you have any fun facts about fungi?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C0C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A1F"
msgid "It's all right. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A20"
msgid "There's not really a reason to go back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A21"
msgid "If it were, I wouldn't be standing here with you. I'd be communing with ghosts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A22"
msgid "Did you ever ship to places outside Jemison?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C36]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A23"
msgid "That sounds like a relaxing hobby."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C47]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A24"
msgid "Is that where you learned necromancy isn't real?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083E3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A25"
msgid "If so, good job. I could learn a thing or two from you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B5E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A26"
msgid "Sorry to hear you're unemployed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A27"
msgid "Sorry to hear that. It's hard to find work in this economy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CE3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A28"
msgid "Same."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A29"
msgid "[<Global=Crew_RecruitCost_TextReplacementValue> Credits] I'm sorry, I can't afford that right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A2A"
msgid "[Pay <Global=Crew_RecruitCost_TextReplacementValue> Credits] That won't be a problem. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C2F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A2B"
msgid "You know, I think I'd rather keep traveling on my own. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D17]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A2C"
msgid "Oh cool, you're leaving."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A2D"
msgid "Assuming you could actually raise them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A2E"
msgid "Now I'll just have to make people miserable the old fashioned way, by mocking them. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A2F"
msgid "Well, you can't. I was a naive little goth with dreams of terrorizing the galaxy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D3C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A30"
msgid "Guess I'll just read a book."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A31"
msgid "Sure. I'll wait."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D39]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A32"
msgid "I'll try not to get bored."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C83]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A33"
msgid "They're just orbiting around a planet, or moon, I forget. I have it written down somewhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A34"
msgid "What flavor Chunks? Asking the important questions here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A35"
msgid "Trick question. Chunks don't have flavor. But I digress."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A36"
msgid "You joke, but that's how horror movies start."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A37"
msgid "Let's get moving."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A38"
msgid "The only real difference is that witches get burned at the stake, whereas bankers get golden parachutes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A39"
msgid "Yeah. It's not exactly apples to apples, but it does come from the same tree."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A3A"
msgid "Don't know why, seems like it'd be an improvement. But what do I know. Certainly not enough to be a banker."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A3B"
msgid "I told him I could pay him with a potion that would turn him into a newt, but he refused."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A3C"
msgid "Well, now I need find work somewhere else. My landlord keeps asking for this thing called \"rent.\""
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C0F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A3D"
msgid "It's just instead of a club, it's like, the universe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C0F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A3E"
msgid "Aren't you like a bouncer or something? Throwing people out is kind of your thing. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A3F"
msgid "But tell you what, come back in a few hours. If I don't get the job, I might reconsider."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A40"
msgid "And no one person can be as evil as a bank."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A41"
msgid "Hm. Tempting. But I want to work for an evil greater than myself. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B51]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A42"
msgid "As one does."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A43"
msgid "Those feelings are what I like to paint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A44"
msgid "Or the moment you realize your youth is gone, and your best years are behind you, but you still have to live, because you're too scared to die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A45"
msgid "It's a lot of things. Early Mondays. Gray hairs. The look on people's faces when they file their taxes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010781EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A48"
msgid "Welcome to Anchorpoint -- the perfect place to relax and resupply."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010781EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A49"
msgid "Here at Anchorpoint, we offer cold drinks, supplies of all kinds and a comfortable place to relax."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010781E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A4A"
msgid "Need a break from traveling the Free Lanes? We're here to serve you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010781E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A4B"
msgid "You've arrived at Anchorpoint, where everyone is welcome."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A4F"
msgid "Make it stop, please make it stop."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A50"
msgid "What's going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A51"
msgid "What if I'm wrong? Oh god, what if I'm wrong? *Sob* The eyes... the eyes! The eyes!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A52"
msgid "Right? I won't be able to see the eyes anymore, right? They won't be able to torture me... but what if I'm wrong? Oh god... oh god... what if I'm wrong..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A53"
msgid "God damn it, why me? Why not torture someone else? I've had enough! Once I rip out my eyes, they can't torture me anymore! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A54"
msgid "Don't be so stupid. Snap out of it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A55"
msgid "Don't do that. That's not going to fix anything!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A56"
msgid "Of course I am, and so are you. We're all being watched. The eyes are watching us right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A57"
msgid "You're having a crisis. Let me board so I can help you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A58"
msgid "You need help. You're a danger to yourself and possibly others."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A59"
msgid "I'm supposed to believe you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A5A"
msgid "Maybe you're right. You are being watched."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A5B"
msgid "Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A5C"
msgid "No, you're blind. I envy you, but you're blind. Blind to the danger around you, around everyone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A5D"
msgid "Please god, please don't be one of them. Please..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A5E"
msgid "You... you... you aren't one of them, are you? One of the eyes..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A5F"
msgid "I can't take it anymore..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A60"
msgid "They're everywhere..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C448]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A61"
msgid "Thanks for your time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A62"
msgid "Do you feel like that's an unfair characterization? Any words for the skeptics?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A63"
msgid "They point to the personal wealth you've sunk into it, and the speculative nature of the venture."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A64"
msgid "Some have characterized Anchorpoint as a vanity project."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C442]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A65"
msgid "I assure you, we're going into this with clear eyes and a great plan."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C442]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A66"
msgid "It's a simple truth that bold ideas elicit strong reactions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C442]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A67"
msgid "I welcome it. Throughout our history, every visionary has had skeptics."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A68"
msgid "Progress is inevitable, especially if there's a profit to be made."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A69"
msgid "As someone who's spent her entire professional life in the world of commerce, I can promise you one thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A6A"
msgid "*Chuckle* I hardly think that's necessary."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A6B"
msgid "Very well, but make it quick."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C44A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A6C"
msgid "Very well, but make it quick."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A6D"
msgid "This is Chief Engineer Gus Gentry of Anchorpoint Station, signing off for the last time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A6E"
msgid "Damn... wish I could be there to see it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A6F"
msgid "Until one day, she'll light up the sky over Algorab II in a last, glorious fireball."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A70"
msgid "Without the occasional correction from the orbital thrusters, she'll start to drop."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A71"
msgid "And now, it's time to say goodbye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A72"
msgid "A whole lot of folks put a whole lot of passion into the job. We built her right, and built her to last."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A73"
msgid "I remember the day we started construction on this station. There was so much enthusiasm, so much pride."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A74"
msgid "You live in a place long enough, it starts to feel like a kind of home, I suppose."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A75"
msgid "Don't know why I'm recording this. Just seems like somebody should say something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D253]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A76"
msgid "Okay. I better head back out. Not like I can stay in the cockpit the whole time. What a bitch..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D25C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A78"
msgid "Hello? Can you hear me? This is Jara Kleel, pilot of the Sycorax."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D260]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A79"
msgid "C'mon... I'm dead in the void here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D25F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A7A"
msgid "Please, if you're reading me... I need your help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D25E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A7B"
msgid "I've taken damage from a pirate attack and lost power."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D504]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A80"
msgid "No! We just finished fixing up that ship!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B165]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A81"
msgid "I had friends on that ship, you monster!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A82"
msgid "Mayday! Mayday! Please help us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B169]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A83"
msgid "Looks like we've got ourselves a live one, girls!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C46F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A84"
msgid "Another pirate ship? I told you this was a bad idea!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C473]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A85"
msgid "Let's find the source of the signal and then get the hell out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C473]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A86"
msgid "I don't know about you, but I don't have a good feeling about this place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C470]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A87"
msgid "Maybe we should just continue on our way..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C470]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A88"
msgid "I do not like this...it feels like an ambush."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B96C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A89"
msgid "Bye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B971]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A8A"
msgid "Waiting for your response. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B970]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A8B"
msgid "Please acknowledge. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B97F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A8C"
msgid "Docking permissions granted. See you on board. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B97E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A8D"
msgid "You're free to board whenever you're ready."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B97D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A8E"
msgid "We'll see you on board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B97B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A8F"
msgid "Good to finally see another ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B97A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A90"
msgid "Please acknowledge. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A318]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A91"
msgid "Still awaiting your response. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A307]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A92"
msgid "If you're able and willing to assist with repairs, please dock with us. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A307]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A93"
msgid "We were attacked while hauling some cargo and our ship was damaged. We need assistance.  "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A307]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A94"
msgid "Thanks for responding."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A96"
msgid "You're boring the hell out of me. Hurry up and say something!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A97"
msgid "Let's go. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A98"
msgid "Well, well, well..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A99"
msgid "What do we have here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A9A"
msgid "*Whistling*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A9B"
msgid "Hey diddle diddle..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C747]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A9C"
msgid "I don't know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A311]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A9D"
msgid "I'm telling you, you don't wanna miss this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A306]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A9E"
msgid "You've gotta be kidding me. No one wants to play? Really?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C74E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001A9F"
msgid "So that's one wrong so far. One dead body. Don't let it get to your head. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA0"
msgid "Seems like I don't have a choice. I'll play."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA1"
msgid "Fantastic. Amazing! Let the games begin!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA2"
msgid "He's insane, help us! He killed the pilot, he-"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4BA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA3"
msgid "Come here, honey, say hi to our contestant! Get over here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C749]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA4"
msgid "Well, then, I guess someone is dying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA5"
msgid "What are you talking about?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA6"
msgid "Well, before I agree to anything, I need more info."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA7"
msgid "Oh? Maybe this will convince you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA8"
msgid "I'm not doing anything with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C74C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AA9"
msgid "The principal. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C750]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AAA"
msgid "Not bad, but wrong. A principal sometimes enters the classrooms, after all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C746]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AAB"
msgid "A potato."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C756]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AAC"
msgid "Not bad, but don't get cocky! We still have two more to go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AAD"
msgid "Help me! Help me, please! He's gonna kill us-"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C753]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AAE"
msgid "Your dead body after I kill you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AAF"
msgid "I don't know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C744]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB0"
msgid "Congrats, you just doomed someone out of an utter lack of initiative. Would it have killed you to take a guess?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB1"
msgid "Well, it's been fun, but I'd better get going. I have some business to attend to. Thanks for playing! Hahaha!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB2"
msgid "Well, you tried your best, but I guess nobody's perfect. Looks like my friends here didn't get out of this unscathed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB3"
msgid "Guess I'll just have to find another contestant for my little game. I better get going then, it's been fun! Hahaha!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB4"
msgid "Wow, three for three. Good job. But now I have my own riddle to solve: what the hell am I supposed to do with these hostages now? I can't let 'em go to waste!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB5"
msgid "You, get over here! Now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB6"
msgid "Before we enter our grand finale, let me just remind you what you're playing for."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB7"
msgid "What's light as a feather, but even the strongest person can't hold it for long?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB8"
msgid "All right, one more to go. The grand finale! You ready?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AB9"
msgid "Do you hear that? Do you hear how scared they are? How exciting is that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ABA"
msgid "All right, all right, enough! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ABB"
msgid "I was bored. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ABC"
msgid "Why are you doing this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ABD"
msgid "Do. Not. End. This. Hail!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ABE"
msgid "Lighten up, they did their best."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C2B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ABF"
msgid "But I also wouldn't be opposed to you tossing it into the nearest incinerator."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C29]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC0"
msgid "You took the words right out of my mouth."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C26]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC1"
msgid "To see me in that uniform, memorialized in this way... I don't know how to feel."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C2A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC2"
msgid "No, it's clearly your evil twin."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C23]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC3"
msgid "Hero? Is that what they're calling me? I find that term almost offensive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C22]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC4"
msgid "Oh my god. Is that supposed to be me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C34]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC5"
msgid "Have you seen this action figure?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C81C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC6"
msgid "I trust you know what you're doing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C816]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC7"
msgid "I'll keep an eye on him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC8"
msgid "Final warning. Back off, now!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AC9"
msgid "You better back off right now. I'm not joking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4EB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ACA"
msgid "Don't worry about your money, you'll get it as soon as I talk to my boss."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ACB"
msgid "Still, don't follow me or I'll shoot you right down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ACC"
msgid "Looks like I made the right choice trusting you after all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD45]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ACD"
msgid "Tell me, is your ship worth more than you life?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD4C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ACE"
msgid "This... wasn't supposed to happen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD4D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ACF"
msgid "I think you've made your point..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD4B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD0"
msgid "I'll... take your offer now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC3E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD1"
msgid "Drop the act. I'll take you to Neon, no questions asked."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC4B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD2"
msgid "You don't know what you're getting into."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC5D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD3"
msgid "What the hell are you talking about, fool?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD4"
msgid "You mean one where we don't shoot each other to bits? Anything's possible, I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC44]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD5"
msgid "Am I supposed to be impressed?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC4A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD6"
msgid "I'm sure you'd like me to believe that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD7"
msgid "Put your gun down now, then we'll talk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC4E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD8"
msgid "I know how this ends for you. It's not too late."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AD9"
msgid "Neither do you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ADA"
msgid "You really don't need to point that thing at me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ADB"
msgid "All right, we'll do it your way then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC41]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ADC"
msgid "You're right, no one needs to get hurt."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC48]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ADD"
msgid "[Attack] Oh well, I gave you a chance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ADE"
msgid "Okay, let's go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001ADF"
msgid "As simple as that, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC4D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE0"
msgid "So did I."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE1"
msgid "I don't need to, I *want* to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE2"
msgid "Then give me your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ACA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE3"
msgid "Every person for themselves, am I right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ACA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE4"
msgid "Aw, stop, you're going to make me cry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE5"
msgid "Anyone looking for you we should worry about?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ACA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE6"
msgid "Not in this area, as far as I know. I got pretty far before the thing died on me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE7"
msgid "I damn well knew it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE8"
msgid "[Attack] Yeah, you know what? I lied."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC93]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AE9"
msgid "So that's how it's going to be, huh? All right, I get it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AEA"
msgid "Heh, why not. Let's go then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AEB"
msgid "I need to get to Neon as fast as possible without being seen. Think you can handle that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AEC"
msgid "Is that enough for you? Can we go now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AED"
msgid "Then I had a grav jump failure, ended up with just enough power for life support, then you showed up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AEE"
msgid "One day there was an opportunity to get out, and I took it. Then I took this piece of crap ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AEF"
msgid "I took the fall for someone else after a bank robbery went wrong. I ended up inside for a while."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD3D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF0"
msgid "What else can you tell me before I take you aboard?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106481B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF2"
msgid "Miss Krause is waiting for me, but maybe we can catch up later? Bye!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106481B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF3"
msgid "Oh, hello! Always great to see you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064819]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF4"
msgid "I have to run now, but thanks again for everything!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064819]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF5"
msgid "Hello! Fancy meeting you here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064813]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF6"
msgid "I'll never forget what you did for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106480E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF7"
msgid "So nice to see you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106480B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF8"
msgid "I have to run, but let's have lunch one day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106480B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AF9"
msgid "Oh, hello! I hope everything is good with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064809]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AFA"
msgid "Until next time, then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064809]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AFB"
msgid "That was quite the adventure we had in that minefield, wasn't it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AFC"
msgid "We're right behind you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AFD"
msgid "That ship better not get stolen while we're gone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AFE"
msgid "Let the record show that I don't approve of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001AFF"
msgid "Lead the way, I'm right behind you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B00"
msgid "Don't worry about Hannah, she can take care of herself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B01"
msgid "I can't wait to get out of here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068028]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B02"
msgid "We're in the middle of a minefield!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B03"
msgid "That's great! Thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B04"
msgid "Can you find a way to open the door?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B05"
msgid "Thank you so much for coming to our rescue!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B06"
msgid "Miss Krause promises that GalBank will reward you adequately for your time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065F9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B07"
msgid "Uh, let me ask Miss Krause."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068033]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B08"
msgid "Shall we go then?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B09"
msgid "The door won't open from the inside."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B0A"
msgid "Come closer!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010655D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B0B"
msgid "We're both in here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B0C"
msgid "So where should I take you two?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B0D"
msgid "But perhaps you can find the key on one of the people who are, um, no longer alive?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B0E"
msgid "No, we don't have the key and the manual override is damaged."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC07SharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B0F"
msgid "We should probably go before any more pirates arrive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B10"
msgid "We are in need of a temporary transportation service, as it were."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B11"
msgid "On behalf of the GalBank consortium, thank you for coming to our assistance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B12"
msgid "I have to say, I was starting to worry we'd never get out of this ship!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B13"
msgid "Great, you found a way to open that door!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B14"
msgid "Can't you open the door from the inside?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068022]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B15"
msgid "What? Oh no, that's fine, don't worry about it. She'll send for me. I'll be fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106803E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B16"
msgid "Did you want to ask me something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068039]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B17"
msgid "I really have to stay behind? What if the pirates come back?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068039]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B18"
msgid "Wait, what?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068025]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B19"
msgid "As I said before, it's your call."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068034]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B1A"
msgid "I'll make sure there are no pirates around before leaving."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106802E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B1B"
msgid "Are you sure you're okay staying here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068029]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B1C"
msgid "Sure, take your time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01069D96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B1D"
msgid "Don't worry about me, Ruby - I mean, Miss Krause needs me too much to fire me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D505]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B1E"
msgid "Just tell me where I need to take you two."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010649A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B1F"
msgid "All personnel, please evacuate the ship immediately."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010649A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B20"
msgid "Warning. Hazardous microorganisms detected. Critical systems damaged."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B98F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B21"
msgid "Hazardous organisms removed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEF7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B23"
msgid "I'll still never forget that last job, and the scars sure won't let us forget either."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B24"
msgid "That was still a good time, though. Even if half of it was in that backstreet ER."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B25"
msgid "I think we both know the less I have to say the better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B26"
msgid "Just don't embarrass me like that last time. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B27"
msgid "Anything going on later?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF21]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B28"
msgid "Only a package pickup. I could use some backup if you're interested."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B29"
msgid "I like how our biggest challenge is figuring out what to do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B2A"
msgid "Got any plans for later?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B2B"
msgid "I don't know. Something with you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B2C"
msgid "*sigh*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B2D"
msgid "But she's never really alone. You know I'll watch her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B2E"
msgid "Are you kidding me right now? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B2F"
msgid "So how long until the next big science conference?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B30"
msgid "No, that was me trying to make a point which failed miserably."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B31"
msgid "Is that like a yes? Because I couldn't tell."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B32"
msgid "Fine, fine... But you owe me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B33"
msgid "For cleaning up your mess? I don't think so."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B34"
msgid "Hey, Yura, do you mind helping me clean up later? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B35"
msgid "Just keep it together. I'd rather hear about your vacation from you, not from SSNN."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B36"
msgid "A real vacation will be nice for you two. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEF1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B37"
msgid "Just don't get kicked out again. Or if you do, don't show up here in the middle of the night."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B38"
msgid "We're thinking about checking out Trident. Seeing if we can do a cute little vacation. He's so romantic."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B39"
msgid "Can you believe he actually mentioned going to Paradiso? Can you imagine me on a beach?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF26]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B3A"
msgid "You and Roman have any plans?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF25]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B3B"
msgid "How are things with Roman?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B3C"
msgid "If only we had gotten here sooner, we could have saved all these people..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B3D"
msgid "You couldn't pay me enough to do that young woman's job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A504]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B3E"
msgid "I should have asked Hannah for tomorrow's agenda before leaving her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A503]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B3F"
msgid "Now I just need to decide what to do with Hannah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A502]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B40"
msgid "That's enough excitement for today, don't you agree?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A500]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B41"
msgid "Well that was quite the adventure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B42"
msgid "I just hope you did the right thing taking Hannah along with us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B43"
msgid "We should leave. Now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B44"
msgid "You ship is smaller than I imagined."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B45"
msgid "I can't wait to be back on solid ground."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B46"
msgid "I feel better now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B47"
msgid "I hate pirates!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B48"
msgid "Let's hope we can get away before more pirates show up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F64F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B49"
msgid "Also, um, a pirate or two *may* have already boarded our ship, so... be careful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F64F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B4A"
msgid "Thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F650]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B4B"
msgid "What? Oh, right... They want to kidnap the VP of Acquisitions for GalBank."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F650]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B4C"
msgid "Mayday! Mayday! We are being attacked by pirates! They want to kidnap us!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F656]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B4D"
msgid "Mayday! Mayday! We have been attacked by pirates and have lost our engines."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F654]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B4E"
msgid "We have lost our shields, engine power, and grav jump capabilities."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106439D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B4F"
msgid "What's in it for me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106439F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B50"
msgid "Uh, okay, we'll be right here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064399]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B51"
msgid "Uh, let me ask."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106439E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B52"
msgid "Uh... Mayday! Mayday!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106439E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B53"
msgid "Whoa! Did you see that? The pirate ship blew up on a space mine!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B54"
msgid "Who knows, maybe we'll meet again some day. Though preferably not in a minefield."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B55"
msgid "Thank you for taking us to safety. I'll be wiring your reward shortly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B56"
msgid "Come on Hannah, let's go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B57"
msgid "You never know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B58"
msgid "We have to help that GalBank ship. Just steer clear of those mines."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B59"
msgid "All right, safe travels to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B71"
msgid " I'll talk to Rishi again, but I expect the answer will be the same as last time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B72"
msgid "Believe me, I know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B73"
msgid "Probably saved us all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B74"
msgid "One of the patrons stepped up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059ABD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B75"
msgid "Our business is concluded. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_DialogueAnchorpoint_TigerSharedInfo_Roar
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B76"
msgid "Roar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeB2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B77"
msgid "Okay, okay, you get to stay a tiger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeB2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B78"
msgid "*Laugh* Not a fan, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058E1B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B79"
msgid "I should make you a new toy. Maybe something you can chase around. What do you think, Tiger?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B7A"
msgid "Not sure who set this up in the middle of nowhere, but it appears a few ships got caught in it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B7B"
msgid "Ugh, space mines. Better stay away from this area, if you want my advice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C393]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B7C"
msgid "Perhaps we should just leave this area altogether, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080463]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B7D"
msgid "It does make for some nice fireworks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080460]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B7E"
msgid "I doubt that was five hundred meters away... We're lucky it didn't go off sooner."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108045E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B7F"
msgid "I do not believe I will be getting used to this any time soon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080477]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B80"
msgid "So what are we looking for here, in addition to the inebriating thrill of discovery?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080475]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B81"
msgid "Let's take a quick tour then get out before this wreck comes in contact with one of those mines."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108046F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B82"
msgid "I find your fascination for derelict ships... intriguing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108046E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B83"
msgid "We shouldn't be in here. This is a place of pain and sorrow."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108046C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B84"
msgid "Let's be quick. Mines usually won't be triggered by derelict ships, but this one still has power."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108046B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B85"
msgid "Places like these give me the creeps, to be perfectly honest."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108046A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B86"
msgid "Exploring derelict ships in a minefield... You've got a sense of adventure, I'll give you that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080468]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B87"
msgid "For the record, I'm not entirely comfortable with this. It almost feels like grave robbing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A4D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B88"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B89"
msgid "Why not take a look? You know what they say, better safe than sorry! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B8A"
msgid "Yeah, I hear that every day. It's normal. Just loose stuff in the ducts blowing around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B8B"
msgid "It's an old station. There's all kinds of sounds. It ain't anything to worry about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B8C"
msgid "Whatever it is, I doubt it has good intentions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A54]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B8D"
msgid "There's something in the air ducts. I can hear it skittering around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B8E"
msgid "I'll consider it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B8F"
msgid "I can't make the parts appear out of thin air and we ain't got anything I can replace them with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B90"
msgid "And before you ask me again, no, I can't just patch it up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B91"
msgid "You already know, cause I told you yesterday."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A4B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B92"
msgid "*Sigh* What is it this time?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B93"
msgid "You do your job as you see fit, and I'll do mine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A48]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B94"
msgid "Ammunition. We're running low. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B95"
msgid "Credits first. No discussion."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B96"
msgid "He might, but I prefer certainty over possibility."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A51]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B97"
msgid "Give me what I need for my team, and Mister Saint can reimburse you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A51]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B98"
msgid "That could take weeks, and I know you've got plenty in stock right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B99"
msgid "Ah, Chan. What brings you by?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B9A"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D75]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B9B"
msgid "What is it, Chan?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B9C"
msgid "I could reach out to a few past acquaintances. I'm sure we could find..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B9D"
msgid "We should hire more security personnel."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B9E"
msgid "If not for outside help, we could have been in serious danger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01058D77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001B9F"
msgid "The recent incident with that Spacer gang concerns me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054571]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BA5"
msgid "I see, well... maybe someone else will come along that has half a heart. Sycorax out. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105456B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BA6"
msgid "Krell Vonn. He's wanted in three systems for raiding civilian convoys. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054569]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BA7"
msgid "Who's this bounty you're hauling?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054567]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BA8"
msgid "Oh. Uh... well if you change your mind, you know where I'll be. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054572]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BA9"
msgid "What's left of their ship is drifting and ripe for the picking. If you get me a Power Cell, I'd be eternally grateful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054572]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BAA"
msgid "I managed to fight them off, but they got a few good hits in and fried my power grid. I just need enough juice to jump to the nearest system for repairs. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054572]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BAB"
msgid "You're a life-saver! I was hauling a bounty to New Atlantis when a pack of pirates came out of nowhere. They must have been tracking me - guess they wanted their friend back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BAC"
msgid "Well... my mother used to say that you can always count on the kindness of strangers. I am eternally grateful. Thank you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BAD"
msgid "I knew you wouldn't leave me stranded out here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BAE"
msgid "Aye-aye, captain. Consider me dust. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BAF"
msgid "*laughs* Don't worry, 'hero'... your secret's safe with me. Thanks again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB0"
msgid "I know. I'm a regular big damn hero. But keep it to yourself, yeah? I've got a reputation to maintain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB2"
msgid "Nice to see you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB3"
msgid "Yep."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB4"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDF9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB5"
msgid "No more specials, sorry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB6"
msgid "Will that be all, honey?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053572]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB7"
msgid "Can I see the specials, please?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE06]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB8"
msgid "Do you always do as you're told?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105357B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BB9"
msgid "Please, go ahead. We're not going anywhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE0B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BBA"
msgid "Can I help you, dear?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE09]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BBB"
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE28]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BBC"
msgid "Always good to see you, my friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE27]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BBD"
msgid "Well, if it isn't my good friend. Come in!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE24]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BBE"
msgid "Good to see you again, traveler! Please come in!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053585]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BBF"
msgid "It's a pleasure to see you again, traveler."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE21]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC0"
msgid "Please traveler, do come in. Don't be shy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053584]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC1"
msgid "Welcome to our humble emporium, traveler."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC2"
msgid "Anything else for you today, my good friend?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC3"
msgid "Will that be it for today?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC4"
msgid "What else do you need?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053568]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC5"
msgid "Anything else, traveler?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC6"
msgid "Sure, no problem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053567]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC7"
msgid "I want to see your regular items."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDF6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC8"
msgid "Coming right up!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105356E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BC9"
msgid "What can I do for you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BCA"
msgid "I'm fine for now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE01]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BCB"
msgid "Good thing we received a new shipment, then!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BCC"
msgid "All right, come back to see me if you need more regular items."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BCD"
msgid "I'm here to see the specials."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BCE"
msgid "Welcome back, my friend!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDF7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BCF"
msgid "Anyway, that's our second ship by that name. The first one was so small, you wouldn't believe!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BDF7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD0"
msgid "That's our daughter's name. She would have turned nineteen a couple of weeks ago..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE3C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD1"
msgid "Will there be anything else?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE14]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD2"
msgid "As usual, take what I say with a grain of salt."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE10]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD3"
msgid "I heard a few things..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE0E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD4"
msgid "You mean, like rumors and gossip? Nothing comes to mind, but I'll keep an ear out for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C828]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD5"
msgid "I think I'm going to get something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F90F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD6"
msgid "Here's what we have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F90F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD7"
msgid "Well that's just fine with us, friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F922]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD8"
msgid "I think I'll just look at regular items for now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BD9"
msgid "Great, just come on over!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F91F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BDA"
msgid "Just tell us what you'd like, and we'll send it over to your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BDB"
msgid "Just the basic stuff for now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BDC"
msgid "Your loss, traveler. Maybe next time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BDD"
msgid "As always, we can deliver normal supplies to your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105356B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BDE"
msgid "Until next time..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105356B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BDF"
msgid "Pleasure doing business with you, traveler."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C808]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE0"
msgid "Oh it's that little space shop I like! Let's pay them a visit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C809]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE1"
msgid "I am kind of curious to see what they have on board now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C809]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE2"
msgid "Well that was odd... I did not expect traders so far off in interplanetary space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B395]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE3"
msgid "I'm done talking anyway's."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B38C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE4"
msgid "If you need anything, just let me know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B387]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE5"
msgid "We can talk later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE6"
msgid "Hey, if you need to sit down, then go sit down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE7"
msgid "Watch where you're going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE8"
msgid "You're going to trip on someone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_YoureRightIHateThatYoureRight
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BE9"
msgid "Alright. Guess I'm doing this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_YoureRightIHateThatYoureRight
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BEA"
msgid "You're right... I hate that you're right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B43F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BEB"
msgid "I wonder if I can snatch a few drinks before I leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B429]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BEC"
msgid "Come on! The party only ends if we let it. Woo!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B427]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BED"
msgid "I do love some entertainment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B419]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BEE"
msgid "Sawyer and Opal said they found a new face. Welcome aboard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B413]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BEF"
msgid "I'm busy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B40B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF0"
msgid "And to think, Opal was my friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF1"
msgid "We'll all have a good time, trust me. Let's have some drinks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF2"
msgid "I don't think you're welcome here anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF3"
msgid "Come on. We don't bite."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF4"
msgid "You won't get away with that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF5"
msgid "Leave us alone!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF6"
msgid "What's going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF7"
msgid "How stupid are you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B377]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF8"
msgid "I just wanted to have a fun time, but no. You had to ruin that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B376]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BF9"
msgid "I'm getting real tired of you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B375]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BFA"
msgid "I can't wait to put you down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B366]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BFB"
msgid "Someone must have set them off."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_SAWYER_EveryoneTakeCover
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BFC"
msgid "Everyone, take cover!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B35D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BFD"
msgid "Way to ruin the party!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B355]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BFE"
msgid "You're only making me madder."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B34B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001BFF"
msgid "I don't want to hurt you. We can stop this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B343]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C00"
msgid "I can't turn them off."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B342]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C01"
msgid "They must have been turned on."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B341]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C02"
msgid "The system shouldn't be doing this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B33E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C03"
msgid "I can't wait to be rid of you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B33D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C04"
msgid "Trust me. You won't be alive for long."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B334]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C05"
msgid "I don't like to start shit, but I'll finish you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B331]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C06"
msgid "Why do you have to be so much trouble?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B328]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C07"
msgid "Ngh!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B322]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C08"
msgid "Gh... shit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B31F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C09"
msgid "Nh! You'll pay for that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B317]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C0A"
msgid "Grgh!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B313]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C0B"
msgid "Dammit!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B312]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C0C"
msgid "I won't let you get away with that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E26B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C0D"
msgid "I..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E274]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C0E"
msgid "Dammit. I better talk to Opal after all this. Here, let's get you back to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E274]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C0F"
msgid "I don't blame her reaction then. I'd be pissed off too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E210]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C10"
msgid "Justice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E27F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C11"
msgid "Sadie! Cooper! Wait! We can talk about this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E21B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C12"
msgid "What's going on is my family and I are heading home. Go on, Sawyer, take us home in your new ride."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E1FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C13"
msgid "Thank you for the advice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E1FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C14"
msgid "Like I should with Sadie. You're right. I'll go tell her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E209]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C15"
msgid "Um, thank you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E209]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C16"
msgid "But she needs to know about this, doesn't she? Right... She does."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E209]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C17"
msgid "My sister always invites me to these. I don't want to disappoint her and tell her 'No.'"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E202]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C18"
msgid "I've been in your position. Trust me, no one should ever go through what you're going through."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E27E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C19"
msgid "If you don't stand up for yourself, it won't end."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E258]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C1A"
msgid "But you can't let Opal get away with harassing you. Sadie is your sister. She would want you safe above all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E24D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C1B"
msgid "Maybe. Unless Opal is jealous. You are Sadie's sister after all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E22B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C1C"
msgid "Calm down. You're on Sawyer's ship. You're safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C1D"
msgid "Oh, yea, buddy. You drank so much! I thought you were gonna puke your guts up back at Anchorpoint. But hey, look at you now. Up and at 'em! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E283]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C1E"
msgid "Hey, sorry! We're not being too loud, are we? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E214]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C1F"
msgid "What are you celebrating?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E232]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C20"
msgid "Take a seat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B28A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C21"
msgid "Hope you drink, and choke on your own vomit. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C22"
msgid "Where did you find that? That wasn't for you to listen to!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E296]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C23"
msgid "Hear, hear!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C24"
msgid "I'll explain later. For now, take this asshole back to the dump where we found her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C25"
msgid "I'll explain later. For now, take this asshole back to the dump where we found him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B273]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C26"
msgid "Opal needs to pay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B440]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C27"
msgid "You should talk with Opal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B298]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C28"
msgid "And she won't stop unless you do something about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B396]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C29"
msgid "No. Do I look that much out of place? Sawyer's parties just never were my thing. I feel like a fish out of water."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C2A"
msgid "You're not the problem. She is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C2B"
msgid "I had this ship before then, but hey, with all the new credits I thought 'why not make this place even better?' I think it turned out amazing!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C2C"
msgid "My parents. We haven't seen eye to eye in a long time till recently. Guess they were happy to have their boy back and gave me a real nice allowance. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C2D"
msgid "I kid. All three of us have known each other since we were little. Been best of friends ever since."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C2E"
msgid "Enough to be invited."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B27F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C2F"
msgid "It beats staying at home doing nothing. And there's booze. Not much else for me to say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B278]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C30"
msgid "Can you tell me anything about anyone here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C31"
msgid "Long. I'd say about three years and eight months? Yea. That sounds about right. Can't say I regret a day of it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C32"
msgid "There's my sister, Sadie. She's a wizard at tech and decor. See how nice this ship looks? Yeah, she did that. Sawyer paid her a pretty credit for it all too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C33"
msgid "If you let Opal of all people bully you, then you must be spineless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C34"
msgid "How long have you and Cooper been dating?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C35"
msgid "You have a point."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C36"
msgid "If I could tell the others I would. But is it really that simple?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C37"
msgid "If you don't feel comfortable telling Sadie, you can always tell Cooper."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D684]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C38"
msgid "I'm sure you'd have a better time with them instead. Or heck, even Opal and Sawyer would be better company than me right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D684]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C39"
msgid "Sorry. My name is Wren. Cooper and Sadie brought me along."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D67E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C3A"
msgid "Yeah. Yeah. I can take you there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D674]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C3B"
msgid "Why would they want this slate? I guess it can wait. Let me take you back to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D699]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C3C"
msgid "Take this slate. It will fill you in on everything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D6A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C3D"
msgid "Barely anything. Here. Make sure Sadie or Cooper gets this slate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D6A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C3E"
msgid "So you're the overly friendly type? Great."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D67D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C3F"
msgid "I just think you'll have a better time doing it elsewhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106573D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C40"
msgid "That's good news."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065746]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C41"
msgid "Perhaps another such opportunity will present itself soon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104BFFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C42"
msgid "Just... go away. Please."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C43"
msgid "I'm so sorry..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C44"
msgid "This is not what I wanted."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C45"
msgid "No wait, that's not it. Let me try again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C46"
msgid "I'm serious! I'll do it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C47"
msgid "This is your last warning. Go back or...uh...I'll activate countermeasures."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D02A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C48"
msgid "I'm right behind you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104074F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C49"
msgid "Well I sure don't want to hurt anyone..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040749]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C4A"
msgid "Why are you saying that? Did someone send you after me? Are you *stalking* me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040748]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C4B"
msgid "I um, I didn't actually... How did you know? Is it that obvious?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C4C"
msgid "You know what? Never mind. I'm not saying anything else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104075E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C4D"
msgid "No please, I can't go back there!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104076D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C4E"
msgid "Nope. Nobody cares if I live or die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104076C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C4F"
msgid "Only one, really...and I was planning on telling them I was okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040757]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C50"
msgid "I'll call SysDef, they should be able to get you back to your family."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040774]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C51"
msgid "It doesn't have to be like this. Help me help you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040768]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C52"
msgid "Kinda? I don't know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040754]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C53"
msgid "Sorry, but I don't trust you. Or anyone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104074A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C54"
msgid "I really want to trust you..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040760]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C55"
msgid "I wouldn't even know where to start..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104076A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C56"
msgid "I can do this all day. You'll tire before I do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104089D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C57"
msgid "I don't need your help. Just go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104089F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C58"
msgid "You wouldn't do that, right? I mean..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D033]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C59"
msgid "Go ahead, I'm all ears."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C5A"
msgid "Kind of lame now that I said it out loud..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C5B"
msgid "So that's it. That's my story."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D020]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C5C"
msgid "Let's go before my stepfather gets here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D01F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C5D"
msgid "I'll just...come back for the ship later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C5E"
msgid "Okay, I'm just gonna go now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C503]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C5F"
msgid "I cannot believe a child would disrespect her guardian that way..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C50F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C60"
msgid "None of us knows what she became, but I often think of her. I just hope she found peace."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C61"
msgid "What's your situation? Are you in danger?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C62"
msgid "Come on... why are there so many buttons!?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DAC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C63"
msgid "I'm all set. I have enough credits to last me for a year. By that time I should have a job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C64"
msgid "Maybe I'll see you around. Safe travels."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C65"
msgid "Here's a little something for being such a nice person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBD7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C66"
msgid "I hope Miles is okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBD5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C67"
msgid "The way you handled those guys was impressive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C68"
msgid "Thanks for what you did. I mean it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C69"
msgid "I don't know. It's been a real long time. I'm not even sure how much he cares anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C6A"
msgid "It doesn't really matter. The point is, I'm here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C6B"
msgid "I'm going to owe her a top-notch dinner at Dawn's Roost in New Atlantis."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C6C"
msgid "Best damn co-pilot a guy could ask for."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104048E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C6D"
msgid "Relationships between fathers and sons can be complicated."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C6E"
msgid "If you're here, that must mean Lucia made it out. Thank goodness."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010435B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C70"
msgid "I hadn't dared to hope."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C71"
msgid "It's obvious he's suffering. You can put a stop to that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C72"
msgid "The subject was so painful for him, he couldn't even talk about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBFF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C73"
msgid "Why do I have to be the one? That's not fair."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C74"
msgid "Believe me, I know that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBEF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C75"
msgid "Some things, you just can't put a time table on."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C76"
msgid "You may not want the responsibility to fix things, but it's yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C77"
msgid "The sooner you reach out, the more time you'll have to reconnect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C78"
msgid "If you wait too long, it might be too late."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C79"
msgid "Look, I don't mean to be rude, but it's a family matter."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050246]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C7A"
msgid "Lead the way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedInfo01_CaptainIntro03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C7B"
msgid "Thanks for giving us a ride. What with our pilot and all... well, we're sitting ducks out here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedInfo01_CaptainIntro03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C7C"
msgid "There you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C7D"
msgid "The thing is, we aren't who you think we are. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F643]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C7E"
msgid "Good. You can speak with the captain on board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EE06]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C7F"
msgid "Sorry if I offended you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EE06]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C80"
msgid "I'm not trying to start a fight here. I appreciate you helping us, but a bit of caution is reasonable after what just happened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C81"
msgid "If you're able to help us get out of here, dock with us so our captain can speak with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C82"
msgid "*Sigh* Look, we're in a pretty bad spot here. We're not getting out of here without a ride. Please, help us out. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D80]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C83"
msgid "No, really, I should be thanking you. You're saving our asses here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C84"
msgid "I think you took that the wrong way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C85"
msgid "That's... wait a second. That's not what I meant."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EE04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C86"
msgid "Wait, hold on."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EE01]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C87"
msgid "If I'm so suspicious, you better find another ride. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C411]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C88"
msgid "Yeah, well, that's easy for you to say. You still have your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C89"
msgid "Your condolences aren't going to get me a new ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C421]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C8A"
msgid "It is what it is. I'm not looking for sympathy. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C414]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C8B"
msgid "Can't believe I have to resort to bumming rides from a stranger. *Sigh* And I just finished paying off this ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C414]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C8C"
msgid "Our savior, in the flesh."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C8D"
msgid "Good, good."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C43F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C8E"
msgid "I'm not trying to get off on the wrong foot here. It's been a bad day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C8F"
msgid "Not sure. I don't think anyone could possibly know what the hell goes on in a Spacer's mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C90"
msgid "A little caution is warranted, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C91"
msgid "Why did those Spacers attack you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C92"
msgid "Damn, you really think there could be more of those bastards?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C93"
msgid "*Sigh* Anyway, we appreciate your help. We can't wait to get the hell out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C94"
msgid "They probably assumed we were hauling something good. That's always a risk with these types of haulers. Easy to attract attention. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C95"
msgid "Kill them!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C96"
msgid "Sorry, but we're taking your ship. Nothing personal, you were just... well, you decided to help us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C97"
msgid "*Sigh* Man, how did things go so wrong? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C98"
msgid "Here to give us a ride? We appreciate it, seriously. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C99"
msgid "Anyway, let's get moving."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C9A"
msgid "Surround them!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C9B"
msgid "Take them down!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C9C"
msgid "My condolences, but we should get moving before more Spacers show up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C9D"
msgid "Why did those Spacers attack you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C9E"
msgid "You know, we were gonna make things easy for you. Painless. We were gonna put a quick bullet in the back of your head when you weren't looking, then take your ship without any fuss. But now, all bets are off."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001C9F"
msgid "We weren't asking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CA0"
msgid "Open fire!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CA1"
msgid "We're flying that ship home whether you like it or not."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_FreestarSceneReentry01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CAA"
msgid "Atka must've come home before Yura even saw the note. That's the only explanation."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B449]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CAB"
msgid "Thanks for the advice on Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B43A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CAC"
msgid "See you around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B438]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CAD"
msgid "I'm gonna miss that critter."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CAE"
msgid "Don't look at me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CAF"
msgid "This is all a big misunderstanding."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D5E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB0"
msgid "If you want some easy credits, house sitting's where it's at."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D56]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB1"
msgid "I just need a minute."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB2"
msgid "Oh, you're dead, pal!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB3"
msgid "End of the line!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035869]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB4"
msgid "Yura is in on this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103589C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB5"
msgid "Right. Milli is fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB6"
msgid "And I am! Hiring another pet sitter is taking care of her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103588A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB7"
msgid "Here, it's what I intended to pay Yura, plus a little extra for the trouble and keeping the plant babies alive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103588F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB8"
msgid "Looks like I could use those credits after all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CB9"
msgid "Once you're all done, find me back here for those credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CBA"
msgid "It's this cutesy place on Muphrid IV, and you'll be taking care of her little milliwhale, Milli. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035884]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CBB"
msgid "'Bout time you got here. Where have you been? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C852]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CBC"
msgid "You're... joking... right? You can't be serious."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035897]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CBD"
msgid "I'll take out everyone here if you don't hand over Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D00]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CBE"
msgid "Count me in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035860]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CBF"
msgid "Instructions are on the counter. Find me back here to get paid, and you're good to go!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC0"
msgid "I don't want to risk anything really..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC1"
msgid "Like I said, all or nothing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D57]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC2"
msgid "Great. Great! Well, this sure went south quick."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D5D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC3"
msgid "I'm under the impression Yura does what she wants."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D5E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC4"
msgid "Maybe..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC5"
msgid "Nice doing business with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC6"
msgid "Here's the key to Milli's room."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC7"
msgid "That's not gonna happen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC8"
msgid "And we will, once we get the credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CC9"
msgid "I don't do favors for petnappers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CCA"
msgid "Thanks for keeping an eye on things while I was gone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D17]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CCB"
msgid "Hmm, I can see your point."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CCC"
msgid "I see a lot of pain and suffering in your future if you don't give me Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CCD"
msgid "Hand over the milliwhale or you deal with the Crimson Fleet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D44]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CCE"
msgid "If you think we're not ready to deal with you, think again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CCF"
msgid "What makes you think Yura's interested in you to begin with?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D10]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD0"
msgid "And it would just be my luck that I'd send someone out there to speak for me and they'd screw it up. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D10]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD1"
msgid "Damn, I never thought about it way... "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD2"
msgid "What is going on here? You know Atka?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD3"
msgid "This was all for her, too. Of course I'd screw it up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D12]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD4"
msgid "You don't think I know that now? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD5"
msgid "I'm the house sitter."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD6"
msgid "The things we do to impress people, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD7"
msgid "Well, yeah, but that was part of the plan... I just wanted to get Yura's attention is all. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD8"
msgid "Petnapping is a pretty elaborate distraction."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CEF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CD9"
msgid "And you really thought Yura would appreciate your prank?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CDA"
msgid "I knew this plan could backfire, but I never thought it'd be this bad."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CDB"
msgid "You found the note? So Yura doesn't know about this at all?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CDC"
msgid "We didn't mean anything by it. We were always going to return Milli safe and sound."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CDD"
msgid "I think we all realize that now, but I swear it was completely innocent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CDE"
msgid "I guess if I've made it this long living in the Free Lanes, I should be able to face down my fears."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CDF"
msgid "Easier said than done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D27]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE0"
msgid "I've got <Global=SFFL_MS03_RansomCredits> credits that says otherwise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D26]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE1"
msgid "[Lie] I've got <Global=SFFL_MS03_RansomCredits> credits that says otherwise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D20]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE2"
msgid "Yura hired me to house sit. She doesn't know about all this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D16]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE3"
msgid "[Attack] Plan C. I'll put you out of your misery."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE4"
msgid "Milli is Atka's baby. We'd never do anything to hurt her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE5"
msgid "Just talk to Yura. Tell her I took Milli and she'll know it wasn't serious. She'll back me up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE6"
msgid "Password."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE7"
msgid "I thought I told you to get lost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A339]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE8"
msgid "I did what I had to do to bring Milli back safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D03]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CE9"
msgid "No more than a few days, I promise!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CEA"
msgid "You know, getting to hang out with her people who are definitely not me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CEB"
msgid "She's some sort of independent researcher, so she lives for these things. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CEC"
msgid "I don't know. Some science convention or something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CED"
msgid "A pet milliwhale? I'm game if you are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A338]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CEE"
msgid "He hates it when things don't go according to plan."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A338]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CEF"
msgid "I can't wait to talk to him about all this. He must be losing his mind. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A343]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF0"
msgid "Milli really is fine. Roman was taking good care of her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A353]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF1"
msgid "Okay, great, so this was all some elaborate scheme of Roman's, probably to impress my sister."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A344]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF2"
msgid "I wish I could've seen the look on his face. He hates it when plans go bad."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A360]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF3"
msgid "I really do appreciate you taking care of Milli. As much as it surprises me, she really does seem fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A360]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF4"
msgid "I agree completely."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A355]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF5"
msgid "Milli does seem fine. Roman's been around long enough to know how to properly care for her. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A33D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF6"
msgid "Help me out here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A32F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF7"
msgid "The things we do to impress someone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A349]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF8"
msgid "Hey, Roman just thinks outside the box. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A331]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CF9"
msgid "What was Roman even thinking?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A331]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CFA"
msgid "Fine? She was stolen right out of our home! She could be traumatized. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A34A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CFB"
msgid "You'll be happy to know, they were just taking Milli for a walk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A336]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CFC"
msgid "Milli and I have had quite the adventure together."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B431]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CFD"
msgid "Hold up. What's that supposed to mean?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A35C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CFE"
msgid "I think your sister is trying to get your attention."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001CFF"
msgid "I think she just knows who will forgive her and who won't."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D00"
msgid "But when it comes to Atka, she rarely comes through."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF6C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D01"
msgid "Depends if she wants to do it or not. If she's responsible for a ship load of cargo, she's as responsible as they come."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B42E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D02"
msgid "Roman is dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF77]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D03"
msgid "If you ever want a little Milli of your own, that's my own personal recipe to give them all the nutrients they need."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D04"
msgid "Oh, and since you kept Milli safe, keep the food. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D05"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF9C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D06"
msgid "I guess so."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D07"
msgid "What do you know about Atka?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D08"
msgid "I guess that's a chance worth taking, especially since your being here means the original plan was shot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF82]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D09"
msgid "Next time you'll face jail time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D0A"
msgid "You've got yourself a deal. Here's the key to Milli's room. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D0B"
msgid "Doesn't matter. I know you like her. I'll put in a good word."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D0C"
msgid "*sigh* That's one plan failed. I guess at this point, I might as well take you up on the offer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D0D"
msgid "You're kidding? Of course she would... "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D0E"
msgid "Give me Milli and I'll put in a good word for you with Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D0F"
msgid "Sounds fair enough to me. Besides, I can't say I never pulled similar stunts back in my day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D10"
msgid "That's a pretty elaborate setup just to impress someone. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D2F"
msgid "To think the plan worked out after all. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D30"
msgid "So things didn't work out. Thanks for trying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D31"
msgid "Hey, you're back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D32"
msgid "Hope you took good care of Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D33"
msgid "*sigh* At least I saved myself some embarrassment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D34"
msgid "So how'd it go?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Support_PostQuestRoman06_Shared
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D35"
msgid "Thanks again for those credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Support_PostQuestRoman01_Shared
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D36"
msgid "Don't worry. Sticking to that straight and narrow path."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEFE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D37"
msgid "I think Atka still hasn't gotten over the plant thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D38"
msgid "I need some time with Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D39"
msgid "I think we need to be alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D3A"
msgid "I'm sorry Yura got you involved in all this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D3B"
msgid "Time to invest in some new plants. Again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D3C"
msgid "See ya."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D3D"
msgid "Thanks again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF1E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D3E"
msgid "Still with me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF1C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D3F"
msgid "I'm sorry, are we done here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF1A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D40"
msgid "*ahem* Uh, please say something..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF18]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D41"
msgid "You were saying...?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF17]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D42"
msgid "This is awkward..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF15]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D43"
msgid "Are we talking or what?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF11]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D44"
msgid "Um, hello?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_PostQuest_Roman_YuraYesReentry01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D45"
msgid "I feel like a nervous wreck. What do I say? I... I need advice. Anything!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D46"
msgid "What the hell?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D47"
msgid "Atka!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035866]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D48"
msgid "A little extra? I knew you were holding out on me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF86]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D49"
msgid "Yura, I'm so sorry. I know how close you were."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D4A"
msgid "I know he would, but he doesn't need to deal with all my emotional baggage. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D4B"
msgid "Roman's great, really, but the moment you start dating someone, that means you start letting them in and I really suck at that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D4C"
msgid "Give him a chance so I can screw it all up? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D4D"
msgid "I really wish I deserved someone like him, but I'm just not relationship material. Not right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF80]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D4E"
msgid "Roman wanted me to put in a good word for him with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF8B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D4F"
msgid "You think so? But I'm so stupid! I never let him in because who could love someone like me? I screw up everything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C374]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D50"
msgid "So what's the deal with you and Atka?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D51"
msgid "I'd like to talk about something else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D52"
msgid "Steady jobs suck. Freelance all the way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D53"
msgid "I just want some stability in her life, so I don't have to worry about her all the time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D54"
msgid "She's the queen of work avoidance. I think she'd rather die than hold down a real job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D55"
msgid "You pretty much experienced my sister in a nutshell."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE89]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D56"
msgid "Can you tell me more about Yura?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D57"
msgid "Why would Roman target your sister for ransom?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D58"
msgid "I guess if I tried to be anything else, she'd immediately call me out on it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D59"
msgid "Yura's going to think about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D5A"
msgid "I'm a fan of the classic advice. Just be yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D5B"
msgid "Yura has some things she needs to work through."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D5C"
msgid "Thanks for trying, though."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D5D"
msgid "As long as she'll still have me around, I'll be there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D5E"
msgid "Yeah, at least I know that much. And don't worry, I'd never bail on a friend in need, especially Yura. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C72B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D5F"
msgid "I want to thank you for being so patient with me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C72E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D60"
msgid "But it'll be fine. As long as she gets me where me, and the rest of this junk, needs to be I'm happy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034F82]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D61"
msgid " "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034E67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D62"
msgid "[<Global=SFFL_MS01_CrimeGold_Amount> Credits] I don't have the money. Can you let this one slide?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D63"
msgid "This could get ugly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D64"
msgid "Damn Spacers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D65"
msgid "We don't hear those words very often in Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D66"
msgid "We're in your debt, friend. Thank you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D67"
msgid "Really? You hardly look any the worse for wear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103439F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D68"
msgid "Feel free to enjoy a drink at the bar. You've earned it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103439F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D69"
msgid "Here. Compliments of Mister Saint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D6A"
msgid "Good luck out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D6B"
msgid "Take out the leader, and they'll get the message."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D6C"
msgid "Now listen, there's no need for excessive bloodshed here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D6D"
msgid "I took care of your Spacer problem."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D6E"
msgid "Lesser of two evils, I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D6F"
msgid "Please, I need help..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056638]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D70"
msgid "If you see Gabrielle, please tell her to come home..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056615]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D71"
msgid "Oh, what the hell am I doing...?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105661D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D72"
msgid "I can't... Not yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D73"
msgid "Go home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D74"
msgid "You're back! Did you find Gabrielle? Please, tell me you've found her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D75"
msgid "I-I can't believe this, my star, she's-"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D76"
msgid "How did it- Let me see those."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D77"
msgid "Well, thank you, I guess. Here. I don't have many credits anymore, but take them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D78"
msgid "There really isn't, is there...?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056604]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D79"
msgid "What? But why? Where did you find her? I need to talk to her!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D7A"
msgid "What? No. Oh, no... Gabbie..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056635]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D7B"
msgid "She's going to find out at some point, you know? Why delay that? Not that there's much that can be done now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105662C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D7C"
msgid "Was telling her that really necessary? Let's just hope she can learn to move on."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D7D"
msgid "No... No. I can't. I have to find her. I have to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105661B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D7E"
msgid "That sounds like a you problem. Not mine. Good luck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D7F"
msgid "This is a matter of ethics. As far as I'm concerned, this tour guide is a pirate, and we have every right to kill them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D80"
msgid "Bald is right. I doubt they can even afford Enhance!'s prices."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D81"
msgid "Wait darling, they might be with the tour."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D82"
msgid "I'm not a pirate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D83"
msgid "Thanks for answering, you filthy little pirate!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031726]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D84"
msgid "Then you can be grateful I hired security."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031728]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D85"
msgid "You needed something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031702]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D86"
msgid "The last thing we need is to attract unwanted attention."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031702]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D87"
msgid "Above all, our customers value the privacy of this station."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031702]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D88"
msgid "As I've said before, I will never consider advertising to the public."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AF02]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D89"
msgid "*Coughing*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D8A"
msgid "*Grunt*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D8B"
msgid "I think I should go..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D8C"
msgid "Your kind. Your ilk. Adventurers, voyagers, vagabonds, wanderers. Your kind... I have met a thousand of you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D8D"
msgid "I made it possible. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D8E"
msgid "Now that I have gotten to know you better, I think it is time to eat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D8F"
msgid "Well, uh... it's nice to meet you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D90"
msgid "*Heavy breathing*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103073D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D91"
msgid "Fine, if it means that much to you. Just calm down."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103073F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D92"
msgid "The food has been set out for you. Please, help yourself. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048D0D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D93"
msgid "I don't mean to offend you, I just don't want to eat that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AB38]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D94"
msgid "Something wasn't right about that food..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D95"
msgid "What is the meaning of this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D96"
msgid "Watch your six out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045ECA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D97"
msgid "Anything to report?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D98"
msgid "Well?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D99"
msgid "What are you waiting for? Get going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EC4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D9A"
msgid "Target's marked. Get moving. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R02_TargetSpared_SharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D9B"
msgid "I'm gonna disappear. I promise. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104609D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D9C"
msgid "That... oh no, what am I supposed to do? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D9D"
msgid "Wait! Wait! Just... here, take my money, take all of it. It's not much but... just let me leave, okay? I'll leave the Settled Systems forever!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D9E"
msgid "Wait, no! Don't do this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001D9F"
msgid "Good, just take it. I'm out of here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA0"
msgid "Oh, thank god... I just have to get my things, then I'm gone for good. I swear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A42D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA1"
msgid "I'm not doing that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A43C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA2"
msgid "I took out the target. Here's your proof. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A436]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA3"
msgid "[Attack] Someone wants you dead. I'm here to make that happen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A430]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA4"
msgid "Huh? Who are you, and what do you want?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA5"
msgid "I have some more targets for you. Interested? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104480E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA6"
msgid "I'm not going to give you a chance to respond because I'm done talking to you. You're a liability, and I refuse to work with you any longer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104480E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA7"
msgid "I received more intel that a target has been allowed to live. I hired you for a service, and it seems you refuse to keep up your end of the bargain. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104480E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA8"
msgid "I had hoped that you learned from your mistake last time. I'm disappointed. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102AF66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DA9"
msgid "[Attack] Not interested. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044804]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DAA"
msgid "Why do you want these people dead?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DAB"
msgid "Give me something that I can say is proof that I killed you, then you need to get out of here and disappear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DAC"
msgid "Just need to figure out how to get out of here, and then it'll be like I never existed. You'll see."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DAD"
msgid "Oh my god, what a relief..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DAE"
msgid "Thank you, oh my god, thank you! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DAF"
msgid "Thank goodness you came! Let's get out of here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DB0"
msgid "Listen to me! They stole most of my money, but I still have some here. Just... just take it, and please let me go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DB1"
msgid "You can't be serious. Even after all that's happened?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DB2"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105911B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DB3"
msgid "What, you're leaving? After what you just told me? I... I'm not gonna let you get the drop on me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059117]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DB4"
msgid "I'm... I'm not just gonna wait here for you to kill me! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029A3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC1"
msgid "Got anything for me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F8F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC2"
msgid "You still there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F8F6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC3"
msgid "See you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029723]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC4"
msgid "Your loss."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC5"
msgid "Reliable as usual, I like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029719]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC6"
msgid "I'm waiting..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FA4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC7"
msgid "I'm going to have to report this to the Vanguard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC8"
msgid "I'm not interested."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DC9"
msgid "Look who it is! My favorite business partner!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DCA"
msgid "I'm not afraid of doing some smuggling. I'm in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C84C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DCB"
msgid "Thank you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C451]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DCC"
msgid "Hey! It's my hero!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059E3A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DCD"
msgid "You got a problem?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059E39]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DCE"
msgid "Get the hell out of my face."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C3EC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DCF"
msgid "This here is our humble little ship services desk. What can I do for you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026736]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD0"
msgid "Thirsty? I've got you covered."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD1"
msgid "Welcome back. Killian was hoping to talk to you.  "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102671B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD2"
msgid "What do you need?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD3"
msgid "Whatever you're selling, I ain't buying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD4"
msgid "Yeah? What?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD5"
msgid "You want to hang back a little?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026707]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD6"
msgid "The drinks here aren't too bad."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDAF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD7"
msgid "Valeria usually knows the latest gossip."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDDB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD8"
msgid "If you'd rather talk later, that's okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDD6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DD9"
msgid "Is something the matter?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DDA"
msgid "You know, I had this ship once... Oh, sorry. I have a bad habit of trying to fill long silences."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DDB"
msgid "It's alright. There's no hurry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDC1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DDC"
msgid "Feeling lost? I can relate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDFF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DDD"
msgid "Take care!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDF6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DDE"
msgid "Well that's kind of rude."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDF3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DDF"
msgid "Until next time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDF1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE0"
msgid "Very well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDEB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE1"
msgid "Alrighty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDE7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE2"
msgid "Good to see you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDDE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE3"
msgid "That's all, then?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A518]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE4"
msgid "I'll solve your Spacer problem, for a price."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE5"
msgid "A few years ago, I purchased it and had it towed out of its decaying orbit around Algorab II."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE6"
msgid "As a result, the station never realized its purpose and was eventually abandoned."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE7"
msgid "Unfortunately, the advances she expected in grav jump technology never materialized."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE8"
msgid "She had hoped it would be a jumping-off point to remote systems not yet accessible by grav drive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DE9"
msgid "The station was built over eighty years ago by a wealthy industrialist named Gabriela LeBlanc.."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A515]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DEA"
msgid "You're standing in that project now. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A515]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DEB"
msgid "Once I'd made enough to retire, I decided to find a project. Something to keep me busy,"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A515]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DEC"
msgid "I spent a few years with Ecliptic, managing their books. It was quite profitable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A515]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DED"
msgid "Frankly, I found the work tedious, and decided to seek more adventurous employment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A515]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DEE"
msgid "I come from the corporate world, where I worked in finance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A515]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DEF"
msgid "Me? There's not really much to tell."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A524]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF0"
msgid "I guess that's reasonable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF1"
msgid "Excellent. I hope this will be the first of many visits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A526]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF2"
msgid "We serve everyone, provided they have credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A522]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF3"
msgid "You serve Spacers here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF4"
msgid "My head of security can point you in the right direction."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF5"
msgid "Deal with these Spacers, and I'll provide the credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF6"
msgid "I believe in fair pay for a job well done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF7"
msgid "Really? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF8"
msgid "This robot is yours?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C020]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DF9"
msgid "You're standing in that project now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C020]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DFA"
msgid "Once I'd made enough to retire, I decided to find a project. Something to keep me busy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C020]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DFB"
msgid "I spent a few years with Ecliptic, managing their books. It was quite profitable and rarely dull."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C020]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DFC"
msgid "I did well for myself, but started to find the work tedious, so I sought more stimulating employment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C020]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DFD"
msgid "I worked in finance, climbing the corporate ladder at a few different companies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C020]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DFE"
msgid "There's not really much to tell."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001DFF"
msgid "You almost lost an entire wall?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E00"
msgid "They're lucky to have you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E01"
msgid "How do you stay in business with such a remote location?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E02"
msgid "Besides, my mom's pretty great. I know he's in good hands."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E03"
msgid "I miss him to death, but I have to think about what's best for him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E04"
msgid "I'm not saying Neon is a paradise, but at least there's room to run around and other kids to make friends with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E05"
msgid "This is no place for a child."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E06"
msgid "Good luck getting a decent night's sleep with that on your mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E07"
msgid "All that stands between us and a horrifying death in the vacuum of space is a few metal walls."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E08"
msgid "Nothing I said is a lie. All those dangers are very, very real."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103142C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E09"
msgid "Show me what's on the menu."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103142B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E0A"
msgid "I could use a drink."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031433]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E0B"
msgid "When he learned about my son's illness, he said he'd pay the bills on the condition I work here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031433]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E0C"
msgid "He tried to hire me for this place, but I said no. It was just so remote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031433]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E0D"
msgid "I'd met Mister Saint while I was tending bar at the Astral Lounge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031433]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E0E"
msgid "I have a son, Gabriel. He became very ill and I just couldn't afford the treatment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031428]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E0F"
msgid "I brought it up with him, but he didn't want to talk about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031428]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E10"
msgid "Seems he used to be pretty well-known in New Atlantis."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031428]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E11"
msgid "We had someone through here not long ago who recognized him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031428]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E12"
msgid "You meet Cutty yet? That's our doctor."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E13"
msgid "That's a very fatalistic outlook."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031444]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E14"
msgid "Anyway, it doesn't matter now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031444]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E15"
msgid "Probably came in on a cargo ship. I don't really know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031444]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E16"
msgid "It's apparently a very rare virus. They don't even know how it got there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031446]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E17"
msgid "Do you ever think about leaving? Maybe starting over somewhere not in space?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E18"
msgid "Certainly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031705]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E19"
msgid "You've got it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E1A"
msgid "Does this place really need a doctor?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037169]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E1B"
msgid "Well ain't you smart?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037174]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E1C"
msgid "Why does it have to be prototype parts?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037172]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E1D"
msgid "You get the drift."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037172]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E1E"
msgid "Better servos to boost mobility, enhanced defensive capabilities, maybe some tool appendages to help with my work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037172]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E1F"
msgid "Well that depends on the parts, of course, but I have a few ideas."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037167]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E20"
msgid "A job? I'm listening."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040486]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E21"
msgid "I just don't know who to turn to."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040486]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E22"
msgid "His co-pilot Lucia managed to escape from the Spacer hideout. She sent me a message begging for help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040486]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E23"
msgid "He got ambushed by Spacers. They seized the ship and took him as a hostage."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040486]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E24"
msgid "It's my son Miles. He's a cargo pilot. Makes some dangerous runs."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047145]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E25"
msgid "Now, let me explain the particulars."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047145]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E26"
msgid "I assure you, the reward is more than equal to the risk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104714D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E27"
msgid "Whoever does won't be eager to share their claim."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104714D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E28"
msgid "When word gets out that valuable cargo has been lost, one never knows who might come looking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E29"
msgid "Killian Brice. I offer various items for a fair price."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104714C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E2A"
msgid "Sorry, but I like to keep things nice and legal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E2B"
msgid "And yet, to force such a repayment on this woman is hardly what I would call humane."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F31]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E2C"
msgid "I'm sure it was no small expense to pay for the child's medical care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E2D"
msgid "Some say retirement should be a time of ease and prosperity, but that always sounded dull to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E2E"
msgid "There are days I wonder if I made the right choice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E2F"
msgid "I called in a few favors to keep costs reasonable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F1D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E30"
msgid "*Sigh* Yes, that was me. I made mistakes, but I have paid my debt to society"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E31"
msgid "You're making a fresh start, and I can understand that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E32"
msgid "Hey, no judgement here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F27]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E33"
msgid "Yeah, as a former \"resourceful ship's captain,\" I know exactly where this is going."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E34"
msgid "Perfect place to conduct all kinds of shady business."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E35"
msgid "Don't imagine I'll ever see my folks again, but hey, I've got a whole new family right here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E36"
msgid "A few favors here, a few bribes there, and I was free."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E37"
msgid "I found my way here, and Rishi offered me a job in exchange for clearing my name."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E38"
msgid "Anyway, I busted myself out, stowed away aboard a courier ship and spent a few years on the lam."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F2C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E39"
msgid "You should feel guilty."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A70]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E3A"
msgid "You betcha."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E3B"
msgid "That's a big, fat no, and I ain't happy about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E3C"
msgid "I wish! Darn things are getting to be scarce."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E3D"
msgid "Well get to it, then!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E3E"
msgid "If you blow up the ship and bring me damaged parts, I ain't paying as much,"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E3F"
msgid "You're going to get me some prototype robot parts from a cargo ship. They'll be in the captain's locker."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065752]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E40"
msgid "I'm afraid not. Rest assured, I'll keep an ear to the ground."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106573C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E41"
msgid "Good. I'll be waiting here when you return."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E42"
msgid "Of course. Enjoy yourself. And... it was good to see you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106611C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E43"
msgid "I understand."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB82]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E44"
msgid "How are things with you and Miles?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E45"
msgid "Nobody can change overnight. Patience will be necessary."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E46"
msgid "I've tried to set small goals and reasonable expectations for myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E47"
msgid "Thank you. Hopefully I can develop a little faith in myself, as well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E48"
msgid "Now it's time to turn the page, if I can. I have to try, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E49"
msgid "I let so many things go. Things I shouldn't have. I made a companion of misery."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB88]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E4A"
msgid "A long-overdue change."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C445]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E4B"
msgid "We should evacuate. The Spacers could already be on their way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E4C"
msgid "Would you make up your mind, please?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E4D"
msgid "I won't lie, this is going to hurt a little."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E4E"
msgid "This won't be pleasant."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E4F"
msgid "I'm not seeing anything too serious."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DCF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E50"
msgid "This is nothing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E51"
msgid "Just know I don't stock as much as some places."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DEA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E52"
msgid "That's it. All finished."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E53"
msgid "You're done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E54"
msgid "I don't know if we made the right vote, but the last thing I'm going to do is cast stones."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E55"
msgid "I might need to go a few rounds with my punching bag after this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316A7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E56"
msgid "The outpost can survive Hal's loss. So long as the people are willing to work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E57"
msgid "Back on the beat. The beat never sleeps."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E58"
msgid "I have to believe New Babylon can survive this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E59"
msgid "We made the right choice. Hal is innocent. Plain and simple."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E5A"
msgid "Exile. I don't know if I agree with it, but if he dies cold and alone, maybe that is poetic justice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103169E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E5B"
msgid "I can't believe we pushed out the only person who cared."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E5C"
msgid "I've decided to stick around. I don't know if I can do any good, but the people here have welcomed my help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031699]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E5D"
msgid "For the sake of this outpost, I am grateful Hal has been exonerated."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E5E"
msgid "I worry about this outcome."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01021668]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E5F"
msgid "But Caruso keeps insisting the robot is better, and Zena won't overrule him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E60"
msgid "My finger slipped."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1D5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E61"
msgid "Yes. The conditions were rough, but together we had tamed its hazards. It saddens me to think of all the knowledge we lost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E62"
msgid "Oh, and one other thing. If the vote ends up a tie, I'd like you to break it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E63"
msgid "I can do that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103CFC2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E64"
msgid "Why me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103F3BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E65"
msgid "Then the future is not written."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E32C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E66"
msgid "Fine. If you won't break this impasse, I will."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103FAEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E67"
msgid "Indeed. When we first met, you said my life was forfeit. Do you still think so?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103FAEC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E68"
msgid "I don't know how I'm going to vote. I might even abstain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051372]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E69"
msgid "Sounds like a bunch of hooey to me, but what do I know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051375]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E6A"
msgid "With Ivica, it'll definitely be a skill worth employing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E6B"
msgid "Yes, and I am grateful. I just thought I would feel differently about this news."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051377]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E6C"
msgid "Then perhaps you aren't being forceful enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E6D"
msgid "The one responsible has been terminated. You owe me one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E6E"
msgid "Maybe relief to get some closure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001E6F"
msgid "Why did you decide to help the folks here? How do I know you won't discard them like the others?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D9A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EF6"
msgid "I read some insects eat their mates for sustenance. Something to think about if you find love."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EF7"
msgid "Just so you know, I don't like chewing noises. It's like a slap in the face."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EF8"
msgid "Nice weather we're having."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EF9"
msgid "What is even the point."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EFA"
msgid "Mushrooms. Wherever we go, there's just never enough mushrooms."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C21]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EFB"
msgid "I need a beer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EFC"
msgid "That's a hit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B87]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EFD"
msgid "Earlier, you mentioned a ship full of dead cultists. What happened to them?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EFE"
msgid "I don't have any more questions right now. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001EFF"
msgid "Did you know yeast is a type of fungus? Basically, no fungus, no beer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F00"
msgid "This is why mushrooms make for the best pets."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F01"
msgid "Did you know fungi are closer to animals than plants? Genetically speaking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F02"
msgid "I would love to see a ship full of creepy cultists."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B62]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F03"
msgid "Were any of these people your friends?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C45]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F04"
msgid "I forget their names though. I'm what you call a bad friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C45]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F05"
msgid "Well, there was a guy with a lisp, and this woman with really long fingernails."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F06"
msgid "If only it were MY head. Well, a girl can dream."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F07"
msgid "Fungus in space can survive extreme conditions. There's stories of blobs of mold on the Mir Space Station that could swallow a human head."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F08"
msgid "Community service. A judge had charged me with two hundred hours for shoplifting."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F09"
msgid "A black hole is technically a bottomless pit, in space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C4B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F0A"
msgid "Yeah, if only. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F0B"
msgid "Not if you're boring. Or a robot. Same thing, I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F0C"
msgid "There was this taxidermist job that looked promising, but it turns out it was for stuffing animals, not people. Joke's on me I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BE4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F0D"
msgid "I have. But nothing sticks out. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F0E"
msgid "Will you work for any less than that?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F0F"
msgid "Don't have the creds, huh. It happens."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F10"
msgid "I've been studying that relationship for years, and I want to preserve my findings for future scholars."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F11"
msgid "It's going to be a philosophical text about my theories on the intersection between science and the divine. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F12"
msgid "Waiting and decaying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D51]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F13"
msgid "So more work. Yay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D50]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F14"
msgid "I hope this isn't one of those promotions without the pay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D4F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F15"
msgid "As long as it's good and mindless."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083D4E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F16"
msgid "Huh. I didn't realize it was a work day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F17"
msgid "As long as you walk real slow."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F18"
msgid "I see what you mean."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083B96]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F19"
msgid "That's a beautiful sentiment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083BB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F1A"
msgid "No place for me huh. Guess I'll go loiter around the bank some more."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083C3A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F1B"
msgid "Very."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F1F"
msgid "*Sob* I have to rip them right out of my skull. Kill them before they kill me. And I won't let them kill me! I won't! I won't!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F20"
msgid "My eyes... they're, they're evil like the rest of them. They're keeping tabs on me, telling the others where I am... that has to be it. That has to be it, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4BD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F21"
msgid "*Sob* I can't take it! I just... god damn it, I can't take it anymore! I need to make them stop, but how? So many eyes... always watching."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4BE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F22"
msgid "I'm not one of them. At least, I don't think I am."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F23"
msgid "Please tell me you aren't one of them..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C443]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F24"
msgid "One more if I may..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C449]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F25"
msgid "Excuse me, Ms. LeBlanc? Just a few quick questions for SSNN, if you could."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D250]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F26"
msgid "I don't get why Sadie has to bring her sister to everything she's invited to. Sure, help her socialize more, but she doesn't do or say anything at these parties."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D250]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F27"
msgid "Man, I had to step out for a minute. I swear, if I don't talk about this, or get this out, or something, I'm gonna explode. I cannot keep this in if I'm gonna be drinking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC06SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F28"
msgid "Mayday! Mayday! We are in need of immediate assistance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B170]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F29"
msgid "Didn't expect that, now, did ya?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F2A"
msgid "Prepare to be destroyed!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD53]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F2B"
msgid "Ha! You fell right into our trap!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B176]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F2C"
msgid "Please wait for further messages."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C46C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F2D"
msgid "A third ship has joined the fight. Watch out!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C46A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F2E"
msgid "Y'see, what did I tell you? The hair on the back of my neck is never wrong!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C469]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F2F"
msgid "We have two bogeys incoming! I knew there was something wrong..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C467]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F30"
msgid "By the Great Serpent, I was right! Two pirate ships inbound!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B979]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F32"
msgid "HopeTech vessel to pilot. Please acknowledge. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A30C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F33"
msgid "HopeTech vessel to pilot. Please respond to this hail."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A317]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F34"
msgid "Please acknowledge. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D1B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F35"
msgid "Are you trying to make me die of old age? Hurry up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C4B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F36"
msgid "I'll get to that in due time. I'd hate to spoil anything just yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C74F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F37"
msgid "Got to hand it to you, you're doing well. Two for two. Let's see if you can keep it up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C74B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F38"
msgid "What goes to school but does not go to class?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C74B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F39"
msgid "All right. On to the next riddle! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C757]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F3A"
msgid "You thought I was bluffing? You didn't want to take this seriously, did you? Well, your actions have consequences, friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C757]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F3B"
msgid "Oh, that's funny, but I don't think the hostage that I'm about to kill will be laughing. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C7F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F3C"
msgid "A grenade."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F3E"
msgid "I don't know if I have the mental energy to pursue such a case."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065C37]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F3F"
msgid "As you know, my time in the Navy was nothing short of traumatic. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ACA1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F40"
msgid "The less you know about me, the better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106ACA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F41"
msgid "It's not that I don't trust you... but I don't trust you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD46]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F47"
msgid "Take that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC62]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F48"
msgid "You should be impressed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC5B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F49"
msgid "Do you really want to die here and now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC58]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F4A"
msgid "Ugh! Enough already!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC43]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F4B"
msgid "Not sure what there is to talk about here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F4C"
msgid "I can give you a ride if you need one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC52]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F4D"
msgid "No one needs to get hurt. I just need your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F4E"
msgid "No one's even trying to rescue you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AD47]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F4F"
msgid "All right, calm down. I'll transfer you some now, and my boss will take care of the rest later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106AC99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F50"
msgid "Sure. I'll just say you're my brother-in-law."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106481F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F51"
msgid "Oh, hi! So good to see you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F52"
msgid "Let's hurry before more pirates arrive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F53"
msgid "Are you done thinking now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065FA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F54"
msgid "Thank you, Hannah, I'll handle it from here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068038]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F55"
msgid "Does she always treat you like this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106802F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F56"
msgid "All right, let's go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068031]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F57"
msgid "Uh, yeah...I'll be all right. As long as I don't drift into the mines, I guess."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01068027]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F58"
msgid "I'm taking you to New Atlantis as well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106803A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F59"
msgid "I'm sorry, I'm not normally this emotional, um...It's been a rough day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01069D95]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F5A"
msgid "Oh, I don't think Miss Krause is on board with that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01069D94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F5B"
msgid "I'm not leaving you behind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CED4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F5C"
msgid "I wouldn't have it any other way. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F5D"
msgid "So what's on your agenda tonight?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F5E"
msgid "Are we the worst at making decisions, or what?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F5F"
msgid "Something that involves food. And you of course."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F60"
msgid "Maybe if you don't have any money, you shouldn't have so many expenses."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F61"
msgid "I wonder what that GalBank ship was doing in the middle of nowhere."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F62"
msgid "Well I don't know about you, but I can't *wait* to meet the VP of Acquisitions for the GalBank consortium."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F652]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F63"
msgid "Please don't leave us stranded here! Another pirate ship could arrive at any moment!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F657]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F64"
msgid "This is a GalBank ship, please provide assistance!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106439A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F65"
msgid "VP of Acquisitions? Is that you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01064398]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F66"
msgid "What can I do for you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106A4D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F67"
msgid "Um, all right then. Safe travels."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F64C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F68"
msgid "Stay out of this, Spacer! This does not concern you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F69"
msgid "We need more security."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F6A"
msgid "We can't expect our customers to handle it every time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F6B"
msgid "There's going to be trouble again someday. There always is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F6C"
msgid "That was brave. But if you ask me, we got off lucky."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059DBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F6D"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059ABE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F6E"
msgid "Get out of here. If I have something for you, I'll let you know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeB1
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F6F"
msgid "Got some new paint in the other day. How would you feel about being a bright pink and lime green kitty?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeC2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F70"
msgid "We'll do it soon, I promise. Just got to fix about a dozen things around here first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeC2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F71"
msgid "*Laugh* Wow! Such enthusiasm!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F72"
msgid "It looks like there's some cargo floating around. Might be worth the risk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F73"
msgid "This must have been a common grav jump exit point once. That would explain the mines."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F74"
msgid "Looks like space mines. Lots of them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F75"
msgid "We should probably steer clear of this area. I doubt any floating cargo is worth the risk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_EC08SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F76"
msgid "Are those space mines? There are so many of them!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080466]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F77"
msgid "We should go before the same thing happens to us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108045B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F78"
msgid "Right, so if one of the mines doesn't kill us, this will. Splendid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0108045A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F79"
msgid "Are you sure that was a good idea?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01080454]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F7A"
msgid "Was that really necessary?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A4F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F7B"
msgid "*Sigh* Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F7C"
msgid "Please just check, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F7D"
msgid "One moment we'll all be feeling tired and dizzy, and then the next, we'll all be dead!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A55]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F7E"
msgid "I heard a hissing noise from one of the bulkhead seams. It's an oxygen leak, I just know it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105456A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F7F"
msgid "Hello? Can you hear me? This is Jara Kleel, pilot of the Sycorax."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105456F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F80"
msgid "Please, if you're reading me... I need your help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4BB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F81"
msgid "You got it! You're a life-saver, truly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F83"
msgid "Hello, how are you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE1A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F84"
msgid "I only do the specials. Talk to Bobby up front."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE19]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F85"
msgid "You'll have to ask Bobby about that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE18]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F86"
msgid "You need to see Bobby for those."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE17]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F87"
msgid "Bobby takes care of that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053582]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F88"
msgid "Talk to my husband Bobby at the front."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105357C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F89"
msgid "Just kidding. Here's what we have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053581]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F8A"
msgid "Of course, sweetie. Here you go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053576]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F8B"
msgid "I was told to ask you about the specials."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE1C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F8C"
msgid "Of course, take your time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F8D"
msgid "Sure thing, traveler."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105356C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F8E"
msgid "Of course. Ask my lovely wife Fanisha in the back, she'll set you up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE29]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F8F"
msgid "Welcome back traveler! We have new wares for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE04]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F90"
msgid "Looking for something in particular?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F91"
msgid "What a nice surprise!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F92"
msgid "A lot of the guards there are supposed to be former mercenaries."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F93"
msgid "Word is, the guy who runs Anchorpoint used to work for Ecliptic."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F94"
msgid "They found the ship, but not the girl, so who knows what happened to her..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F95"
msgid "Apparently there was a teenager that got stranded in a ship she stole from her stepfather."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BE3B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F96"
msgid "That's it. Do you need anything else?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C82F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F97"
msgid "Always happy to see these two, living the dream out here in the Free Lanes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C82E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F98"
msgid "How are we on Chunks? I'm thinking of getting some."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C82D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F99"
msgid "I am thinking of buying something this time... but I do not know what."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C827]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F9A"
msgid "This is a quaint little space shop, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F920]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F9B"
msgid "Excellent, we're waiting for you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F911]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F9C"
msgid "I don't need anything right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F91B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F9D"
msgid "Don't be shy! You won't regret it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F919]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F9E"
msgid "You won't find better prices anywhere in the Free Lanes!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F918]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001F9F"
msgid "Whatever you need, chances are we have it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F913]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA0"
msgid "Ah, well, maybe next time then. Safe travels!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F91D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA1"
msgid "All right, I'm coming aboard."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F910]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA2"
msgid "Perhaps next time, then!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F910]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA3"
msgid "Such a shame, I'm sure you would have found what you needed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F914]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA4"
msgid "Greetings traveler. This is your lucky day!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA5"
msgid "I think I'll come aboard to see the specials."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F916]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA6"
msgid "Hello there! Are you ready to save big on everyday items?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EE9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA7"
msgid "Very good, we're waiting for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EE7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA8"
msgid "Got it. Here's what we have today."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EE2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FA9"
msgid "Hello again, my friend!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FAA"
msgid "See you around!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FAB"
msgid "Take care of yourself out there my friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FAC"
msgid "Safe travels!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D4E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FAD"
msgid "Always a pleasure, my friend."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545E1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FAE"
msgid "Hey, don't shoot at us, we're just traders!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010545E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FAF"
msgid "Okay, I think we'll wait until you're in a better mood..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C807]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB0"
msgid "Well if it ain't Bobby and Fanisha. Let's go say hi."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C806]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB1"
msgid "Well if it isn't our friends the space traders. Want to go check out the wares?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B391]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB2"
msgid "Bye."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B38F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB3"
msgid "Have fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B38E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB4"
msgid "We can talk later, alright?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B38A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB5"
msgid "We'll be here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B389]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB6"
msgid "Hope to see you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_ImreadytoreturntoAnchorpoint
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB7"
msgid "I'm ready to return to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_RightthenLetsgetyouback
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB8"
msgid "Right then. Let's get you back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_IfYouWantToLeave
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FB9"
msgid "If you want to leave, go tell Sawyer. I'm through with this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_WowThatsOneWayToRuinAVibe
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FBA"
msgid "Wow... That's one way to ruin a vibe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FBB"
msgid "Woah, having too much fun there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B399]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FBC"
msgid "Don't pass out again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B437]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FBD"
msgid "Sawyer's parties are the best getaway a girl could ask for."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FBE"
msgid "Damn, just when I was starting to have fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B431]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FBF"
msgid "I hope they don't attack each other."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B42F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC0"
msgid "Cheers to tonight!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B42D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC1"
msgid "I love this song!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B42A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC2"
msgid "This isn't anything a drink can't fix, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B426]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC3"
msgid "Now this is a party."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B425]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC4"
msgid "Don't be afraid to grab a drink. Sawyer's place is always stocked up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B423]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC5"
msgid "Hey there! Want to share a drink?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B421]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC6"
msgid "You didn't cause that fight, did you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B41B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC7"
msgid "I hope this party never ends."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B415]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC8"
msgid "How could Opal do this? And right under my nose."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B40D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FC9"
msgid "I'm not in the mood to talk right now, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B408]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FCA"
msgid "Not now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B406]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FCB"
msgid "I know this is a party, but don't cause too much trouble, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B402]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FCC"
msgid "I can't wait to get home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B400]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FCD"
msgid "We can talk later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FCE"
msgid "Not now, please."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FCF"
msgid "I really should go check on Opal soon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD0"
msgid "Not now, alright?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD1"
msgid "No point in just standing there. Go on. Join us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3DC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD2"
msgid "Not right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD3"
msgid "Have you decided to join us yet?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD4"
msgid "What's happening?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD5"
msgid "What the hell?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3CE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD6"
msgid "Hey. Stop that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD7"
msgid "We got trouble!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3C6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD8"
msgid "Cooper, Wren, be careful!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FD9"
msgid "You need to stop!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B31A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FDA"
msgid "I can't take much more of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B319]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FDB"
msgid "Stop, please!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B30B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FDC"
msgid "Lucky hit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B37A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FDD"
msgid "You've made quite the mess for us to deal with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B379]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FDE"
msgid "Hope you're ready to die."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B378]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FDF"
msgid "I won't let you get away with this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B373]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE0"
msgid "I just wanted a day to relax, and now you've ruined that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B36F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE1"
msgid "Now this is getting interesting!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B36E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE2"
msgid "You honestly think I'll let you get away with this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B363]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE3"
msgid "What the hell?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B361]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE4"
msgid "I didn't want to do this, but you forced me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Cooper_EveryoneGetDown
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE5"
msgid "Everyone, get down!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B358]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE6"
msgid "Wren, Sadie, are you guys okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Wren_Help
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE7"
msgid "Help!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B34E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE8"
msgid "Someone, turn them off!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B34D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FE9"
msgid "What's going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS02_Wren_WhyIsThisHappening
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FEA"
msgid "Why is this happening?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B344]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FEB"
msgid "Sawyer, what did you do to the turrets?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B33F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FEC"
msgid "You really had to start this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B33A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FED"
msgid "Dammit!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B337]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FEE"
msgid "Sadie, how do we turn them off?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B336]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FEF"
msgid "Sawyer, do something!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B32C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF0"
msgid "Grugh!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B324]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF1"
msgid "N-No..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E24C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF2"
msgid "Man, did you do this? What the hell...? *Sigh* I never should have invited you. I'm ready to get you out of my hair, alright? Let's get you back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E1FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF3"
msgid "You did what? Shit, man... You did that just to leave? Yeah. Yeah, sure. I'll take you back to Anchorpoint... Jackass..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E208]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF4"
msgid "Woah, woah, what's going on here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E1FF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF5"
msgid "Wait here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E21D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF6"
msgid "It's best she's not around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E292]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF7"
msgid "How did you get through it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E292]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF8"
msgid "You have? I haven't talked to anyone about this. It's just scary..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E256]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FF9"
msgid "No. You're right. I need to tell her. Okay..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E256]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FFA"
msgid "I know she would, but-"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E26C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FFB"
msgid "Alright. I can do that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E26C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FFC"
msgid "If I tell Sadie, maybe she can talk to Opal and clear all that up?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E207]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FFD"
msgid "What? Why would you even ask that? Opal and Sadie are best friends. I'm Sadie's sister, why would Opal do anything to me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FFE"
msgid "Did you hear that Wren was at Reliant Medical? I heard she got crazy sick. No wonder Sadie has been gone for so long. She was probably taking care of her sister. Whatever it was, I'm just glad Sadie's back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "001FFF"
msgid "It must have cost Sawyer a small fortune. Well, probably cost his parents. But I guess what they don't know won't hurt them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002000"
msgid "Not that it's gossip or anything, but doesn't Sawyer's ship look amazing? Sadie is the one who hooked him up on it all; From the design to the security system."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002001"
msgid "You wouldn't happen to know any juicy gossip, would you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002002"
msgid "We would never. Besides, we just knew all our other friends would love you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5D2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002003"
msgid "Hey, now! Calm down a moment. Relax. You're on my ship. Safe and sound."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E287]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002004"
msgid "Right... I should get back to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E239]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002005"
msgid "Of course! We'll be here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E218]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002006"
msgid "That tends to happen, doesn't it? But you're safe now. Sawyer and I took you to his ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002007"
msgid "Hey again, stranger. Thinking about taking us up on those drinks?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E23A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002008"
msgid "That's a shame. Well, if you ever want to have a few free drinks, you know where to find us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E25C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002009"
msgid "I finally got my new ship paid off. Even sounds wild to say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E284]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00200A"
msgid "Look who it is. Is that Sleeping Beauty? How are you feeling?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00200B"
msgid " Really, Sawyer? Her?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00200C"
msgid " Really, Sawyer? Him?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E2B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00200D"
msgid " Really, Sawyer? Them?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E279]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00200E"
msgid "Who knows. We all may end up being peas in a pod!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E279]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00200F"
msgid "Don't mind Opal. She has a hard time making new friends. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002010"
msgid "Where in the hell were you? I thought you ran off to get some rest after all that drinking. I couldn't find you. Good thing you're safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104E213]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002011"
msgid "So, when do you think the others will get here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002012"
msgid "I'll explain later. For now, take this asshole back to the dump where we found them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B297]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002013"
msgid "Opal, what's going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B280]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002014"
msgid "You don't deserve these friends. Soon enough they'll know what you're doing and leave you behind. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2A3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002015"
msgid "Say no more. I can't wait to get you off this ship. Sawyer!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002016"
msgid "Tell Sawyer to bring me back to Anchorpoint. If not, then this slate goes to Sadie."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002017"
msgid "I should give it to Cooper. He'll probably love hearing this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B289]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002018"
msgid "Don't you dare show her that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B27A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002019"
msgid "No, no, you really shouldn't."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B274]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00201A"
msgid "And she's not going to like me either. Wait here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00201B"
msgid "What? I'm sorry. What is this? What- Why would she even say this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00201C"
msgid "A slate? Is this Opal's? Why do you have that? Let me see it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00201D"
msgid "I think Sadie should have a listen to that slate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B28C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00201E"
msgid "Where did you get this? I just-"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00201F"
msgid "I'm sorry. Yeah, it's fine, I guess. I don't know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002020"
msgid "Someone told you that? It wasn't Opal, was it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B279]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002021"
msgid "You set up Sawyer's ship?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002022"
msgid "I heard you haven't been out much. How are you liking the party?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002023"
msgid "Is this your first party?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002024"
msgid "Are all your parties like this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B288]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002025"
msgid "Do you know Opal or Sawyer very well?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002026"
msgid "How are you liking the party so far?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002027"
msgid "Not as much as I wished. For example, Opal hasn't been around Cooper all that much tonight. They've been dating for so long now, but it's like she's avoiding him. I hope the two are okay..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002028"
msgid "Yeah. Just, be careful about Opal. She gets mad easily and I think she holds a grudge too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2AA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002029"
msgid "I'm not sure I should tell you this, but if you see Wren, please be gentle with her. She's been sick for months and is finally getting out again. I thought this get-together could be good for her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B29A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00202A"
msgid "You can tell her whatever you want, but she won't believe you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B299]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00202B"
msgid "What? No. No. Please. You don't need to tell her anything. She should hear it from me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2B0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00202C"
msgid "Trust me. I would love to drop this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B292]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00202D"
msgid "I guess if you see absolutely nothing wrong with this, then fine. Drop it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B301]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00202E"
msgid "You don't know what you're talking about, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00202F"
msgid "No one should have to go through this. You can't hide this from Sadie forever."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002030"
msgid "You may not be an isolated case with Opal. She could be bullying the others too."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B2A6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002031"
msgid "It's not that simple. I wish it were, but it's not. Opal has been friends with everyone since, I can't even remember."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D685]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002032"
msgid "I'm ready. Take me back to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D69E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002033"
msgid "A slate? You caused all this over a slate? Whatever. I'll take a listen later. For now, let's get you back to Anchorpoint."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D68B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002034"
msgid "I gave her what she deserved."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D686]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002035"
msgid "What did you do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D673]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002036"
msgid "I think Wren mentioned you, so I wanted to say 'hi.'"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D678]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002037"
msgid "He's a bit much for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D697]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002038"
msgid "You're Sawyer's new friend, right? Surprised you're not partying it up with him. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D692]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002039"
msgid "I guess so."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D68C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00203A"
msgid "For talking, a name tends to be a good place to start."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D696]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00203B"
msgid "Sounds like the alcohol brought you then. Opal told me she met you at a bar. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106DC21]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00203C"
msgid "Maybe..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106573E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00203D"
msgid "I knew that you would come through."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106574F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00203E"
msgid "As we agreed, your credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485ED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00203F"
msgid "Please don't hurt me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104BFF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002040"
msgid "Sometimes I feel like the only teenager in the entire universe..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_BE_EC01SharedInfo10
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002041"
msgid "Ugh! Why are you still there!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D029]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002042"
msgid "So, we can just get on your ship then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104076E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002043"
msgid "Trust me, you don't want to end up with some of the people out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040740]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002044"
msgid "I'll take my chances."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040767]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002045"
msgid "What do you want now?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040745]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002046"
msgid "What's up?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104073D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002047"
msgid "Tell me who you are and why you're on this ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104075B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002048"
msgid "Um, all right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040753]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002049"
msgid "I'm sorry, I don't really know how to deal with kindness..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104073E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00204A"
msgid "I'm not going to hurt you, I just want to talk."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040773]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00204B"
msgid "It's okay Gloria, I know you ran away. I'm here to help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040772]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00204C"
msgid "Yeah I think I'm just going to sit here and say nothing, now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104074D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00204D"
msgid "Why don't you just leave me alone?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040759]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00204E"
msgid "Fine, I'll tell you! Maybe you'll leave me alone then..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040762]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00204F"
msgid "And if I do, you'll let me go, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010408A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002050"
msgid "Sure, go ahead. See if I care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C0D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002051"
msgid "What's your destination?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048C0B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002052"
msgid "Not my greatest idea, I know. I really thought I could handle it..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002053"
msgid "I don't think I should get involved in this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002054"
msgid "Just... leave me alone, okay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104A1C3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002055"
msgid "Of course not. What was I thinking?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040764]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002056"
msgid "Sure, I can do that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D027]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002057"
msgid "Me? Oh, I'll be fine. I enjoy being stranded in outer space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002058"
msgid "We can go right now, I have all I need."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002059"
msgid "Here, take this. I don't need it anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D01D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00205A"
msgid "I could take you to a spaceport if you want."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104D022]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00205B"
msgid "You should go back to your ship now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B988]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00205C"
msgid "But but, you said you wouldn't hurt me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B986]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00205D"
msgid "You'll tell me what I want to know, or else I'll hurt you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DACC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00205F"
msgid "Ugh. Grav jumping makes me feel nauseous..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DACB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002060"
msgid "I can't wait to get there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DACA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002061"
msgid "Wow, I really sounded like a kid just now, didn't I?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DACA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002062"
msgid "Are we there yet?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DAC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002063"
msgid "Haven't been to New Atlantis in a while. I wonder if it's changed much..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DAC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002064"
msgid "Nice ship you have here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C50B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002065"
msgid "See, I told ya she was a teenager. A pretty ballsy one at that!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C506]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002066"
msgid "Are you sure we should get involved?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C504]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002067"
msgid "Where I grew up this would not be tolerated."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C509]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002068"
msgid "I hope this act of kindness doesn't come back to haunt us..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002069"
msgid "All right, see ya! I mean... over and out!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00206A"
msgid "I'm coming on board to help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485FE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00206B"
msgid "Really, there's no need to respond."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00206C"
msgid "No, we're fine! Oops, starting to lose the signal now...okay bye!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010485F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00206D"
msgid "How can I tell if this thing is working?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DABB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00206E"
msgid "I don't know yet... Where my feet will take me, I guess. It's like an adventure!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DAC3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00206F"
msgid "No that's fine. Thanks for the lift."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DAC0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002070"
msgid "Sure. I'll find someone to, uh, help me get my ship back in order."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DABF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002071"
msgid "Oh yeah. As long as I'm far away from my stepfather, I'll be fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DABE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002072"
msgid "Are you going to be all right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DACF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002073"
msgid "Good luck out there, <Alias=Gloria>."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002074"
msgid "Here, take this. For being such a nice person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104DEB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002075"
msgid "I'll never forget it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBD9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00207C"
msgid "Damn Spacers. Bloodthirsty savages, the lot of them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBD4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00207D"
msgid "I thought that was the end for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00207E"
msgid "You really saved me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBD0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00207F"
msgid "Those bastards took my ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBCE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002080"
msgid "Get me out of here, I'm begging you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104048A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002081"
msgid "I'm afraid I've got nothing to offer you but gratitude. They took everything else."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104048A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002082"
msgid "I'm going to rest here a little bit, and then use their transmitter to call Lucia for a lift."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002083"
msgid "You have every right to want him out of your life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040483]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002084"
msgid "[Lie] That's right. She's the one who hired me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002085"
msgid "I'm guessing she must have sent you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002086"
msgid "Truth is, after all this time, I'm starting to feel the same way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002087"
msgid "I really didn't think he wanted me in his life anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002088"
msgid "I haven't seen or heard from him in so long."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002089"
msgid "I'm sorry, did you say my father?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040488]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00208A"
msgid "I'm the famed galactic superhero called... The Mantis!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040491]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00208B"
msgid "Who are you? You're not one of them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBE7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00208C"
msgid "I wish I could believe that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00208D"
msgid "I guess I could have been wrong."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00208E"
msgid "He said it was the greatest regret of his life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00208F"
msgid "Believe me, he regrets his actions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002090"
msgid "I've thought a lot about that. About being the better man."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBDB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002091"
msgid "Maybe this has gone on long enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002092"
msgid "It's obvious he's suffering. You can put a stop to that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002093"
msgid "He's in pain and you're being selfish by not helping."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBFD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002094"
msgid "Yeah, there's no denying that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002095"
msgid "So it's on me, huh? Yeah, I think it is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBB6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002096"
msgid "You're his own flesh and blood. I promise, he wants to hear from you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002097"
msgid "He's your father. That has to count for something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002098"
msgid "It's funny, my wife used to say that too. I should have listened."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBCC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002099"
msgid "I don't know if my father will ever feel like family to me again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00209A"
msgid "Sometimes, my inability to get past all of this feels like my biggest weakness."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBBA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00209B"
msgid "There are days when the grief of everything I've lost is unbearable."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBB9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00209C"
msgid "It's true. It still hurts to think about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00209D"
msgid "You should reach out now. Nobody knows how much time we have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00209E"
msgid "If you want to talk about it, I'm listening."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C41D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00209F"
msgid "Uh... please respond, over."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C41B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A0"
msgid "Aren't you gonna say anything?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C426]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A1"
msgid "Thanks a lot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C424]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A2"
msgid "Thanks for doing this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedInfo01_CaptainIntro02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A3"
msgid "I... well, I feel I have to ask this, for my crew's sake. We can trust you, yeah? I don't want there to be any more problems after the day we just had."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R03SharedInfo01_CaptainIntro02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A4"
msgid "We appreciate you doing this for us. I know it's a burden, but we'll stay out of your way as best we can."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A5"
msgid "Anyone there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A6"
msgid "Please respond. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A7"
msgid "Can you fly us out of here? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A8"
msgid "We could've used your help back there. Our ship took heavy damage, and the captain's not sure if we'll be able to fly out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020A9"
msgid "Hate to put this on you, but could you fly us out of here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020AA"
msgid "Unfortunately, not all of us made it... we lost our pilot. The rest of us crew aren't trained to pilot this class of ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052EA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020AB"
msgid "Thanks for the help back there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020AC"
msgid "Could you fly us home?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020AD"
msgid "Our ship got torn up during the attack. The captain isn't sure we can fly it back home safely. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103D1B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020AE"
msgid "Appreciate the assist, but I'm afraid I have to ask for your help again. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D81]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020AF"
msgid "Yeah, I have an eye for ships. *Sigh* I Should've just been a mechanic. Would've kept me out of a lot of trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103EDFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B0"
msgid "No offense taken. We should get going, now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B1"
msgid "Sorry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B2"
msgid "Look, forget I said anything. We're all just a little shaken up after the attack. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B3"
msgid "I didn't mean it like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C422]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B4"
msgid "I get it, but we should get going now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B5"
msgid "All right, we're all ready to go."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C429]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B6"
msgid "I'm just glad they got what's coming to 'em."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C429]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B7"
msgid "How the hell would I know? Spacers will be Spacers. They see a ship and they want to blow it up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D8A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B8"
msgid "No need to get defensive. I have to ask. I have a crew to look after."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539D7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020B9"
msgid "*Sigh* This is really not how I saw this day going. Supposed to be a quick delivery job. Yeah, right..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020BA"
msgid "This was the first time we worked with him. Poor bastard. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010539DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020BB"
msgid "You don't need to apologize. It's not like you killed him."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530CC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020BC"
msgid "Yeah, he was a solid pilot, but to be honest, I didn't really know much about him. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020BD"
msgid "Nothing we can do now but move on. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020BE"
msgid "We're ready to leave whenever you are. Thanks for this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020BF"
msgid "We were just minding our business, and then, bam. They came out of nowhere and started firing on us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530F1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C0"
msgid "Your guess is as good as anyone else's. Who knows?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C1"
msgid "Do you have any idea why the Spacers attacked you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C2"
msgid "My condolences, but we need to get moving. More spacers could jump in at any moment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010530FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C3"
msgid "Thanks. He was great. He got us out of all sorts of jams, but I guess his luck ran out today."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C4"
msgid "*Sigh* God, I need a break. I'm so sick of fighting. Fighting to take over this ship, fighting the Spacers, now we have to fight you, don't we?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D8D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C5"
msgid "You actually seem like a nice person. I almost wish I didn't have to do this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D73]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C6"
msgid "No condolences necessary. He was a pain in the neck."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C7"
msgid "Huh, didn't think of that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D9E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C8"
msgid "He was a good guy, yeah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020C9"
msgid "Huh? Oh, yeah. I didn't know him much. We practically just met."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020CA"
msgid "Sorry about your pilot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D83]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020CB"
msgid "Tell you what. You let me and my crew fly your ship. You can just relax. What do you say?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020CC"
msgid "Take them down!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020CD"
msgid "We weren't asking. We're taking that ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020CE"
msgid "Your ship is ours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020CF"
msgid "All right, I've got them cornered!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D0"
msgid "And don't fight. We can make this painless for you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053D91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D1"
msgid "Don't move. We're taking your ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037161]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D2"
msgid "And here you go, payment as promised."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037171]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D3"
msgid "I've got your prototype robot parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105D547]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D4"
msgid "They look to be in good shape."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_CrimsonFleetResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D5"
msgid "Take her. She's all yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_CrimsonFleetResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D6"
msgid "Whoa, what? We don't want any trouble here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Yura_SceneReentry01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D7"
msgid "So, how about that house sitting job? You in?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_Yura01SceneReentry02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D8"
msgid "But she knows about the note, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Roman_Yura01SceneReentry02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020D9"
msgid "So you're the one that found the ransom note? Is Yura even there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B44B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020DA"
msgid "No more breaking laws for us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B448]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020DB"
msgid "Remember to talk to Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B444]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020DC"
msgid "Keep an eye on that little critter."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B441]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020DD"
msgid "Thanks for letting us go on this one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B440]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020DE"
msgid "Sure will be nice if you can help Roman out with Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B43C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020DF"
msgid "Thanks for the credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B439]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E0"
msgid "Take care of Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D6D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E1"
msgid "No sudden moves."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D62]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E2"
msgid "We didn't do anything, I swear."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D5D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E3"
msgid "Still looking for someone if you're up for it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D5B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E4"
msgid "You really are saving my sanity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E5"
msgid "Thanks for taking this off my hands."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E6"
msgid "We're gonna mess you up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E7"
msgid "I knew this was gonna happen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E8"
msgid "You messed with the wrong crew."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020E9"
msgid "Get 'em!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020EA"
msgid "Get her!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103587A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020EB"
msgid "Yura... Never mind. We'll talk about this later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103586A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020EC"
msgid "You've proven yourself a far better house sitter than Yura ever was."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103586A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020ED"
msgid "And, miraculously, all my plants are still alive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035875]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020EE"
msgid "Well, since she seems fine to me, I'll take your word for it. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020EF"
msgid "Oh, so this is my fault? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D1D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F0"
msgid "Oh, so this is my fault? There's no \"take Milli for a walk\" listed on those care instructions."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103588E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F1"
msgid "Well, you could've left a message or something... anything to explain why you weren't here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103587D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F2"
msgid "Excuse me, Yura. Are you going to tell me who this is or what?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358A4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F3"
msgid "Milli was petnapped. I had to get her back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103587E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F4"
msgid "Getting Milli back from your friend, Roman."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035887]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F5"
msgid "Wait, Roman? What was he even doing with Milli?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035879]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F6"
msgid "What do you mean \"the pet sitter\" has Milli? You were supposed to be taking care of her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035881]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F7"
msgid "Here's the key to Atka's house."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035DAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F8"
msgid "Here's what I intended to pay Yura, plus a little extra for the trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035876]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020F9"
msgid "Well, she certainly seems fine, so I guess Yura was telling the truth for once."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C85A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020FA"
msgid "I can't believe Atka came home early and Milli was nowhere to be found."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C851]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020FB"
msgid "Don't talk to me!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020FC"
msgid "In that case, hand over Milli, or we do this the hard way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035867]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020FD"
msgid "Negotiate? Sorry, I'm an all or nothing kind of guy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C843]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020FE"
msgid "So, you gonna pay up or get the hell outta here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C841]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0020FF"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035895]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002100"
msgid "So, here's the key to my sister Atka's house. She lives on Muphrid IV, outside of the Freestar Collective."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002101"
msgid "You know, we are polar opposites, but that's why you're perfect for this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002102"
msgid "Did I mention credits would be involved?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002103"
msgid "Wow, really? You'd let a poor, innocent creature die?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103587C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002104"
msgid "Oh and I know I said \"favor,\" but it's not like you wouldn't get paid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103587C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002105"
msgid "You don't have time to care for an innocent, helpless little pet? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035861]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002106"
msgid "Sure, let's hear it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002107"
msgid "All you have to do is water a few plants and feed a little milliwhale until my sister gets home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002108"
msgid "Oh you're gonna love it. Easiest credits you'll ever make!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035890]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002109"
msgid "Depends on what it is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035899]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00210A"
msgid "I heard what you did for the station, taking out those Spacers, and I was hoping you could do me just the tiniest of favors."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035899]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00210B"
msgid "Ah, so I did catch your attention. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00210C"
msgid "Hey, hold up!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A7A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00210D"
msgid "The way I see it, you're the only one taking risks here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035A76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00210E"
msgid "Do you really want to risk everyone here over a milliwhale?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00210F"
msgid "At this point, I'm considering raising the price."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002110"
msgid "That ransom's too high. You're being unreasonable here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D7D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002111"
msgid "You're not going to consider lowering the price?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D85]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002112"
msgid "Pay <Global=SFFL_MS03_RansomCredits>: Here's your credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D1F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002113"
msgid "Nice story, but I'm just here for Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D89]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002114"
msgid "Shows how much you know about Yura."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002115"
msgid "Here I am trying to impress her to ask her out, and I don't even know her well enough to realize how stupid it all is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035D8C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002116"
msgid "Damn, maybe you're right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002117"
msgid "I get it, I do..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D18]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002118"
msgid "Milli's rare, though. She's not your ordinary milliwhale."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002119"
msgid "Nope. Credits or nothing. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CCE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00211A"
msgid "You got those credits for me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D3F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00211B"
msgid "I'm not looking for a fight here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D79]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00211C"
msgid "I'm willing to do this the hard way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D78]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00211D"
msgid "Do I look like someone you want to piss off? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00211E"
msgid "You should tell her how you feel. She'd appreciate that even more."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00211F"
msgid "If she says no, at least you told her how you felt. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002120"
msgid "You should tell her how you feel yourself. It will mean more coming from you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002121"
msgid "Here's the key to Milli's room. Little critter's all yours."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002122"
msgid "Good because you were about to wipe me out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002123"
msgid "Milli's all yours. Please, just take her, and this will never happen again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D2A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002124"
msgid "Lucky for you, no one's pressing charges here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002125"
msgid "Don't worry about it. No harm, no foul."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002126"
msgid "And believe me when I say Yura is not the type to get the law involved."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002127"
msgid "I figured she'd be excited to have something fun to do for a change."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002128"
msgid "I never thought Yura would take this seriously. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D33]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002129"
msgid "Petnapping for fun is still petnapping."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D2E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00212A"
msgid "Wait, what?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D15]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00212B"
msgid "It's hard to put yourself out there, but you can do this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CD0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00212C"
msgid "Suit yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059D2B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00212D"
msgid "I swear we were always going to return Milli safe and sound."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00212E"
msgid "Good enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00212F"
msgid "Pomegranate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CF7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002130"
msgid "Open this door or you're all dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CFB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002131"
msgid "If this job is so easy, why can't you do it? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CCA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002132"
msgid "Where is Atka?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002133"
msgid "And don't worry, she's small, tame, doesn't even bite."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059CBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002134"
msgid "A milli-whale! It's like a big pillow on too many legs."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A364]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002135"
msgid "The Settled Systems is safer with them gone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A35D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002136"
msgid "Here. Take it. Now please, just leave us alone."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A357]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002137"
msgid "I think I should get paid."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A341]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002138"
msgid "God, don't scare me like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A335]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002139"
msgid "Look... I... I think you should leave."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A361]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00213A"
msgid "Petnappers don't deserve to live."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A365]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00213B"
msgid "I'm staying out of this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A35A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00213C"
msgid "This seems like something you two need to work out on your own."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A351]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00213D"
msgid "Roman took Milli and was holding her for ransom."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105A35B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00213E"
msgid "Don't try to change the subject on me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105B430]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00213F"
msgid "Roman's not thinking anything anymore."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002140"
msgid "Is she always pawning off responsibilities on other people?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002141"
msgid "Every time I work up the courage, she seems to sense it and pushes me away."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002142"
msgid "But I'm afraid that even if she likes me, too, she'll still say no because she thinks she doesn't deserve to be happy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002143"
msgid "Well, rejection for one. I don't want to ruin the friendship we already have."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002144"
msgid "If they were still alive, I'd give them a piece of my mind."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002145"
msgid "She's not successful like Atka, and I think her parents made her out to be some sort of failure."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002146"
msgid "Yura acts like nothing can hurt her, but she really doesn't think too highly of herself. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF7F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002147"
msgid "Why does she have difficulty with compliments?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002148"
msgid "I tell her all the time, but when it comes to taking compliments, she hates it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002149"
msgid "She always knows what to say, too. I just wish she knew how cool she really is."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF6F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00214A"
msgid "Yura's great. She's like that person that makes you feel better just knowing they're around."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00214B"
msgid "Plus Milli makes sense for a ransom. Most millies are easy to come by, but Milli's a rarity."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00214C"
msgid "We could've emptied the place out, but that would've been too much work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00214D"
msgid "Milli was the key. She's the only thing we could've taken that would've gotten Yura's attention in the first place."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00214E"
msgid "I guess if you're smart enough to know what's going on, you know what you're doing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00214F"
msgid "Obviously, it's beyond my... whatever. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C9CB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002150"
msgid "If I told you, I'd have to kill you. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002151"
msgid "I assure you, Milli's received only the utmost care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002152"
msgid "We guarded this creature with our very lives."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01084FE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002153"
msgid "No way, I'm not getting involved in this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1E4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002158"
msgid "Thanks for helping out Roman."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1E0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002159"
msgid "Those two are never gonna get it together."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00215A"
msgid "I'm almost afraid to ask. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF0E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00215B"
msgid "Yura told me you convinced her to give me a shot. I owe you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF0D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00215C"
msgid "Thanks for talking to Yura. These past few days have been the best of my life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Support_PostQuestRoman03_Shared
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00215D"
msgid "Thanks again for letting us off the hook."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Support_PostQuestRoman02_Shared
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00215E"
msgid "Just another law-abiding citizen."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEFF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00215F"
msgid "Thanks for all of your advice. You were right, and I've never been so happy."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002160"
msgid "Just get out of here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFCE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002161"
msgid "I told you it'd be easy credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002162"
msgid "I guess Atka's gonna be mad at me for a while, but she'll get over it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002163"
msgid "Roman didn't deserve to die. He was a good person."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002164"
msgid "I'm sorry you had to be involved in all this, but I think we need some space."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BFBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002165"
msgid "This is the first time I returned home to find all my plants alive and well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002166"
msgid "Remember to take care of Milli."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEEA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002167"
msgid "Until next time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002168"
msgid "Take care."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEE0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002169"
msgid "Stay safe."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEDC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00216A"
msgid "Catch ya later."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF16]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00216B"
msgid "Come on... I don't have all day."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF13]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00216C"
msgid "Anybody home?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Yura_RelationshipResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00216D"
msgid "Until then, it's better this way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS03_Yura_RelationshipResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00216E"
msgid "I only hope Roman understands. I keep saying I'm going to get it together, but who knows when that'll be. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00216F"
msgid "Why are you doing this?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106D5B6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002170"
msgid "Never should've trusted you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358C1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002171"
msgid "Hey, you aren't the only one! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002172"
msgid "I swear, Yura, you're so irresponsible, I can't believe we're related."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010358B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002173"
msgid "Please, first of all, you're family, and second of all, you don't even deserve half of what I offered you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF6E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002174"
msgid "But if you never try, you could lose him, and the regret would be worse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002175"
msgid "I know how you feel, but I also know you can work past that together."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002176"
msgid "Well sure, not right now. But give it time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF74]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002177"
msgid "Let's just say I've got some issues that don't let me make the best decisions and leave it at that. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105BF76]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002178"
msgid "I can't believe he did all this for me. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C373]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002179"
msgid "I think she got it from our parents who couldn't handle the fact that I never went to college or bothered with a steady job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105C373]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00217A"
msgid "Atka's always trying to get me to do stuff so she can \"teach me responsibility.\" "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CF0F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00217B"
msgid "What can you tell me about Roman?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00217C"
msgid "As for that ransom, though... He must've been hoping I'd get the credits from Atka because he knows I don't have that kinda money."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00217D"
msgid "He gets along with Atka fine and he loves Milli. I think he just wanted to make things interesting for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE91]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00217E"
msgid "I think he did it for me, as weird as that sounds."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CE98]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00217F"
msgid "The parents' view of success doesn't always match the child's."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002180"
msgid "Atka just wants to make sure you're taken care of."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEF8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002181"
msgid "Have you told Atka you're not interested in that kind of life?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002182"
msgid "So I occasionally take a job that may not be legit, but if I can get enough credits to coast for a while, no way I'm passing that up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105CEB7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002183"
msgid "Right? You make your own hours, set your own rates..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002184"
msgid "I understand. It sounds like you're just not ready."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002185"
msgid "You could've fooled me, but you did get me this far."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1C2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002186"
msgid "If things work out, just be patient."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1BF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002187"
msgid "No way. Oh no. That means I really get to go through with it now. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002188"
msgid "What? You're not joking? Oh god, so I really get to go through with it now. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002189"
msgid "Thanks for saving me the pain."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00218A"
msgid "It's probably a good thing you came along. I can't imagine doing all this just to get crushed in the end."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00218B"
msgid "Gah, I don't want to move on... but if she can't trust me at this point, maybe she never will."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B1B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00218C"
msgid "You need to move on."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C8DE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00218D"
msgid "I knew this wasn't gonna work out. Why do I even keep trying?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C727]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00218E"
msgid "I should have listened to her. Begged for me to get a job on land. Happy wife, happy life, right? But the pay - It's real helpful now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C72F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00218F"
msgid "Oh? Give me one moment. This ship always has something to complain about. Guess I better check on it. See you soon, Love. Promise."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106C72D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002190"
msgid "Speaking of this ship, she's a real piece of work. 'Best for the price,' my ass! I'm telling you that seller must have pulled a fast one on me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_MS01_CrimeDialogueSharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002192"
msgid "Suit yourself!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034E65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002193"
msgid "I'm not paying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034E69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002194"
msgid "Unbelievable. Well, I'm in a forgiving mood, so I'll let you go this time. But next time, you're butt is mine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034E68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002195"
msgid "Wise choice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01086506]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002196"
msgid "[<Global=SFFL_MS01_CrimeGold_Amount> Credits] I don't have the money."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034E66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002197"
msgid "[<Global=SFFL_MS01_CrimeGold_Amount> Credits, stolen items confiscated] I'll pay the fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002198"
msgid "Take out the leader. That should be enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343B9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002199"
msgid "Words of gratitude are fine, but credits are better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343AE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00219A"
msgid "If that's true, maybe you should abandon the station."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00219B"
msgid "I can't guarantee your safety."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010343A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00219C"
msgid "We'll do our best to protect you, but there's only a few of us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021A5"
msgid "Hello? This is the right button, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_Z01StarbornResponse
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021A6"
msgid "You did? Please tell me she's alright! Where is she?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056603]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021A7"
msgid "You're still there, right? Hello?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056602]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021A8"
msgid "Can you hear me? I can't hear you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056601]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021A9"
msgid "Hello? Are you still there?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105663D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021AA"
msgid "What am I going to do...?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105663A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021AB"
msgid "Oh, Gabbie..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056639]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021AC"
msgid "I'll find you Gabbie, I promise..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056613]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021AD"
msgid "Hello? Hello? Can you hear me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056612]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021AE"
msgid "Have you found Gabrielle yet?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056610]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021AF"
msgid "Do you have any news on Gabrielle?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056618]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B0"
msgid "Shit. Shit!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056621]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B1"
msgid "I didn't come out here to fight!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056620]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B2"
msgid "I don't want to hurt you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105661E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B3"
msgid "I won't let it end this way!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B4"
msgid "I'm her wife. She went on a job and it's been months..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B5"
msgid "Please, have you seen a cargo ship out here? Piloted by a woman named Gabrielle Baker?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010325F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B6"
msgid "You seem like you're more versed in this whole flying thing than me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035300]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B7"
msgid "Oh... Well, take care of yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035305]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B8"
msgid "I don't want your credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01035306]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021B9"
msgid "She didn't say. I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021BA"
msgid "[Lie] I found her, but she said she can't go home yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021BB"
msgid "Her ship malfunctioned. I found these slates in the wreckage."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021BC"
msgid "But I couldn't just sit and wait for her to come home any longer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021BD"
msgid "She may call me foolish for such a thing. We've been saving for so long. She wanted us to have enough money to retire in peace."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021BE"
msgid "I did. I took our savings and bought a ship to find her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021BF"
msgid "Please, if you find her, tell her I'm out here and to please come home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010352E5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C0"
msgid "Dammit... I'm sorry. I just-"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056634]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C1"
msgid "I can't imagine what that poor woman is going through. All we can really hope is one day she finds some peace."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056629]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C2"
msgid "If you find her, please, let her know I'm out here. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056629]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C3"
msgid "Really? Thank you. Thank you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01056609]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C4"
msgid "If you haven't found her yet, then I guess I can help."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C5"
msgid "Please. If- When you find her tell her to come home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010565F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C6"
msgid "You can? Thank you. Thank you so much! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388C8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C7"
msgid "Well, if you aren't gonna say anything, I guess we'll let our guns do the talking!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C8"
msgid "Goddamnit! Honey, power up those weapons!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021C9"
msgid "[Lie] I did. Dibs on any Crimson Fleet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021CA"
msgid "I didn't. You clearly got scammed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388C5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021CB"
msgid "Never mess with a pirate."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388C0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021CC"
msgid "Any last words before we blow you to smithereens?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021CD"
msgid "Hey, where's he going!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021CE"
msgid "I know you can hear me! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021CF"
msgid "All right bub, you asked for it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031723]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D1"
msgid "Yeah you would."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D2"
msgid "I'll see what I can do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D3"
msgid "And while you're doing your job, try to remember where you'd be without my intervention."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316F7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D4"
msgid "Just do your job."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE4C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D5"
msgid "This is not right... this cannot be right..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104AE48]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D6"
msgid "Time for you to eat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D7"
msgid "I've felt better, honestly."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D8"
msgid "Join me on my ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021D9"
msgid "Hello, stranger. I am offering food and company, if you are interested. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCD3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021DA"
msgid "I need only your company."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCA5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021DB"
msgid "Do you need help with anything? Supplies? I could take you to port somewhere if your ship needs maintenance."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021DC"
msgid "Look, I'm just here because you promised food. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021DD"
msgid "No, no, not yet, not yet. Not before the meal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021DE"
msgid "I'm not answering that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCB2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021DF"
msgid "How is that possible?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCC8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E0"
msgid "It is hard for this body to move and clean. Too old."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCA6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E1"
msgid "It looks that way. No offense. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E2"
msgid "I regret that it has fallen into disrepair as of late. It has been... years since I have landed anywhere. Years and years."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCAA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E3"
msgid "I can see your eyes wandering about my ship. I extend my apologies for the state of it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E4"
msgid "My ship isn't much better."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102FCBC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E5"
msgid "I don't find old women very scary."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300D1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E6"
msgid "Yes, I apologize for the delay. You must be hungry."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E7"
msgid "About time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300D4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E8"
msgid "Excuse me. Just hungry, excited to eat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021E9"
msgid "Something isn't right with you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021EA"
msgid "*Heavy breathing*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010300C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021EB"
msgid "*Heavy breathing*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030741]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021EC"
msgid "We will never let you leave!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103073C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021ED"
msgid "We invited you to eat, and yet you spurn us. You may as well spit in our face!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103073C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021EE"
msgid "You are making us very angry!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103074D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021EF"
msgid "What did you do to me? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030751]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021F0"
msgid "Impossible. No one has reacted like that before."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01048D0C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021F1"
msgid "What's in it?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01050239]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021F5"
msgid "What? Wait, don't leave me here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105023F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021F6"
msgid "What... what's going on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105022A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021F7"
msgid "What's going on here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EA9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021F8"
msgid "Do we have a problem?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EC9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021F9"
msgid "Have something to show me?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EBF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021FA"
msgid "I have some more targets I need taken out. Interested? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R02_TargetSpared_SharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021FB"
msgid "I thought I was done for..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R02SharedInfo01_CaptiveNPCSpared
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021FC"
msgid "Just need to figure out how to get out of here, and then you'll never see me again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_R02SharedInfo01_CaptiveNPCSpared
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021FD"
msgid "Thank you! Thank you!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590E8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021FE"
msgid "I swear, you won't ever see my face again!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0021FF"
msgid "No, this can't be happening!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A43F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002200"
msgid "No, no! Please!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A42E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002201"
msgid "What? What do you mean? Oh shit... what do I do?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01044808]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002202"
msgid "Uh, do I know you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A438]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002203"
msgid "A good day's pay for a good day's work. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EB5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002204"
msgid "The target is at this location. When you're done, bring me back proof that they're dead."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A43E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002205"
msgid "My intel shows the target is at this location. Take them out and bring me proof of the kill. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002206"
msgid "Of course, you'll never see me again! I swear!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010447FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002207"
msgid "How is this any different than what the Trackers Alliance does?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002208"
msgid "Now I just need to figure out how to get out of here..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E90]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002209"
msgid "Thank you. I swear you'll never see me again!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00220A"
msgid "Look, I have some money. It's not much. Just take it, please just take it!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590DF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00220B"
msgid "This can't be real. Oh my god, this can't be happening! "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E94]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00220C"
msgid "Wait, no! Don't do this!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00220D"
msgid "What? Oh no... haven't I been through enough? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00220E"
msgid "[Attack] You have bad luck. Someone wants you dead, and I'm here to make sure that happens."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EAD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00220F"
msgid "I'm not looking for work right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E8E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002210"
msgid "Not this time."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045EAC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002211"
msgid "I don't know what this is about."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002212"
msgid "However much their life was worth."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590C7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002213"
msgid "Nothing I haven't done before. Give me the details. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590CD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002214"
msgid "I'll do it. Hell, sounds like fun."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059116]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002215"
msgid "Wait, where are you going? You... you're just gonna kill me, aren't you? No, I can't die in here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059114]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002216"
msgid "Where are you going? What... what the hell is going on? I'm not going to die in here!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01059AB8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002217"
msgid "No need to explain yourself. We've been through this before, you and I."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F8F3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002218"
msgid "Watch your back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104F8F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002219"
msgid "Everything all right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029721]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00221A"
msgid "Thing is, I know my limits. I'm a smuggler, not a fighter. I don't like to get my hands dirty like that. So, here's the deal - I'll pay you to get the contraband and bring it back to me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029721]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00221B"
msgid "Trade Authority is paying a pretty penny to anyone who can get the contraband from some potentially dangerous areas. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029717]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00221C"
msgid "You there. If your pockets are feeling light, I've got an opportunity for you. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01029724]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00221D"
msgid "Suit yourself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00221E"
msgid "Good luck out there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00221F"
msgid "Oh, before I forget. I have some intel pointing to some valuables in another location. I'll mark it on your map as a little bonus."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F9F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002220"
msgid "If I have more opportunities for you in the future, I'll find you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043FAE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002221"
msgid "Nice work!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01043F97]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002222"
msgid "Perfect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002223"
msgid "I... *sigh* All right. If you're gonna twist my arm so much."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002224"
msgid "Wow, you really know how to guilt trip someone. Fine, if it means so much to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002225"
msgid "No. Let's just drop it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051B9B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002226"
msgid "Yeah. It's not really a good story."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002227"
msgid "I got badly injured on a job before, and that pretty much put an end to any of my gunslinging days. Not that I had very many."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051BA7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002228"
msgid "I said it before, I'm a smuggler, not a fighter. If what the Trade Authority says is true, this contraband is in some pretty hostile locations. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C3EA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002229"
msgid "I've flown pretty much everything that flies. Even a few that crashed."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104C3E9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00222A"
msgid "I don't know much, but I do know ships."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026724]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00222B"
msgid "I fix one thing, and two other things break."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102671F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00222C"
msgid "Opportunity can be found even in a place like this. Or perhaps especially in a place like this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102671E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00222D"
msgid "What do you need?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026719]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00222E"
msgid "Hm? Yes?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026718]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00222F"
msgid "Looking for something in particular?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDB3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002230"
msgid "I've been in worse dives, but not many."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026708]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002231"
msgid "Ain't looking for company right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026702]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002232"
msgid "Grab a drink and relax."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDEE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002233"
msgid "Bye then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDED]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002234"
msgid "Oh, my time's up? Okay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDE6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002235"
msgid "Goodbye now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDE1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002236"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDDD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002237"
msgid "Alright."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002238"
msgid "What's the matter? Tiger got your tongue? That must have hurt."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDC7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002239"
msgid "Uh oh! Looks like your jaw quit working. Should I call Maddie? She can fix just about anything."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104EDBB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00223A"
msgid "Are we done here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00223B"
msgid "The Spacers will likely be coming in force."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00223C"
msgid "In the meantime, make sure your team is ready."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00223D"
msgid "Maybe we offer the job to one of the patrons, then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00223E"
msgid "Our contract is security only."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00223F"
msgid "No way in hell I'd give that order."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002240"
msgid "To attack a Spacer stronghold head-on?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266FA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002241"
msgid "Damn. We can't risk sending any of your people while we're under imminent threat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010266F8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002242"
msgid "Did the Spacers give any indication of when they plan to hit us?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002243"
msgid "What's the history of this place?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A51C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002244"
msgid "Good. I suggest you make a habit of not prying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A535]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002245"
msgid "It's as simple as that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A535]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002246"
msgid "We provide travelers with a place to rest, grab a drink and pick up supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A535]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002247"
msgid "I'm not sure what you're asking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002248"
msgid "I'm not exactly great with rules."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A520]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002249"
msgid "Please do."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A538]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00224A"
msgid "I won't cause any trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00224B"
msgid "We might just be able to help each other out."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00224C"
msgid "If that's truly how you feel, then you should speak to my head of security."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A52F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00224D"
msgid "Bold words. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A53A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00224E"
msgid "Don't you worry, I'll handle the Spacers."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A516]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00224F"
msgid "Unless you have any questions, I'll leave you to it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A529]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002250"
msgid "It also gives us a degree of protection from those who might seek to plunder our resources."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A529]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002251"
msgid "Our location provides some distance from the busier ports of the Settled Systems."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A529]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002252"
msgid "That's not by accident."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A536]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002253"
msgid "I heard you talking. Got some kind of trouble with Spacers?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A540]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002254"
msgid "Welcome to Anchorpoint. I'm Rishi Saint, the owner of this establishment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A540]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002255"
msgid "Yours is a new one."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102A540]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002256"
msgid "I make it a point to remember every face that boards this station."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C019]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002257"
msgid "But you can bet that if there's a way to make a fix without spending credits, that's what he wants."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C019]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002258"
msgid "We do get traders from time to time, and Rishi haggles with them best he can."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C019]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002259"
msgid "Truth is, most of my fixes are patch jobs made with whatever's at hand."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C019]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00225A"
msgid "It ain't like I've got a steady stream of top-quality parts coming in."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C027]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00225B"
msgid "Unless, of course, you get in my good graces by doing a little job for me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C027]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00225C"
msgid "Just don't mess with my stuff, or I'll sic Tiger on you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C027]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00225D"
msgid "Anyway, the workshop's my quarters, but you can use the equipment if you want."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C023]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00225E"
msgid "If it's so dangerous, why do you stay?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00225F"
msgid "Whole station buckled. You should have heard the screams."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002260"
msgid "Came in too fast and slammed into the collar like a damn sledgehammer."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002261"
msgid "Some ignorant dusty got careless while he was docking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002262"
msgid "He's got his fist clenched around his credits tighter than a restrictor clamp on a busted sewage line."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002263"
msgid "I'd ask for a raise, but trying to get even one credit out of that skinflint Rishi is damn near impossible."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002264"
msgid "Hell yeah they are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C02B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002265"
msgid "If its so dangerous, why do you stay here?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C013]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002266"
msgid "What's the history of this place?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002267"
msgid "That, plus a degree of discipline with expenses, keeps us afloat."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002268"
msgid "Instead, we rely on word of mouth from a loyal base of frequent patrons."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002269"
msgid "I prefer not to advertise, both to save credits and because of the unwanted attention it risks."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C01C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00226A"
msgid "I won't deny it's a challenge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0102C00E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00226B"
msgid "What's your background?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00226C"
msgid "Now that I've told you my life's story, how about a drink?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103142D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00226D"
msgid "How long will you have to work here to pay off the debt?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031417]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00226E"
msgid "Why did you leave your son behind?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031414]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00226F"
msgid "I didn't love making the deal, but my son is the most important thing in my life."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031414]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002270"
msgid "In my case, the cost was ten percent interest on the loan."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031414]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002271"
msgid "It's kind of the way Neon works. Everything comes at a cost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002272"
msgid "What choice did I have?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002273"
msgid "I had to agree to pay ten percent extra as interest."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103140E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002274"
msgid "It might seem that way, but he's making a tidy profit."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002275"
msgid "Facing the adventure and the danger of the Free Lanes together is kind of romantic, if you ask me."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002276"
msgid "There was a married couple through here a little while back. They're traders who do business from their ship."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031426]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002277"
msgid "In fact, I heard her talking with one of the patrons. Sounded like she was in the market for more components."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031426]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002278"
msgid "She's always tinkering with Tiger, her pet Model S."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031426]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002279"
msgid "Got a real gift for machines, especially robots."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031426]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00227A"
msgid "Have you met Maddie? She keeps the place fixed up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00227B"
msgid "And what are you thinking in those seconds? Maybe I should have just stayed on terra firma."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00227C"
msgid "Now you're plunging like a meteor toward the surface of some moon, only seconds to live."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00227D"
msgid "Then one day, boom, your landing thrusters fail."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031434]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00227E"
msgid "When you do a dangerous thing over and over and keep getting away with it, you get complacent."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00227F"
msgid "That's all it takes."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002280"
msgid "You think your ship will protect you, but one loose bolt in your hull, one faulty circuit in life support..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002281"
msgid "Not to mention micrometeorite storms, cosmic rays, and the icy vacuum of space itself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002282"
msgid "Think about it. There's pirates and Spacers out there who'd love nothing more than to blast you into atoms."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031412]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002283"
msgid "A rickety old star station on the fringes of explored space... what's there to be nervous about? *Nervous laugh*"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031412]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002284"
msgid "I just can't stop thinking about the dangers all around us."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031412]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002285"
msgid "Yeah, I get that a lot."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031420]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002286"
msgid "You should be! Every time you press that launch button it's a roll of the dice."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103141A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002287"
msgid "Yep, happy to have made it here safely."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031443]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002288"
msgid "I guess after a while, fear becomes a kind of companion."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031443]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002289"
msgid "At any moment, I was afraid that gravity could fail and I would plunge down into the sky."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031443]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00228A"
msgid "See, for me that never felt like looking up, it felt like looking down into a terrifying abyss."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031443]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00228B"
msgid "Do you ever lay on your back and look up at the stars? I used to do that to test myself."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031445]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00228C"
msgid "Such pathogens do exist, but it's unusual to see only one case in a city as populous as Neon."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00228D"
msgid "I'd like to see your inventory."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FD2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00228E"
msgid "I'd like to see your selection of medical supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FD1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00228F"
msgid "Now, how can I help you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_DialogueAnchorpoint_CuttySharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002290"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_DialogueAnchorpoint_CuttySharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002291"
msgid "No haggling. The prices are the prices."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FCB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002292"
msgid "What did you do to land in jail?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002293"
msgid "I'll send along the latest tracking info and let you do your thing."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002294"
msgid "If you blow the damn thing up and bring me back damaged parts, I ain't paying as much for them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002295"
msgid "That means boarding the ship and dealing with whoever's inside."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002296"
msgid "The parts are small but valuable, so they'll likely be stowed in the captain's locker."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002297"
msgid "Good. Now listen up."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037162]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002298"
msgid "You bring the parts back to me, and I pay you for them."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037162]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002299"
msgid "I give you the info and you go pay a visit to whatever cargo ship is making the delivery."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037162]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00229A"
msgid "I get reports from time to time about shipments of these prototype robot parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037162]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00229B"
msgid "How about I quit wasting both of our time, and just level with you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037160]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00229C"
msgid "Only then will I know what I'm truly capable of."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037160]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00229D"
msgid "I want to bust through those limits like a sledgehammer. Boom!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01037160]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00229E"
msgid "I've reached the limits of what I can do with off-the-shelf stuff."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00229F"
msgid "I want the cutting edge stuff. Prototypes. Parts that ain't even on the market yet."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A0"
msgid "Now, the parts I'm talking about ain't your standard items. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A1"
msgid "Thing is, I don't have the parts."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A2"
msgid "Tiger here's in need of some upgrades."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103716A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A3"
msgid "That's right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040484]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A4"
msgid "All I know is, he's in serious danger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040484]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A5"
msgid "You hear stories about forced labor, blood sports, torture for no reason."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040484]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A6"
msgid "All kinds of reasons, I guess, and every one is awful."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A7"
msgid "Right now, all I've got is hope."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404A1]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A8"
msgid "I can't, but Lucia said they had some kind of plan for the captured crew."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040495]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022A9"
msgid "How can you be sure he's still alive?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104049E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022AA"
msgid "I'm available for hire, if you can put up the credits."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01040499]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022AB"
msgid "I'll get your son back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404AC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022AC"
msgid "I'll get your son back."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010404AF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022AD"
msgid "Already forgotten."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104048F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022AE"
msgid "There's no need to be defensive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01045E66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022AF"
msgid "I'm <Alias=Player>. Good to meet you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0104714F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B0"
msgid "I'll think about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047148]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B1"
msgid "When you have the cargo, you can find me right here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047148]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B2"
msgid "I'll pass along the coordinates to you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047148]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B3"
msgid "You'll do well for yourself out here."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047148]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B4"
msgid "A sense of adventure, I like that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047146]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B5"
msgid "Danger? Good. I wouldn't want to be bored."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047144]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B6"
msgid "You can find me here when you have the cargo."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047144]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B7"
msgid "I'll provide the coordinates and let you be on your way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01047144]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B8"
msgid "It could hardly be simpler."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022B9"
msgid "And if you believe that, I've got some pristine real estate on Earth to sell you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010516D6]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022BA"
msgid "I'm sure it's all perfectly legal and above board."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022BB"
msgid "I'll say no more about it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F30]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022BC"
msgid "I'm well aware of Vanguard's deficiencies, but none of that excuses what you did."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F1F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022BD"
msgid "Anyone who thinks otherwise is being naive."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F1F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022BE"
msgid "But let's not pretend I was the only example of corruption within the hallowed walls of the MAST."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F1F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022BF"
msgid "What I did was selfish, and yes, I paid the price."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F35]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C0"
msgid "Wait a minute. Aren't you the guy behind that big Vanguard embezzling scandal?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F26]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C1"
msgid "By which he no doubt means a ship's captain willing to risk breaking the law."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F22]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C2"
msgid "They were always working late, so I had to entertain myself. No wonder I got up to trouble."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052F22]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C3"
msgid "It's true that I was alone a lot back then."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C4"
msgid "Otherwise, the job is a piece of cake. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C5"
msgid "Oh, and how could I forget working every day on a decrepit star station that could fall apart at any moment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C6"
msgid "Nothing serious. Just supply shortages, drunk pirates, angry Spacers, bad pay, low morale, not enough staff..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A59]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C7"
msgid "Challenges? You're asking me about challenges?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A50]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C8"
msgid "What can you tell me about Anchorpoint?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A5F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022C9"
msgid "Got a few, yeah."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A5C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022CA"
msgid "Sure do!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01054A72]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022CB"
msgid "Sure thing! Let's have a look."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022CC"
msgid "So, up for a little profitable piracy?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4D3]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022CD"
msgid "Sure have!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105F4C9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022CE"
msgid "Got any leads on more of those prototype robot parts?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065756]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022CF"
msgid "You have good timing. I have indeed heard something."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065753]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D0"
msgid "Not recently, no. But soon, I think."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01065743]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D1"
msgid "Do you have any more leads on lost shipments?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01066118]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D2"
msgid "Then forget I said it. Just, please, get my son out of danger."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01066119]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D3"
msgid "What happened between you and your son?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106611D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D4"
msgid "I appreciate that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01066117]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D5"
msgid "I'm not looking to get dragged into any family drama."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D6"
msgid "Miles, there's so much I want to say. No, I need to say."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBAB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D7"
msgid "You always were the one to look for the silver lining."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D8"
msgid "In fact, if you don't mind, I'm going to go check out the bar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBA0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022D9"
msgid "One thing at a time. Let this be a first step. We'll get around to the rest."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BBCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022DA"
msgid "Hey, at least it's not boring, right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BC02]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022DB"
msgid "A shave and new clothes can't change who you really are."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB7C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022DC"
msgid "It won't be fast or easy. Be prepared for a challenge."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106BB81]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022DD"
msgid "You can do this. I have faith in you."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DF0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022DE"
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DDC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022DF"
msgid "All right, I'll take a look."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DCD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022E0"
msgid "Let's get this over with."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022E1"
msgid "This isn't serious at all."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DD9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022E2"
msgid "I've seen worse, but not a lot worse."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DF9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022E3"
msgid "You're going to need more credits first."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DF5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022E4"
msgid "Come back when you can afford this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DF4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022E5"
msgid "You kidding me? You think I'll do this for nothing?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DE8]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022E6"
msgid "All done."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01053DE5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022E7"
msgid "I'm through with you. "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103169A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022EB"
msgid "The outpost needs Hal's labor, so I am not against him staying."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103E417]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022EC"
msgid "Caruso's a survivor. Wherever he goes, he'll make it work."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647D0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022ED"
msgid "So who are we putting on trial next? "
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647CF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022EE"
msgid "God I love drama."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647CA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022EF"
msgid "Hal may be a free man, but that doesn't change the fact he fooled us. I'm going to be extra vigilant now. Everyone's a suspect."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010647BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F0"
msgid "In time, I might call this place home."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316AB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F1"
msgid "I take no joy in condemning a man to death. But the vote was fair."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010316A2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F2"
msgid "Wherever he goes, I hope Hal makes peace with his past."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313DD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F3"
msgid "I am going to need a long vacation after this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103071B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F4"
msgid "All things you believe honorable and chaste, mean nothing when you are cold and starving, crossing swords with death."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103071B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F5"
msgid "Once you open your eyes and see the world for what it really is, you will realize the truth."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030762]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F6"
msgid "Is something wrong with the water pump?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01034F7E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F7"
msgid "I'll follow you until we reach Shinar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F8"
msgid "All I have to say is, nobody's above the law. Not even Hal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010313B2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022F9"
msgid "This vote may decide the fate of the outpost."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031117]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022FA"
msgid "We'll talk once we get to Shinar."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105594B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022FB"
msgid "I'm not sure how everyone else is voting, but I guess we'll find out soon enough."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030767]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022FC"
msgid "Someone stole my keycard. I'd bet both my thumbs it was Sunni."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052C8F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022FD"
msgid "And New Babylon is no exception."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01023C99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022FE"
msgid "Yeah, criminals are all the same. They never want to do the work. They rather just steal."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01026B71]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0022FF"
msgid "But I know better than to disobey Hal. Here, this key should open the dumpster. Let Hal know what you find."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01030763]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002300"
msgid "Yeah, Hal and I thought it best to lock it down until we could do a little sleuthing. But if you're on the case, I can give you the key."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388BC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002301"
msgid "He can say that, but I don't think this helps our case."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388B7]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002302"
msgid "I would not know a chem if it fell into my tonsils!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01031FB0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002303"
msgid "Well, it's a chem. That doesn't means it's related to Yeats."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388F4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002304"
msgid "Unbelievable. You think this is a joke?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002305"
msgid "Still, with all that's happened, thing around here are really looking grim."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388F5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002306"
msgid "But fine. He admitted to killing Hal, and the vote would've only went one way."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388F2]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002307"
msgid "The vote is how we stay civilized."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010388F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002308"
msgid "I didn't want to have another pointless vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103C65A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002309"
msgid "On that note, I should announce the outcome of the vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0103C659]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00230A"
msgid "On that note, I'll reiterate the outcome of the vote."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105136E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00230B"
msgid "Very well."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051373]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00230C"
msgid "At the very least, it doesn't seem like it's a local prayer you recited."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051370]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00230D"
msgid "I do not know you, or what doctrine you speak."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01051374]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00230E"
msgid "Ivica's a stubborn man. I'm not sure force is the right tactic. But I'll leave it to your judgment."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105137A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "00230F"
msgid "We can't make any promises, but we'll see."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0105136D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002310"
msgid "Suffice to say you have a lot to answer for."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E99]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002311"
msgid "You're right. I just thought I'd feel better. But it's more complicated than that."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E9D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002312"
msgid "That's what I thought but... I don't feel joy. Why doesn't it feel joyous? Maybe if I had seen the body... I don't know."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01052E92]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002313"
msgid "You should be elated."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002314"
msgid "I never felt such bondage here. I don't know if it was the right place, or the right time. But I chose to stay."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002315"
msgid "Even at Shinar, I was a prisoner to my own fear and paranoia."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [010590B4]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002316"
msgid "A fair question. I will say that everywhere I've been, I've been a prisoner."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_AnchorpointSharedInfoQuest_MaddeA1
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A0"
msgid "Hmm... if I made up some pouches, you could carry my tools. You know, like saddlebags."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B6A]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A1"
msgid "I thought we were just going for a bit of shopping... Next time, leave me out of it."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B69]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A2"
msgid "Let's not tell Cora about what happened back there. I wouldn't know how to explain it to her."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B68]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A3"
msgid "I can't believe we just attacked these poor traders without provocation..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B67]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A4"
msgid "Truly, that show of force was... impressive. But also concerning. Is everything all right?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B66]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A5"
msgid "What is going on? Why are we attacking these people? They're not a threat to us!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B65]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A6"
msgid "Whoa there! What was that for? These folks haven't done anything to us!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B64]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A7"
msgid "Why are we fighting these people? They're just a couple traders!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B63]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A8"
msgid "What is happening? Are we under attack?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B62]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023A9"
msgid "Please let them leave, they're harmless!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B61]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023AA"
msgid "You really have it in for those people, don't you? What did they ever do to you?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B60]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023AB"
msgid "Just let them go away. They don't deserve this."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B5F]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023AC"
msgid "Please be merciful with them. They are not worthy of your wrath."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B5E]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023AD"
msgid "Why shoot at them? They're just a couple of space traders. Also, we're low on supplies."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B5D]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023AE"
msgid "Now why shoot at these folks for no good reason whatsoever? That just ain't right."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B5C]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023AF"
msgid "Hey, these people haven't done us any harm. Leave them be!"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01088B5B]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B0"
msgid "Why shoot at these people? They seem quite harmless..."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B407]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B1"
msgid "How are you liking Sawyer's little get together?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B401]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B2"
msgid "I'm sorry... I'd rather not talk right now."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3FD]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B3"
msgid "I don't feel like talking."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3FC]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B4"
msgid "Did you want something?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3FB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B5"
msgid "Sorry. I didn't see you there."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3F0]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B6"
msgid "Have you had time to mingle? I have a feeling by the end of tonight you'll be a staple in the friend group."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3EF]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B7"
msgid "Don't worry, the party is just getting started."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3EE]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B8"
msgid "Having fun?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3DB]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023B9"
msgid "If you're needing something, it's best to go talk to Sawyer. He's the host."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3DA]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023BA"
msgid "It's you again."
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [0106B3D9]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "0023BB"
msgid "Are you enjoying yourself?"
msgstr ""

#. List: 2
#. EDID: [01083CC5]
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
msgctxt "002521"
msgid "Sounds like fun. I know a few people I'd like to throw in."
msgstr ""

